[{"Name":"Karen Castelino","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV7hhw7USB5QEJWbaxhDcx84xG1_szAmojdVvw-2W8v9vRmg6g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We just happened to stop here for a quick lunch and were warmly welcomed by the charming owner.

When taking our order, she warned us the food is already spicy, so perhaps choose a medium and she'd add extra spices on the side - she was right! And it was a great suggestion!

We tried the BBQ Pork Shewers and the Beef Pad Thai and both were delicious!

The Pork skewers were a generous portion, grilled perfectly and were slathered with delicious herbs! SO tasty!

The PAD Thai was very tasty, fresh and spicy and a large enough portion to share!

There is plenty of parking available, and if you are a plant lover, you're in for some eye candy here!

I was highly amused at the way the owner reserves her tables - she places plants all along the table!😁

This restaurant has charmed us and we'll be back again!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMrZH94z6_q9cO5iRNUeMrsni7xGZ3nG64eShf_&fid=0x0:0x283647f8cd72e153"],"When":"2024-9-29"},{"Name":"Elmira Nazari","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUS8psOPde-fgvVYsglTVKj-j9hpNdB1347mGr_T9d11yAStREO4w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Overall highly recommended for the food. The service is fairly slow, so if you're going for a quick bite - reconsider. The red seafood curry and coconut rice was actually nearly out of this world. The papaya salad and crispy fried chicken were fresh, uniquely flavoured and great appetizer choices. The pineapple fried was alright, nothing special.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO_cnwMIIY7cUyPrOKprynAav4yQke62Kk7Lsdb&fid=0x0:0x283647f8cd72e153"],"When":"2024-6-3"},{"Name":"Ekaterina Spooner","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKDSglxx2dUJfzmltQnzShmE40EBsZJWhLxAmzj0Z87TKVqZdhB=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"We ordered pick up for the first time today. The food is delicious, but the wait is enormous! We waited 1,5 hours for our order. It is too long. I could have made it by myself faster. The service is not existent: there are two teenage girls on the front end who is arguing with customers trying to explain why the wait is so long, aka we have a lot of problems and it is your fault. There are lots of great restaurants in the area and I would not give this business a chance, unfortunately.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jessie Vo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWMevy9XgA4BcCLtVUMn6rX4-CsoOtL-AuhwLDVEclQDLN6HnO0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I came here for lunch by recommendations from my coworkers. The owner greeted me with a friendly gesture when I walked in. I’ve tried several restaurants but Thai-Isaan is in a whole new level. Their Chicken Pad Thai is very flavourful. It’s a perfect combination of spicy and sour. Especially it’s not too oily. That’s exactly what I’m looking for. I tried their new fried chicken dish as well, and yes, it has to be a must try item because it’s so crunchy and delicious!!!!! I also overheard how the owner carefully gave instructions for TOGO dishes to another customer. I bet we all can see that she put tons of love and efforts to this place. Prices are absolutely affordable for good food and the services. I’ll definitely come back again!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMRQqAF_g0wZ1Y_1UYNxJww0XHpsIRejXDlZL6c&fid=0x0:0x283647f8cd72e153"],"When":"2023-10-12"},{"Name":"A P","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKrx52nE6v95kIA5QUoIqBRqKszeGvzHBNs44ln2jwiBUdhmA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"The food is delicious, that’s why we keep suffering through the service. Every few months we order take out from Thai Isaan (eating in is definitely not an option) and are reminded of why we never order from them. Called in an order at 5:29pm. 2 noodle dishes and spring rolls, nothing crazy. We were told to pick up in an hour. It’s now 7:10pm and I’m still sitting here. The 2 ladies working the counter have done nothing but apologize profusely to the 6 of us waiting at tables for our to-go food. Some of us have been here so long people are ordering beers. It’s wild how bad the service is, I haven’t a clue how this place makes any money. Please give yourself time if you’re planning a meal.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cassandra Chan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXgQLgSPpYH1f3LTRKfx7urUyWgCr7ATgQO4mDlzQtLR0Va18kn=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We came for the first time without reservations. Not busy but service is slow as they are a bit understaffed. Food was delicious - especially the eggplant pad and the bbq pork skewers! My partner liked the very hot level of spice - he said it’s enough heat without being painful haha. The coconut rice is tasty but may not be liked by some for its sweetness. Overall would order again. :) We ordered more than what we needed but it was so tasty we ate everything!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOBi4mAH3mTmglxD5ePEnLvAPOx18o8OdS_22X2&fid=0x0:0x283647f8cd72e153"],"When":"2023-8-13"},{"Name":"Braden Hale","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJfnv-j3IVdu4R9ihNCj1_rLpVLdnJ59yrLF3XHdG1ZlKBa_A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I order from Thai-Isan rarely because I know the service is slow, but recently it has become inexcusable. Everytime I place a pickup order, the wait time is quoted at 45mins-1hour, but the food is never ready at that time. It will take at least 1hr and 30 mins, if not longer for the food to be ready. There either needs to be dramatic changes to the kitchen to improve the prep time or the service staff needs to be honest about the wait times. The food is good, but I avoid ordering from here because I now know the service is excruciatingly slow.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"J P Singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUVv-TZdheQ2KRgbv66PStcV7Bg2Aya6_K0c9TCrcSOX10hChF3=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had an amazing lunch here at this cozy Thai restaurant , food was authentic we ordered chicken lettuce wraps and Thai green curry with coconut rice","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNaYF4_Kbr-ZM1Tnic6wUt2OYfUBIxTU_Mg-nZY&fid=0x0:0x283647f8cd72e153"],"When":"2024-4-6"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"matt wagoner","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJjWROtGa0pMQvfSeeyAFH3Wd8YjoUYs1NCTbZYocCsIetg9Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I'm not sure why this place gets high reviews,  it was not a good experience for us. The rolls were put together very poorly. Uneven height and falling apart / not wrapped properly. I don't really wanna eat at a sushi place where the chef can't even cut rolls evenly and wrap them tightly. The ingredients were fine but the way they made the rolls was actually kinda embarrassing. The staff was actually kinda rude in a weird way. Not saying goodbye when we said bye and being weirdly silent like a family member just died or something we're just passing through so I'm not sure if there's any good food in this town but there is not a chance we will be back","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cassandra Chan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXgQLgSPpYH1f3LTRKfx7urUyWgCr7ATgQO4mDlzQtLR0Va18kn=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Nice staff and very well presented and tasty sushi. My partner who doesn’t like fish enjoyed the spicy agedashi tofu very much! It had a different texture than other places we’ve been to. I am a raw fish fan and thoroughly enjoyed their rainbow roll, which was fresh and pleasant to the pallet. Would go again and try something more intriguing like the Toto Tower!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMkbI0mbxdPCpSWWJ35sKB16R3gsPICSArYYYMZ&fid=0x0:0x706a70c1d2aab9a9"],"When":"2022-9-26"},{"Name":"Deanna Wallace","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKFhbpQidGlBQjnxU2xZT3hD9E8xBMnzWA_TWZY50WDGlCD6A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place is my favourite hidden gem when I’m passing through sunny Tsawwassen . The owner / sushi chef is a literal sushi artist ! She’s always so friendly and remembers my order ! The food is consistently fresh and you need to try the monster bites they are my favourite thing in the world ! Below is the monster bites and the tuna aburi roll 🥰 they have daily specials as well ! I guarantee you won’t be disappointed in this food ! The restaurant itself is small but it’s a homey feeling 🥰","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOoBA5X_WsDX5WnAfVqOP5M5LQERYval7ME_WDD&fid=0x0:0x706a70c1d2aab9a9"],"When":"2024-2-1"},{"Name":"Martin Jankowiak","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW_WSOO2iIt47NL02EctJZhW3XjqY-DdgYJoPsl9fCrFLxScj5K4w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We were in from out of town and craved sushi, and boy did we ever find a hidden gem!  Small and quaint, the food, atmosphere, service, and everything else were absolutely top-notch.  Very fresh and tasty food at a great value.  We will be going out of our way next time we're in town to come back for another meal.  If you want some great sushi, this is the place.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOCAcy5k1xHTEy8p2uxBZmFKOoFTS4QVjHepmks&fid=0x0:0x706a70c1d2aab9a9"],"When":"2023-12-21"},{"Name":"Munchica","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXbQ6ACs51IPQJlRLrmnunOErED8bimOf5-y1uov4EWpuZvjQQjrA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent food! Such attention to detail in presentation too! I had the Twwassen Set ($16.95) which included assorted Sashimi, California rolls, miso soup, ebi sunomono salad, beef teriyaki, rice, and assorted tempura.

Sashimi: fresh, clean, mellow, not fishy at all

Assorted Tempura: very good, crisp, flavorful, and delicious. Nice crunch factor

Beef terriyaki: just like Edo so average but fresh and good

Rice: nicely steamed, above average

Sunomono: tangy, done right

Miso Soup: generic but with added fresh soft tofu

Great lunch.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO7ZSjnkWhzfuqiN_m_9eLVemEspPl7cgdToJr2&fid=0x0:0x706a70c1d2aab9a9"],"When":"2021-7-28"},{"Name":"Ray","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXGVd5s-06Fr3JDo-bYWWNiziS7uiGN7g2hEorOk1Vp-qtDK_-cTg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Cozy decorated place. Presentation was lovely. I was craving tonkotsu ramen and they did not disappoint!! The pork was so soft and flavorful and the broth is creamy and subtle. Unagi, tamago and salmon were fresh. The roll was bursting with flavor. Croquettes were perfectly crunchy and crispy too. I definitely want to come back soon. Thanks for the great lunch.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMZKSuHvUfS6j5RSZBdb2BsUv271y9XnZWaBzED&fid=0x0:0x706a70c1d2aab9a9"],"When":"2023-1-14"},{"Name":"Steven","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIwhlFiHPSDGYcBNEBZjiV401CUR-8LRwpy-nj0JN_nYZzCJQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A small sushi place across from Tsawwassen Town Centre Mall. Seems to be family run. They are closed between 3-4pm for lunch break. The sushi is fresh and has some nice flavor and plating. Tried the monkey brain, a deep fried avocado with tuna and imitation crab appy - was pretty good. The toro sashimi was quite fresh. Some of their rolls do seem to be similar in terms of ingredients but they were good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNPYk9xyJIUrpD5ViJUKFaw3tNKew17ZZSK_UiH&fid=0x0:0x706a70c1d2aab9a9"],"When":"2023-5-1"},{"Name":"Jaeger Mah","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVt7hXDkFIcG6P61qcK0wBTq3t5gD1ANgzOWhiOupEWI1RBHtWj=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very friendly staff. Sushi rolls were excelled. I found the chicken teriyaki a little soggy (I like it when there’s a crunch crust on the outside of the chicken). Over all it was a great experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMEj1Q8AyhiSrRIEr9hRdPBJ5RfnwJqWnO6PyWq&fid=0x0:0x706a70c1d2aab9a9"],"When":"2019-8-11"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Ray","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXGVd5s-06Fr3JDo-bYWWNiziS7uiGN7g2hEorOk1Vp-qtDK_-cTg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Personally, not a fan of their regular menu items. They are quite salty and lacking fresh flavors to contrast the grease. This may scratch some people's cravings, though, as this is just my personal preference. Their curly fries are a classic, though, and always hot and crispy!

Every now and then, though, they will make limited time items that are great. Their pulled chicken sriracha sandwich and triple cheese turkey BLT sandwich are absolutely delicious. The sandwiches were so saucy and cheesy.

The strawberry milkshake is really thick and tastes like gummies.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOXUQRgUcDt8NQs7dtgX0SeAAfkmqjijPlKtj5n&fid=0x0:0x95a4e6b532ee2163"],"When":"2024-5-23"},{"Name":"justin mckillop","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXycL53shbjuiaMD6urzpkXK-Gz6EEnmXV8W8247HHolXRLn9Od=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place was nice & clean. Friendly staff, good food! Very spacious. Lots of seating. Public washrooms available.  Highchair available for conveniency. Kids menu for the little ones. Good variety of food items to choose from. Lots of parking. A little tricky to get into the parking lot if you're not familiar with the area. Would go here more often if it was closer. Sucks there's only 2 locations to choose from!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPICWDwtVvykz1zRHAYGHg16tPNwpYp_mjt8M_q&fid=0x0:0x95a4e6b532ee2163"],"When":"2024-3-24"},{"Name":"Jen H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU4ziiKSXqfIKf0bikiIoBftFD2DejYRf_RBnE0G-0IBOO3x2vx=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This location sold Gift Cards last winter, I received one as a gift. For the last 6 months I have not been able to redeem the card as they “don’t have a Gift Card Machine”. At first they said the issue would be fixed shortly. But months later, they have no idea if or when the issue will be resolved. So, they stole from their customers. They took our money in exchange for Gift Cards and now they refuse to allow us to redeem them. I’ve talked with the manager, I’ve asked if they can at least give us our money back or food coupons to compensate us, but nope. They took our money and they are content to not be responsible for their end of the deal. I’ve written in to Customer Service and I have called them. No one from this location or Franchise cares to deal with this illegal situation. This is totally unacceptable!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dylan H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUewRUS3Ydq2RJWFjKxTIaCd2qba4AaBYAfKLd_MEk6mfo-j8cy=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"This is my first time going to Arby’s and I’m not sure what I was expecting. The mozzarella sticks and 3 cheese sub were decent, not a fan of the sandwiches. Milkshake was great.

The staff were friendly and the location was quiet except for the drink machine making some strange noises.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jon Lo (VancityLolz)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVyHXIvO6zjUGBm2q5mj88BnbYXYXFce_0_r9hk7c_P-UzKlHQRTg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Got the double roast beef sandwich and curly fries and chicken nuggets with crinkle fries. It’s pricey without a coupon but Arby’s is hard to find these days and the amount of meat you get really fills you up. Chicken is good quality as well.

Store is relatively clean, washroom so clean. At 1pm on a Sunday it was just full enough without feeling too busy.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOJ6xOzhiQlvoD92VtZGMLgbaKmgQ2xPAT9ESld&fid=0x0:0x95a4e6b532ee2163"],"When":"2023-7-10"},{"Name":"Mohammadreza Behnejad","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXbfFjgusvHBDGevsLnSFlRH6CqkrxaSYgN1dtBgif3eqTdhnw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely delicious sandwich,
I wish they had more branches in lower mainland.
The store is clean and not too busy during the day.
Staff are nice.
Prices are decent and worth the taste.

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Mori","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUzjNclSLYHoLurDMy1z6lBJJfgC1i3gQXUk28JpQQw8EIfuYkF=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Came here for the first time and it wasn't too bad.
Ended up getting a veggie combo, which ended up being the same price for combo #1, so that didn't make much sense to me.
The Pad Thai noodles were slightly dry, but the spicy green beans and eggplant & tofu were delicious. However for the price of $13.53, I wish they would have given me more veggies, especially the eggplant & tofu.
I'd come here again if I found myself back in this area.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOfCoL2ZiaK7R_6GEvNJB8RgOg3-45Ekv-uwMNX&fid=0x0:0xc8d067500ae0a33f"],"When":"2024-9-8"},{"Name":"Sahil Sharma","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUbOc3dzhE_9Pbb77s_W_XokyHPOCX-9blq84YZ_VmCr7TfZmO7=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Trust me 3.2 stars are lie I think. Taste is so damn good. Veggies are fresh! We had vegetarian diet! Navneet was so good in her service. Thumbs up for her! 👍🏻👍🏻👍🏻","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipONbRsj8RoI7YFFqlTQkY5S78WuOdtpaKe-tIg&fid=0x0:0xc8d067500ae0a33f"],"When":"2024-6-13"},{"Name":"Shuo Zhang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVe81hdfjBnnxhP9sqLb0UilLEfO4wp68ilSQlpf1l1DMUsvJY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"California Thai is an absolute must-visit for Thai food lovers! The dishes are authentic and burst with the flavors and spices Thai cuisine is known for. The diverse menu caters to all tastes. The owner and staff provide warm, attentive service and the restaurant has a cozy, inviting atmosphere. Fantastic value for money. California Thai has become my go-to spot.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Maria M.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWDRG-yUxmCRTeMbgMR7M_AtJoVP10dGVk-ujVbXfA_LDZYf_QKOQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I WAS PUNCHED!!!...
by the flavour. Just wow , I was not expecting the freshness and experience from the foodcourt food. The fish... oh my the fish so fresh and flavourful. The fried Rice.. wow. The quality of a Restaurant and the prices from a foodcourt. Delicioso!!
Like The Terminator says "I'll be back".","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPAXYOOsoEBRn_Uhb_7HXgNqoA26v8YiSjARzRG&fid=0x0:0xc8d067500ae0a33f"],"When":"2022-2-10"},{"Name":"Ke Ng","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWObD5IWOBs-APOtdvbqz7AHVG41WaKvZIQnbJMSG181NS6YPU3=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Confusing experience. The server told me if I am ordering, I am not allowed to try the sample they provide. Do they prefer people to try the sample and NOT to order instead?","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOg1pNEB6b_-6-4VDe-Eo6MM0hRTSkH7oaaWqQA&fid=0x0:0xc8d067500ae0a33f"],"When":"2024-7-7"},{"Name":"Sherwin Quilay","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU46rfoheSfvIQONToEKkejzhkSa1wImF0GNRLIYDvcMziumOlP=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Line up was fast.  They had 5 people working which was awesome.   I got the 2 meats, plus veg or salad Medley 3 combo.  I added extra veg. I paid a total of $16.78 including taxes.  I do not feel that the value for the amount is necessarily good. From the picture they didn't supply enough protein in my opinion if I used the standard food court portions.  Across the way into rh same food court is Bourbon Street Grill and I highly recommend them as opposed to California Thai.  The noodles were stale and not much flavor.   Just my opinion.  See picture for the amount of Medley 3.
I spoke to the cashier about the portion and asked if I could give some feedback.   He just smiled and said ok and moved me along not wanting to hear my thoughts.  I was a bit disappointed I couldn't provide any feedback and I see this as a way of not wanting any feedback whatsoever.

This is not Thai food.  The food is quite bland","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNgqG9oyyOuZ5ftCW0cgsFjTZc3MHS1xeyBYPM3&fid=0x0:0xc8d067500ae0a33f"],"When":"2022-7-3"},{"Name":"Cat D","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK2XulyvfIm27enRQOA5aVd1I3ElNt9le5Fu364a08KUSJJ4rI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Subpar Asian food from food court. Got the mango chicken and spicy green beans which were good but the greasy and lacklustre noodles were definitely a miss. It’s a decent meal if you’re hungry. The staff are very nice though!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMj6CuUrZD6ad-Ol_CFP4OJw7BVaiudMWDU1O-7&fid=0x0:0xc8d067500ae0a33f"],"When":"2022-5-29"},{"Name":"SiYuan Ma","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJbn9A007nqhW7t9Yxzgrg5g_kStMl9TMeUt7aJLRn3by3cBg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The variety of food options was impressive,Bangkok BBQ chicken and Santa Barbara chicken I tried was absolutely delicious.
Their service was outstanding. The staff were incredibly friendly.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Stephanie Maber","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX8DGahQWQUa0E7cP6I5VrKcm-LE2NJiKP7PuCPCO_GcV8y7op3Ng=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I used to get Freshii all the time and loved how big their salads are. Maybe it's just this location, as it's my first time at it, but for $13 I have never had such a small salad.

The salad base is $8.99 and then an additional $3.79 for chicken. As you can see from the photos there was hardly any chicken. And the bowl was not even full. When she handed it to me I thought it was a joke. It's empty. I actually asked for more dressing as it was invisible.

To top it off, they didn't even have lids so I had to drive home trying not to spill my little salad all over.

The girl working was lovely but I won't be back. Not worth the money. I'll go to subway next door who make the same kind of salad.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN7DCp2vWHD4CJqyrvbvydQUnbO5DkTIPn1BVxs&fid=0x0:0x5d8d834085e8c4ec"],"When":"2023-4-4"},{"Name":"hesam bahremand","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWaf9uwWVj1F8UIlbqdk6V0gJ7Z8TmfSp3PUAwWhgOCv0Q07lVv=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing delicious foods. I absolutely love their custom-built burritos with steak. Also, the bowls, wraps, and smoothies are sooo good. The staff are very nice, friendly and professional. It's also new and very clean. I'd definitely recommend it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMPYA5_kP6VPoFyxf5cw7kecyCs_ZMuAZ4tzK_H&fid=0x0:0x5d8d834085e8c4ec"],"When":"2019-9-30"},{"Name":"Lucy Yep.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWyWEm1iVA5BhD52EO30x5805b5fs28qVCdlDvtJbrD1_d2ndv1=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The manager is a very kind and friendly guy his customer service is incredible. The soups combo with a pocket are perfect for lunch and it is big enough for the price. The squash soup is amazing, must try it! The ginger shots are good too. Bowls are always recommended. Juices are availbleas well. The place is always clean. Close early on Fridays.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPUAYx0KxeWwDk_ri-fEkcD2VZOzKk1TZvwSZMR&fid=0x0:0x5d8d834085e8c4ec"],"When":"2022-3-4"},{"Name":"NJM","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKBkR932MbCAjGkzPVGYDorKNxOypr_oVD5Ao1M33EKI23cq_U=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Want to pay $9 for syrup drink that just loaded with chemicals and no real food come here... They try to say their all natural and healthy but just selling over priced syrup drinks watch them make it little to no real food is added... never again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Bell Ini","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIpRQhpgiMNwMiv-rrcHn_mSsRr-Y6iJ71DS78ZQ65Li5JoQw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Thought we would try out their new Freshii Beyond Chilli. Quite disappointed. The portions were small for the price. Rice on the bottom was dry and hard. Their so called beyond protein  was diced up.hard dry pieces overpowered by the rice and hot spices. We would like to know where the rest of our chili was. The smoothies were watered down
Again, half size cups at full cup prices. Will not be back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOR8_YAxw87AqVQIKB7E5ejgqZpfj722G4qfU6B&fid=0x0:0x5d8d834085e8c4ec"],"When":"2019-11-17"},{"Name":"Lydia Elder","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXK4bFpSYWG4_r0XgZnnQPB1AU3Pu_Gldz-QG608aTBr8uNUB6K=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The staff here are lovely. So friendly, prompt & kind. The food is tasty, fresh (as the name implies!) and healthy. I always end up ordering the same thing (Oaxaca bowl w tofu) because it’s soooo good.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Giordi Giacomelli","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocInSIkWNDV-4XEk3bR52dzgFj5TqktS4LFGMxFC37_WzshzJA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The man who served me had such a nice smile and was one of the friendliest workers I have ever encountered. Such a pleasant surprise! The food was also great and everything was sparkling clean. I'll be back!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jasmine Davis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKdgu4G8_G1Grr_RmxDp0FIl47we0IfE3SZ35mQP1UtAFj7C-A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This was such a great place to stop for a quick dinner! The food was delcious, tasty and OH SO FRESH. and their smoothies are to die for.

The owner and other workers here are so lovely and make the experience one to remember.

Thank you for your hard work, it was an awesome dinning experience, and I left feeling super happy and welcomed.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Sunny Yerra","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWwX9GsGvRD4Rmzpnxnt1YRL-Eg5T-wGNmWnsfNs3vgSTgJL4bc9Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"They were nice enough to cater to my dairy allergy. I got the Salmon Oshi, which I must say, is the best I ever had. I like uncomplicated, simple sushi. This one had 3-4 ingredients tops, rice included. The sauce on this salmon oshi was exceptional, and dairy free. The cone was a dymamite cone without sauce. Delicious, and enjoyed in many bites. Thanks ladies.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMPCGkrpQ2HS6I1EjTxpZly-HKqMCsmed6gCqKP&fid=0x0:0xa6b5ce82c4b7c075"],"When":"2024-2-22"},{"Name":"Da Wanderer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW6gUX2zsQKdIE8uVzYWBnKKtvYQAJfEKJppzMJqd4hE4TuUun8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place has been my favorite spot for a grab and go sushi. The price is pretty reasonable and their rolls are extremely tasty for the price. I love their mango cream cheese roll. I can eat 3 servings on my own. That's how good it is. Lol. I also love their other specialty rolls. I keep coming to try other rolls each time. You should all give it a try. Rolls on a budget.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMBAw-dUjne5phSSqRvZv87lixMYDcGe34Cb2U6&fid=0x0:0xa6b5ce82c4b7c075"],"When":"2021-3-27"},{"Name":"Ghadir Ch (Mrs.G)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWwjuNsaBSf2IBRFYsspvbwSVtpFjr_juVjGQ7H4_kAvKKtBHnD=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I was craving sushi at the mall and had to give this place a try. Their sushi is ok, but not wow. I’ve tried many spots and this one was slightly different. Their spicy salmon had some sort of red hot sauce over it which is unusual, but it was nice. As for their other rolls, they put way too much crab meat and honestly it was hard to taste anything else. I wish they just made it less filled up with crab. There is nice seating and the service is pretty quick with good price.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOnHc5uW31sIsULB3SWipNxDFvIn95m-6pCUSPI&fid=0x0:0xa6b5ce82c4b7c075"],"When":"2023-10-7"},{"Name":"Ray","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXGVd5s-06Fr3JDo-bYWWNiziS7uiGN7g2hEorOk1Vp-qtDK_-cTg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been eating here for years for lunch breaks, never had an issue. Fresh, high quality, much more restaurant grade than food court/fast food grade. Lovely service. I love their rich udon and special rolls. Great value too.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOjlwTvkEXzQGXfTclcLMZVuTsCYCkhYiJdI4wK&fid=0x0:0xa6b5ce82c4b7c075"],"When":"2023-7-16"},{"Name":"Hilda Wan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL1IEUOgBg8GjPLOMmPUEkV-QJiXwsFYXZSX4OLAsqeLg1bLQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Food is ok, Maki rolls doesnt taste fresh
Counter person shows no interest of taking order
And i see the 15% minimum tips ( thats another $8 ) , i didnt bother to customize tip options, since its a food court kinda service , i picked no tip
When i picked up from counter, she said nothing , dropped food , turned around and left, like stone cold.
I am happy i didnt tip","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Paniz Khajeh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUAIWbzhe2RsJWmfXIIrxjsFYp8QPWeLOPiJO0Zmh8094Vf4_Wv=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food was super fresh, and delicious. Highly recommend it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN71WX5Wsc-XOCdw7vC5n4gWOH1cs7ckYY3L0BR&fid=0x0:0xa6b5ce82c4b7c075"],"When":"2024-12-8"},{"Name":"Peyman Sadr","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVqWFn0ePe18uaG7kAYgUMrxS50pUSoy6sVewCdKiGzix56M_e-=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Good atmospherer, nice food","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPXZER5fRlkG35Z9nPf9bPOMsprjAc61s_ZTmeS&fid=0x0:0xa6b5ce82c4b7c075"],"When":"2024-12-8"},{"Name":"Rosalee Gingras","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU8dnT5P4MYDzEYDk-587QiOzall9_Bma8uAV2EFIGinRVF5LtM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Absolutely love this place, as it has super kind staff and they have very reasonable prices.

The only reason I am giving 4 stars is because the last time I went here I got brown avocado and it wasn't very good. But every other time I've eaten here it's been exceptional and super fresh.

Would definitely recommend trying their mango cream cheese roll too","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM-9_RcD42VBfJNcRydsVzlLKqXjmwd2SSWN-Gy&fid=0x0:0xa6b5ce82c4b7c075"],"When":"2019-6-27"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Michael Lacson Ello","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJus38Jm8x4a4FpscwrnNrQTjVBeHPRdqtc6sWQWa80xSZEdw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The beef patties of the burger that I got was dried but the vegetables was ok and the looks of the burger 🍔 after they wrap it was greasy outside  and the fries is very salty and it tasted like they still using a very old oil on their fryers …
Service was very slow looks like they don’t care if their customers will wait very long time
- food prices was ok and it’s not bad it’s affordable and reasonable price.
The atmosphere of the store was ok but their dining table some are dirty and their floor was so sticky

I will definitely not coming back again and I will surely not going to recommend to all food lovers this location .","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMzpQftR4GQBydJfm0UwflChL9gVrw3XsK1A1Kx&fid=0x0:0xfe08ab308275d736"],"When":"2024-11-27"},{"Name":"Emma Kirby","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLUCBRFq35cMp6DuUPjCYr3huuvOvq9FOWwaORU024UlktyAg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Will not eat at the Tsawwassen location again. Wendys lover since forever, ordered food there last night. Ordered two double JBC, and two large fries, received 2 single JBC, and the fries tasted like mould. Very disappointed. My child who loves fries ate one, and wouldn't touch another. Threw them away.
It really turned me off ever going back to this location ever. Lost loyal customer.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Grant Joseph","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVzfLTwRDWmiz8P9LraNx0eAs71Icdpz_urWQcsKQbeeFTpgagY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This Wendy’s location was filthy, there were FLIES in the dining area. The dining area was not kept clean at all, the tables had garbage on them from previous customers. There was also a toaster on one of the dining tables, like why keep kitchen appliances in the dining area? The garbage cans were overflowing, could barely put my garbage in. There was a spill near the soda fountain that they didn’t deal with, they just put a slippery floor sign up. There was food on the floor as well, also didn’t get cleaned up. The food wasn’t bad though, but what’s the food worth if a fly lands on it or if you can’t dine on a clean table. Do not eat here it is disgusting.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPWOq3mwjGYnGmTgvXRLyaNX2PQvIpM-xeegeCw&fid=0x0:0xfe08ab308275d736"],"When":"2023-9-2"},{"Name":"richard edmonds","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIRhBtL8rhQt1wza-QsGoceLRjvJAB2Cb0mFy_W_X_-XGKGMA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Don't eat a ton of fast food but Wendy's is the choice when on the run. I've given this location a few chances over the year and it's finally time to leave a review. Every time I've visited the food quality is absolutely terrible. Cold fries, dried out burger with no taste. Service is equally as bad. No sorry for terrible quality food.  Stay away from this location, if anything they are reliably bad.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Wayne Lav","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUk880jfctdjiDn4tRAvocN5rCVUdtgArCHWFDiv2yxg-QvIz4L=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Quick drive thru service.  Frosty’s are always amazing.  Last few visits the take out window servers haven’t been welcoming or friendly.  It doesn’t take much to improve the service.  Say hello, smile, focus on the customer and stop socializing with other kitchen staff, pass the food over and say have a nice day and finish with a smile.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Casey McEgg","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXIv7MkA8aQLH8nt_J7FcjdNdNkj6Po8QXnG1pSxblEgBBpTmGH=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Came early evening on Wednesday, March 8. The lady at the drive through was  SUPER friendly. I can't remember the last time I had to wait for my burger to cool down because it was so hot and fresh!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPn5FMLslcKh2ODNqXomllj01r2RsXGJ4aeVjMV&fid=0x0:0xfe08ab308275d736"],"When":"2023-3-11"},{"Name":"Gregory van Tol","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVxw6QSC8o8XMfCmNcSw6lMeU2PFxE3V8NpWLchAdJ-fO1uclzSIA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"What can you say? It's Wendy's food. It's fast food so you get what you expect. Staff could do a much better job cleaning tables. There were maybe 10 customers in the place, and staff were standing around talking instead of checking if tables were clean.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Victor Ashish","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU5yDGsHeJgzKstxa8rP4Gv_Fpd2kv7iISSV0cdfsyJ0a6tL6aeAA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Although we understand that we came during the closing time, the place was a mess. There was water all over the floor near the pop wending machine, paper napkins on the floor, tables not cleaned, and tons of mosquitoes everywhere.

Felt like I was in a very unhygienic place - not even feeling to dine in. The restaurant was very much understaffed, and the staff didn't even know how to manage and prioritize the orders.

Wendy's being an established place - in such a situation surely wants me not to visit the place.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Grace An","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU3EK2a7K177Sf6bXqILIYZjHE92GM9sTU9EFaLTvxP3GPOEiEz=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently had the pleasure of dining at Sushi Gurume with friends, and it was an extraordinary experience! We ordered the nigiri sushi, and it was nothing short of perfection. The fish was so fresh it practically melted in our mouths, and the flavors were out of this world. Every piece was beautifully crafted, a true work of art that tasted as incredible as it looked.

This is the kind of sushi that stays on your mind long after the meal—it’s that good. The ambiance of the restaurant was cozy and inviting, and the staff were friendly and attentive.

If you’re looking for the ultimate sushi experience, I highly recommend Sushi Gurume. I’m already counting down the days until my next visit!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOJfnBmceB0HdPIGDit41xG2lBWK_5GH627yRYF&fid=0x0:0x167045d44866b380"],"When":"2024-11-25"},{"Name":"Peter Estrada","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVw52Fx60bw34dCukF0QbSF82RCB7ujq7YTAahYaTLdvpQbj8VVtg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Dropped in for lunch a few minutes before noon and was seated immediately. The server was friendly and welcoming. We ordered the sashimi salad, the teriyaki chicken lunch set, and the pork katsu lunch set. I am so impressed with the freshness and generous portions of the sashimi salad.   My wife and I agreed that the teriyaki chicken and the pork katsu sets were just ok. The pork katsu was thin, crunchy, but lacked seasoning. The agedashi tofu was bouncy and tasty. The gyoza was disappointing and lacking taste. Maybe we need to try other items. The miso soup was warm and could've been served hotter. Our server was the only one to handle the entire restaurant, which did create some delays for service. That won't stop me from coming back to try other items which I'm sure will be delicious. Lastly, the atmosphere is comfortable and it is nice to see they have private tatami style rooms for groups. Thank you.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPZf6LvPlaMH5cKx_97jL8MlcNfQaEu2aejFloZ&fid=0x0:0x167045d44866b380"],"When":"2024-9-2"},{"Name":"Min J","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXtIPeoqhkFl03jdSzCVlzaTMjgQGC_vY4FoHEuuXhMwN_H016i=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I went to Tsawwassen Mills and stopped by while looking for a nearby sushi place. It was more delicious and fresh than I expected, so I had a good time! My daughter told me that she’d like to come on her birthday again! May be…I could come again even thoght it takes 50mintutes to come. 😅😊😊

I have only this picture since we were busy to eat after this…","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNrdgK1xjsjDeRl55ENhw7Mt-WZ_FL3WDN7xO4&fid=0x0:0x167045d44866b380"],"When":"2024-11-26"},{"Name":"Joving Kalbo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWPbEx34CDXynwER2kXZvyRmV5oUv-dwB_ke3K5wyO82u4FovkVqQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A good place to have your lunch. Reasonable price, good service, nice ambience. I ordered the katsudon lunch special. I will come back if ever im around the area.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMSFSo47etpnxUgyBNJHGquc1iN3Ff7qF9oriuH&fid=0x0:0x167045d44866b380"],"When":"2024-8-10"},{"Name":"angel lo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK1IzL3-IELA7R7E3oFObEFF5jKqUJ8mIkFOIr338r21pBTPQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is a very nice sushi place in delta. They have the rolls called Tsawwassen Rolls, which has the yam on top, avocadoes in the middle, and made so delicious rolls.

They have the miso soup for the appetizer, and the bento box - sashmi box is a very nice one as well.

Love the saba grill, and is very yummy, plus not much bones, it is very good!

This is a recommended sushi place that if you go Tsawwassen for a visit!

Recommended","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPDLuu1qFRY6bzgVQthTHqHPpvu_Hld3Svusgxz&fid=0x0:0x167045d44866b380"],"When":"2024-5-21"},{"Name":"eun hye Kim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKuoV9-0Xysj3Xql7Lq9Xfl97H18XSz78ZLoHXZi2XbWpVPCA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great experience ever! 대박! Can't believe its freshness. I've had rolls, sashimi, and other sushi plates so many times from different places, but I can tell this is the most amazing sushi place ever! Friendly staffs, great service, and fresh ingredients impressed me in so many ways.
I could see their passion which I really appreciate it!!(loved their deco on the sushi plate)
I STRONGLY recommend this sushi place ♡ thank you so much for your service today! Made our dinner so happy :) 감사합니다 :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM0enbaunS_9KC1VSNJwc8BH0q2wyyq0mhZLKG2&fid=0x0:0x167045d44866b380"],"When":"2022-3-14"},{"Name":"Carmen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK7_XzKFE0aHZ9ICJ3wvIpujcc7ckTtZQJfitcVujDUNzE7STI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Came for dinner right before they closed last Friday. The staff were very attentive and friendly. Though they were taking their last tables they didn’t rush us. The food was delicious.  I’d like to say it was nice seeing staff work as a team. There were 3 girls out front serving and they deserve recognition for their work. Great job! I didn’t have a view of the chefs but I’m sure it was the same with them!  Very nice experience! Recommend 😁","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nancy Deol","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUZcj0j-KSE8pJJOduKFby0tUkthuFEhXCa-SU3qKcHQl97zfn2=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"We waited quite a while for our order to be taken, despite the restaurant being relatively slow when we arrived. Our server seemed busy with other tables, and it took around 20 minutes before they took our order.

When our food arrived, only my meal came out, my partner’s order seemed to have been overlooked and arrived about 20 minutes later, so we ended up sharing my meal while waiting. We also noticed other tables, seated after us, receiving their food before us.

Additionally, we experienced the cooks openly yelling at the servers, which was uncomfortable to witness. It seemed inappropriate to handle this kind of conflict publicly, and it certainly affected the atmosphere and overall experience.

While I understand that delays can happen, this experience was quite disappointing on multiple levels.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Susan Ninow","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXvpaRTEsl5529afMOwnBLq388-585p02laQsfHHAaEAmlKrIjM6w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I enjoyed an excellent Vietmese lunch. I ordered the  #39 Grilled lemongrass chicken, grilled shrimp skewer & deep fried spring roll on vermicelli. The server was warm and friendly. It was a nice quiet break from the shopping at Tswassen Mills.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO72GY8-dhldxyawhYUZGrTC2AacHuMfoBl_ead&fid=0x0:0x556fbf4d6a36e4d1"],"When":"2024-11-30"},{"Name":"Manigill Artistry","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJK9NIda3oChxEGR3J-3v3ycBS2zLnkW6R17UPv48bu28LosA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I would love to share my positive experience at Simply Pho in tsawwassen. The customer service was excellent!! (Which I feel is a rare thing to find these days)
They got my order wrong (which is fine accidents happen). I called to let them know. She apologized and right away offered to remake it. I wasn’t able to come back the same night. She said that was not a problem and that I could come back anytime and they will make sure it’s made just like I wanted. She was so sweet that she wrote down the exact order in a book with my name in it. I went there the next day, told them my name and they quickly made it. I personally I talked to the day before (I think the owner) was in the back. She came up to me handed me the order and kindly apologized again.
I was so impressed by their costumer service and professionalism.
Would totally recommend. Don’t even get me started on the pathetic mall food court. This is one of the better options in the area if you want a step up. Is it an amazing bowl of pho? Nah…. But it’s better than decent and the restaurant feels clean and fresh.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNmQG6x9xFzjXQBEILpb_obOw4NS3XE1lrgqnwa&fid=0x0:0x556fbf4d6a36e4d1"],"When":"2023-5-1"},{"Name":"Vinculis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVjQ_62BAyqo-Ft14RaNkBZoMPoW-RyhYZgEg5uKOF95TtvT7_I=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We ordered a #3, two #59 (mine with no onion or sprouts), an order of chicken wings and an order of the fried squid. All of the noodle dishes were delicious! The bun bo hue had nice flavour and they gave us extra chili oil since we like it spicyyy. The wings and squid were fried fresh! Crispiness on the wings were in point. Definitely recommend a squeeze of lime on both the squid and the wings!

The staff were all super attentive and kind. It was very busy in there today but the staff were all in great moods and constantly checked in on how we felt about the food. We didn't feel rushed and our tea cups were always full! Definitely my recommendation if you're looking for pho in Ladner/Tsawwassen!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN7w6NJBs913rqpsH_8yM_Nt3SH1JTT0YdnWZV7&fid=0x0:0x556fbf4d6a36e4d1"],"When":"2023-12-27"},{"Name":"Da Wanderer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW6gUX2zsQKdIE8uVzYWBnKKtvYQAJfEKJppzMJqd4hE4TuUun8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"A lot of people walked in during the time we dined in for lunch so I thought this must be a popular place in the area. It is clean and the atmosphere is so so. The servers are pleasant and efficient but the House special pho is very basic. I could name a few more pho places who serves a lot better.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMA7XkozF61B3APzpNc93kJT9ClS5c_Rcu-AeRG&fid=0x0:0x556fbf4d6a36e4d1"],"When":"2023-4-1"},{"Name":"Alexander Hunt","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKntg94WsHup3cVgJBk3yO0jaRf4K-ndL2T0xGy94s_gBQtie8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Came here with my family earlier on in the year so this review is long overdue; however, I still want to share my opinion. I was actually surprised by the amount of soup in the noodle soup as I was expecting the dish to be primarily made out of noodles, beef slices and beef balls. Let the other Google users know if that has changed in the last couple of months when you dine or takeout for this restaurant.

Please refer below for pictures of the menu and restaurant dining atmosphere.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOP6gNRAhOqOYnJI3kjt3CjIjIsFUFonSW8ZNj6&fid=0x0:0x556fbf4d6a36e4d1"],"When":"2022-9-3"}]

[{"Name":"James","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW7dYAF0BBmR0pl-gZdCg6QNbyBu-6C9pD1ZiWYuTCPpcwlwUU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Today, my family and I visited Mucho Burrito and had a fantastic experience. Kuldeep and Twinkle, made our visit even better. We ordered the Mucho-sized chicken burrito, which was delicious—juicy, perfectly seasoned chicken with a mild kick. We also enjoyed the tacos and a bowl. Last Saturday, I tried the chicken and chorizo burrito alone and loved it so much that’s why, I brought my family this time!☺️","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMfruxUIoYW3Vsc2IALhafElf4oyWSaLD2xaFp_&fid=0x0:0x348601124d1e0e1f"],"When":"2024-12-1"},{"Name":"J P","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJPNOwczxQeYq8Qup51h2PTCgzkWZZqiOeXeOFsoHWK1IWAROM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ate here on Saturday June 8th for the first time, had heard of Mucho Burrito but wasn’t aware that they offer plant-based protein options. There are also no locations near where we live, since we were shopping here, we decided to try it out. Overall very happy with the food, service and ambience, 100% recommend you visit this location if you are anywhere near the area.

The interior decor is really nice and welcoming, restaurant seats 30-40 people, lots of seating options from regular tables to couches, booths and one high table. We were greeted by the employee behind the counter. We used the app to place our order and it was a very smooth experience but also could have ordered in-store.

The burrito was 10/10. The portion was generous, the food was very flavourful and the ingredients looked so fresh. In fact the staff was preparing some meat and vegetables on the grill behind the counter when we came in.

The bathrooms were clean too and the service from Twinkle was fantastic.

Overall, this location of Mucho Burrito blew our expectations and left us with a very good taste. I hope this location gets a lot more business when customers see the incredible value they offer.

I consider myself a fairly tough critic but the entire experience at Mucho Burrito was a 10/10.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOkNzurAX4BewBCOI3MbxFxEJwZDGRJI3MPXXay&fid=0x0:0x348601124d1e0e1f"],"When":"2024-6-10"},{"Name":"Wild Wanderlust Photography","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXYPQeHy2fRvptt6V1NtTq0t9CdOFiP_rQd_Emm8iYNczU9hCDSwA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I just love their monster burritos! Man they are huge!!! It's like a fast food dining experience, as in the atmosphere....BUT it's cozy enough and you're there for the food ..not fancy ambiance. Get the faint burrito....with all the toppings, you won't be sorry!!! Hot sauces and Deliciousness.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kenneth Lai","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVaxVGYXfpPoTmAfNhLJtbs31BGbuX8DK_7Hj5GOcCBNwv8VjrvXA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Mucho Burrito Fresh Mexican offers an exceptional dining experience with its use of fresh ingredients. The vegan tacos are a standout, bursting with flavor and freshness. The service is top-notch, with friendly and attentive staff making you feel welcome. The cozy environment adds to the overall charm, making it a perfect spot for a relaxed meal. Highly recommend for anyone looking for delicious, fresh Mexican cuisine!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNCwRRBBDkCy2RT5gpqg07FY6naonO6J86dZSL_&fid=0x0:0x348601124d1e0e1f"],"When":"2024-5-21"},{"Name":"Jared Woolgar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX8ioo_99XbpSJIRyn9cRIyf71-v-U8Jja7KTwBzGJjWmOo4_-J=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Food is delicious and you actually get alot if you order a regular burrito 🌯  which is really nice. [{"Name":"xxxhearteaterxxx Meow","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI6V2Wm_XqUa_aUk33-GPqWYZq7L24ZQP_nhY_9mbefGcMyLg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"For a pizza that I ordered that was supposed to be 5 cheese with Alfredo sauce, and extra cheese, it’s clear that mozzarella wasn’t even put on the pizza. Zero “cheese pull” factor and because of that, the Alfredo overpowered the whole thing. They didn’t even add cheese close to the crust either. Super disappointed. Won’t be ordering from here again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ray","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXGVd5s-06Fr3JDo-bYWWNiziS7uiGN7g2hEorOk1Vp-qtDK_-cTg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I've had several bad customer service experiences here, once I was reprimanded for placing a small pickup order half an hour before closing and the other time an employee ignored us while we waited 15 whole minutes just to find out our order was there the whole time--she seemed very annoyed when we tried to grab her attention.
Quality wise it's ok but a little bland. You'd be better off getting pizza elsewhere by people who don't hate serving customers.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alex Grundy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUh3zxS9QxZsRTtIzXiRV89XaemSZbcHJl9FgW2ISwM3Rp53ecL=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I had order a few times with very little problem until yesterday.

I ordered two pizzas and an order of wings. Arrived a few minutes early. Waiting at the door and I see a mouse scurry from under the drink cooler back into the kitchen. Right then I should have just left, but I stupidly decide to continue- justifying it with the pizza ingredients are kept in the fridge and it’s fresh out of the ovens.

Get the pizzas and wings home, opened up. The pizza tastes fine. Grab a wing and suddenly feel like my thumb has been cut. Look down and there is some kind of shard of metal mixed in with the wings. Almost like from a dish washing brush but much stiffer. Okay. Well not ideal, but these kinds of things happen, right?

I call the number provided in my online receipt and after it rang through it routes me to corporate, explain the issue and they say it has to be done at the store level, transfer me. Rings through again and send me back to corporate. Explain the issue again and she goes to transfer me (again). I explain we have done that already. The next thing…... It was as if the phone was set on a table and left. Quiet. But I could faintly hear people in the background. I say “hello?hello?” But nothing. 15 seconds later I’m hung up on. Call back the store. Someone answers and says I need to call back at 6pm to speak to a manager. I call at 6:12pm. Manager isn’t in today, he is at Ladner- call there. So I do. He takes down my number and says he will call at 4pm the following day. Guess what? Doesn’t call.

These guys just don’t care at all about serving good food or you having a good experience. Money in the bank account, and they are stuck dealing with customers. Oh and the mouse issue. Yes, I reported to the heath inspection authorities.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Parm Sandhu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ9WRZGfqIdhPQjjwt2OgSs0i3tsZ82VEOIxhGl7h1UyIbS3g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The worst customer experience.  I called to place and order and first I got put on hold for about 4 minutes.  Then when the international student came back on the phone she couldn't take down my address correct.  I asked her to repeat it back to me and it was wrong.  I corrected her and asked her to repeat it back to me again and it was wrong.  I gave up and hung up the phone.  The food is garbage, it’s not Pizza Hut level.  Somebody please help this place or shut it down!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Richard Glasner","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVlFSX_UUx6rW0lix6i7dkX9lVOSyBZB-F5xxqlskw_ZqxWVSPR=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Great Definitely better than the Ladner location .","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shawn Hollywood","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJgEeOwuitaJvOzIZfynjqWUznHDHIVGoyFK-UPcXzT7ALV5Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Decided to try this again after 6 months to see if anything has changed. CLEARLY, the owner doesn't care. Hard to believe, but it is WORSE. A triple crown pizza had not even enough meat to cover 1 piece per slice. They used, at best, 1 medium mushroom, sliced so thin, throughout the whole pizza. There were MAYBE 6 cubes of green pepper on the whole pizza. It's not like the chef couldn't tell either, as there was barely any cheese whatsoever onthe pizza. It was essentially undercooked dough.
Do yourself a favor, go to your local grocery store and buy a frozen pizza. It will be 100X better than this garbage. How this place is still open, is beyond me. They should be in jail for robbing their customers. This is anything but pizza. Even the raccoons that pillage your garbage wouldn't eat this.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chris Murray","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUvm-9fmZsNh3XhAST_u28ot_ESL2KvdrqyhUNJBCGbZ0fuKE-I=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Gross cold pizza, more disgusting than pizza hut normally is. I don't recommend eating here. 4/5 of those in my house at the pizza and we all feel unwell today.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ruth Kaune","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKyjydWNOPwrxUrbmb-PeUkwOxJk8sTrxbRZyG8NLcztWTztw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Food wasn't ready on time. I used up my whole lunch break just to pick it up. When I got back to work, I discovered that they had given me those breaded boneless bites instead of the traditional wings. There was a dead mouse in front of the counter on the floor...","Images":null,"When":""}]

We will go here again! I'm just sad it took us so long to try it !

(For the record...I think our servers name was Izabell? Or something like that)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOqycXoD1CmIek7TzEoJKROFabbcA8K5j6aDwoV&fid=0x0:0x9a78f20219c35a07"],"When":"2024-3-12"},{"Name":"Joanna Grayston","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUrC7KjOQnUkpDb0o1Z5QoMiOQSSH_WTFV9ongUvTT0mRd6jQpS=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The breakfast menu is enormous.  Perhaps a  little too big.  Great service, good breakfast, pleasant and clean restaurant.   Pannekoek was delicious, and my mum enjoyed her omelet.  Food would receive 5 stars if they improved their hash browns.  1 cm, frozen, fried cubes are a little disappointing","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jay A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX0RELLdGDmU4mUU2O4splg5RoL3yTJnShh825sqC7IizJnW3IrnQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It has been awhile! When de Dutch closed their location in Richmond, that was basically the time when I stopped eating from their chain as well. Didn’t want to go to Vancouver since parking was as bad or worst than what we had in Richmond. But!!!! When I heard they opened up a new one in Tsawassen, I got excited. Didn’t pack my bags and went but waited it out since it is a long drive from Richmond; moreover, prices are a bit high. Anyhoo!! When my family and I eventually went (we took a bigger table), the place look clean and modern, on top of it, their pastries are from COBS BREAD! Support local! Food wise, it was because of de Dutch that I started loving eggs bene! And I still love it! Their serving were still big.. the orange juicer was interesting as well. I should say, our brunch was well worth it! Service was awesome too! Sorry, we forgot our servers name but you know who you are! :D everyone did an awesome job there! Keep it up!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM7c5Qv_Yz0n7UclRutxkJTsyNDLWDW6QKMBU8r&fid=0x0:0x9a78f20219c35a07"],"When":"2023-6-19"},{"Name":"Aida Cowdy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXYOSMyUOPMwT4wqDue1PDS2-0KlV4tjaFl0JOj2dSBgi8VQ6U8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It’s nice to see that there’s still a De Dutch that you could go. My pannekoeken is just a bit overcooked (a little toasty) than usual, the ambiance is nice and tidy.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPzTZn-vz9adBc56AqKw7xacMQPoqqW5MagUBH6&fid=0x0:0x9a78f20219c35a07"],"When":"2024-8-17"},{"Name":"Mike Burge","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUNAufzm35P7WKYUsGaq4nX78UrH9cF6tcGhMUNx0wZkbgLkg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Food was really good. user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Kenneth Lai","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVaxVGYXfpPoTmAfNhLJtbs31BGbuX8DK_7Hj5GOcCBNwv8VjrvXA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"South St. Burger in Tsawwassen Mills is a must-visit for burger lovers. The highlight of my visit was the super nice manager, who took the time to thoroughly explain the ingredients of their vegan burger, ensuring it met my dietary needs. It’s rare to find such attention to detail! The option to add as many toppings as you like to any burger is a game-changer, allowing for endless customization. The entire staff was incredibly friendly and made the experience even better. And the fries? Absolutely outstanding—crispy, golden, and perfectly seasoned. Whether you’re vegan or a meat lover, South St. Burger offers something delicious for everyone, with service that goes above and beyond. Highly recommended!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPnIX1xgDfabS5_3QlFs283kfDTq2AekYOSZaxT&fid=0x0:0xbf00fbdb798de4ab"],"When":"2024-8-28"},{"Name":"Davin Kwan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVswJ2-NLO2quiErTaF9hiqRQfT94JwutZOBbqHCI54Aq4Q9VeU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I’ve been a loyal customer of this restaurant for a while, and one of the main reasons I kept coming back was the quality of their burgers. However, during my most recent visit, I noticed a significant change in the patty, and unfortunately, it wasn’t for the better. The patty was dry, lacking the juiciness that made their burgers so great before. It also wasn’t tender like it used to be, making the overall meal less enjoyable. It’s really disappointing to see such a drop in quality, especially since this place had been one of my favorites. I really hope they reconsider this change and return to the juicy, flavorful patties that made them stand out in the past.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPGtFdjpf8ihr0u_CMMj2sYNi-m9d4InKZA3m1-&fid=0x0:0xbf00fbdb798de4ab"],"When":"2024-10-19"},{"Name":"Uros Nikolic","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXqZKUGj61BfmTYu8vecdYC7cNoaJsQnfWJB3zipm50mUOPG3Y=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I don’t remember when was the last time I eat such a tasty burgers  🍔 everything from menu was really fresh and we ordered 3 different burgers with poutine and other fries.
If you’re in Tsawwassen Mills I highly recommend this restaurant, you won’t regret it 👏🏼","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO3cCOZUSjEF_ku1zdFkwNJ9U5Mer_O793yS2-U&fid=0x0:0xbf00fbdb798de4ab"],"When":"2024-8-27"},{"Name":"Chan Owen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU2m58ulSaNORbkm-gDhzx99iQT7v0dK1KjY8tZMsv_TprAr6-w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I used to love coming to this restaurant, but recently they changed the quality of their patties, and it’s disappointing. The patty I got was dry, not juicy, and lacked the tenderness it used to have. It made the whole experience less enjoyable. I hope they reconsider and bring back the quality they had before.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNSgsPGhNIrLk-w4En_Lo4HoDaFhMOjTvaxf8Wz&fid=0x0:0xbf00fbdb798de4ab"],"When":"2024-10-19"},{"Name":"Minipa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXLkpsoXCUt-uCoPDrB_Mv40ZqSioejOqdNEdMQaklHEBDE1W1x=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Amazing burger, fresh fries, free refills too. Gave the food in bags though which was a bit cheap but decent pricing","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOooFEY3PS3fFdpfm2Du_he9sdw6eIjYLlO-ScQ&fid=0x0:0xbf00fbdb798de4ab"],"When":"2024-7-17"},{"Name":"Wayne","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV8QJBi6QcTRAi7AdEdYaGH_JW0AEF7e6HzgNdEU0sa_JSuPyNJ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"First time visit during a busy (long weekend) Sunday evening. But the restaurant was not busy.

+ Mushroom Swiss Burger was tasty; beef patty was grilled.

* Southern Fried chicken was ok. Same price as the beef burger. Not crunchy but it's fine. I'd prefer the beef burger.

+ fries was good.

- Drink costs $3+ per cup (part of combo); Not recommended. More expensive than fries which is less than $3.

- No services. You get food when they call your number. The payment machine has options for tipping.

- Space not so clean. Had food crumbs left at table and seats.

* Had to ask the staff for napkins.
* Not sure if the drink is refillable.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPGwXXquj5NV93v079dMhI4kIHdygJahqqaTjEO&fid=0x0:0xbf00fbdb798de4ab"],"When":"2023-8-7"},{"Name":"Dean Winchester","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVQlXwDDY504zo8RECz7OcOc-gAUoIquol-YQOfDwmBK5q4h_VpnA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The burgers are amazing, the patty itself is so juicy and flavorful, and love that you can choose your own toppings. I've been coming here for years but recently had the chance to meet the owner, Tom. He is super friendly, hardworking, and passionate about his work and it shows! We came about 40 minutes before they closed and Tom told us to take our time and don't rush, he also gave us a little back story about the franchise and even took our trays to the garbage for us. He also told one of his employees to take off a few minutes early! He didn't have to go the extra mile especially before closing and we really appreciated his customer service!

We went back 2 days later around the same time and Tom wasn't there but another cook was, and he wouldn't let us order fries and after we placed our order he was making fries for another person? He seemed annoyed that there were still customers coming in 35 minutes before closing. Besides that, everything here is great!

Also the poutine is amazing!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Richard","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU7z5da4u6KStFu-rcLjoMcJTDqNHQUSVXfDdACqwKMPCpmCXXj=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Excellent cheeseburger, nice and warm...... french fries were also top notch and very warm.   I,ve been here a few times now..... never been dissappointed.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP0XYCZo2bizyNLAkXNS7nq6YK0_fzNsIcbwlG0&fid=0x0:0xbf00fbdb798de4ab"],"When":"2024-10-15"}]

user_reviews: [{"Name":"Steven Legatto","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV8L2nKw1EPV1ph0AIhYhg-v_kV3CGDAO6pDONWluuSVXOOO3oo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Always a positive experience at Freshslice Tsawwassen! Pizza is always fresh and made perfectly to order. Care given to each one made and never just thrown together. It is our go to local pizza as we love the thin crust. Excellent customer service and friendly staff. Recommend to anyone who wants high quality food at an affordable price!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMq_1pR_zAmi3xVw8g57F-exCdxJCpmf3vCcsxV\u0026fid=0x0:0x142d31aeefc8249b"],"When":"2024-9-28"},{"Name":"Louise Yeoh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKn6H1v99edwzRk8pxHxqcfGWgIZaHgZyHlx8FsGc__i8U2ig=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We were craving Fresh Slice Pizza so was thrilled to find one on Tsawwassen. Lady who took our order was excellent. She checked with us to make sure we were ok with every vegetable topping as we asked for all the vegetable toppings they had on our pizza . The place was spotless. Ingredients ok pizza was meticulously placed and not simply tossed or thrown in like some other pizza we had. It was clearly crafted well. When we had our fist few bites, we were blown away as to how good it was . Definitely the best pizza we have had in years ! Kudos to the lady who took our phone order and who prepared the pizzas 🍕! We found out she was the owner operator as she came out to talk to us when she saw us in the car. We will definitely be Back when we need our pizza fix.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOBYqhpzobBFPp4Z8iaNG7-SJqqOXpt6vFSyfjU\u0026fid=0x0:0x142d31aeefc8249b"],"When":"2024-6-21"},{"Name":"Ray","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXGVd5s-06Fr3JDo-bYWWNiziS7uiGN7g2hEorOk1Vp-qtDK_-cTg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've eaten here a lot of times. When the pizza is fresh it's crispy, savory and nice and gooey. Custom pizza or hot pizza slices are especially good and the crust is not greasy, it's more of a thin crispy cut. Love that they do sauce srizzles! It's not very tasty after it's cooled down and reheated but that's how most pizzas are.\nPrice is AMAZING and really affordable! Probably my second favorite local pizza place (sorry, I just love Domino's thicker saucier pizzas). From the times I've been in person, staff is always friendly and helpful. Much appreciated.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMSYPZld3SUgQAeRGnpG6T1_qxrQ61j5pNzY6y_\u0026fid=0x0:0x142d31aeefc8249b"],"When":"2023-3-9"},{"Name":"Sukanya Pawar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV4kOaZclz4KN-R_APgLcghAoA9eFA1A2nlgOtT-K0kDsFzkUs=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We have never been to a restaurant but we ordered food many times and the pizzas were awesome.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM1GpP_T5T01fISc5yzdyOGzPvIBkAFyKtedt_q\u0026fid=0x0:0x142d31aeefc8249b"],"When":"2024-10-5"},{"Name":"Tony Li","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWPKcy0N8L_e03kCanD-kbqBYJvghgec1_Wu16Qs-S8YjI-PLg2nw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I've had their BCAA special, a few slices and a XL custom pizza before but Canada Day did something special to the crust because it was extra scrumptious. The crust was like the pan pizza style of Pizza Hut but not as oily. And there's plenty of toppings on each slice. If you like thin crust and everything on it then get the BCAA special. It's a great lunch deal with a drink too. And for those who love to save money, get a whole XL pizza for under $10 with the Too Good to Go app.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOS4BJzuCS6QGk3hfn_A_PUBl5sOeMWSGp2uSvR\u0026fid=0x0:0x142d31aeefc8249b"],"When":"2022-1-25"},{"Name":"Tony Li","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXf8VP49ZjSvgG0JnhT1tc6Tv6OzLL9YEi_yNvwH1rW_K8-7VE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Dropped in for a quick lunch. Ordered the Big Splash Hamburger with lettuce, onions and tomato. Want cheese? Add $2. (Not today).

Does it come with a drink and fries? No

They cost extra. That’s how money is made.

Burger was pretty much Costco Kirkland burgers. Nice bun, but pretty basic. I ordered onion rings which was super greasy but fried good.

I watch two young adults working while waiting for my burger. One girl was filling up dressing into little plastic cups while another was arranging salad. They both looked miserable which made the food miserable.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Barista Okina","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUUjOvY2uGwjb3KxDPyohnKw7C1DrN_aYzj47PSJi2rpbAz4nCj=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The pizza was amazingly good!

The receipt numbers are different for each till,so the staff said that the ticket number wasn't a good way of measuring when your food will come. When I asked what was taking so long, they told us that they were waiting for a restock of hot dogs to come in before handling our order and that I could come later to pick it up. This should bring many red flags about the service here.

1) They sold hot dogs even though they were out of stock.
2) They decided to put aside the order instead of informing the customer that there was no stock.
--- I watched my order get covered on their paper list by another order.

I was able to get a refund for the hot dog in the end, but overall the experience was horrible and there was no order management at all, causing other customers to be angry as well.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"R M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJeUNTo22HXcXcBqqYyA3eUx0AaUrAskGeQeDhJqwTSM8q6pw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What can I say... Food prices are reasonable as well..","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Andy Worth","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXFhXLTxO6vHz2IkrjH1W6xuBqWmC6HJSh8Ry8GSzN3ehQ4RKZSPQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"The park was way smaller than I expected and none of the rides are very fast or thrilling. [{"Name":"Jamie G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW4K5nJ1yxY_yvRsH0bM-7wF3ZRgltXkRm5DubSyC4vqkn-2OW-=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We got into town starving and I ordered from Pizza Factory based on the fact they were still open and the pictures on website looked more appetizing than the others.
I never order pizza because it always disappoints me and the family.
Well not these guys! The pizza was fantastic! Gooey. Cheesy, great toppings to sauce to dough-cheese ratio. When it got cold it was still great; meaning dough didn’t dry up and the left overs turn into cardboard.

If you’re looking for good zah, I highly recommend Pizza Factory in Tswassen.

More over, there was a mistake on their end for my online order and they were not only transparent about it but also fixed it and had the pizza delivered within 20min.

Support this business. They’re wonderful.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"S S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjULFs4uMqpehzBeGp8XHUvb6uZTSHxz0HmMZTQHlxvUx0atflM2Gw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A Tsawwassen staple. They have been around for a very long time and taste delicious. Their sauce is our favorite. They even have super tasty and flavorful samosas. However, I definitely recommend ordering in advance especially online as their system can be a bit finicky.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ricki-Jean , Popadynec","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJG9g8lJFg-2mOEp2wUAQLWhDL1JaVtQgyaifG9bWyz4qxl0w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"First time here,June 21 2024..
I ordered 6wingHoney garlic .
6 wings BBQ.
2Garlic Toast.
The wings were cooked well,but the sauces weren't put on.
I returned them both thinking they had forgotten to add the sauces..She just squirted BBQ onto the one box
No napkins  given out for Wings or forks..Sad really!

These would've been grand,if sauce was added before cooking took place..
The BAR counter I say at to wait,was very dirty ..The owner said she would wash it when I left","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Fish Taco","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVGRc_hZX9QUCi-SFjoFenuL-Gv2Lg3hmYR3XsN6BxT-eTJuE6o=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best pizza in town open late . Stick to vegetable options","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMsf-F2IpZK_0C1BctnSa5G8bl4-yIxdUnjydrX&fid=0x0:0xe53bcf930c48fc60"],"When":"2018-7-1"},{"Name":"andrew wagner","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVIJfcKbAf7_SmMmAVv4mBrKV7tKPeY-rwpoKvwocgsQaWL3GMT=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The top spot in town for a quality pie. Also I'm not usually into meat free pizzas but ... the vegetarian pie absolutely slaps","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jass Atwal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLPK_sykHN-LGJ-gvdvo4pnWuw0Rh5w44vA6gR3K9U5w5bLKQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Overall, my experience at pizza factory Tsawwassen was exceptional. With its unique features and high-quality dining experience, I highly recommend this food court to anyone looking for a memorable dining experience.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"P.A. We asked if they were going to weight it and they said no because it was considered a "combo". It's too expensive, if we had known we would've gotten more food. They were really quiet and didn't really explain it to us. The food wasn't even so tasty, the noodles tasted dry and there was too much sauce on the chicken.
