The wings in the picture were so good in regards to the quantity.... Like big sizes....but when Wings came on the table...the wings looked like some Small Size bird's wings. Garbage","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shery On The Move","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVmAA3VItm5d-LzZjMzSS_FZs12aHSse1X5w-nXQqVmdbUvhBBJ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I don't have a problem with the food but the problem is about the staff.

She wasn't rude to me or other customers, but she didn't know how to greet and smile. Not friendly at all. If she doesn't know how to make an extra effort, such as a simple one (smile), then go find another job.

The owner of this outlet should take note of this issue.
Date and time : 26 May 2024 / 6:35pm.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNWP0A0yt3bOkaXCsk1OEwkcsJHGJOQ6k-EdTSy&fid=0x0:0x40d689667d96df50"],"When":"2024-5-31"},{"Name":"Maria M.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWDRG-yUxmCRTeMbgMR7M_AtJoVP10dGVk-ujVbXfA_LDZYf_QKOQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"UPDATE: 28.JUL.2023 -I continue buying  their food. Love the skewers+fries. To go.. I like the taste.///Omg so yummi. When i got it i was doubtful on the presentation, but I finish it ..All , that's how good it was. Really well cook not dry at all and not raw.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO_ONIqHINMAaJtlunBp0lyBfIojFDkxImm6utS&fid=0x0:0x40d689667d96df50"],"When":"2023-7-28"},{"Name":"Cole Davis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVAOU6XCX3s_R0vWndse-P-J59JZDVGZbi6kfyG2pJARhX4qsYzZw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The quarter chicken breast is actually a whole chicken breast, maybe a little more even. Exceptional service, workers there serve food pretty quickly since there's only two people.

The chicken breast was dry, I mean too dry even. Do note they don't provide your chicken with rice, so make sure to add a side. May come again?","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNuF02YCTZnUgFEAbext4t-21eJo6MDZZgV_J60&fid=0x0:0x40d689667d96df50"],"When":"2023-4-16"},{"Name":"A J","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI-f7spaj8JAhf1B51XDlbAyZCHzo2h2WTASaAfBaaGTh0Pqw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Purchased Large Peri Fries for $8.65. This is what I received. Bag about 3/4 full. Went back. Manager's reponse. "Go complain to the Head Office"; which I did still waiting for a reply. Manager gave me a regular Fries which was half full.

TERRIBLE Customer Service!!!

WISH I could give thia location ZERO STARS!!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNN_pjMrNI7f9-3DmxVSjxWHYKLXMJzRAsQ8DNZ&fid=0x0:0x40d689667d96df50"],"When":"2022-12-29"},{"Name":"Gayla J","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXonqVkSyZ0kj4L10z7xgxgHrVwLs1vu7F6PXXTIeflvEXHoYh3=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I ordered six family dinners for six and expected to feed 36 people. It did - sort of, we were really short on the side dishes. There was a communication breakdown, so when placing an order, ask them to be sure you have ordered correctly to feed everyone. Thankfully they did send enough chicken, the Owner called and helped to explain the short fall, was due to ordering too many different sides instead of just two sides.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lucy Yep.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWyWEm1iVA5BhD52EO30x5805b5fs28qVCdlDvtJbrD1_d2ndv1=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I love Barcelos and I used to go frequently to other locations but specially this food court location has very poor service and products. Last time I ordered half chicken to go, first, the girl that is accepting payment does not wash her hands and touches the food to pack it. Second, part of the chicken break is missing like they took all the meat from the bone. The pieces are already small and they serve the food like that? As owner you are not saving, you are just loosing customers...","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOUrIQ2JYii7LnXZjGyq9WYL4w94r-rRkwW15YN&fid=0x0:0x40d689667d96df50"],"When":"2022-1-20"},{"Name":"Joe Uppal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLuumM3GoJ92r_B_Agk5l5t0c-BkgeXxmyhF9y8n67x0B-hCA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"If there was a zero star, I would definitely give this location one. It was my son's birthday, and he really wanted Barcelos, and we had guests over. I had placed with Uber eats about 30 minutes before closing time. On the Uber app, it said the order is getting prepared, and the driver is on the way to pick it up. When my Uber driver went to grab my order, the restaurant was closed. The restaurant didn't cancel my order or contact me saying it's too late. It's 8:30 pm now my Uber driver calls it's closed. I have no food for dinner my guests went home hungry. Will never order from any Barcelos ever again.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Shannon Blackmore","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ8pMnRNN5UQrJ1wUEsvfGgtB4YWU8h63doSSpRCEWSkRCEkQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Great lunch special, halibut and chips for 16$.

The fish was very well cooked with a nice light batter

The mushrooms were a little bit oily but still tasty.

Nice plain simple menu with a good variety.

Service was very good and a nice clean restaurant.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNwG59doMXWvgobRzSTBtYJC0lmOZ1AX8SpgM8f&fid=0x0:0x1684471f6dd4a3c8"],"When":"2024-7-23"},{"Name":"Riley Ryan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI5qJQlQZUlr3T7tudhKtAZ_F4oZ6nPr_TS-zgoIXTeJwC3_w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We love all the dishes that we’ve ordered.  Everything is very tasty and not greasy.  We loved the tartar sauce very much.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMer0OiZTes-_J6fGBvka3UDXWec8dsp_gto0Uj&fid=0x0:0x1684471f6dd4a3c8"],"When":"2024-11-24"},{"Name":"Eric Chand","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVIWwIbQtdY6WUaFS-i1AZmEc25ZCY0xVJCasCgn8djMLpSdWUMTQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"WOULD NOT RECOMMEND!!, the service is super slow, we ordered took about 30min for the food to arrive.  Once we got the food it was overcooked, placed another order as we had the all you can eat thinking it would better than the last one, however which took more than 30 min again also overcooked. The waiter never comes to check if we needed anything or ask how the food is. I RATHER JUST GO TO MALL ACROSS THE STREET CUZ ANYTHING ELSE WOULD BE BETTER BECAUSE IT AINT WORTH IT HERE.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOEi3BiJQzZ95X4QIgF91ZOotocEobk-uXCU4OY&fid=0x0:0x1684471f6dd4a3c8"],"When":"2024-12-19"},{"Name":"Jay L.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLCQoS8NlWNxDjO6o3kh2TYTZ28b3n0ueXzOO3bzkd8cLzLiA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently tried Harry’s Fish and Chips and thoroughly enjoyed it.   I couldn’t resist trying their new all-you-can-eat option, and it did not disappoint. The fish was crispy and flaky, while the fries were just right — crispy on the outside and fluffy inside.

The staff were very friendly, adding to the overall enjoyable experience. If you’re in the mood for great fish and chips, definitely check out Harry’s!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jordan Martin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXUCr0tr9YlhzAUVvUDA0uh1N_E9-qD-QRXTWP98RAIztJCmEjV=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The food gets 5 stars while the service was very slow.

I do NOT like fish and chips. Honestly, I think the vast majority of fish and chips are bland and rather sad. However, anything made well can overturn that sweeping generalization. And I am proud to say that of all the fish and chips I've had that Harry's  is worth it. The fish is perfect. I highly recommend the haddock. The batter is thin, crispy, well seasoned. Not too oily. The chips are great. The tartar sauce is excellent.

The curry sauce was very disappointing. It tastes like some cheap powdered Curry sauce and I feel if they put the same love into it as the rest of the stuff, it would be a knock out. But most importantly, Harry's does what a fish and chips place should do well.... The fish and the chips.  Having eaten fish and chips on white rock, steveston, Granville Island, Melbourne and across numerous other places, the batter is always too thick so it gets soggy quick or overpowers the fish or is thick and soaked with oil and grease or it is just plain underseaoned which often seems to be the case in The Vancouver area. An aversion to seasoning. Harry's gets it right.

It took almost 40 mins to get food while there were only 4 other tables there so that is a negative and they never checked on us to say that the food was going to take a while. So the girl working the front should have been a little more proactive. We happened to be in a particularly patient mood that day so we waited without saying anything.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"G. Thandi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKK0fbTfKn4oJsVqGQVuttQWILwxEXzV2YpkNcaTKaWAeczLQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Harry’s fish n’ chips took me straight back to the UK! The fish was perfectly crispy on the outside, light and flaky inside – delicious. The thick-cut chips were golden and just the right kind of soft. Plus, the service was spot-on, with a warm, welcoming vibe that makes you feel right at home. If you’re craving a taste of classic British fish n’ chips, Harry’s is the place to go!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sofi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK-opTzuNthCUcMRRjR05ACdKoDeruLOEirZI-e_FPMXXNiFXs=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Unimpressive! Our first time at Harry’s Fish & Chips, sent my mister there to pickup our dinner after off the phone with a lady about substitutes 1 of the fries for yams and pay $3 different. The man took the orders for a 6 pieces Cod Family Meals, but refused to honour the substitutions and charged us a full price for a full yam order instead! The order wrapped as 3 separated of 2 pieces fish & chips orders. The L (Large) coleslaw was really tiny, like 3 tablespoons, more like a portion for 1 person. The tartar sauce is like 2 tablespoons, which barely enough for even 3 pieces of fishes. The foods were decent taste, fish on a bit small sizes, good size chips. Overall, had a much better experience at other restaurants with taste, portions, and prices!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMFLoMR_ci6MCXyfeOUOzz_S4BNwdCzsCcuSmdf&fid=0x0:0x1684471f6dd4a3c8"],"When":"2024-3-30"},{"Name":"jeeven chatha","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLBfOmzwVZ3U-hOgo89yBurBlrS_c8n4XH7loEzGr4XL0cCVA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Harry’s Fish and Chips is hands down the best place to get your fish fix. The halibut is beyond amazing—perfectly cooked, crispy on the outside, and tender inside. The in-house tartar sauce takes everything to the next level, with a fresh and tangy flavor that complements the fish perfectly. The fries are spot on, crispy yet fluffy. If you’re looking for top-quality fish and chips, this is the spot. I’ll definitely be coming back for more!","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Shawkrat Bogda","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVrsOjmCZ5t1t9qzS0-fojDP_RC_lsLL9v2fdkXeKRxhdjA0bM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"If you are not hungry and tired after shopping in the mall, AVOID AVOID AVOID this store. Don't throw your hard-earned money into the lake.

In the 5 or 6 years I've been going to MaryBrowns, this was the most disappointing experience. To be honest, I've always liked the juiciness of the chicken and the professionalism of the service, but this store pleasantly surprised me.

1, When placing the order, the front desk staff press the big mary as the original price without hesitation. He didn't look like a new employee who got the job that day. After I mentioned that today was Monday and the sandwich should be half price, he continued to mumble a reason instead of a simple "sorry" and changed it back to half price. This is the first time in many years that I need to remind the staff what day of the week it is.
2, I ordered another box of "made for 2". It has always been served in one box before, but today it was packed in several paper trays. Maybe it's not a big deal, but I still need to confirm with the staff "Is this what I ordered?", and the gravy bowl is also covered with gravy. Maybe it's not a big deal, but this is the first time.
3, Finally, I came to my favorite part of the chicken. The five pieces of chicken were obviously mixed. Two of them were newly made, and the rest were unknown. How should I understand this? Is it leftover from the previous customer? Or is it the same order with different cooking skill? The first time in many years.

So, long story short, This will be my last time here, maybe some people will confuse"just because of a mistake?", okay, let me tell you, in the past few years, I have enjoyed countless excellent services and delicious chicken in many MB stores in BC, they are still there, why should I come back here again? Now the big economic environment is not good, it's not easy for everyone, but don't treat customers as idiots, right🤝","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNMlWjuIZ9y8a1w3wTnRvKkBeMzjVdLdTHu64FF&fid=0x0:0x30da3eb802012ba8"],"When":"2024-12-17"},{"Name":"Peter Estrada","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVw52Fx60bw34dCukF0QbSF82RCB7ujq7YTAahYaTLdvpQbj8VVtg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"First time here. When we arrived we were the only ones there. We ordered the classic crispy chicken sandwich combo. It comes with an order of crispy partially seasoned potato wedges. It was cooked to order. The wonderful order taker brought out our order out once it was ready.  I'm happy about that. The order taker was friendly and wonderful. The chicken sandwich was juicy but needs some more seasoning. The wedges are definitely super crispy but definitely needs more seasoning. I added some salt and vinegar and that helped. Pricing is right for this type of food. I hope this was a one off. Please season your wedges and chicken better. I'd love to come back and try their fried chicken meals next time. Thank you.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPXe5gTZXGhDkydM7jfMsNczq_FxStLnb8t5F49&fid=0x0:0x30da3eb802012ba8"],"When":"2023-11-6"},{"Name":"Yannic","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXiPcmDTwcIkbAuU20IUFgKkCBjFYjG9sUQdPEW0BqDMa7FOx92wA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Stopped in to get a quick bite before hopping on the ferry. Highly recommended for some quick chicken and fries if you need a snack  prices were reasonable and the food was hot and well seasoned. Ordered the popcorn chicken and fries combo and would get it again.

Service was  pretty quick and the staff was nice.

Will return again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMSXQiuMcx3DzIUN8t9_WWAd8DRqyRguVzFWROu&fid=0x0:0x30da3eb802012ba8"],"When":"2022-6-13"},{"Name":"B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ7xBoDZXzB2dAR1aPyzB6D_OyfCRl0KTZjcXntbq7Hug5PH6A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I had never tried Mary Brown's before, but today was not the day. The oil was definitely old. The wedges were burnt dark brown on the outside, but almost raw on the inside. It was so disappointing, especially since we didn't open the food until we were all the way at the beach. We had to throw away both the wedges and the chicken. I should have read the reviews for this particular branch. There were so many comments about old oil tasting products. Mary Brown's corporate should reassess this store. I definitely expected better quality from this brand name.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"M K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWg_KAqTQxsDLwon6O6f-_8Lc1dsT_DysWASplu1udt_XQYNiNq=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This branch needs improvements, and fast.  Firstly, when a client enters, the staff need to learn how to greet clients. It's awful seeing sad faces on the counter. Secondly, there has to be some flexibility to satisfy a customer. I requested a small fries instead of two biscuits, but no communication whatsoever, and request wasn't granted. FYI, Popeyes ALWAYS replaces our biscuits with a small side upon request. Thirdly, they charge an upcharge of $5 if you request either dark or white pieces of the chicken. I have yet to see a friend chicken place here do this, except them. Fourthly, FOUR of the twelve pieces in the order were wings.. again, unacceptable. If I wanted to order wings, I could have done it. I ordered chicken, and I expect chicken, not wings. Also, my 11 year old son went to the counter to ask for hot sauce. He came back seconds later with a sarcastic smile telling us "they charge $0.99 for hot sauce, so embarrassing, no?" What is with all this greed honestly? Are we not already paying enough!? The management really needs to work on this. On the positive side, their chicken tastes good, the location is good, and the washroom is very clean. I remember when this place opened up, things were much better. However, because of these negative experiences, I wouldn't think of going back here. There is a reason my sons asked if there was a Popeyes nearby.. If I was the restaurant owner, I wouldn't have been happy to hear that from a young kid. Overall, very disappointed, not worth the money.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Richard J Bergeron","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXZExnbUKFKvplHQ_0M_2nTN2L_GFTHbWz1_5aOGcpxIqn_GckSKQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I ordered the Buffalo Mary chcken breast in a bun , tater fries , gravy . Was disappointed.  Way too much sauce in the bun . Dripping all over , bun got soggy , went through about 6 or 7 inadequate napkins . Bit of buffalo flavour in the breast , not that spicy. Enjoyed the tater fries , bit of tang to them , gravy is really good . My partner had three piece chicken dinner with taters and cole slaw . She ordered one piece extra spicy and thought it too spicy ! And she likes spicy . Thought the chicken was greasy . Liked the salad and taters . She have her meal a 3 also. Im going back again in a  couple of days to try the fried chicken . They're having a special this tues and wed . Two piece meal for $4.95 . Reglar $9 + change . Basically half price . Good deal for tryout .","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNTJA6EZ73sw8Mo8Agp4fNiVquGPtaR0IVQvlUR&fid=0x0:0x30da3eb802012ba8"],"When":"2022-6-3"},{"Name":"Richard Tang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLFUWw11hwMWa1Sk1hj41XH2mlcFHo0UUpVl7eiUsH79LJa=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The food is ok but not spectacular. The portions are good. However the potato wedges are sometimes dry and not edible, while other times they are as good as steam potatoes.

The standard franchise situation leads me to believe that they are frugal like KFC. For some odd fact, they give styrofoam Dixie cups of tap water. It's almost as though they are punishing the customer who decide not to buy their expensive bottled drinks.

The chicken of Canada franchise follows the same pattern as KFC of the south (USA)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mary Yang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLQk0jIsRLjuxxQCKwQrqojoDQ0JITPr57raFYAQmTpBeL4VA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The best fried chicken place I’ve ever had in Van. The Big Mary Sandwich is the most favorite dish. All the staffs there are really friendly and professional. Had a really good experience there. Will definitely highly recommend to all my family & friends!","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"May Zhagro","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU9KviWdU_UGm6yjKPv-6aFaljm1EC_ecrxYhnt_LO3duiyBNho=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Expensive food for portion size, not really worth it for fast food Greek food. Best part of the chicken souvlaki platter was probably the bread that came with it that was seasoned well. Service was ok, they made the plate on the spot and it didn’t take too long. Plate was filled but mostly carbs and one chicken souvlaki.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN3TuTi-MrebOogPIkG7ATjJANNTU8HMDwb2fbG&fid=0x0:0x21b1f23020283612"],"When":"2024-9-17"},{"Name":"Jong Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWsj66d8DdmBbxiBfPXwcsaGu37_5Q5dlKhqvY11hATgPvGuCHOqw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Fries were good and cooked to order with yummy saice. Nice people working there, but the pita is very very thick and the meat was too thick and over cooked. Greek salad was hand tossed and fresh.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN2ND3brPZ6aEQHSKJMzgly2xbtY-Zrr0WOaAYJ&fid=0x0:0x21b1f23020283612"],"When":"2024-7-3"},{"Name":"Fuzzy Nemo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWMhjGNDhI-RZYgIiVRXnRDEQCiyyP-dsVjb7EhBkcymNr9MvYi0A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I have visited many Opa's and it has always been my go to when in a food court that has one.  The experience was disappointing to me.

I had ordered a meal, the menu said it was an additional $2.69 for a drink.   I was shown the bottle drinks and was never given the option of the fountain drinks, so when I ordered the bottled cranberry juice, it was an extra $3.49 plus 10 cents bottle deposit.  No one told me about the extra charge for the bottle drinks.  That's misleading.

I was told to stand in the back to wait for my order, while everyone else was congregating with their trays right on the counter, so when my number was called, someone almost took my food, because they didn't check the number and just handed the food off.

The food was rather bland.  I had the calamari with a Santorini Salad.  There was no seasoning at all on the Calamari or the salad.  For the most part, it was tasteless.

I never knew ordering food in a food court was so stressful.   First you have to question if they overcharge, then you have to fight over people to get your food. Would I come back?  I highly doubt it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPBYQx_INXBRS0ZUU6gCvcO81jk4jjjBEeXrmC2&fid=0x0:0x21b1f23020283612"],"When":"2024-8-30"},{"Name":"E. Ho","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWapxfDmUmneoBwxC1ihDSroK6TaIbvpgMe2GHZhKT4HcESHYsOew=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Whenever I come to Tsawwassen Mills, I always grab a pita wrap from Opa. Amongst all the other options at the food hall,  Opa's selection is probably the healthiest. The pita feast has decent Caesar salad, freshly fried fries. Not bad for mall food. Avoid the baklava, however. it's soggy and not fresh, not the crispy mouth feel that we associate this dessert with!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPBolG1Xh61aMYOj-APN4DNpKNTDeOX0ahDd7uZ&fid=0x0:0x21b1f23020283612"],"When":"2024-9-27"},{"Name":"Shery On The Move","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVmAA3VItm5d-LzZjMzSS_FZs12aHSse1X5w-nXQqVmdbUvhBBJ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I always come to Opa and order Calamari with ceaser salad. Greet service by staff. Keep up the good work..","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNT8V2vU8G123IfWESUIjfsU4jL9Wlf4ALdPJZ7&fid=0x0:0x21b1f23020283612"],"When":"2024-5-31"},{"Name":"MRD","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVs3AD8byZ8WbxiDuCx06SKC6vjPah01MHg0pn3mF9O-9tEU3xDhA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent food great company!
Like any food service PH is very important! I saw complaint about miss handling food... believe me unfortunately it's happen specifically with FAST FOOD!
SOLUTION: Managers to supervise
Company to have a training procedure with test! And  a mandatory Food an Safe certificate.
Otherwise great food booth and tasty products
Thanks","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ray","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXGVd5s-06Fr3JDo-bYWWNiziS7uiGN7g2hEorOk1Vp-qtDK_-cTg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Pretty tasty! Hot and fresh, especially the falafels and the pita. Nothing like a hot pita with a crispy exterior and soft interior. Don't sleep on this place.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMepCU_rsrC2zYXyIlSCqZjztNN8x8EyBgrwxvz&fid=0x0:0x21b1f23020283612"],"When":"2024-5-26"},{"Name":"Edward Solidon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK4ufShUKSB1-h0YAcv0VpNQPhvTLBKv4_mVr-YY2o5jHLNNg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Small portion sizes for the price as others have stated. I had the olympus bowl with falafels and fries as a base. For $3+ more than the fry bowl you get 4 tiny falafels. The kind you get frozen at the supermarket.","Images":null,"When":""}]

Super salty (like weirdly salty) and lacking in anything remotely Vietnamese (no pickled vegetable, no peanuts, etc…nothing was good) Way too expensive. Poorly cooked (noodles were way over cooked mush) Salad Roll was hard and flavourless.  The allure of the modern aesthetic and seemingly happy staff really sucked us in. Money down the drain.\nKeep walking folks.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO2PT8FdYauh2d1kSJXj7v-0FMZuvHkPKzQ-DpM\u0026fid=0x0:0x2f5507b307d0fc60"],"When":"2024-9-7"},{"Name":"Chris Ko","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL9SsBcY4lTka-GimbphO7it5-Fo-2sY_7F-UcjooXVsjzldA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"literally the worst pho, i order a pho beef noodle and a side dish for 22 dolloar, but there is not much food to be honest","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMJAeIdIBDDO1UOyEkRFki2X_PxdqzhAFYm9vhi\u0026fid=0x0:0x2f5507b307d0fc60"],"When":"2024-12-15"},{"Name":"Proud Ilongga","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUiHeOExRM-uGrTqyinzIv67eBTLdQ_u0px17by_RWn5ot-4rxG=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"June 25, 2024 at 1:15pm. I do not recommend to anyone.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPJBqS1FWuAvlKA7mRPTiCWyyz2nPUjrPYjqmcM\u0026fid=0x0:0x2f5507b307d0fc60"],"When":"2024-6-25"},{"Name":"Spring Wang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLMOpz_v4ssMlsZT_0g7sOO22cdL07mWO_x_lTFjjkEzlY4vg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Hire friendly staff please. I really enjoy when she is working. Also this pho is great, the 1 star reviews must have gotten extremely unlucky. Anyways that is my 2 cents. Thank you kind pho person! PS. Order extra meat you will not be disappointed.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Taz C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ235c-1POJF85QGI4N_CFSzUmrADwRBXdKObCvBIDceTrCYTc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"2 stars for food and 0 for service. We have eaten here a few times when they first opened. The portion size was decent and the food was average. I happened to be at the mall twice in a a row recently and was craving lemon grass chicken. The first time, as I approached the place, the lady at the front was busy doing something, she saw me but didn't bother acknowledge me and continued to do her thing at the other end. After about a minute, I had lost patience and was just about to leave, and she came over to the ordering side and just stood there. Still no acknowledgment. I said hi and proceeded to place my order and the lady just stared at me. I thought perhaps she didn't hear me, so I repeated my order. She just looked at me and said \"No\". Not understanding what the no meant, Im looking for some details, she just walked away. What a bizarre experience. Lol\nThe following day, we ended up ordering the lemongrass chicken meal. This time it was served by the tall guy who I've seen there since day 1. He was nice enough but the food was really bad. The noodles were overcooked and soggy. The chicken barely warm (instead of keeping directly on the warmer, the chicken was in a bowl on top of the warmer - this is also a food safety issue). Thoroughly disappointed by this location. Will definitely not be going back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM9E1dVo1F8b6a_tyPYVZx7_X6zLjg_6kXo6Lhp\u0026fid=0x0:0x2f5507b307d0fc60"],"When":"2019-11-19"},{"Name":"Ray","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXGVd5s-06Fr3JDo-bYWWNiziS7uiGN7g2hEorOk1Vp-qtDK_-cTg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I got food here and a drink at freshly squeezed. The cashier was very friendly and the lemongrass pork is so yummy. I'm not entirely sure what the food on the top is (it's like a crispy roll with meat inside) but it's amazing and flavorful. I love it 😁 And thoughtful of them to include water!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOTxbq6qLOFOG7kPvY3aWYQj-j3VpR0MJbRuLUy\u0026fid=0x0:0x2f5507b307d0fc60"],"When":"2022-5-28"},{"Name":"Martin V.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWHUWeLQtzrLwznxOz1qtEg2BlpBpzkU8Lx0nL6UaQRn9ju0mbz=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Not only quality of the chicken is down, now even the portion is half size what it used to be!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOaqC7D4F_4mJnvi6_4IgMJBFEWpYlZ3sGpoGUa\u0026fid=0x0:0x2f5507b307d0fc60"],"When":"2024-7-16"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"K H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVo2hR2qKHBGSuFyVVc1kqvuNnr23GVLd19IdZCsiU8tz8tbtW-=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This place needs to be shut down or needs FoodSafeBC to investigate. The cashier took dirty crumpled gloves out of her pocket, toyed around wth it, with the same dirty hands that handled cash. Then she made the sandwich. Sneezed without covering. The workers have 0 competence on food safety. People like this should not be making your food. Can’t comment on the food itself but it was grossly smothered in sauce. Save your money and go elsewhere","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP1TLj1g7jrTbyONdn0mrDIqhDCB_On4ojnzs1m&fid=0x0:0xde5d0863713ac02"],"When":"2024-3-6"},{"Name":"Taranjeet Kaur","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIARR6J7_dLhOQgf3_IPPrdIv548jXn7WkFu9ntMyVQDXXntw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A Must-Try Spot!
This is one of the best, and my favourite sandwich shop. Highly recommended for those searching for a satisfying meal. The food is delicious, and there are so many options. I tried a veggie sandwich with a side of mac and cheese, which is creamy and cheesy with chips and chachis palmar, and it was the best combo. Amazing Food!
The staff at Chachi’s is truly friendly, and always willing to help if you’re having a hard time choosing from their amazing menu.
If you haven’t been yet, you’re truly missing out on an incredible place.
Trust me, once you try it, you’ll keep coming back for more.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sarah L.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKaogBp5lS_siDflafszGD_mScnGnQ5K1SZB3BJajDlo2gKzg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Spent Many minutes TRYING TO ORDER. The staff were talking in the back behind closed doors (it was partially open and we saw). I shouted hello several times and gave up. My partner went back there to try to order from them 10mins later and they ignored him too and were laughing and chatting in the back. What a joke of a business.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMj3rKjMh_5IEdqh_JOfbyIeUjO2LPi_BUY4aO8&fid=0x0:0xde5d0863713ac02"],"When":"2024-11-15"},{"Name":"Gurleen Kaur","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKjY7HSCovoYGeG6ejoQ1-WSg_X2CHY9klJDN48vh05JRWLzw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The place Chachi’s is a hidden gem! The food is authentic and delicious, and the staff is very friendly and welcoming. I highly recommend the  Cajun chicken sandwich and the Mac n Cheese. You won't be disappointed!"","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lambarr Amrit","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocITM-hUBhHR9GoCDUHNasy6H_DShR_57m9UwmThRHAs_6xB0Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food is cooked to perfection. The staff is always welcoming . I have tried cajun chicken sandwich and suggest everyone to try. You will not be disappointed.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Joseph","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXFewP3uluLt8du6fEFaFzomfwJ5EkLfCMKaQWiwPEzhFG5NHhOfQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I love sandwiches and had high hopes for Chachi's. The sandwiches on their menu sound delicious and I ended up going for the Cubano. The Cubano ended up being pretty mediocre. The sandwich size was okay but there was not much marinated pork. There was also way too much sauce so it was overpowering the taste of the other ingredients. I expected a bit more for a $15 sandwich. The service was fast though, there was no line up and the sandwich was made quickly.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPRAW3iKS3mlsEnZ4dKJkC24ICjE4E1PYyEDv-l&fid=0x0:0xde5d0863713ac02"],"When":"2022-10-24"},{"Name":"Anne F","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI22FM57MnL6nTwIy_HLBevmQ1pVvxs8_tROXxFuEZTSVPTyg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The staff working on Friday morning were great. Friendly and helpful. The sandwiches were delicious.  We had the turkey and cranberry sandwiches. We had peach lemonade, and it was a refreshing drink that wasn't too sweet.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Michelle Ottens","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXVOO4PFnw-933em-16EoatsLWiyk679iIoF3AMiC8obmadJRQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Chachi’s has been my go-to place for well over a year now. The staff are always so friendly and accommodating and their mac and cheese is heavenly! Definitely an underrated spot at the mall— Make sure to go check it out!!","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews: [{"Name":"Rish Denner","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocITgdSa4iAuc96Z3cJfFyK-ZBzLzmLzDS_KG-gm2YSGt4XQ6w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Popped by for a pickup pizza special and was greeted by the manager who was extremely friendly \u0026 helpful suggesting the Vegetarian Fans pizza for me. Got it home and YUM! Really delicious and fresh. That crust though with the sesame seeds is a new twist on pizza crust and I love it. Will definitely be back. Great prices and if you're a family with picky eaters they make a personal size so the little ones can each have their own. ❤ I also ordered a piece of the tiramisu cheesecake...Best dessert ever from a pizza restaurant.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNCv9BYBDtVZMmZ84w2ANeVJle6PB3Q_kijb959\u0026fid=0x0:0xf2fb667237895032"],"When":"2024-2-24"},{"Name":"Daniel Yoo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJkwUOJ8cq94o-FfkcjXNXS5c4R9UaGmSSQdNis4XJFKokdBQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Reinstated as our favourite pizza place, we had an issue with an order, so they remade it for us and showed us why they're worth going to. The pizza was delicious!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM46fRagLzxhaUNLQkm6daTnmDKhSCGYvlz1Ej5\u0026fid=0x0:0xf2fb667237895032"],"When":"2024-10-21"},{"Name":"Anjith Jayaraj","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWc1tiafNzAuqIWPNK_3dMEWjMQESB8VfSZRafegoGRiU48LCb8Pw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Visited there yesterday for a quick bite. The person at the front was very helpful and friendly. Loved the service. Parking is available at the location. The pizza was amazing, loved the crust and the sesame seeds topped on the crust. The store is clean and well maintained. Will definitely visit there the next time, if in that location.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM4S5X49D9pam042VZV-aqGe-YYyLagk-m8khTu\u0026fid=0x0:0xf2fb667237895032"],"When":"2024-3-11"},{"Name":"Arsha S.R","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI9cF1OLmULGXBDEmb6jUJ2kT1dx7pTMjkszptvRYnfIBFycg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Red Swan Pizza is fantastic! The sesame seed crust adds a unique touch, and the toppings are always fresh and flavorful. Their Butter Chicken pizza is a must-try. Great service and reasonable prices too!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Richard J Bergeron","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXZExnbUKFKvplHQ_0M_2nTN2L_GFTHbWz1_5aOGcpxIqn_GckSKQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Had two different pizzas here . One was better than the other . Lots of toppings and crust was good but just not that tasty ! Can't explain . Will try again though . We're getting a bit pizza store heavy in tsawwassen !","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPwtxGxOy2E5u1g5S5TM_H-c4YMkE-yOsvEzBUd\u0026fid=0x0:0xf2fb667237895032"],"When":"2024-5-7"},{"Name":"Daniel mathew","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLLozA_qxJmy-MrTupAyeyZP95YCqUcKP6C92t7D2YF6DQFNA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great pizza, friendly staff and clean place , highly recommended","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP9pvd8_kdWLPO-0MIUoo8eOA56qxVsHZRa2r6m\u0026fid=0x0:0xf2fb667237895032"],"When":"2024-11-16"},{"Name":"Ray","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXGVd5s-06Fr3JDo-bYWWNiziS7uiGN7g2hEorOk1Vp-qtDK_-cTg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Tsawwassen has got a lot of great pizza places and this one really made its mark! I had the tuscan pizza with sesame seed crust, spinach, pizza sauce, hot chicken etc. The sauce wowed me! It has a very nice crunch and chew to it. The sesame seeds are a great touch.\nAlso, the desserts are really good too.\nNot the cheapest pizza eat around here, but highly recommend to try.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMtJ4QpaDrViICDMewVzQ_dwe2gkiZhZWLBG-x8\u0026fid=0x0:0xf2fb667237895032"],"When":"2024-2-14"},{"Name":"Maple Blood","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW2_tKZXzUxrm6T1n0qNCJsX65Kxa4HE7ZBl47w9lGm10E2-AM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great pizza, and management is quick to fix any issue with your order. The pizza always tastes good.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Jesse","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJSDyGy576NjOpFot9rCBdIpO7u4qZP6Qzr6EXuEXmqpkbcdQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Not sure what happened to this place. Haven’t been here for a couple of months.  Used to be pretty good.  Just got the pepperoni meatball sub.  The bun is stale and hard I could hardly bite through it.   The meatballs were dry and rubbery.  This place has really gone down hill fast.  Definitely won’t be back turned me right off these subs.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPFwIiMPOnsiSbDO4nrLB-WHZ92epDri8rWeBuc&fid=0x0:0xf3d18fd9288a10ad"],"When":"2024-9-25"},{"Name":"Marcus L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWAm1ka_ESYBlOFfTbfcnGmFcYKuqYakfSxihPN9UkLOeVieLhZ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Tried this FireHouse location for the first time. Definitely better than Subway in the same area!
Good flavor, soft bread, and hot meat.
It ain’t cheap tho! $46 bucks for 2 subs!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOC0TWbguundM8ehXDzWTwgCvlZFTd6iyN6i5H7&fid=0x0:0xf3d18fd9288a10ad"],"When":"2024-10-25"},{"Name":"Lee Gildemeester","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUmwK5TPiyJO9K2BikS-yqaHifl8H0QHLdeDujEGzwKhWsKSXQ7=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"had some great sandwiches here back in the summer, if overpriced, but todays was pretty bad. tried the french dips, 2 of which ran us over $40 (just the 2 sandwiches, not even a meal). the sandwiches were thinner than any other Ive had here, with the filling being chincy compared to the others Ive tried, at over $20 a sandwich it was much, much too thin. Super greasy, surprisingly cold considering it was made fewer than 10 minutes before we sat down to eat, and the Au Ju dipping sauce was super small for the size of the sandwiches. the container was only filled up about 1/3 of the way, and I feel pretty ripped off for more than $40 for 2 subs. the image of the dipping sauce is literally the amount they gave us, it was not partially consumed when the photo was taken. one sandwich went entirely uneaten it was such a disappointment. this was a 1 star meal, only because of past decent meals is this review a 2 star, but if this is the new business model I don’t think Ill be going back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMa7VBV9lmbb9fKsmu5D7UaimwYiHErRqPcMqif&fid=0x0:0xf3d18fd9288a10ad"],"When":"2024-11-21"},{"Name":"Joey Mullins","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVjA9hfj_Ijm7nk28n3Pwuv3ZUU8ObFM0Pq6x9qasT5gDb6RMN8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Definitely a sub place that's worth coming back to!

The Italian sub was excellent. Fresh ingredients, large portion size (I had leftovers). The staff were really friendly and helpful too. It's one of the best sub places around for sure!

Can't wait to come back to try the Meatball. Thanks Firehouse subs!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNAWJ4DDReXWk6INSiFVTLrv8zbcfKZ-QiRbm9Z&fid=0x0:0xf3d18fd9288a10ad"],"When":"2024-5-13"},{"Name":"justin mckillop","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXycL53shbjuiaMD6urzpkXK-Gz6EEnmXV8W8247HHolXRLn9Od=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"AWESOME SUBS! first time at this location. Was served with friendly Service. Plenty of seating & surprisingly not to busy. I got the Large Brisket Hatrick & my woman got the Large Smoked Turkey Italian. We usually go to the Abbotsford location but found ourselves in Tsawwassen craving Firehouse Subs. The service at this location was way quicker than the Abbotsford location. I've said it before & I'll say it again, Subway & Quiznos is NO LONGER an Option for us! The Quality & Quantity here is so much better. Definitely a better bang for you buck. This location was clean & exceeded our lunchtime cravings. Looking forward to our next visit.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMx2RCxB9IAFlTHUPXVh4RrICeBPVxQ8POYVRrT&fid=0x0:0xf3d18fd9288a10ad"],"When":"2024-6-2"},{"Name":"Brennan Matharu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLtf-lCZ0-sAH6Kjr__M4ylU-MIv4Is4kMCK-YJ7wc6HMHM0w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Heard this place opened recently in the tsawwassen mills area so I had to come and try. We got the brisket hat trick and the hook and ladder sandwiches. Both were pretty tasty, and nothing to complain about, I would say the sandwiches are like an upscale subway. One thing I did really like was the soda machine in the store, that thing had so many different flavours and options it was awesome! Pricing for the food was reasonable you get a pretty large portion. Will be back next time I have the chance!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNtX_2KoplfCPqwcLxFHKlvEnCU23n9T64FPazR&fid=0x0:0xf3d18fd9288a10ad"],"When":"2024-5-2"},{"Name":"Ray","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXGVd5s-06Fr3JDo-bYWWNiziS7uiGN7g2hEorOk1Vp-qtDK_-cTg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I seriously never knew subs could be good. I don't know how these subs are so good. Is it the sauce? Great staff? Even just a plain deli meat with cheese sub was a delight to eat.

If you order in store, it will be a little bit of a wait for your sub, but it will come out hot and fresh with melty cheese. Great quality. Lots of different types of subs. Prices feel a bit expensive but what isn't these days. Honestly, just sooo savory and tasty, really not what I was expecting!

Also, they have a soda machine with a lot of different flavors.

Can't wait to come back for more!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNQnOvnK_I--vBquNSvPAqkJQpxGA3-rPdsVcUb&fid=0x0:0xf3d18fd9288a10ad"],"When":"2024-5-23"},{"Name":"Dmitri B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLdxsyfOxNZ3JROY2TPuZvZYKsy3nqn1s0Pu1pbKehWbCiDng=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time trying their subs. They taste great and the service was fast. Loved the real smoked beef. I definitely recommend. Great choice of hot sauces as well.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Azeen Khehra","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJbM4K_boQ6PMOv25M1oqKSMGP8lxPEx1Yl6h3dWkGtJQA0Vw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Worst Service By Komalpreet..
Firstly i asked for Flatbread pizza n she said we can’t make it n then i ordered 3 bagels and she burnt them all n when i asked for atleast 1 new bagel she started arguing like this is not your store..
If u have authority to remake the stuff then why u can’t just make it without arguing..","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPPKU7qMUy3CG5W4k5w38TYqusFfu-hqi71YMe-&fid=0x0:0x6a3e2578d4976537"],"When":"2024-11-3"},{"Name":"Joan Crawford","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLLEB6f0HvP3lLgbpMMDeVhv3jySnL9qESYJriLzyQB-uGSBw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"l had the worst experience and last experience at this TH.   The drive through young woman charged me over $7 for steeped tea and a croissant with plain cream cheese.  I asked her why it was such a high price today???   She didn't answer just started to give me my tea and then a water bottle.  I had not ordered a water bottle.  She said l did. I had ordered a cup of water.   She gave me back my money and then got another order to deal with.  I drove away without my sandwich.  I came back and went inside and told the girl at the til.  She said she saw me get my money for my sandwich back from the drive through girl.  I had to argue with her that was for the water bottle l did not order.  .  Then she kept backing up her co worker.   The girl at the drive through forgot to HAND me my sandwich after she had to refund that water bottle.  Holy talk about two rude young women.
I think the two men who run the driveway through are very rude but they are great compared to these two young women.   I also think some of the drive through staff talk way to fast.   It seems like a competition to them to get everyone in and out fast.  This person. At the window was talking way to fast too.  Good grief.  Slow down.

Train your staff better!!!!!

I have heard many people upset about the staff in this particular place.  You are loosing customers.  There are no long line ups at this TH like at Starbucks on Canoe Dr.  Maybe a short rush at lunch sometimes but not really compared to other TH.

They need to learn some skills for dealing with the public.
I will never go back to this place.

This article does not include the few wonderful polite ones they have there.  You know who you are.    Get a job somewhere else quick.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Bradley Dougherty","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJqgGwHhnGDE0p20s1bs7ju-N01GgzCaA_vBAarBf3FDMzl3w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Never had a problem here up until today, actually have always raved about how fast and accurate this particular location usually is.

HOWEVER!
Lately service has been lacking, as has friendliness, which is evident by the negative reviews as of late.

On a more serious note.
Today, there was a very long line, and as I was sitting there watching and waiting for my turn at the drive thru window (I was next), I watched as one of the Tim Hortons staff members threw garbage out the window onto the ground.
I clearly watched this happen, and it was absolutely intentional, there was no way it was an accident.
When I got to the window a few seconds later, I told him I saw that, and I received every excuse possible.
I just want to make it extremely clear, that there is absolutely no excuse for this. And that this is absolutely despicable behaviour and does not represent the value and culture of Tim Hortons.
If I ever see this happen again, I will be making plenty of phone calls
1. To corporate and reporting the franchise
2. To Bilaw and filing a complaint
3. To Tsawwassen Mills as they will fine the location

Honestly, shocked that I witnessed that this morning. And I expect some sort of conversation to happen within your staff.

This happened Thursday Dec 19 at approx 12:15pm","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Harshpreet kaur","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI5Cj17k5VGtavNvEKNXlsO0TNgLjgRGfjoOu0k0yqqzuXFYA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I usually have a decent experience at Tim Hortons, but today was exceptionally frustrating. We ordered a bagel through the drive-thru and politely asked the staff member, SUKHMAN to cut it in half, as we’ve done countless times before. Shockingly, she refused, stating they couldn’t do it. When we mentioned that this has never been an issue in the past, she remained rude and unhelpful.

Customer service is crucial, and being treated with disrespect is unacceptable. I hope management takes note and ensures that all staff members are trained to be courteous and accommodating. This experience has made me reconsider returning to this location.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Prikshit Rana","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLq5VJ7JI4qmRlPo86l2o2-zO_2DcOzTGR_PrhvjdeVPjLqTZw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Worst experience ever, the staff is rude and untrained. Firstly, they took the wrong order, Secondly, they kept the order on the counter and didn't even call for it. When we asked if it was our order, they had no clue the guy who took the order literally said to his coworker "I have no idea whose order is this". We were confused too, because we ordered Oreo ice cap and it was a normal ice cap. But, later he confirmed it was our order. But when we went to call out for the wrong order, it's hard to get hold of them, they act so busy when there are hardly 1 customers and they are 6-7 servers. Then the person insisted, we have ordered the normal ice cap ( trying to say, we were wrong), but changed the order later and took too long, almost cleared all orders before our's. No wonders why the store hardly had any customer.

Lastly when we asked to talk to manager, he was the same guy who took our order. Even we were speechless, if the manager doesn't know what he is doing, I can imagine the team. In customer service Half of the battle i lost, when you have a uninterested face while talking to customer, and these guys was uninterested to take the order and deliver the right one.

All the staff including the manager are so busy when there is no rush, I don't understand how?, when I was calling a guy, literally standing next to the counter, he ignored as if he didn't listen, after 4 loud calls. Guys if you want customer to wait despite listening to customers call, please ask the customer to wait, don't straight away ignore. All the faces were full of disappointment and feel like they don't wanna work. I have been to such busy Tim's where they have 50 orders at a time, still they smile, and treat customers the way they should be treated. At least call for the order when it's ready. Uninterested faces while taking orders, rude looks when someone is calling out for wrong order, will not make your life easy, it will piss off the other person, ruin their mood and endup in a bad review.

And when I saw the reviews of this place, no wonders there were a lot of people not happy with the service. TH Management please look at it, you are losing customers. If the staff don't wanna work, please change them, because looking at the reviews I am sure they don't wanna improve themselves.

I am not visiting this Tim's again, but this is concerning for Tim Hortons management, so many complaints from one particular branch. Please act now do not wait for a major mess in the future.

P.S:- Kudos to Tim's King George SkyTrain station, one of the best Tim's, they seamlessly handle such a huge rush at all times and most importantly with a smile.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"James Quiros","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVKBj9KhrHnpMxkWmoQzGoAbAt71NnBp7_tWZzxU2BlPDYiaYF8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I went last night about 5 minutes to closing time and was told they were already closed?! Then i read the reviews on this location about how incompetent the staff is, needless to say i will NEVER go back there and will advise everyone to read the reviews for this location so they can save themselves the trouble of going  to a Tims where the staff clearly doesnt care about the clients.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Abu Osman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUNYQrpSAPmNBexWcQ-TK_wz6eRdBlO1nmK8dr1rofYisDgjlNB=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Watch out your bill always they will charge you extra and when you cache it they will claim it's donations by Tim Horton out of ourcontrol & I didn't get how dare charged without your permission.? 😤
And the worst they cancel your orders if you don't except it.!!?","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Francesca","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLSsNoBEHmQ0RfDPJstcswSnNys4JvxuLG7zyvkRIgS0XbOLrk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Worst customer service ever. The girl at drive thru said “Hello what can I get for you” and we waited for at-least 30 minutes only for another customer to tell us that they are closed.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews: [{"Name":"Jeremy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ3C2VQPms3Y2ECnyhVtbvLvGpFJupKY7ZP92P3XfKRiwNZaw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time here, I was really happy. They only had two employees there… and a big line. Managers, staff better. There ended up being a wait for the food, but the staff was hustling and doing the best they could so.\n\nI was really happy with the food. I had the pad Thai with crispy beef. Really good amount of food, lots of beef… super hot even after I took it home… tasted great. Great option other than a burger for fast food. Will be back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNZqojHpJ10wLJu6qR_w5x34sqE6cIjFNJUHow9\u0026fid=0x0:0xc433e8ca3cb8209a"],"When":"2024-9-25"},{"Name":"Laura Elout","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUBg9fHbXsEgZIbtE51F5pT8QP7WuFEjNo377sVa8SK0tKVAFPE_Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is my first time going to the Noodle Box. I had the crispy ginger beef with jasmine rice. Sooo delicious!  Such an extremely clean and welcoming atmosphere. The customer service was top notch. Rajveer spent time with me to make sure I was comfortable with the spice level.  He also walked me through the various noodles I could order with the crispy ginger beef.  There is also a section you can sit at and watch them cook your food.   All in all it was a 10/10 experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMJ-i-oynVy2lkI8uRI6XSUo3HT7p3Tpo6wcVDm\u0026fid=0x0:0xc433e8ca3cb8209a"],"When":"2024-8-18"},{"Name":"Jen Jackson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVuWBLOHPAK5UtFjqk_k6fMLzerE_c_s_XiTG4Zrf9vrRFSamxh=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Have visited this location several times with a good experience but today was terrible. We got the Szechwan bowl and the Drunken Noodle along with some add ons. The Szechwan bowl had a very off-putting sweet flavor and the Drunken Noodle was incredibly bland and boring. The “crispy beef” breading was soggy and like chewing leather when you bite into it. Order very carefully if you choose to eat here.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMZxkLU6IBCoDiwHbAlYqENRFHGAuAKIcRwpCE_\u0026fid=0x0:0xc433e8ca3cb8209a"],"When":"2024-9-7"},{"Name":"Jesse","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJSDyGy576NjOpFot9rCBdIpO7u4qZP6Qzr6EXuEXmqpkbcdQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"What a disgusting bowl of slop they just sold me.  I can’t believe the difference between what the food looks like on the menu and what they really serve you.  Looks at these pictures.  Absolutely disgusting!!!  You can see in the pictures what they say it looks like and what it really looks like.  Just drowning is sauce.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipObwTgj5Vd5_vo7C63SPd24uM33DBQRV_JEUZx7\u0026fid=0x0:0xc433e8ca3cb8209a"],"When":"2024-11-24"},{"Name":"WWG.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUn78hs1gyPa62w7hNh3K-ZPDxvzydvZVSMCMdGqbbmzV7yyzWs=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great experience here tonight. Greeted with great customer service, food was fast and delicious. Drowning in sauce, but thats what I like. Its quite pricey, but its nice and fresh, if noodle box is what you're craving, this will hit the spot. Bathrooms are clean and the restaurant is comfortable enough to sit in and eat in peace. Will be back again. Thanks guys,","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Percy, Jones","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV6g-5jtl_Yq69yPlFaWbeURqM1ztOJz4LoJ0yyO10RQF78nmU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I've visited this place a few times and let me tell you, it's like a circus! The cashier must have taken a crash course in how to mess up orders. And don't get me started on the kitchen lady who keeps running in and out, asking the cashier what to cook. She's so forgetful, she probably forgets her own name! Oh, and the way they handle bowl plates? It's like they're playing a dangerous game of finger gymnastics( at least one finger on the inside of tue food bowl..)It's a total disaster in there, like Hurricane Katrina decided to take up a part-time job at a Noodlebox. IMO you'll be entertained, but maybe not satisfied.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMfMDL4djEjVLA9gh3mglu2WgIJbFso4SrMHI0D\u0026fid=0x0:0xc433e8ca3cb8209a"],"When":"2024-7-8"},{"Name":"Parmeet Purba","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLXhlsGn1AoGnvIIKAlg5yFw8KkhjG6wGTUx6oDOLQVly7nMw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Noodle Box is a fantastic spot for delicious noodle dishes with a variety of options that are full of fresh ingredients and authentic flavors. user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Jordana Howley","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLcyXBlLdHydYsF_Gj7ansJBTnASxt14ZYfUHCYEyBPCyl3vQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Brunch Chorizo Bowl was amazing the first time we were in! Hollandaise was perfect. Quite a wait the second time we were in as the ticket machine malfunctioned. We are service humans too, so we get it bit would have been nice to know. Food still tasted good though.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO89grvHZ5cJAwoiQrBSc3inoz3pB7Uniu_xiQy&fid=0x0:0x1bce997010bf8161"],"When":"2024-12-23"},{"Name":"Fernanda Coelho","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVedTXYXr1zyxhZdZOPmfv5AfLwGhLcGc5suzn7a9G_hXu7LFla=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"LOVE this place, I drove 20min to get breakfast here lol, photos are the traditional breakfast and a cappuccino. So cool to see that they started a pay it forward program, so I bought someone a classic breakfast wrap! I also recommend their roasted veggie panini if you're vegetarian, it's delicious!!! The only feedback I have is that there is a lot of foam in the drinks sometimes, so it's a bit tricky to drink at first lol but very good nonetheless!!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMYmZQx0CdTMmNoKuE-Kj2ONBSeq2_hROVV2GVv&fid=0x0:0x1bce997010bf8161"],"When":"2024-10-26"},{"Name":"Linda Hansbauer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVbhYntSwrf3fPiWmrNihB_RxxZEX6epZ6NkhTpeBuOWgHv5aaF=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am visiting my family for a week. From Australia 🇦🇺 🪃  - this new Southland Community has a lot to offer. Went for a walk and spotted L'aromas - nice "pitstop" to energies you for the next couple of km of walking. I had no food - the Matcha I had was delicious. Interior modern and pleasing to the eye - clean - staff friendly. I will be back, willst I am here!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNqNAmfTvp-3eQGO9gnRfm4VShwuU8L59RB61Bw&fid=0x0:0x1bce997010bf8161"],"When":"2024-8-21"},{"Name":"Malani S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLv2sekt8bQvCrOL6j9X6m8xvp17ZCvNYrMy0rl1w80IWruAA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I ordered a chicken curry salad. Like most chicken curry salad, it is mayo based, but this is clearly mayo stew. The crunch of celery and apples are missing and only 1/2 of a grape is present. After taking my first bite, I went up to the till and tried to explain to a worker that there’s too much mayonnaise. Her response was that it’s the way they make it. It’s their recipe to have your curry salad drowning in mayo. She didn’t offer to adjust or correct anything.

They received  2 stars as my husband and sister-in-law’s breakfast were decent. Overall, I wouldn’t come back or recommend this place.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMDYgatG7rgRo0IwMmZDUCEr8YKxQcqJJRJh03m&fid=0x0:0x1bce997010bf8161"],"When":"2024-8-31"},{"Name":"Jamie Glennon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWLOjs5-jqgyQWUX_yOuzgUG9TpUgCo3VZBWVH5vnxr8HdflLs=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is a really great place to go when you are in Tsawwassen looking for a coffee shop that also has breakfast, lunch and dinner.

They have expanded their breakfast menu quite a lot recently and are priced very well against other places.

They have beer, wine and spirits and live music.

A large south facing patio with fire pits and plenty of seating makes it a great location to meet friends.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNmRjb6p9ZV4kxJ2mtzZ4N7DClfiDnTVaU4sOY3&fid=0x0:0x1bce997010bf8161"],"When":"2024-8-19"},{"Name":"Eddie So","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocISSdmRal6WEYNToT2BfCZQ0cdumKRhmtyRM82KD93UMkc0-g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A really good coffee shop and restaurant in this area. There are lots of good seating area indoor and outdoor. The staff are nice and friendly.
Usually we come for coffee or tea with some baked goods.  But we are late this time,  we decide try the pizza.  It is good too.  We can have more options later.
They also offer happy hour drink and food too.
There are more menu.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNAqnPs8Gtav8n8y6dKUDQfEGcJqmRcocje4RhA&fid=0x0:0x1bce997010bf8161"],"When":"2023-6-13"},{"Name":"Ray","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXGVd5s-06Fr3JDo-bYWWNiziS7uiGN7g2hEorOk1Vp-qtDK_-cTg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a nice time here; cozy atmosphere, not too busy on a Good Friday. I absolutely loved the blueberry danish, could tell it was fresh with delicious cream cheese and juicy blueberries. Avocado bacon wrap took a little while to make but that seems to be because they make it fresh as it was nice and hot, and it was deeelicious! Like a sit down restaurant style. Definitely coming here again to try the wide menu selection.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNktMPXK3EiTgxwdxipCNPxZXdiyhssOtCvM5qP&fid=0x0:0x1bce997010bf8161"],"When":"2023-4-8"},{"Name":"Jeanine Manley","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKsiCSl_kDu5HLPcil1hcAWowgG5wYruXebcQF0I1lDL6C3XA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Stopped by early afternoon for a bite to eat. Hubby and I shared the Roast Chicken Sandwich 😋 and Carrot Cake 😋, drip coffee for me and English breakfast tea for him. Service was friendly and polite and the food was amazing. We will definitely be back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPmj5c_IEOJaexSjVu_k-TvrZT2HpAH01IQL_m3&fid=0x0:0x1bce997010bf8161"],"When":"2024-1-5"}]

[{"Name":"Beatrice Gandu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW-m69YxvoaMOoMimuj6-sA4-k4eYqu5MNiPHLVrevqzu-K2Gac=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I was at the Tsawwassen Mills and had the beef ramen soup, and I was satisfied with what I ordered. My husband had their chicken teriyaki.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPwq9wNBdxKGk85n4eZy94eL98MU7-AAl_CeIWC&fid=0x0:0xd7238af858a364f2"],"When":"2024-3-2"},{"Name":"Adam C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVq5dzaFoYr2lIhRH1dcut99VIjmI2-PJTWQy4OQa5sNKBay1btEQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Worst sushi ever.  And the longest wait ever...  it was slapped together almost as if they forgot our order.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMQJWNseEL76uVII2r96B3hr-0_vilXInHJa1SX&fid=0x0:0xd7238af858a364f2"],"When":"2024-10-16"},{"Name":"karanvir singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJmhSTkwf552ii13luYjLCu_N5AKepHjDsEI26QJqQpG06RylI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I recently visited Edo Japan restaurant Tsawwassen mills location on Saturday around the afternoon and unfortunately, my experience with their customer service was quite disappointing. From the moment I walked in, it seemed like the staff were uninterested and inattentive. We waited almost 20 minutes to give our order. my experience with the cashiers left a lot to be desired. There was a old lady on there cash. It was clear that she struggled with basic tasks like reading the order correctly or understanding simple instructions. I had to repeat my order multiple times, and even then, it was still entered wrong.
When I tried to explain the mistake, the cashier seemed confused and unable to fix it without calling over a manager, which slowed down the process even more. The lack of basic communication skills made what should have been a quick and easy transaction incredibly frustrating.she doesn't seems professional as at all.it was almost impossible to get cashier's attention for simple things like water refills she cannot even understand that basic thing.It's alarming that a restaurant would allow such poorly trained or ill-equipped staff to handle customer orders and payments.Customer service starts at the register, and if your cashiers can't handle even that, it really diminishes the overall dining experience. I hope they invest in better training or hiring staff who can provide a smoother and more professional experience.The overall attitude of the staff made the experience uncomfortable and unwelcoming.
I had heard good things about the food here, but with such poor customer service, I don't think I will be returning anytime soon.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jada f","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXBMbFjOAN3hgEEo2BAevmyr4y71okWigCdxsj9jXJ-PgQrPXW95A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"As a former Edo employee I'm pretty sure you are not allowed to deny service to someone claiming you have 0 sushi then proceed to sell the same roll to the person behind me, not sure how you can have no rolls period and then sell them right after you tell me no.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mory M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUPs8avgpY6Oe_Ytsg4rqTPRpKj-6YZ9I59NE5Wd6hmPPMEz98=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"My son tried the kids sushi and he liked the taste so he had to go for the second one😅

He also liked the kids sugar free apple juice.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNRUu5YD0Fietl_4iXu9MZrvAIKJrmCY2ZgbcE&fid=0x0:0xd7238af858a364f2"],"When":"2024-3-28"},{"Name":"Romy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJV8-S3VeeKeT0pn9n2DdxFX14BmtdMp_HhzVdEx3f6OGeOaQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Been here last week, and got myself a chicken teriyaki bento with thin noodles, spring roll and california roll. Food was good, but sushi and customer service was alright","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tanajia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWRPYyFPaczOeV6zQiyh40y9OOlQPgcBRd8Osbgjgw8A-bl5Ovi=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Very unpleased with the service here. Quality of food wasn't the best for my first time eating here. Also, Customer Service needs improvement. Check the reviews before attending!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Prem Pan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV-bRwMUR_3lhjYRPU862sn_F6CcK9W1DMD9tQZpIfh1gPi2RxM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"➡️We ordered food and we were not given the option of different rice.(white rice/Brown rice.) They were so hurry to send us when i asked them about brown rice, They gave me silly reason that the white rice is already on the plate and they cannot change it.
➡️ The guy on the grill literally touched the raw shrimp with the spoon of Teziki sauce and he didn't washed the spoon. Which i think is food contamination. ☢🤢

⛔Bad experience don't go here.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM7cOOTpZ73Kr1tFFdccd6NydPvIj3PAS_I5fEX&fid=0x0:0xd7238af858a364f2"],"When":"2018-9-2"}]

[{"Name":"Andrew Giassa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKs2M8Lm_fO5YMx6QeBO4bPk3OR_tJ-4_oCO6-v2DtArGT_4g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time going there this morning... Americano and bear claw were so delicious that I had to go back for lunch too! The coffee had such rich flavour to it! The sandwiches and desserts were very tasty! Nice atmosphere and friendly people! The staff were very polite, accommodating, attentive, and kept the place very clean! My new favourite cafe in Tsawassen, which I will absolutely be returning to!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM1XsfVfdEQM3AlTzGmkwA5TaRQsJ8Odu3YARVk&fid=0x0:0x8313008a81ad6f69"],"When":"2024-11-3"},{"Name":"Christine Kelly","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjViXAovH45MnNLisSYPlbAdr50-xqpXW5iVtG6G2pYCk32fQOB_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is such a cute little place! Close the ferry, we stopped here for brunch before heading to Victoria. The English muffin sandwiches were delicious as was the yogurt parfait. Idk why it is but all yogurt in Canada tastes better than in the states. My friend ordered tea which she loved and my latte was delicious!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOtOzY8pSi0G7i9sHHpze27FfzvCskVrdjj2VoL&fid=0x0:0x8313008a81ad6f69"],"When":"2024-10-10"},{"Name":"wah chi yip","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKKBykHMUbkrtJ4cwRRXsjOnAzAcOzwrpq-XVjovUt6A3trFQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A hidden gem in this small town.  It's a small family restaurant.  The baked goods are homemade. I think all of them are good. I love the coconut cake.
The staff is super nice to us.  Since we only order one coconut cake, she cut the cake into two and serves us by 2 plates.  Thank you for her caring to seniors.
We always come here only for afternoon tea since we live in Vancouver.
We didn't try the sandwich and soup.  But the sandwich looks good from the other table, we have the bagel and it is always good. The coffee and tea are good.  They still offer the pot for the tea and I love the tea set.
They always have great services, friendly and helpful.
I think they have reasonable price for their customers too!
If you are in this area, this is the place you should not miss.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOInc5bUVJsDxWi-GB6RnbyTMSAGphovRYCCCgb&fid=0x0:0x8313008a81ad6f69"],"When":"2024-6-21"},{"Name":"Celi Ribet","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVoYG5slbals5vHoHXxhmSpAKY1SRqjtLQwadcKXsFpTDJ0esn3=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It was so fun to stop here and see all the frogs! Also it has a very cozy, homey vibe. Friendly staff will greet you and it is clear that they take pride in their service and products.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMmY7UtlX1fZmzfpH_xm8IJRCdP9NQkvxn59P04&fid=0x0:0x8313008a81ad6f69"],"When":"2024-8-3"},{"Name":"angel lo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK1IzL3-IELA7R7E3oFObEFF5jKqUJ8mIkFOIr338r21pBTPQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is a nice breakfast place in delta area, and it called Frog in restaurant title, then I ordered the London frog as my drinks of the day.

Plus, they have varieties of the breakfast to choose from, and we choose the avocadoes toast and the chorizo breakfast wraps, these 2 items were so delicious!

The london frog and cappacino were very nice and yummy also.

The environment is very good as well.

This is recommended for everyone in delta to try it out!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOlScBHkrRW3YmZy7D8d9UfUnrQIjVWpQ7AoJ0D&fid=0x0:0x8313008a81ad6f69"],"When":"2024-5-21"},{"Name":"Maria M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXmuhUB-INQ3XCbE2M9HT-MdzILSuqxW6ls6tLvy0JgUoxl1f3wCQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great spot around TSW mills area. The Gingerbread hot chocolate was delicious, the eggnog latte and the muffin were just okay. Lots of options of treats and merchandise. Nice place to sip on a coffee while staring at the rain outside, nice vibes.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPVy4cLh4udfq61IKbbllHLJhrRF7O1dXbS0gnG&fid=0x0:0x8313008a81ad6f69"],"When":"2023-12-16"},{"Name":"XJ Chan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV7WcjqVdoNPNDRqOZSiFSZHUDbel5oDzpy4rSaDZj54EOkAa5x=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a huge cuppa great oatmilk cappuccino and the best roast beef sandwich I’ve had in a while. Love the place too with the funny little frogs as decor - a great place to stopover for breakfast!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNFi7iVKUBhkHM7gU4NS-YNWXVX0GaYFzWWWdNe&fid=0x0:0x8313008a81ad6f69"],"When":"2024-6-3"},{"Name":"Eddie So","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocISSdmRal6WEYNToT2BfCZQ0cdumKRhmtyRM82KD93UMkc0-g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A small lovely place to enjoy the coffee and cakes.  The staff are super friendly.
My wife loves this place and she loves the store baked goods.  She still remembered the coconut cake that they made years ago.
Now they offer a really good outdoor eating area.  They keep the place so tidy and clean in and out.  As before the owner and the staff are so nice and helpful.
If you come for afternoon tea, you must try their baked goods.
The indoor is a nice area too.
We have the coconut cake again in January 2024 again.  It's as good as before.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPZIqAQvyssAgnAPyUGhWIUVg2VZGAlVRWEiJHY&fid=0x0:0x8313008a81ad6f69"],"When":"2022-8-14"}]
