[{"Name":"Anne Marie Mantofa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWOHbTcgo4L5n1fem29aqT8SAdU9sjLA5z5jT9b2z2Kmwbu2_I=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Lovely  place in tsawwassen mills! They have both savory and sweet crepes and everything is delicious, was very nice to have them after walking around shopping. Gelatos was very nice as well, and the kind owner told me that it was all freshly self-produced. Should try if you’re stopping by tsawwassen mills! 😊","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNK6LISWIUZ2ldDx59PaqWIGWtrqFnA_ppIa6Ea&fid=0x0:0x648de26d18ef0b81"],"When":"2024-9-21"},{"Name":"nary note","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVyML8yeIGpjcOrFUPOZpY-8KQ7AbSJTsUMPfVsPw7NoNuRfxCR=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am from Singapore. Came across this Delicious Crepes store and it has left the best impression on me. Truly delicious crepes with beautiful presentation and flavorful gelato ice cream to go together. The owner was outgoing and friendly. He was very meticulous in the preparation. The staff was hospitable. Have a wonderful experience & I recommend to everyone! I would like to come back here again and again. Well done!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPG2n7SDNU_jaDLgbH7FHIvmUa16fHpuSnOMoe1&fid=0x0:0x648de26d18ef0b81"],"When":"2023-11-13"},{"Name":"Guri kaur","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVtHHKq6wnhRgKBh6zfDzs6RJF_CFwvcFKtbHxZnyPBBd1M35FVFw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"We have been there today around 6pm. There were two girls on the shift. One girl was having lollipop while preparing crepe. I looked at her, she took it out from her mouth for few seconds and put right back in. We had purchased gelatos so it was  not my food.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dominique Anes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI3IAEvnE0r8hi6giXw69MS4oRv8JCa-VIdXhWLC2yKQBNXNA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I went here with my boyfriend and we both loved our crepes, lots of care and presentation put into it. The cheesecake nutella strawberry crepe is the most decadent dessert in town!! I would love for this place to be on SkiptheDishes or DoorDash or UberEats because I'd order crepes all the time!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMfv_MQere6zllgWo59R1xXIFkSQ983JClbwmnC&fid=0x0:0x648de26d18ef0b81"],"When":"2020-10-3"},{"Name":"Rahim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU4wlgtmAJFCPZ0n_3Eyp_TfiUVd1vo8vP_cRZSDslqagrvFfLC=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The sign says 8.25 for 3 scoops and they charged 8.75. When I pointed that out to them, instead of apologizing they started arguing that that's the old price and it has increased... They also said "it's not a big deal" and I shouldn't even talk about it. That was amazing!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOW6-zwTNlu0WheburXSPB_kUg7BXCtVFrBwsaO&fid=0x0:0x648de26d18ef0b81"],"When":"2023-11-5"},{"Name":"Peter Wheatley","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW-Xx8bh9dxpBvjBaF-CRp109ZVqhRQDrLZVS95xtfx3MN8EHSp=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a tasty Tuttie-Fruittie crepe with my wife. Very friendly owner and quick service, perfect for a 10 minute break from hitting the stores.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNcmZ0_q3us7pN--IdG17mr9id_W3kSwsgRlTR8&fid=0x0:0x648de26d18ef0b81"],"When":"2020-8-22"},{"Name":"Swapnil Kambli","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUdhhWN0KCMgQl8JxSlRxuwT7oQItuYRCMRTco9Mv-DKvRQLHe2=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"- Crepes did taste good, but hey anything with Nutella and strawberry would. :P
We found them a bit chewy (perhaps a lot of refined flour)

- bottled water here sells for 2.85$","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMmODtdCrPP2Xsvsi7oOkJGYN8smTVxkdiezFk5&fid=0x0:0x648de26d18ef0b81"],"When":"2022-4-16"},{"Name":"rudy hartono","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL999upeItmaE3vfA1wInh21bng-DUcxoq7wz9oOghEUfKf7A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best gelato I have tasted in a while. The service is very fast and the seats are clean, along with the seating outside. We came on a Sunday evening. We had 2 single cheeseburgers and a plain vanilla cone. Would come again if I lived closer.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOMKJp5uSrzTcCWfKWSGb0mO3L4YCzsVDy-gBLW\u0026fid=0x0:0x99767913b8168ab2"],"When":"2024-8-5"},{"Name":"Raeburn MacDougall","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVIoXHoCNiCsL0dOjQhl4dr7HXmy8LsAXROqZKdAcT-ThcE0fCn=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great follow up and awesome final product. Needed a birthday cake for my daughter's birthday party. Ordered Friday morning and it was ready for pickup on Saturday at noon. Everyone loves the cake. Thanks again DQ Tsawwassen. Definitely recommend. Btw right decision to get the 10\" was perfect for the number of guests. (15ppl)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPNTI1sUTIlqKr82RKW4rq90UfpkTe4WIZM77hf\u0026fid=0x0:0x99767913b8168ab2"],"When":"2024-10-7"},{"Name":"Ray","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXGVd5s-06Fr3JDo-bYWWNiziS7uiGN7g2hEorOk1Vp-qtDK_-cTg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What can I say? Great little place. Great crew. Somehow, out of every fast food place, I've never had an issue with this DQ. Blizzards always got all the fixings. It's a shame the company has such expensive prices, otherwise I'd eat here more often. They do have online deals though.\n\nIt can get busy. Patience is a virtue, though. I never mind waiting for quality stuff.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN5QjIUyyMp4P54YWZpfsK2uRIaKFoK6MGXMVTp\u0026fid=0x0:0x99767913b8168ab2"],"When":"2024-5-22"},{"Name":"Dan Lorenz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVa_eC-U0kV3zmKzI4E1osV8_z7ABPGLuq9fXQNAmdOuVhfXvuZ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The quality control here has changed over the years. Unfortunately it won’t be a place I return to, I gave 1 star for food and 1 star for service because I feel they are related to the problem, 2 stars because it looks like a Dairy Queen. Take it at face value, you can see by my profile I don’t ever leave negative comments, but as you can tell in the photo it was necessary to do so.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPGP9oQzs239gWgvDjBrF9Xv6AfHBUB4rXoy1hg\u0026fid=0x0:0x99767913b8168ab2"],"When":"2024-4-20"},{"Name":"Shayna Mutter","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJiBCFejhN8RptXER0ououzV6EEYzCE6CN9lrCTnhdrK7JZ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Have bought small blizzards twice over the last 3 months.  Both times my blizzard has been missing the chocolate in my Chocolate cherry love. I understand this perhaps isn’t a better known one to make but the blizzard has also been soup like each time it’s been served to me. 17$ for two basically uneatable blizzards.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Wei x","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX_gqktxpcwm5-Ae9lvoeXAyfIgSzBgJfFmiGs2nilpJU5Zx6z7jw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The burgers are pretty good. Convenient location as well.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPJ8GTCSNV9QWOkjbXZyV_Poq-9n0EkhW1x3Iln\u0026fid=0x0:0x99767913b8168ab2"],"When":"2024-8-5"},{"Name":"Izabelle Stevens","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW0xor0LTuCME09A2xaIU8St031SfzJF5d9RYay38Nfv_2H470F=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I ordered a cake for my best friend’s birthday from here and they were awesome about getting it done and ready for pickup. [{"Name":"Lygia Misquitta","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVXN3CUbzt47zfh4dameFA6V05sbmmVOgatGglaH24z_uJvtyeXkQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Buenos Dias Cafe is a hidden gem located in KinVillage Community Centre in Tsawwassen. Chef Adrian is a magician at his craft and he Cooks wonderful gourmet meals for reasonable prices.
Muffins and Almond croissants are baked fresh in house daily.
The Kombucha here is exceptional.
Specials and Soup changes weekly.
The Fish n Chips is a customer favorite and Curry Fridays are busy, so if you are a curry lover  please pre order.
You will love the food here. Very authentic. Absolutely great quality and presentation. Chef Adrian also does all kinds of Caterings from small gatherings, celebrations of Life, weddings. Buenos Dias Cafe got voted Best Caterer by peoples choice Awards in Delta.
The Cafe is only open Mon- Fri from 8am -2pm.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNBl3hHoCPHEwKixI0_a31p7AVGyi5WTBdcLy_-&fid=0x0:0x229670dd9344c12e"],"When":"2023-4-17"},{"Name":"Becky Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLs8PLbMvH6iUPlyNF1_71YGyZOKFVKo9JmWQrggiF2sxpUXURN=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"such a hidden gem! chef adrian's food is so good, especially the unique weekly friday specials. today's friday special is keema ghotala which was super tasty.

I'm normally pretty stuck up when it comes to Sushi. However, for mall-grade food I was actually pretty impressed at the flavor and how fresh it tasted. Also good value, although there is an additional charge for extra ginger if your after it.
I can't speak for the hot dishes but overall pretty happy.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN_o7QI9wwipAFm9mQdsvGZWzgVBlkiNE8Iw-BQ&fid=0x0:0x992886a809fc679e"],"When":"2021-1-3"},{"Name":"A F","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX2iTrJszKnOcVhaa1e58UFNYfDr104Vsfh-lMQyoAuxyXXhAux=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Food was very disappointing. The chicken "Katsu" on their menu is a very lightly breaded piece of chicken that is reheated and not made fresh. It's soft and mushy. Then everything is drenched in a "teriyaki" sauce that does not taste good. Please spend your money elsewhere until they drastically improve.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"May Zhagro","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU9KviWdU_UGm6yjKPv-6aFaljm1EC_ecrxYhnt_LO3duiyBNho=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Relatively healthy, affordable food option among the fast food stalls. There are bento boxes, individual sushi roll sets, noodle soups, teriyaki rice dishes, and even bubble tea. I bought the beef bento box and saw the person at the counter cook the beef on the hot plate and it was nice and warm when I got my meal. The bento box came with 4 pieces of California roll, a salad, some sweet potato tempura fries, white rice, and some sort of teriyaki protein. The sauce could use a little more flavour, but overall, $12 for a food court bento box, it met my expectation.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOFaPVAy5j41Sc0sPjCBu-WRyqG5ch552NnKkro&fid=0x0:0x992886a809fc679e"],"When":"2022-2-14"},{"Name":"Vanina Araujo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVjKF--2uXxIft-QMgc9mell_JJo3aWx3WX1i7qnQ369NEYV6o9=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Not fresh at all.. the chicken was sitting in a pan full of oil and they 'warmed' it up when I placed the order. Never coming back here.. wish I could get my $ back","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOOn-aPU7_rNNxd6DnS4IHNCGwRIXTIJ2ObwwNc&fid=0x0:0x992886a809fc679e"],"When":"2023-11-1"},{"Name":"Samantha Etzel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVFig8jP_vTW9seypmhCsH4jK-TXC2kJsSsHI2g9E92j5lCQuUYDg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I won’t eat here again! about: [{"id":"service_options","name":"Service options","options":[{"name":"Takeout","enabled":true},{"name":"Dine-in","enabled":true}]},{"id":"dining_options","name":"Dining options","options":[{"name":"Lunch","enabled":true}]}]
user_reviews: [{"Name":"Jennyfer Cassar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVd4aVfS8EqavvsCB7LHNP274bCbTusCOh-WoQpYXUzWRBRXZJq=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Friendly service, great value for fresh and flavorful Vietnamese cuisine. The space has it's charm with the rickshaw and grass hut bar.  I am not a fan of the guest messages all over the walls but that's a personal preference as it seems to be a popular thing to do amongst the guests. We enjoyed the combo plate and were thrilled to have a nice variety of rice, salad, brochettes, spring roll and a cup of their flavorful wonton soup. Would recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"A Scott","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXZ0gBdn2_gLX3VjTXIj39WE6m8fhadY1Lkb4SU5mCqxWTtPPMVPg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My partner and I needed to be in the area, and wanted to find some yummy food nearby. We looked Pho Saigon up, and after reading reviews, decided this was the place. And boy, were we happy with the choice we made. We live in an area heavily populated by Vietnamese restaurants, so we tend to be a bit picky if we're eating outside our normal selection. The restaurant is very cute (I'm a pun lover, what can I say?), the staff were friendly/quick, and most importantly, the food was delicious! The salad roll with grilled chicken is something that I haven't seen in many restaurants -- and the selection of pho/bun (vermicelli bowls) were amazing! I actually finished the entire meal despite feeling full because of how yummy the food was. I highly recommend this joint and I will definitely be returning if I'm ever in the area :)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chris Lewis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWG08u6x-hUe3WXpoMiz8-xe9LcxS7W_AgUgjqqjX5cUH2ERIVcsg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great food, reasonable prices, nice staff, I recommend it!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN0CHJd_Xd9SkfnMrOnRRGoH3uPmuZiGNuDsPau\u0026fid=0x0:0x2b607db133f16d51"],"When":"2018-10-6"},{"Name":"Karl Gregg","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWBQjFv242KzRvZ9q7x8e2JdYXQd5cVQTQoKVkdrkt-aDKONvy-NA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was given a plate of the best bean sprouts I ever had. Fresh and crunchy they were the nicest unordered appetizer I've experienced. I ordered a Real Crab and seafood soup with tofu. Piping hot and based with Vermicelli noodles it was very spicy. The prawns were delicious and it all disappeared very fast. YUM!\nPHOBULOUS.  THANK YOU.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Richard J Bergeron","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXZExnbUKFKvplHQ_0M_2nTN2L_GFTHbWz1_5aOGcpxIqn_GckSKQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Very good Vietnamese food. Reasonably priced , delicious food. Generous portions . Quiet , friendly family atmosphere and friendly staff. Always has repeat locals including myself. Nothing fancy here , basic restaurant with good food. Make an effort to come here if you re tired of what you usually eat for lunch or meet some friends here.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lance Kersey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWR3WRn7HK2MQheFyDOVZykp-TWmPuOU3RYPYGWUvPDx5hFgCiG=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I got the house vermicelli dish. The minced pork taste fairly low quality and the beef wrap didn't have any flavour. The lemongrass chicken was ok, and the spring roll was decent. The veggies in the salad were properly washed so you don't get the pesticide flavour, which is a problem I have encountered at Phamtastic Pho. This place is just ok; Vietnamese restaurants in Vancouver and Burnaby are much better.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"marcel C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU5bw94tOf9becAWwqWV9qZv8zy89gYRnz4cFhD1dnLP6CvfmED=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best Pho in Tsawwassen and has tripe and tendon yummy","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOuZfR7Y7uLwDcEmTgg7U_51aZZCpTErA-cO0Ru\u0026fid=0x0:0x2b607db133f16d51"],"When":"2016-12-13"},{"Name":"Jonathan Ng","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXab-oSYaMpHMG62T1CLCS0ZbqkLpJUoMBBPFjeLBwweZanrksH=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The pho quality is pretty good. The pho broth was flavourful. The vermicelli bowl was big and the quantity of meat was great. I can't say it's the best pho I've had, but it is a great alternative in the area.","Images":null,"When":""}]

Definitely worth a visit and I'll be back again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNDVk0k0b1gHaXjp78mrwyYGBe331mfF5P7q9YJ&fid=0x0:0x36673326a66854e7"],"When":"2024-6-12"},{"Name":"JS WP","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX3ieifuGNwdoddzk3aAh9OzspcRwyjucsDzIUXZIbfufct3fWg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We have been frequenting Doon for a number of years. Their buffet has been my family favorite and has always satisfied us. Thank you and keep up the great work!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Yvonne C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWiht0ZFoJ6DOgr6bSZnnGy8rPYprmRtmKG0EWCYdy5NpcfLUEr=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Kids craving Indian and this place was 1.5km from the rink we were at.

Surprisingly really good good with good portions.  Ordered:

Garlic naan x2
Lamb biryani - huge portion
Lamb vindaloo
Butter chicken - not a ton of meat
Yellow daal - very tasty

Server checked on us constantly!

Used a groupon
White rice","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPwGDx9UcZGoW1nmKMpu1BIGBNfPCnjb631cTUi&fid=0x0:0x36673326a66854e7"],"When":"2023-10-23"},{"Name":"Mohit Kumar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLHazSQow9QCvNSX4-9qFXiQDocgoLACI1ZpsSK5ugC9IPhVg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I got chicken biryani today from them , absolutely disappointed in taste , too much food colouring, got exactly 4 pieces of chicken in it . I haven't tried the all you can eat buffet (reg $16, on Thursdays 1st person $16, 2nd person 1/2 price. No matter what you order, it is worth it.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"glynn gates","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWRLDFBx3wWalMgZBYsrJwtpNeAD8RVns-Sx-kcJiMTBGl3yyz0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Been wanting to try this place for a while now and just had their dinner buffet.   Really excellent and at $16 quite the bargain.

Butter Chicken was excellent as was the beef curry and chili fish.  I was happily surprised with the variety of dishes on offer, which was 3 proteins, a paneer and 3 vegetarian dishes plus basmatti and fried rice.  And a variety of salads and Gulab Jamun (indian donut balls)  The naan and garlic naan were fresh and hot and also excellent

The Mango Lassis we ordered ala carte were again, very good.   I'd highly recommend and will definitely be back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNiMNFDvHDo5cZuNfW4ywoAjA6wpDaW4F70z_xJ&fid=0x0:0x36673326a66854e7"],"When":"2021-9-20"},{"Name":"Tj Lamba","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWmOAhgYB7P764wij9df4_24Pk7sYzp3Pl5vCb2bpAFV3lgO5e2=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing food. Keep it up Doon Express.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPkQQUST6omFcVzs7uo6MuXOGATEzak7UvrS7F9&fid=0x0:0x36673326a66854e7"],"When":"2023-11-2"}]

[{"Name":"Edgar Ignacio","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV7oexz4qXoBKr6ujKuYxwMvlf16ckv-ovFMKFmC4nzUqeMSoelFA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The service at this establishment is notably slow, and the staff appear disinterested in their work. The floor is littered with debris and could use some care. Surprisingly, the restroom appeared unclean, despite it being early in the day. While the food and drinks were satisfactory, it is evident that this location requires significant improvements. I will try again next time and update my review.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipON0rgjA7BPzp1h9WVK_MDxg3z383Bgh7qPr1mp&fid=0x0:0x208435ea171a178c"],"When":"2024-6-9"},{"Name":"Bernie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVPXTBFQGy4UZogf6r0hGxUGZ8fvtwePPN5iicbAtQksaWtpwOP=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Tim Horton is always my go to place.  First visit to this store on my way to Ladner.  The place is spacious and with sitting place outside.  I got iced coffee and everything bagel with cream cheese. Service is fast, staffs are nice.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMEUNU4nsBt0hYPpI6UVzXL44QBm7tCgHWwZ2Nb&fid=0x0:0x208435ea171a178c"],"When":"2023-7-17"},{"Name":"kamal bajwa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL0QItB3zyrgEf1cIPkF2XMhV-6RUPrvVBmgSzoFJMLUFl98Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Usually this Tim Hortons is great I never had an issue since my last visit through the drive thru. As I was ordering my drink I changed my mind still at the speaker and cancelled the drink and the girl replied “but I’ve already made it,” I legit was like okay but I don’t want it I haven’t even finished ordering if you already made it in the 1 minute I decided to change my drink what am I supposed to do. I’ve worked fast food myself and the customer is always right but the employees at fast food restaurants don’t seem to understand that.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ryan Cloutier","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWtgjc-VpD47FnwRT-ZNc7T4kp-Y8nwKTEXIWIP8HZRpfFs6D_N=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This Tim Hortons is so slow in the morning, that can barely get my order right and the one time I order food they make it wrong. The staff need better training in efficiency and there needs to more staff working the front in the morning. If I had a choice to go to a different location I would.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"K R","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIuMeOcQiUVW9FKji21Uft1PhAKvsjSr1ifvZpWB_WKqrLtNBk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Last 3 times I've ordered a mobile order - just a bagel with cream cheese add x2 bacon
It was ALWAYS either missing both orders of bacon or half of it.

I mobile order so I don't have to wait for my food to be made since I'm always on a break at work picking up my food","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jeff Davis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL0p375pVGMCh46WGb2BpKvpjxa4WDhSPi6wIUkJut38ftcGw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"good food nice staff just two things to be aware of their decaf coffee is instant, though it is also one of the better tasting instant decafs I've had and bring your own disinfecting wipes to wipe the tables. they are either short staffed or forget to clear and clean the tables. 15 tables with 50 seats we walked in 4 tables occupied but every table was dirty. We were in there for 75 minutes and no one came to clear/clean tables and there were several 5 minute periods where no one was waiting at the counter for service. Tim Hortons has places to put your garbage and dishes when your finished clear your table when you are done your maid is probably not with you !","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Stephanie Alberastine","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVgQdq8q_eF2Vcio_EZoeRqVLLcoTuG5Ub_VNIFIwMHmlI39O4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"They messed  up our order . We  ordered a meal but they missed our black coffee and the staff were shouting at us when we went inside to follow up our black coffee. They are not  even sorry . They even laugh at us. Staff seems not trained properly to get order.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Navya Kaur","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVP_v6JNjrz7BHYgIsln05rIbtKVYoREnmCtEub4OnQl0JpTF8G=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I recently came here and well they literally have nothing available
I formerly wanted a hazelnut brew and they didn’t serve that
Thats okay right
But then i asked for slowly cooked chicken wrap and then they only had two
I mean your store is located in a much crowded establishment atleast have the proper resources. People get exhausted and then expect a good meal which we pay for!! Whats the fun if there’s nothing available at all.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"tease69666","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVfCDNnaDyUdqQO787NHuRKytnlKGA_aYQlxxQ4lU5tO3Td63xB=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"my boyfriend and I went here with a friend of ours who is a regular costumer, and...oh...my....God....this place was so...good...the food was amazing. the service was great even tho it's cash only and small its still a good place to go when you just want a home made male or sandwich and meat.cant wait to go agin.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO10SBn_yJZH5p-eXGr9PzSncFv4VC7UfyVNUJ8&fid=0x0:0xb8a3fd710275a869"],"When":"2024-12-23"},{"Name":"Louise Yeoh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKn6H1v99edwzRk8pxHxqcfGWgIZaHgZyHlx8FsGc__i8U2ig=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"While having a pedicure at Bay Nails in Tsawwassen this morning , I smelt some delicious food. After my pedicure, I found myself drawn to a deli which was full of people . I ventured in and was amazed by the menu. It has been awhile since we has schnitzel burgers , cold shrimp sandwiches, etc. The split pea soup that 2 ladies were having looked really good. So told hubby to park the car when he came to pick me up as I think we found a new place to have lunch. The 2 ladies were super friendly and welcoming when I asked if our fur baby was welcomed at their patio table.

We ordered the Shane burger which had schnitzel and corned beef , chilled shrimp sandwich and split pea soup . First bites were heavenly.  Looks like we stumbled on a hidden gem.  Pricing was reasonable and portions were huge. Will definitely be back .","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPTmkatfYiZ8PlCD7C1oMlg_gThhqscVvUROb5u&fid=0x0:0xb8a3fd710275a869"],"When":"2024-7-2"},{"Name":"Ray","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXGVd5s-06Fr3JDo-bYWWNiziS7uiGN7g2hEorOk1Vp-qtDK_-cTg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The Shepherd's Pie has no business being that good. Why is it so good?!
The atmosphere and interior is cozy and old-fashioned. The lady who serviced me was lovely and gave me warm smiles all around.
The burgers are absolutely massive and hot. Really liked the Dave Burger. They are all so good.
Definitely recommend and will come back.
Btw, there are "cash only" signs all around the walls and windows.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMhFD5c7TSEDWL26fTbFLwuBZrSS9sDHkbGPVIA&fid=0x0:0xb8a3fd710275a869"],"When":"2023-10-7"},{"Name":"Ps H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXWZH4u5uxDfJNhnL_l8W1S4uIzr1H4HDeoj_eCHzg7xFQspTGN=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best. Roast. Beef. Sandwich. EVER.
My whole family feels the same way - we just get it how it's made, no special requests. AMAZING.
Cash only, but there's an ATM at the 7-eleven a few doors down.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPEqC7wsj0cdQZZLNDIIzUixwNiB5C9ozHvUh-F&fid=0x0:0xb8a3fd710275a869"],"When":"2024-5-29"},{"Name":"Drew Meikle","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJouGVykfUCqec0xQBo-ea8IIIqdcCFU3ZRS_OZlsR60YLITw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ozzie's is a step back to a time of quality food and outstanding service, not to mention fair prices.  I never go in without feeling welcome and appreciated.  It is Tsawwassen's jewel.  Don't forget to try a few of their homemade cookies, too.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"AJ R","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLo4tIvUrcwNXdNPm8MhPpZgzsQXb-_lGpW8MEceFXJ5buZ1dI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Just went here for my first time, and I loved it! The place is run by two wonderful ladies - the customer service was fantastic and the food is delicious, filling, and very well priced. I’ll definitely be back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOOOAyIJ5zkh_foYb7nH4nM5HMlU63w2sg3hcBm&fid=0x0:0xb8a3fd710275a869"],"When":"2024-4-15"},{"Name":"Jeremy Hannaford","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVJh4gJaa4fTCJIngBRIGMrmmqMdx4ZxIh5c_eHCdtOqz7VOAFhyQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Before I ordered, three different people ordered the Steve Burger.

[{"Name":"Marco Ropke","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWkFcDdZrGOV_ZEyfdKDMOAjSOrXoSHuAfL7QJQtzfZqg2THv13=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Sunday evening, rainy day and a really pleasant surprise for dinner at Sharkeys. The Nachos were loaded, chowder was delicious, the pulled pork Mac & cheese was one of the best ever, mussels & frites awesome and the big seafood Choppino was outstanding. The food was very good, you could tell there was a real chef in the kitchen. However, best of the dinner experience was server Diana, who was just a lovely lady who provided service the way it should be. Choosing the right moments to approach our table, same time super attentive with a natural service. Kudos to the whole team at Sharkeys , well done ! We will be back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNvfZaZhTERBxzHrEaWki63ZIXnjs9SnflPnbc6&fid=0x0:0x14372c4ba9bb6c15"],"When":"2024-12-23"},{"Name":"Spoke Spurr","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU6SBXwfGoUXIMfCRHI82vggrz0MEiQ4COzIjzyCQuY_w8CfkTv=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This is a nice place but I think we came on an “off day”. Servers were very busy chatting with selves but I get it, only 6 patrons 🤷‍♂️
One star for the $17 for 5 shrimp!!
The rings were good as were the Caesar and $5 pint.
$45 for a snack seems unfair.
I’m happy the locals support it but we won’t be back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPV-X2I7ffvdaamqkNfrEEr7F3svgv_T_qiyEWU&fid=0x0:0x14372c4ba9bb6c15"],"When":"2024-7-29"},{"Name":"Raymond Campbell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXldjV3i4-BTickKCXNM1ff98zOTT1RjfPjijGIUlY6ZcOfNWAP5w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ok… if you have not been here before. Jump in your car or bike or walk here Asap. The patio is amazing. The food is spectacular. I have been here about 4 times over the last  4 years. It honestly feels like it just gets better every time. The garlic steak bites are a 10. Clam chowder is a 10. I promise you you will not be disappointed. Yes it’s that’s good. Plus the beer is ice cold ♥️","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPXs3ogNR3amJ6ZsF7dllX2180-jZMX-Qxm7CHu&fid=0x0:0x14372c4ba9bb6c15"],"When":"2024-4-18"},{"Name":"Graham Young","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJxN9FUaBPDzGoSAkZd5lDRepWEvNLzTSr9VZyeNWRs12MDuw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"As of Nov 2024, 2 for 1 Cod & Chips on Monday with 2 beverages.  Good deal and helps patronage on a normally slow day - smart!  Attentive service, super fast and batter was not too thick.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMBbzbJeGxxHZuCq2nflOPd1FlCFroAPdouLiGo&fid=0x0:0x14372c4ba9bb6c15"],"When":"2024-11-6"},{"Name":"Karen Ashcroft","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKOCMzrTEO-OdpEhLtNZWge2eQ0j9FmUbiNfT-8yyUjm011-g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Food was good. I had the Ladner burger. It was tasty but nothing special. Service was great. We ate out on the patio watching a bald eagle or two in the trees. The location was scenic.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP6fxUppglbRyjSJZtSyORtOCQ0HTTfjHCXZ1cM&fid=0x0:0x14372c4ba9bb6c15"],"When":"2024-6-9"},{"Name":"Silvia Ramirez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVa6JSptOp2BQVu9z96XMoK9p5Kyo9-2r_Gs3c5u4eE5VGwH9iuAw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love their chowder soup. Honestly, I'm not a big fan of their fish and chips, but their salmon burger is amazing.
The service is great, the staff is very polite and the place is clean and cozy.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"T-sky w","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW0uEsH9cmoXM44maq4LpVeMX01iq76aPxdjsa_7JuBIb5Y9RZO=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place has been one of my new favorites since I moved to lander. I remember only one staff member out of all them and she has the biggest and kindest heart ever when you get to know her. My partner and I just went to the place yesterday because we haven't been there in a while. I love the food for sure.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Janet Kinneard","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXUrFMNe2dnbyyDEDJe_5HyjCcWPtvwJj_e56YgNduZoVKJqZM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The service was excellent, the food was alright. Mostly I was disgusted at how the chairs stick to the floor so badly that they can’t be pushed back or brought closer to the table. There is a urine smell near the washrooms. This place is in dire need of a deep clean and a floor sander. Wooden floors shouldn’t be black with sticky filth.
I’ve been going here for decades but I think I’ll give it a pass from now on. There are cleaner places to eat in Ladner. 😟","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Shery On The Move","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVmAA3VItm5d-LzZjMzSS_FZs12aHSse1X5w-nXQqVmdbUvhBBJ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I'm a first-time customer to Nat's Coffee  House. My husband ordered caramel macchiato, and I ordered ice mocha and blueberry lemon muffin. We were so happy with our drinks and nothing to complain about.

Meanwhile, about the muffin,  I was attracted to the blueberry/lemon combination, but unfortunately, i didn't get the combination taste.
Furthermore, the muffin was not fresh (probably not baked on the same day), and the staff didn't offer to warm it up.

All staff were friendly, but the mistake was that she didn't offer to warm up my muffin. I don't mind eating muffins at normal temperatures provided if it's freshly baked, but the muffin I ate wasn't fresh.

I will definitely come again because i really like the atmosphere. The last time i came here, it was a Woods Coffee. So when i came yesterday, it reminded me of Woods Coffee because the management didn't change any indoor seating.

Next time, i will try another drink on the menu, but I'm not interested with bakeries anymore.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPBRKK8aS7njRgSXVnofgRMTCdYr4C31jX96APS&fid=0x0:0x41ce6f043a990a56"],"When":"2024-5-21"},{"Name":"Ravneet Kaur","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXGzmrD1cHYpATlUMH47NlKB0BDLL0MfGLBo2b5dzUPZNB42R9f=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I came here like a week ago and tried their chicken strips,they were really good. So i brought my husband today to have that good taste but the first order that we got were burnt chicken strips and they were so stiff that i had to give them back. The staff made new ones for us but same issue, stiff again. I dont know if its just today or what happened. We ate them anyhow and did not even feel like ordering anything more. Also, the staff today seemed not interested in serving the guests. The other day a tall lady with black hair served me and it was wonderfull.
FELT Very weird today","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sean “Seanwiches”","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVnTzFWGQfJQMbbpjucIHtu1smaGLNpsJGa5YTtcfzP5sTrd0k5=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is my go-to spot when I’m in town. The service is great, it’s got a great atmosphere if need to do a little work and you can beat sitting at the tables out back.

I haven’t tried the new flatbread, but it looks pretty good. I did try the gelato and let me tell you, it was amazing! Do yourself a favor and try the cookies and cream, maybe a double cone. 🔥","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPrOTN_Sc7_qFpSLYP57MX5J8pydsdEDJ6pqsF-&fid=0x0:0x41ce6f043a990a56"],"When":"2024-5-15"},{"Name":"Dan Lorenz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVa_eC-U0kV3zmKzI4E1osV8_z7ABPGLuq9fXQNAmdOuVhfXvuZ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place serves fantastic coffee, and bagels. It also serves as a place where I can grab Powerade and water before my gym session!!! Keep up the good work Nat’s Team!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Daljit Bains","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWdA-hMsR_2SCDC3RksfT-_GWaGnswzYErwlgBNeNz1TpmQ9tbs=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I went for the first time in drive thru.  A girl named Iliana was so amazingly wonderful.  I asked her for suggestions because it was my first time.  She told me what she really liked and she made it for me.  It was a modified white mocha with less sweetness with Irish cream and Cinnamon.  I took a sip while driving away and immediately stopped my car, backed up into drive thru, knocked on their window and told her it was the best coffee drink I have ever tasted.  I don't really write reviews, but this experience was exceptional.  I'm hooked on their coffee now.  It's sooooo good!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Bradley Dougherty","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJqgGwHhnGDE0p20s1bs7ju-N01GgzCaA_vBAarBf3FDMzl3w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"To the employee that was annoyed and grumpy that I had my SERVICE animal with me and was visually pissed off because she told me to take her outside and got mad when I told her she was a service animal, shame on you Karen.

As a local, I probably won’t be back for that reason.
Management please inform your employees that service animals are allowed and it is unacceptable to get mad at the customer for having a service animal.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"jason wong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLAr7OPM3u3i7bBkh0r7Q9kS7_8Gu_88Crv223BgydShD66TQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Good coffee.. wish there were more locations.. Great place to hang out and get some work done on my lab top..","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMdpJDiBtGutF2kMJIPhahn8ul9zT5BClQd9a8A&fid=0x0:0x41ce6f043a990a56"],"When":"2024-3-2"},{"Name":"Sally Chae","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKIrMOZBorysV9LFGtDjWGmlbuifIIYKfb6HSAS-4aTe2ZVZQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Visiting from Seattle. Dropped by on the way to the ferry terminal... what a perfect little place! Really cozy and nice atmosphere  and the staff is extra friendly. I had Chai Tea Latte and husband had hibiscus tea. We both really liked it :) I want to come back on the way back :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPY-_idUmwc8kSdeSBaMllyP4V7ueF0-v-jOtJG&fid=0x0:0x41ce6f043a990a56"],"When":"2022-10-19"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Pouyan Dehno","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUtwhkr-cJdKmoYQrxfRnXcXnvOyhOTcEYJpa6EHWO8tS2Gmx8o=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"While the onion soup was overly onion forward and the wings slightly dry, the fish and chips were exceptional crispy, perfectly cooked, and paired with an outstanding tartar sauce. The calamari was also expertly prepared and delicious. The setting was pleasant, though the service was notably slow, with long wait times detracting from the experience. Despite these drawbacks, the standout dishes make it worth a visit.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMC8DYJAitzaxT2gQXIL-xQa5_Co0TLozQ7Jmra&fid=0x0:0xbe0f7eec186d1db8"],"When":"2024-12-14"},{"Name":"Gigo Navarro","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJjpSRfgiVd7FGLteYcEIxlAuYk62vFeD6G-4X0GbzYQ52EWQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been going to this place for a while now, and I always have a great time. And last time was not the exception as my family and I had an absolutely wonderful experience. The service was outstanding, Rueburn our server was attentive, friendly and went above and beyond to ensure everything was perfect. And the food? Incredible! The clam chowder in the bread bowl was hands down the best I’ve ever had—rich, flavorful, and perfectly seasoned. The bread was fresh and crusty, soaking up the chowder beautifully. Hope this menu stays permanently as I know this is just seasonal :). Highly recommended","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMGINX7NNBNzmk4Zn1AzZvo3gU8gg8nv4GfZQIv&fid=0x0:0xbe0f7eec186d1db8"],"When":"2024-12-14"},{"Name":"Robert Polickoski","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWnWPQJMTZcKDiSfRRRxF-aXnxD9B-5Q59aHdVs2QZKiYRpc_Br=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The fish and chips was wonderful
. The tuna stack was delicious.  The sticky toffee pudding was the best we've had, including my own. But the real treat was Donna and Dominik who really made us feel welcome and set us up for our whole stay.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMwomrdOOgoPZnwDLlrymozN0SmNxuLUDch3W-Z&fid=0x0:0xbe0f7eec186d1db8"],"When":"2024-6-4"},{"Name":"Corinne Love","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUokO6T7rGH_Fihx4Mzid3i1bIJFmoWLWh3lRFVoMwTcn5nHIOOIQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Our company held the Christmas lunch here. Fantastic food, exceptional service - Raeburn was a fabulous server!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNMuy21RP2l7l7VtUn5q5MN7HAglO4rxbMQn2wl&fid=0x0:0xbe0f7eec186d1db8"],"When":"2024-12-13"},{"Name":"Jerry Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXvvBpZoMjueQB2J1i0SQDP1pCBU-HRcyxN-CW8114Ou5CuSCkJYg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went for lunch on a weekday at the Delta location. There were six of us and one couple was late due to traffic. Our server Donna was understanding and kept us refilled with our beverages until our friends arrived.
Donna took our orders promptly and was outgoing and friendly. The food arrived promptly and was hot so it did not sit in the kitchen waiting to be picked up.
The menu was varied and anyone should be able to find something they like. Food was delicious and at a good price point

We will return and hope to get Donna as our server again","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sanders Mah","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX8oSgPkwwOZHTBvIh2Qeq7JA6BBw3zBFQdgzlc1Wr9ngbPQj0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My first visit. Friendly, hospitable (and happy!) staff. Our primary server, Raeburn, was attentive, but we were gladly served by others as well. We ordered two BBQ Pitmaster Platters (summer promo), serves 4 or more. We added the tender beef brisket to one platter. The setting was clean and contemporary. Comfortable ambiance.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN8C5ltVBd51J4rJqbGES0I3flfF1JCTH2aqXFt&fid=0x0:0xbe0f7eec186d1db8"],"When":"2024-8-3"},{"Name":"Stephanie Maitland","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIO5GUSOFaBEMmzFD5ZJ8-X2bm8bdYdL-N93bamQM60AAVA_g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great food, excellent service! Our server Raeburn was awesome! Very knowledgeable of the menu and made a suggestion to try one of the feature cocktails… it was Awesome! The Holiday Brambler will not disappoint!!!! Cheers!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMjUm8NOHS9AHggklD0J4LXXnCWMU_ReH_Dv6XW&fid=0x0:0xbe0f7eec186d1db8"],"When":"2024-10-16"},{"Name":"C D","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUiCNr9lxlwWhKqCOXf2rmN6L2e7MZVP5-xL_d6Ty6v0A7OWHYo=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had the pepperoni pizza which was quite good and a Stella which is always great, only downside, it was a bit overpriced. However, the best part of the experience by far was Natalie, our server. I have never had such a professional, well mannered and lovely server at a restaurant! She had a wonderful smile, was extremely pleasant and attentive. I honestly thought she was a manager based on how she carried herself. Turns out she's only been there for a few days! This restaurant should giver her a raise! I recommend this restaurant fully and the only reason it didn't get full stars on the food was the prices being tad too high.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"EV NA","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKkrFEYUDX56vJrEozPX61XeE38WxjNbtQFPsVaCY2-cAwrUA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Simply gorgeous location on one end of the mall, with views over the parking lot and we were fortunate to arrive here in a very warm day, hence seating outside on their very comfy areas, with hardly any people around - it reminded me of one of those restaurants you find in Florida.  Well, I was in holiday mood!!!
- lovely young servers, very friendly and polite, taking our orders straight away
- very clean toilets and clean cut place altogether
- excellent food  with the chef paying attention to my requests
- not far from the ferry terminal (maybe 20min by car), if you prefer to eat in a proper restaurant, rather than in the small and many cheap cafes at the terminal","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOeOjnAIdoEVVCVYoXXUT6GPWpzYx-uVrvgq3EN&fid=0x0:0x7036a98cb704d7b9"],"When":"2024-7-8"},{"Name":"Wayne Lav","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUk880jfctdjiDn4tRAvocN5rCVUdtgArCHWFDiv2yxg-QvIz4L=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This restaurant, located just outside the mall, offers both indoor and outdoor seating with a pleasant ambiance. The menu features a wide variety of dishes, and the staff are friendly and attentive.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNvJIgJru6E_tyHr3PkzsGEQyWMUHjOspVxNx2T&fid=0x0:0x7036a98cb704d7b9"],"When":"2024-8-10"},{"Name":"James Hopkins","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI7pWUJCXAZ3TFKPOMmqiGEYyfSlYMeW4NeUBtiEZBMRXSEuQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently dined at Milestones and had a wonderful experience! The food was delicious and perfectly cooked, making every bite enjoyable. Our server, Whitney, truly went above and beyond to ensure we had a great time. She was attentive, friendly, and made excellent recommendations that enhanced our meal. Overall, it was a fantastic outing, and I can't wait to return!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kaili Hagel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV1yzsrk8SwqNNuCyYuKlRn3_9eHqDoZ4DHy3of0cmYzrn0vXPe=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Usually really enjoy eating here but had a horrible experience today. Very slow service even though there were only 4 tables in our area in the lounge. Had to keep asking for refills, my husband order a burger with no tomato's and I ordered the spicy Korean. When we got out meals my husband's burger came with a tomato and my burger was completely the wrong burger I got a beef burger with bacon instead on the chicken. When we asked the server he said he totally forgot, if he can't remember orders he should write them down.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Olivia Levesque","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUb4zZbV0YXKhHkU2F_3dwx03KNXKQqTHdsRQyeSWJ9SjDYl5kv3A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Always such good food and drinks, service is great. Still my all time favorite restaurant","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMWhB5mTOuu8Nu--rZKhOcPF7dobNAxYq5law35&fid=0x0:0x7036a98cb704d7b9"],"When":"2024-9-3"},{"Name":"WILLIAM REN","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWKRmqUVmhhErGGqKi-Bzn0et1-EnBX9lgvZO2NQ0f1pzZpZEA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This restaurant is always one of my favorite restaurants. The foods are always excellent and the service is always good. I appreciate the elegant atmosphere. I love the box seats, which are very suitable for friends to meet and chat. Todays foods were still delicious, cook well and beautiful presentation, especially the steak sandwich. Today ETHANthe serviced us, very considerate and thoughtful, and he is very handsome. I wish his service gets more compliments from customers.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNhtKfwaNue2wc2XxbSd7Aq9KvWtYR2KiJvwgGz&fid=0x0:0x7036a98cb704d7b9"],"When":"2023-4-7"},{"Name":"Carlo Thirtytwo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJbR_vlyW79qWuGGVcDHaz7U0_HyYvsOHMhgJmUWxIJEKzvVQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Really enjoyed my experience at Milestones the other evening; they've really stepped up their food game. It's been a while since I've been to Milestones so I was impressed with what they've done with the menu.

We ordered mostly handhelds, but I was enticed by the portobello chicken dish which seemed to be popular around other tables. We ended up with the Wagyu Smash Blue Burger with garlic parmesan fries, the Caprese Chicken Sandwich, and a standard veggie burger. California Spring Salad on the side was a fantastic addition as well. Quality was really impressive on the Wagyu burger, chicken sandwich was a little bland, and the veggie was above average.

Our server was super friendly, made thoughtful suggestions on the menu, and was attentive. She was great. Only qualms were the small beer selection that evening (they didn't have a few beers available) and the inability to use our gift card (which apparently ceased applicability in February). Other than that, I'd swing by this Milestone location again next time I'm in Tsawwassen Mills.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMjTKk63tf4I3Q9K0jnxecBYvkVVgUgX9O-SQEz&fid=0x0:0x7036a98cb704d7b9"],"When":"2023-7-26"},{"Name":"JB CHU","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVgWSLLs0R--vY6HThjK4A_oQpcCL09XMjbjMMjW_zVqw3j73-u=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Wonderful service and awesome food.

It's Milestone! I'd say this is one of the best franchise restaurants in the area. The quality of food was great, and the pricing was reasonable. The portion was generous, and the selections were wide.

After a long day of strolling in the mall, this might have been the best decision to end the day with a happy meal!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMAdk4CbqQh1AE0bUFaTDoTovETIp8_WKIr1s9s&fid=0x0:0x7036a98cb704d7b9"],"When":"2019-3-7"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Devon Phelan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXorWAedHbb59VsAXuR_js0R_xERF5lT44CmILYrHhE3b98PaXr=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great classic pub dining and drinks. Happy Hour was a great value, and the chips + dip with a pitcher of beer wasn't crazy expensive.

Excuse the half-eaten food and drink. Absolutely delightful and refreshing coming straight out of the kitchen.

The room ended up getting completely filled shortly after Happy Hour, so be sure to go in and grab a seat before the storm arrives.

The staff are very polite, kind, and make you feel welcome even if you are sweaty from biking!

I was able to bike here from Tsawwassen and was pleased to hear that they had a bike rack available AND visible from inside of the pub.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP88uDKJH14Zit44mY8BnWMTKMIcF2ZC_lnuriI&fid=0x0:0xac558cb712c2f718"],"When":"2024-11-6"},{"Name":"Lister Chen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVWbNvO55wOzkDRxCcJ-fMoCcdWyut5hlx-H_zUreRnwso9_V0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Enjoyed shared beef dip sandwich and grilled chicken avocado salad with wife. Attentive server Kaya filled our water without asking. Nice view of river","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP_BF3u_oFkquzClJQ5jUVASFlhl5RLakL4T1OM&fid=0x0:0xac558cb712c2f718"],"When":"2024-8-27"},{"Name":"R B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXvwlyjB4u92gNs2XkVMCtEEv1bbhznwa-XyALuorQtBg64Yw0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Great place, warmer months you can sit outside with a great view and peaceful view.
Food was very good, I had the pulled pork sandwich. Very good, we tried the pub area but want to come back to the dining room area. Great bar area also !
Plenty of room, good seating areas. Comfy chairs, those little things make a difference 👍","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOtHpbeuPf9EcOsFnLVXnEfiKZVkRBkdaYtp59a&fid=0x0:0xac558cb712c2f718"],"When":"2024-7-29"},{"Name":"Kanako Sakurada","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKYybgPjG_d3LYq66Ui47Ocd_2PMrfkKaju5V_L0IyVTR19lQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Fantastic location by the river! We enjoyed the patio seating with nice view! Good service and food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMzMvLeDxFMBh5o4qzVIOwOIC69SYGi1nbdHbhR&fid=0x0:0xac558cb712c2f718"],"When":"2024-7-1"},{"Name":"Leona Zheng","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXmB6XMzxTi6G9GEmyD0MJjB6nkqYOP7GVBTMUakDrRUolumXkH=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We thought we booked a dine-out Vancouver lunch here but quickly realised that River House only joined Dine Out for the dinner. But, with this view and a very nice brunch menu there's no regrets!
The server and the host were very friendly and accommodating, and knowledgeable!
The food: We ordered Pork Skillet Benedict and crab shrimp bacon Benedict. Both were tasty, full of flavours. I particularly want to recommend the Pork Skillet Benedict, crispy, rich, soft, gooey, the right textures of everything. Hands down. Will come back again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPubVkEn1dnJ6_wrSs3eq02ZayEU18zlM3xFIv0&fid=0x0:0xac558cb712c2f718"],"When":"2024-1-20"},{"Name":"Megan Lennstrom","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUCSf5LnFVz8T-B1pDG3eAlTscSGC5k2LLxD6Fh9oGTIKiBWAaRqQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Nice patio, good view. Fast service. The spiked strawberry lemonade was refreshing, I didn't find it too sweet, but someone who is more sensitive to sweet drinks probably will think it's very sweet. The Cajun burger was juicy, and I loved the crunch of the pickle and lettuce.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPnjXsRK4m5U711hEf68WbIkpLEt917zmq592LI&fid=0x0:0xac558cb712c2f718"],"When":"2023-8-22"},{"Name":"Scott Gue","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJWeS1I23-ZSSrp-hQHJIqnUKAZH-wxHH03ODf79qlSTiO14Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My girlfriend has a gluten allergy so I had to inquire about the menu. Danielle was super accommodating and an excellent example of what customer service should be.

I've eaten there three times and the service and food has always been awesome.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Debbie H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ7pWLCBcdrOZz-aP0miN89E6nSOdYsj46m0wJ4iC_PJpkqgA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First visit to the RiverHouse and I was impressed.  We sat on the pub side outside which was gorgeous and not too hot.  Our server she was excellent. 3 guests had brunch eggs Benny, omelette,and eggs and bacon
Everyone said it was very good. I chose the fish & chips which were one one best I have had and chose the curly fries. We live in Vancouver and it was definitely worth the drive.
Highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Dan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVWzXiyy8Y-jGojJLZYothXYqV-jJhV_uOxt9dttxKjLzDS8zKdsg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The service was impeccable, with the staff being attentive and accommodating throughout my visit. It's clear that the team takes pride in delivering a top-notch dining experience. The location within the golf course added an extra layer of relaxation and enjoyment, making it an ideal spot to unwind after a round of golf.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMh1yJ2CKTMo3Ec0P2h-OMm5hWax5Qt8R0X9PUj&fid=0x0:0x43e3d449c10dc3d7"],"When":"2023-8-28"},{"Name":"Kieran Purewal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLpsPXqRQa5lSQQbUcJ-pLRyGzdXE2MzyreRO2yhH26kI4Ucg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a fantastic experience at the restaurant located within Delta Golf Course. It's a wonderful locally owned establishment that offers a delightful selection of drinks. The staff was attentive and friendly, creating a welcoming atmosphere. Whether you're a golf enthusiast or simply looking for a cozy place to unwind, this restaurant is definitely worth a visit!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNmsr7r7gwWdslZFp0Ml69dLhpjPztzxkyswill&fid=0x0:0x43e3d449c10dc3d7"],"When":"2023-8-15"},{"Name":"Taylor Bedwell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXXZWLJ3RcudeRgXIVBblH3jVecf-tsQTZwINuAN24YjEHWWjEz=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great atmosphere, customer service is top notch always making sure the customers are looked after. Great spot to have a burger and beer on the patio during a round. The happy hour appetizers are arguably the best in town at a great price.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNPN-WqVt0xCf2DxjqzjVC-5zAfrXMmrNbXX46c&fid=0x0:0x43e3d449c10dc3d7"],"When":"2023-9-7"},{"Name":"Steven Kumar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX-x7cQwEtj11Axf55kjZunlEnP5kAzpOHZ1osDVDUecbGF-xg2=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had the pleasure of dining at the Delta Golf Course Restaurant and was truly impressed by the overall experience. The atmosphere was incredibly relaxing, creating the perfect setting for a memorable meal. The serene surroundings of the golf course added to the ambiance, making it an ideal spot for a leisurely meal.

The standout feature of my visit was undoubtedly the food. The menu boasted a diverse selection of dishes, each prepared to perfection. The flavors were exquisite, showcasing the culinary expertise of the chefs. From the appetizers to the desserts, every bite was a delightful journey of taste and texture.

Equally remarkable was the service I received during my time at the restaurant. The staff was attentive, friendly, and knowledgeable. They went above and beyond to ensure that every need was met and that the dining experience was nothing short of exceptional. Their genuine warmth and professionalism truly enhanced the overall enjoyment of the meal.

In summary, the Delta Golf Course Restaurant is a hidden gem that excels in creating a relaxing atmosphere, serving mouthwatering food, and providing top-notch service. It's the kind of place where you can unwind, savor delectable dishes, and feel truly taken care of. If you're seeking a culinary haven that combines tranquility and culinary excellence, this restaurant is a must-visit.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jordan C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJjM9Rrddd4BGlei5U4rYSx9cI_mVXDYx5cDGL7il0O1EvDrA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Delta Palms Bar & Grill is the go-to spot for awesome pub grub. Their burger is great– super juicy and packed with flavor. It's the perfect place to kick back before or after hitting the golf course, and the staff is super friendly. Plus, their beer and cocktails are on point. So, whether you're teeing off or just craving some top-notch pub food, it’s a great spot.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tristan D'Cunha","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWpHaH20-kKiUCiDkLg1FgbTbBAskciaolD0CPhXnwoWIhieFY2uA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Awesome post golf experience! Hannah was great with attending to our order following our round of golf. The burger was excellent and the masala fries were a hit!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Romeo Balicaco","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLfjBOPXAvFUxN4q7ocjmN5iMLbqn3L8WfucIjuEgLomiD6qA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great restaurant not only after a round of golf but any occasion.
The staff are very efficient and very nice to their clients like me and my group of golfers.
I would recommend this restaurant to family and friends.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dale Cadeau","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXPzMToz-IZYTaQpOAH5GjhcO03MVs-CamC4QgHe3uhoYsYPJ5bEQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Surrey/Delta’s hidden gem.
Well rounded menu with unbelievable prices. All day happy hour and great service to boot! Breakfast burrito is massive, tastes great and healthy with the added beans. Quesadilla is also great. Took leftovers home both times so great value. Another time I did take out dinner: Lobster cakes, pasta and some Indian pakora- all great too. Make the trip down highway 10 to check this place out.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Candice Wice","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWKhVfKbOHPuvQhM32VgWC0bkonWnNHiqMEQATDOE5E9txn09E=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This was the most disgusting pizza I’ve ever had.
The pizza was soaked with who knows what, crust was dry and overcooked, no sauce, and where is my bacon? I tried to call the store to rectify the issue, only for them to pass off my complaint to door dash who in turn decided I only deserved an $11 refund, even though the pizza was $45 after everything said and done.
DO NOT ORDER HERE, this is the most disgusting pizza in Tsawwassen, not to mention the terrible customer service for the uneducated manager that just repeated the same rehearsed lines over and over again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipODjZAGws01x_c6K99dUGAZqEsnXw33L5tBrf0M&fid=0x0:0xf1e66614ebe774e1"],"When":"2024-8-7"},{"Name":"feras Jundi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU-M3P9Al5xMES3GCCOZq1Se8RaOGv7I7wtEvR229PcL9MZebM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Arjun was amazing!
Panago is definitely the best spot for pizza. Arjun should be the manager one day
Showed my son how to make a pizza!
A life time customer was made by Arjun! 😍","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNHGJGqxZAGCgWh6eesMqIYcgEkFyKubFwzcKvN&fid=0x0:0xf1e66614ebe774e1"],"When":"2022-10-20"},{"Name":"Maria M.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWDRG-yUxmCRTeMbgMR7M_AtJoVP10dGVk-ujVbXfA_LDZYf_QKOQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Yummy. I have try all pizzas around. PANAGO tastes the best. My kid likes the chiken bites with cucumber and garlic cesar dip.❤","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO_hwlzxXosAKZgXpPfBqfGPetnRg_h4VeUDPIO&fid=0x0:0xf1e66614ebe774e1"],"When":"2021-4-30"},{"Name":"Derek V","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWRFoyHN3CFgRDZUccMDKFlr3Y5ff3IemN9Fd1NwIkY2UQD5jcbsQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"We had a taste for pizza Friday night and decided to give our local Panago a try because I used to love their Chicken club pizza. First I'd like to give top marks for the person who took our order, she was very pleasant to deal with. The pizza however was very disappointing. The pizza was lacking in both sauce and tomatoes which when done properly makes this pizza delicious. Some pieces didn't have any tomato at all.
Sad that trying to skimp on a couple of toppings will cost this location any of our future business.
There are a lot of other choices in the area.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Matt Wood","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX7XWx2MRzHt81gm3hRVPXTJJv5-0JmskWSRNNdLpXkD47IIqek=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Tasty pizzas, good service, reasonable prices. Can’t ask for much more than that!

We specifically choose Panago because of their community outreach and support. Other commercial pizza chains do nothing to improve the community.

Thanks local Panago owner and staff!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Amy S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIloBNU8BqrMXEu-c0fToNelRGoBG-Xq5zGAs5nrI9YjYWKmQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Long overdue review as this is by far the best Panago location I have eaten at . The staff is all very friendly - owner & employees;  I am always greeted with pleasant smiles even before I walk in through the door. What’s even more amazing is that my order is always custom and not once have they let me down. 10/10 every time . It’s ready within 15 minutes or less , tastes amazing and is always hot ! It is because of this amazing service and consistency that I’m eating here pretty much every other day now  and I will continue to do so until I get fed up of pizza haha  :)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Richard Glasner","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVlFSX_UUx6rW0lix6i7dkX9lVOSyBZB-F5xxqlskw_ZqxWVSPR=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Just placed an order for over $50.00 it was online for pickup. Waiting outside for 20 minutes then went to the  door its locked not a sole around inside. So I called 1800 and they had to call the shop still in progress it said 2 guys wander in from out back. Finally I was put to customer Care now its 20 minutes late still not making the 2 pizzas.
And I was only offered $10.00 credit for the next order.  Needless to say I just canceled the order.  The tsawwassen location is the worst for mistake orders .","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Henry Luan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJV3o9ovKjC50gaewyyVx644uNJMEvGGzEfe11dsssYdY0hBw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I really like the taco pizza with chicken. The combination of the sauces, meat and ending with crunchy cabbage was a nice touch. The glazed pepperoni was rather mediocre and practically had no difference compared to a regular pepperoni. The fried chicken was total wack as the baked pickles made the pizza almost inedible and the cabbage did nothing. Feels like panagos pizza design is very hit and miss but their smoky cilantro sauce is to die for","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Tony Li","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXf8VP49ZjSvgG0JnhT1tc6Tv6OzLL9YEi_yNvwH1rW_K8-7VE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I'm a huge fan of the Grinch so when I heard the Grinch meal was here, I hurried down to get an adult happy meal and a child happy meal. Was I ever disappointed with my Grinch meal! First of, the cashier didn't even know I could choose a Big Mac instead of chicken mcnuggets. She had to turn around to see the big screen advertising the Grinch meal. Ok, staff wasn't aware of the new promo. When I got the food, it wasn't in a Grinch box. I was disappointed. The Grinch meal wasn't cheap to begin with. At $16.89, you get a Big Mac combo meal with a pair of socks. When you add it up, its not a deal. You're paying for every item in it including the socks. You can't buy the socks directly but you can buy the toy only that comes with the child's happy meal.

I noted they had a stack of Grinch boxes behind the cashier and yet they did not package my Grinch meal in it. Why tempt me and charge premium?

The child happy meal was in a regular box with no Grinch advertising at all. Another disappointment. We grabbed our meals and found the napkin dispenser was empty. First time, first McDonald's that supplies were depleted.  When we got home, we noticed we had the shaker bag and dill pickle package but no fries. Blasting mad, I jumped back into my car, drove back to McDonald's and complained. There was no apology. The cashier grabbed some fries and gave it to me. I told her that the rest of my food was now cold and all she did was shrugged her shoulders. Poor service. Poor attitude. Not returning here, Grinch or not.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPqSbE2_7IdKJiTTbrnPDKW8P_Xz1uqlZ4iJGhe&fid=0x0:0xde2bdf2901b0b7"],"When":"2024-12-4"},{"Name":"OVO6","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWyXOvdNyUNZpAWB2xPkw0KDrh0AySj0B-o9Y20rJaGYmyKt43h=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Simrin (somehow a manager) & her staff were completely rude & disrespectful rushing us to take our order saying we were wasting their time. Also none of the kitchen staff were using gloves or using any sanitary precautions. Never leave negative reviews but just had to share this horrible experience.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kamikaze Digital","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXIHs1Q_XuT0SrensVjICNSGvWLexmem0hVqJ-mE5kC2M8cboje=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Food was prepared well but they forgot items and for some reason McDonald's refuses to give napkins anymore. You'd think if I order food for 2 adults and a kid you'd give us a couple napkins, especially now that we pay a billion dollar corporation 25cents for a paper bag.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shinn Inagaki","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIpF1gPQ6II9FjL7HoACMWpgmrVznxivHZdomkvTJ9wRIkWHw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"No wonder this McDonald’s is so empty.
I had 3 issues with my visit.
1. It started with no receipt paper on self-order computer.
2. Employees are so busy making drink lid and straw to make a drum kit at the cashier and not helping me.  Then he forgot to serve my food and had it sit 5 min  until manager realized that I have been standing for a while.
3. When I ate, my chicken wrap had minimal lettuce and also over cooked chicken.(see the pictures)

Manager had to keep telling employees what to do.😭😭😭
She needs to fire these lazy ones that she needs to tell what to do.

Definitely I am not coming back to this location.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMhPwN8ioh0reMTA-ppwTNWAmdR49nKwkUsdUQ&fid=0x0:0xde2bdf2901b0b7"],"When":"2023-6-18"},{"Name":"jaja twins","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVioOpD7ZxV4B5M1Whof5_vCJ04Ro3TCSWprMtJR6UnYqpe4GoA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I have been going to this McDonald's about three times a week and the quality of customer service I received today was atrocious. I left my job for my lunch break and when I ordered my usual meal I realized that my wallet was left in the school where I work. After doing the lineup (because I couldn't back up anymore I told the customer service representative that I had found some cash and asked if she could help me, she agreed but then her manager told me that there was a lineup and I needed to go lineup again. At this point the manager made it obvious that she did not care about me as a customer and that other people were more important than me. I offered to move out of the to the special drive through area but she did not care. I cannot count how many times I have waited on orders that were not ready but today that I needed great customer service; I received a horrible experience that has made me rethink my choice of restaurant","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Pascal G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLwhl3cvs4iFJlsGpEEvBQuO6yFuS3rvDKX-L2PKKxPZriqnOEy=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"One of the worst McDonald’s experiences I’ve had. The wraps were very poorly filled, and the service (takeout) was extremely bad. We ordered takeout, but they served everything on a tray. When we asked for a bag, they made us pay extra (not much, but still). The staff member was unpleasant. Paying $35 for 3 people to eat poorly and get bad service? Definitely the last time.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"qian lu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVPpRjLjrDmBemH5k5i2JLQYffNLqpFDAtf-jeL9OvgR-AhUQs=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I have never encountered such a rude manager. After repeatedly confirming whether there was sauce for the McNuggets when picking up my order, I received a definite “yes.” However, when I got home and opened the bag, there wasn’t a single packet of sauce inside. Even the toy for the kids’ meal was missing.

When I went back to ask for the sauce, they told me it was a minor issue and said, “Just take the sauce and leave.” They even blamed me, saying, “It’s your own responsibility. Why didn’t you check before leaving?” Furthermore, they claimed that only those who pay their salaries are entitled to reason with them. The service attitude was the worst I’ve ever seen.

This isn’t the first time something like this has happened. On many previous occasions, the number of McNuggets in my order was less than it should have been.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Harmandeep Singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV8wV6X6c4fwv5bbjWD3rfJqQAVaYG9vuWHWz6XrJ5UMa91y9eTUw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I was excited, especially since the staff were polite and welcoming. However, my experience quickly took a turn for the worse. As I was waiting for my order, I noticed something absolutely unacceptable in the kitchen. The sandwich makers and other kitchen staff were preparing food, including burgers, with their bare hands. Not only that, but they were also touching various other surfaces and items in between handling the food.
It was both unhygienic and disturbing to watch. I couldn’t eat my meal comfortably after seeing that and ended up throwing it away. I am extremely disappointed and disgusted by the lack of proper food safety practices here. I won’t be returning, and I would advise others to think twice before dining here unless they address these serious hygiene concerns.","Images":null,"When":""}]
