[{"Name":"Donna Izabelle Abes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUmbe8krcBH6aWNPHx97hR5NlSV-iP3Rn3nrjA5v7O3c1gJw9M=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Came in (first time) for dinner last night. Place is quaint and homey. Floors were a little slippery though, not sure if it's really that way. Anyway, the lone server was very soft-spoken and nice and kindly explained the menu for kids as we had our toddler with us. The lighting was a bit dimmer than I liked but they had these little oil tea lights on the table but server did not light it up because of our toddler which we appreciated.

The food took a while even though we were the only ones there. But it made up for the wait as the food was really good. The flavours were amazing. We had the roast lamb, chicken skaras, and kalamari which were perfect. The portions were huge and we still had one container full of leftover after dinner was over.

We used to go to this now-closed restaurant near our place and the flavours were a hit or miss as sometimes it's too salty or too bland. Greek Fellas had all the flavours right.

We really enjoyed our dinner last night and I hope this place gets more foot traffic because it's that good!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMsAyAFsLdPl7gHye0VANspc1qwXv2TgnYOBuik&fid=0x0:0x92cf93aaf202eba5"],"When":"2024-10-23"},{"Name":"Tom McDougall","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV0J48kC1hZM1V1aRsvHOZVDophlDmEISwqhKMFe94oVeHk06c2=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐

Greek Fellas in Delta is a hidden gem! This small, family-run restaurant offers an amazing dining experience with its authentic Greek cuisine. The food is absolutely delicious, with each dish bursting with fresh flavors and traditional spices. The home-style atmosphere makes you feel like you're dining with family, and the warm, welcoming service only adds to the charm. If you’re looking for a cozy spot with outstanding food and genuine hospitality, Greek Fellas is a must-visit. Highly recommended!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPiVfm1T1AeQA9FFM3RYY3Cp9snp7BYHp0rQU18&fid=0x0:0x92cf93aaf202eba5"],"When":"2024-8-12"},{"Name":"Jonathan Chung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXNgq2ykZbLe2d_u0ExFniyHMucdZBry6o2uBaXifHbvE2ISiM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Possibly the best Greek place I've tried in the lower mainland. My wife and I each had different lamb entrees, which come from New Zealand. There was a saltiness to the meat, but it only enhanced the flavour rather than another it. The potatoes were infused with some sort of lemony zest, while topped with some sort of mustard that wasn't overpowering, still allowing for the potato to be enjoyed, rather than covering it up completely. And the rice wasn't a filler, but rather something I couldn't bear to miss a single grain, devouring the entire platter. Oh yeah, did I mention the salad? The sour and the freshness of the olive oil was so refreshing, balancing the flavours from the savoury bits.

The portions were sizeable. Thank goodness I forgot to eat lunch that day. The service was limited, as it's a small mom and pop type of shop. But the place was full on a Tuesday night, along with take out in what looked like a 2 person operation. And even then, the food didn't take long to come out.

So thoroughly impressed by this hidden gem in Delta! The pictures are nice, but they don't do justice to what is happening on your tongue.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPBABiOogJ_3L37sEkPCAIipuQzLK5-YWnikFiq&fid=0x0:0x92cf93aaf202eba5"],"When":"2024-6-26"},{"Name":"Paulina Pedrero Miranda","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXoiOld2vaC2Dv18bWNi8EDRiykD7MSCRsU3RK7RESh6xQghXxb=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We arrived and enjoy the happy hour deals, the place is comfortable and the staff was very polite, the calamari was delicious, the spanakopita was a bit oily, as main we ordered a beef souvlaki, the portion was great!, the salad was a bit bland, but the potato and the rice was good, the food in general was ok.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPJ4NtMGzEWyb9KkVu1gMOcKar36IxvcEGI7S8V&fid=0x0:0x92cf93aaf202eba5"],"When":"2024-10-14"},{"Name":"Leslie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUMMk25HwUFhyQjoG0usKDYaMIy_Vp018yNzS4uqMl_zDyr1No=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolute hidden gem! happy hour before 6pm. calamari, keftedes, spanakopita, ekmek and pita breads were all tasty. but what knocked my socks off was THE TZATZIKI!! So refreshing and light, I could just eat it alone. Took home all the leftover tzatziki.
Cant wait to go back and try their other dishes.
The restaurants seats less than 25ppl with 1 server, so expect a slower pace or go early.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPRQjpoUFpB_LjDy45PTHLzA9_6KIZODU940xco&fid=0x0:0x92cf93aaf202eba5"],"When":"2024-11-12"},{"Name":"Wild Wanderlust Photography","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXYPQeHy2fRvptt6V1NtTq0t9CdOFiP_rQd_Emm8iYNczU9hCDSwA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Food was worth the wait. It didn't take forever but long enough to know that it's made well. Lamb shoulder was delicious. The pasta was also huge and delicious. My moms bday today and they brought out a dessert with a. Candle and it was also.... DELICIOUS LOL. Small place. All tables had 4 chairs, no booths. Each table had a little paraffin candle which was nice.. ambiance is important in restaurants, esp during dinner.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMtOUAAIeEcxYZdtm-xncw3z9OLAfLknSDGYgnn&fid=0x0:0x92cf93aaf202eba5"],"When":"2024-11-20"},{"Name":"Rod McKenzie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLk7i0CDRtHjxSLOFIM1MJnNG4AA6zjDm6JcBm9lJVvSCWIsA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Since a small family-owned Greek restaurant. Nothing fancy.
We were a table of five sitting for dinner at 6:00.
Two couples each shared an appetizer. One couple had escargot the other calamari. The escargot was nothing special but the calamari was great.
All the dinners came with a lovely Greek salad. I had the lamb chops. There were four of them, a substantial portion and quite tasty. Two of us had the roast lamb which was lovely. One had beef souvlaki and the other the shrimp souvlaki. Everything was wonderful. And we shared a dessert which was described by our waiter as a Greek tiramisu which was also very good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO7uu0ratzl5H9ZkOnGAHoRBa0fD-7CHKrrsxEA&fid=0x0:0x92cf93aaf202eba5"],"When":"2024-8-15"},{"Name":"Jeff Hohlbein","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIPlNcDi8i8PzH35XOvMQTzasIafq7V7xqYqm0KIPq1H59B8A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The place is small but it kinda adds. Very homey authentic place with amazing food and friendly service. A hidden little gem that I highly recommend","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMW_7DA-Q3yT-Prcx3GcXhW1qSl47CQglENsIs2&fid=0x0:0x92cf93aaf202eba5"],"When":"2024-8-11"}]

If I have time to kill at the ferry, I ALWAYS go here for the salad buffet and a bubble tea 👌🏼","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ava Clay","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUmnDmzZ-JfuTGiP61xGM8OFi06UC408vkWsVGnZpNqfZaGcD8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Huge complaint against iSalad food kiosk. Serving sub-standard, low quality food that caused me to really worry if I would be sick in 8 hours. Chicken Bacon Caesar salad wrap: I actually opened it up because I was concerned at the overall flavour, strange texture and rock hard bits: old dark chicken leg meat, cubes of another tasteless chicken substance, bacon bits hard as rocks, dressing tasted off like it could be turned. Only the veggies seemed fresh. As an islander looking for non-processed food during regular trips across, I was so shocked at how bad this was that I took it apart to actually see what was inside and then threw it away it was so disgusting. They should not be allowed to serve OLD BAD FOOD inside their wraps. A year ago, this same wrap was delicious... WHAT HAPPENED?","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dawn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKjYh42XFubLgC0A48wVPqytlWh9BdXHyTv1FzlLw8wxtrm9A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent vegetarian wrap, freshly made, crunchy and lots of filling. $12 is very reasonable price for the product. I do not recommend it.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sarah Baitis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVnWRenExFTMBLnlCMtR1xY7M0JxuZGMSd3YBIn9faeCk-AeX4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I ordered a spicy chicken wrap and it was terrible. Super strange combo of flavours... I think the spicy sauce covered up every other flavour which is strategic considering the chicken was grey! Yuck!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Michael Eaton","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV24BG5IoOkpdTq9pGnBiwzTZjdbOBX1LQnZjiDoz_NRRNNyeE=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I always get the veggie soup, it's so good. The broth is delicioussss.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"G GOSS","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVWgKvIty2XBi10CBRMKJHtYufxIeckvYOftfr0yAilMlWseG1sGA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"One of the potentially healthier options, but I can no longer recommend it.

The wraps and salad bar used to be good, but higher priced. Typical of vendors at airports etc.

Service has always been borderline poor. It's now worse than that.

Smoothies are thin now and wraps are smaller, with less filling. Between that and the poor service, I'm going to pass from now on.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews: [{"Name":"Telemark1107","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJUpVy0BwbUBm1hRVoKm9qdT6KU-oGzmNFiKfvYbAQdr6ujhA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Have had meals from this restaurant many times over the years.  Service has never been 5 star and food is typically 3 star but this time was a new low 1 star all the way around.  Ordered a 2 dish combo on noodles.  Portion of noodles appeared to be fine but then watched as the server picked through the broccoli, piece by piece and green beans the same - no scooping.  Opened the box as was about to pay to have a look and maybe 5 springs of broccoli and 10- 2\" green beans, barely covering the noodles.  I complained about how small the proportions were.  They wouldn't do anything about it so walked away as not worth the $13. No plans to eat there again, will eat ferry food instead.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kyrstie Nesplak","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWPTVE1rXZNkbf10_Ki1hdT1n5UVcmmjL81CY97dUTpp6wve8iJ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"hair in food, and service is pure hate 🤣🙉 food is always, \"acceptable\"","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP6I8qnof4yzmECrPYfIZensSjoRp5cdTVSw8Gi\u0026fid=0x0:0xe305600b54a814fa"],"When":"2024-12-22"},{"Name":"Joey Berezanski","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXOPJevacCQOMcpP_OO2JYMps2lAWumv8LiRYnWJhisFZl-sOws_A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I just had lunch here. The guy serving me was obviously hating his life. He was very blunt and looked angry the entire time. I bought a 3 item meal for just under $15.00 and he put a very small portion of chow mein and 3 very small portions of the items I ordered. The vegetables looked great behind the counter but his little scoop he gave me was just cabbage. He avoided the good stuff. The lemon chicken didn’t taste of lemon at all and was very hard and crunchy. The lady that took payment was in a better mood. I showed her my tiny meal and said that the portion size is small and doesn’t reflect the price. She said oh and clearly didn’t care. The lady in front of me got a 2 item and had a very small portion as well. I wouldn’t be surprised if I get food poisoning. If this is how they run the front of their business, imagine how they run the back! I hope the dude behind the counter finds some happiness in his life because he’s nothing short of a miserable, rude little man. Cheap cheap cheap!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kenny A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIszkS3SPMCAMG_Zt7q84-znT660uc0lWm6BjOs10PChRby8w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I should have checked the reviews on this place first.\nDishonest service. Old lady tipped herself 15% on the machine and made it face towards her so I wouldnt see. I asked for the receipt which she was hesitant to give. I found she tipped herself and called her out for it. Don't eat here. Food isn't good either but the worst part is the dishonesty","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMX4wfw-5S_6oP17qGQOjMWCSOKNzh8y_tmn8AC\u0026fid=0x0:0xe305600b54a814fa"],"When":"2024-2-22"},{"Name":"Freddy Pina","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVuY9Tfv2Iq9Tx3FO-J6XJSShBI910xU413L6-PRxhXfnJaeU9Z=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The food so so, but the service is awful. The people there are rude and they don’t even care. It seems that they know that they can do whatever they want. Customers are so passive and see no one complaining about their behavior. Since this is the only “real” food in that terminal, the choices to eat at Tsawwassen Ferry terminal are very limited.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dale H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUrzIxelfLvOsb2q0wLQBfux-LrSREuhcYcy4WgP0MX3zMo7nugKg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The over priced sandwiches had too much cheap bread and not enough ingredients. The guy making my sandwich didn’t ask if I wanted anything added, he just threw meat on a bun and put it in the toaster. I had to ask for mustard and some lettuce, I wanted more but he was obviously angry. Never again. The pics are false advertising.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"justin pellen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIKXcL-rjQLKN29KpEOKJ8YfZ_U17JVqZ7y35NYd4F5fswaEA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Not sure why everyone is bashing this small business. $13 for a bowl of noodles and barbecue pork when you're in a pinch is not bad. It's sad that people don't realize what kind of impact they might have on someone's livelihood. It's 2024, were you expecting a giant platter? 🤷🏼‍♂️","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Donald Mertton","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL0QGbb-9U7FNK3w26aZcKtdpGnhLTbkP0q8CZ8xyPgZlRYRQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Well don't go if your hungry the two choice box was embarrassing  4 pieces of lemon chicken ? I asked if that was all and she seemed stunned I would ask about it lol, maybe bc ferries should lower there rent so customers can get a fair meal for 13 bucks ( what a cash grab )","Images":null,"When":""}]

This is my 3rd time in 3 years trying to give this place another chance. Everytime I am majorly disappointed.

They need to add a panini press and more condiments- if it's a sandwich place. They also had an issue adding hot sauce to my sandwich, offering to give it to me on the side to add. user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Andrew Melville","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWPE8YK95HJDhY7cASAaoJAorc8OeKtZyg_wZ5oMnnQktmUO1SP1A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Ahoy, wanderers of the sea and seekers of the divine crust! Pizza Daddy here, casting tales of the Ali Baba Pizza stand at the Tsawwassen ferry terminal, where each slice is a legend woven from the Arabian Nights.

Here, amidst the bustling throng of travellers, lies a treasure as coveted as any found in the caves of wonder. Each pizza, a caravan of flavor, travels far beyond the ordinary, offering solace to the hungry soul with its bountiful, belly-filling delight. As the Quran enlightens, "And He it is Who feeds but is not fed." (Quran 6:14), Ali Baba Pizza nourishes us, mirroring the generosity of the heavens.

Yet, amid this feast for the senses, the crowd swells like the tide, bustling and vibrant. And like our wise old friend who once faltered atop Coit Tower, the sheer delight of these flavors might just sweep your feet from under you!

Four stars to Ali Baba Pizza, a beacon of culinary mastery in the Tsawwassen ferry's ocean of motion. Here, every pie tells a tale as rich as Scheherazade’s, and every bite is a passage through the gates of flavor paradise. Sail in, fellow mariners, and let your taste buds embark on a voyage of discovery!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPEaOlYe9A1p6hsraHj2Yuu0Iv3ZEJ63WxghIYf&fid=0x0:0xc8dde9ead8481237"],"When":"2024-6-11"},{"Name":"Byron Sheardown","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXNqxb0c_42J36yKVRNJaOWQgsDJlMUDs94sxLG_b3F9RGXTQ_D=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Good size of slices and fair toppings for a locked in market (ferry terminal/airport/stadium you don’t have much choice!)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP5k7G81dVOd6BsDjDky4Muj0ujgEMGpIqLyPU7&fid=0x0:0xc8dde9ead8481237"],"When":"2024-11-26"},{"Name":"Grace Tsang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV77q3lDBN8pyeGIjZJpsbYkDymBOHRI6bxP5NZw6IAoley5AER=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"10 minutes wait time for a freshly made whole pizza. Crispy yet soft crust with ingredients loaded on top. Ingredients were a tad on the salty side, but it was overall delicious. Would return if craving pizza while waiting for the ferry sailing again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPmLiHEbeNGhH8Rrynt9TMYJNt_kiymQkpCQhxR&fid=0x0:0xc8dde9ead8481237"],"When":"2023-6-9"},{"Name":"Jens Frederiksen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVLsrhdCHPY2OrPKIjsdNbpAjF_nXtXu6vGlOOj2CS-je8U2rc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Taste like cold cardboard for 8 bucks a slice. Do your stomach a favor, don't eat here","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMv_LDKHXUDSwPncD-tBOCmES_KHjHXq4znkOzb&fid=0x0:0xc8dde9ead8481237"],"When":"2024-8-2"},{"Name":"FlowChange 54tyr","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocICGPrTjhTgGbTQcSAnbtb1J0YUgbAn6naDFjb4mBlhRlbVjA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Gross cheap tomato sauce probably made from green tomato and vines. I also thought you guys had multigrain, why do you never sell multigrain slices, I don't want to eat 'enriched' bleached flour.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ester Toews","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK0lvfEbti3pFbGKEKUkNLb5_iyrWcQnExXZNYtJ6DBEvlJYn4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Pizza is pretty good, and the slices are large.

Service was okay. On the slow side and not especially friendly.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Noah","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWMIWXtiOkjovWGo1mbbKniEe1eklCMvUnlzMTTz6YbMYlYj_TO=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"This place was so good idk why it has such a low rating. Sure the prices are a bit high but the slices are huge and for ferry food this is amazing. Pepperoni with parmesan added on top and it was delicious. Can’t wait to come back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPtpMmi-woNPg_TtYnMP9ZmPEDxrDLDsip9mmKk&fid=0x0:0xc8dde9ead8481237"],"When":"2022-7-11"},{"Name":"momentoftransition","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXJigyNdUAXTr6SzaLVHnR9mEaUlZkHmTRVXTHXPau6viFta5K8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Zero stars. They had one kind of pizza only and for 6 f-_$#&ing dollars it is half the size of an Ali Baba slice in town. This is a  joke. I want my money back. Never eat here. Totally taking advantage of the captive crowd at the terminal these vultures leave you dissapointed. Other reviews of satisfaction make me wonder if the guys I dealt with were actually ripping the place off by selling twice as much pizza and pocketing cash sales. If you're trying to decide between eating on the ferry or eating here, just eat on the ferry. The best choice in this complex would be surely Starbucks at the end....I wish I could find it sooner.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Scott Osselton","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKjonqtCZN6XwoFo8pronPjlTmfjuoCUhY_FzwegLVDFdKsHw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I'd rather go hungry then eat here again. Save your money you'll be better off hungry.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMLJS0sBTxeXzVR2GpeHVbO_JWm9IZxwAbnIncf&fid=0x0:0x7ec8345a36365c41"],"When":"2023-8-14"},{"Name":"Dez Robin Mudryk","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV_cPTWAlnaqJ5O1sMeAmtFRpKiRe3sj-ufWHOeANNNwNqamRPG3Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The absolute grossest beef dip I’ve ever had the unfortune of eating. 🤢. Skip at all costs.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sharen Fraser","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUBfu-TQambQsa34adUgRSfH7DJgBxECc8sqPj3Lh_tuq_2c4Ly=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Absolutely inedible hard as a rock old,and I mean ancient old cooked many days or weeks ago and then microwaved. Gross food way overpriced and you get not to see the food inside the container before they hit you with the huge bill and the person stands over you watching as you have the tip screen before you can pay.   Expensive and total garbage I would not feed an animal.  Seriously I had no idea that chicken wings could be that hardened!!   You would need an ice pik to eat these.  What a total waste of money. [{"Name":"Tania Arora","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWTM3cK0Tza8sQADEGxXloyJRDpBZYkaTTxxRbwY3aPKKl7pqbW=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Omg the most amazing food I have had in Surrey so far…. Very unique creations. Staff is very nice & professional - service is as quick as it can be. On the weekends they have a 2 hour dine in limit - there might be a wait so make sure to check if should get a reservations.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMQA5W2pqC0Id9ErFZ4-o2bcWL6Rau9SyLCGC2w&fid=0x0:0xa3ae60553b040e35"],"When":"2024-8-19"},{"Name":"Videesh G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXhwNGfq3r6NW4xapwGlC05lcGIwtehlR0cWbDA5XMl2N8bqM_i=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The ambience of the restaurant was inviting, and the customer service was exceptional. We tried two appetizers: the butter naan with garlic, along with keema and paneer curry. While the naans were decent, they didn't quite stand out. However, the curry was flavorful and had a nice level of spice. Overall, it was a pleasant dining experience, but there's room for improvement in the bread.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMNUGFezLrCmQv6Gi50WqlVN3Nl_fJM3iv3EKgZ&fid=0x0:0xa3ae60553b040e35"],"When":"2024-11-4"},{"Name":"Tav Dhillon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXrRGAiccrCPtDxnsbL4iLIukwM_7N5NEOQxwb3h34PPRTBKpXk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Visited for breakfast and brunch for the first time, but unfortunately, it fell short. The açai bowl received was far from what was marketed. The granola was just raw oats, and the toppings were noticeably different. The base was incredibly runny, more like a smoothie. Overall, disappointing and not recommended.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPBG2TuhSuwDkgQpogi1dVkwXpKig2NaiEa11rr&fid=0x0:0xa3ae60553b040e35"],"When":"2024-12-8"},{"Name":"Gaganpreet Singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWS6CRVqFqr0pKuY5BtNvJvQAzqSCn7OZw-ir7-rgecN3Nga8w8hQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A Great Dinner at Tasty Indian Bistro

We just had dinner at Tasty Indian Bistro, and it was such a lovely experience that I had to share. From the moment we stepped inside, we were welcomed by a cozy, inviting atmosphere. But what really made our evening special was the incredible service we received from our server, Jas.

Jas was simply wonderful. She greeted us with the kind of smile that makes you feel right at home. Even though she was taking care of several tables and handling all sorts of requests, she never missed a beat. It was clear she’s incredibly hardworking, yet she made it all look effortless.

One thing that really stood out was how much Jas knew about the menu. She didn’t just take our order; she helped us choose, offering suggestions that perfectly matched what we were in the mood for. Whether it was deciding on the best appetizers, entrées, or the perfect drink, Jas had great recommendations for everything. Her knowledge of the cocktails, whiskey, and bourbon options was impressive, and her suggestions made our meal even more enjoyable.

And speaking of the food—it was fantastic. Tasty Indian Bistro really lives up to its name. Every dish was packed with flavor and beautifully presented. You could tell the chefs put a lot of care into each plate, and it made the whole experience even better.

But honestly, it was Jas who made the night memorable. She was so friendly and attentive, making us feel like we were her top priority, even though we knew she had plenty of other tables to look after. It’s rare to find someone who’s not only great at their job but does it with such genuine warmth.

All in all, our dinner at Tasty Indian Bistro was a great experience. The food was delicious, and Jas’s outstanding service made the evening special. If you’re looking for a place with amazing food and even better service, Tasty Indian Bistro should definitely be on your list.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOCQeqGjvYvdLALA1ahCXbrag7z4jLhNunAsJn6&fid=0x0:0xa3ae60553b040e35"],"When":"2024-8-31"},{"Name":"sreedevi radhakrishnan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVbgXwP26_52lKSsrN3V_BQpBNEYeYagTgwp1HSsvPT4knUcusU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely phenomenal food! We’ve been here twice now and they’ve consistently served us delicious authentic punjabi food. They definitely pay attention to every little detail. Service is great!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM8OlZj-KypKYAkcWfH8VODpPLjW9CcyhoYU_xX&fid=0x0:0xa3ae60553b040e35"],"When":"2024-10-8"},{"Name":"Divyanshu Chaubisa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLwycq9sqfcIYjmWvmrsgjiWg5fGw-galqSoUY7mlNY_XKBvTI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"No doubt it’s one the best Indian restaurant in Vancouver. The ambiance is amazing and soothing vibe overall. Somehow I felt the food quality and taste was not at par with other good restaurants we have in the city. They have ample of free parking to accommodate the guests, the waiting time for table may vary on the rush but it’s reasonable.
I went with my family last weekend and had a good time. We tried mini burger sliders, kulcha chhola, malai koft (main course) with garlic naans and aloo paratha.
The food taste was average, the service was pretty good and quick.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNX3AGv8EK7cc4l1cv0zhJc_UByz6zC6S-e1wlK&fid=0x0:0xa3ae60553b040e35"],"When":"2024-9-6"},{"Name":"Amarjeet Kaur","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIwuqo1tqouoVJlCdwYJ3Yrr0cn0IrKRgbjXwXxz6jc5GaxxI1k=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently had the pleasure of dining at Tasty Indian Bistro, and it was an exceptional experience from start to finish. The atmosphere was warm and inviting, with elegant decor and just the right level of ambient noise to make for a comfortable and enjoyable evening.

The girl named Puniya(sorry if I pronounced the name wrong) was incredibly attentive, friendly, and knowledgeable about the menu. They went out of their way to make recommendations and ensure that everything was to our liking. The service was prompt but never rushed, which allowed us to fully enjoy each course. Overall, is a fantastic place to enjoy a memorable dining experience, whether for a special occasion or a casual night out. I will definitely be returning and highly recommend it to anyone looking for great food and excellent service!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nikhil Patil","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU_kaPBj58IwRUgFf0stQWxv34s-JNKYUd5fFrMxzXTGf9TuOkHcA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"'Tasty Indian Bistro' consistently exceeds my expectations. The food quality and taste, ambiance, and service remain outstanding. Both the veg and non-veg thali were truly delicious. In the veg thali, the palak paneer stood out as our favorite, while the lamb curry in the non-veg thali was cooked to perfection with incredible flavors and complex notes. We concluded our meal with the staff-recommended dessert, the 'Cardamom Dream Bar.' It was the perfect ending to a wonderful meal. We will definitely be returning to this place many more times.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNz3w5AfmI9rcR-mTAOiziJ2JvKR0WRnG1pVme7&fid=0x0:0xa3ae60553b040e35"],"When":"2024-10-1"}]

Highly recommend this place for great food and excellent service!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOYywyb06I0PysWllDcyu52RP8VSRz6IeEBElCP\u0026fid=0x0:0x598db8e999254468"],"When":"2024-6-26"},{"Name":"runny maan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWs3LSkqGf3mzpywlSo_WPoreouYvBSuhH3FUJFD98VTVT5LupO=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Delight Street Eats offers a decent selection of street food options in a casual setting. While the food is tasty and reasonably priced, the overall dining experience leaves something to be desired. The menu lacks variety, and the portion sizes are on the smaller side for the price. user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Monique","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUQcAgOL4v2U_VirmCaadFrb2IzIMWiSeW-tX_pA5B7GcJn2vN8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of my favourite places in the Surrey/Delta border to order sushi rolls from!

I absolutely love their special roll menu. It is definitely on the pricier side, considering how much you get for what you pay. But with that said, the rolls are delicious and full of flavour.

I highly recommend the Fantastic Roll and Amazing roll if you like things like aburi and oshi and want that garlic umami flavour.

The crispy roll and yam crunch roll were great options, but the Crispy Roll was a lot better flavour wise if you were debating between the two crispy options.

Their lunch set (available before 3PM) is a fantastic value if you do order around that time!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMr33KzXn3OIRHo9rm1iYf1Z8wk92kFHH-hAAe-&fid=0x0:0xb2264364bab7e267"],"When":"2024-9-7"},{"Name":"DLH","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKNxoVJChN19TlxEyh2PqXcySZWcsWGp-pw0aGewSStRgeU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Update: Sept. 9, 2024
Even though we are within walking distance we don’t go for japanese often enough so it’s good to know that the quality is still A1.
We made a tatami room reservation and our Special Dinner ($27) and Akari Dinner ($28) Combinations were excellent.
All staff are Japanese here.

Friendly staff in this cosy neighbourhood restaurant, tables and tatami rooms.
Booking on-line is easy.
Vaccine passport/photo ID checked.

Menu is large so we ordered far too much. Everything was delicious and nicely presented.
Highly recommend the Awesome Roll- crunchy bits and popcorn shrimp, suits the name.
Tea refilled a few times.

Over the 20+ years, we’ve eaten in and gotten take-out many times and quality is consistent.

Located in a strip mall (Scott/72nd) with ample parking.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOgZuRKeheynAs5d0XcRJpPNo6WWJjrsuTqN2A&fid=0x0:0xb2264364bab7e267"],"When":"2021-12-26"},{"Name":"Ben Moreno","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXbXIQA5QNY2om_rvFeJhZDcAcErydWjpf8dpxFoZ8JJurbSZgE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Delicious sushi,  friendly and fast servers,  bento boxes are great choices,  reasonable prices,  recommended.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOc9Vb9U5wjij4Jhw7N7xvZnVNwq5wxxouvmziF&fid=0x0:0xb2264364bab7e267"],"When":"2024-9-7"},{"Name":"Ueli Hartmann","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU7Fd4w8RA0hoxJvIo4cVNTkMMMVZflfjrD9cusB0rnaVp3t4T_ug=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing Sushi, quality was extremely good, I can only recommend this place! Good service and always going around with tea!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMK03wIwT7jW1iU1c00XbfeUk8sD7uoxNzDk1Mr&fid=0x0:0xb2264364bab7e267"],"When":"2024-11-16"},{"Name":"sng1002001","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLTfKdGFrJyL8jc4znhIMXimj1BkuJ1S_SEthxZmoeo2Gf8Rg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Long time sushi establishment across from Scottsdale Centre. Good variety of sushi, sashimi, special rolls, and lunch/dinner boxes. The seafood ingredients used are fresh. Really like the various rolls (e.g. Fantastic roll) - good size and good blend of different fish. Fast food service. Apparently they have a sake sampler during the Christmas season - 3 shots for $7.50!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPGOjEx74RpX5u3_OCN8pF6GRj0t6RYRAe-MBa5&fid=0x0:0xb2264364bab7e267"],"When":"2023-12-26"},{"Name":"Ethelyn David","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXK4VlApGUESMpUmHtkuNaKascPX1JKNkMvVUC-VoUsoOtTyUJ6IA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been a faithful client since they opened. Always felt welcome and the items I ordered never disappointed (whether eat in or take-out).  Good size portions very tasty, great presentation, fresh sushi and sashimi, and the service is always great. Pleasure doing business with you Julian and staff!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM1JnJFCZ-GzpnpFSpITvTLhxRci-gSRmGDvWwg&fid=0x0:0xb2264364bab7e267"],"When":"2024-3-25"},{"Name":"D SAM","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVAPZJhKwbwofRMAxzu-Q9mFomEMmhsUcyi8-_CMghvFMl0UXMbEw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"This place is busy. Reasonably priced. Customer service was good but not excellent. Hard to call waiter’s attention. We had to get up and no one checks in on us. The food was fresh except for the stir fry veggies and black rice. The veggies was overdone and the rice was dry and obviously not freshly cooked. Otherwise the chicken and tofu teriyaki and the prawn tempura were perfectly cooked. It’s a good hang out place for family and friends.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPhaXqQpnUmguN9ivS9aS5wDQ2dSDqNMa7Kfiqg&fid=0x0:0xb2264364bab7e267"],"When":"2023-6-1"},{"Name":"film by lily","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUUSiIn37gm0M4cUD38_C7-DlPW8VoGO46izDz__BjLERifsXLSAw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Food was bomb! Our first time here and we will definitely come back:) If you’re going with a group of friends definitely do the deluxe boat!
Must-try items: Akari House Salad, Tempura, Agadashi Tofu, Crispy Roll.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMZFTU289eU_YZsBaJTLO7sGc5pIlaxMSftDcQf&fid=0x0:0xb2264364bab7e267"],"When":"2023-12-29"}]

[{"Name":"Munro Stuff","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWj0Wcuk6ox5dfAeJ4fAaMbhX_F-nzzt3p5oc_f0hBd0NpbGSM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"New to the area and have been trying samosas at local places, including some well-known/highly rated. The veggie samosa at Delta Indian was WAY better than any others we've tried - excellent flavours, crispy pastry, not greasy. I didn't like the chicken samosa as much, though my partner did. We're definitely coming back to try more of their food. Friendly service as well.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOhaUBuXspLVUpupXMmA3G1wBTtExkmYjCvQ5gH&fid=0x0:0x5306a4347950c7f7"],"When":"2024-11-5"},{"Name":"TG","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjULhqU_yLPB5ZAPCEsV5nl0xiZrNbTJqxBrKjH-leYiaFJ3899K=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Stopped here for lunch and ordered from the Lunch Specials. We had the Amritsari Kulcha Plate and Non Veggie Combo. The stuffed bread and Naan were greasy. The butter chicken and chickpeas were tasty and good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOyyEgHohbJbLYVD1nAeccGx_zvQhArkJGIuNwg&fid=0x0:0x5306a4347950c7f7"],"When":"2024-12-15"},{"Name":"Chia Ching Wang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVwe2GGT3rdI6ALckS6UIqajkjqJBCpxGDpeE1RlxKE9CKicjp7fA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I ordered Butter Chicken (reg) take-out today. I think the food taste is good, but for $16.49 (before tax), the amount of meat is considered little.

But I still be willing to try more dishes when I am in the area.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN_29uTi-LyBP0UlIqnJD3d1moh5ieOyjgViWcq&fid=0x0:0x5306a4347950c7f7"],"When":"2024-10-10"},{"Name":"Wilhelmina Bateman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLy2k0C7Bj9ygMsmApx4UCd2IxlQ2pmcYnMHZAXXFlSNy3_Nw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Delta Indian Cuisine is a superb eating experience. The ingredients are fresh with perfectly blended spices. The Mango Chicken is velvet and the Shahi Paneer perfection!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM9nHoRMiUYL5Tu2qjjgDIT7NHvG9Hm4iowUTrS&fid=0x0:0x5306a4347950c7f7"],"When":"2024-7-28"},{"Name":"Aphelia R","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUiujnnp-r6a54qfOz_Nt8RloZYO2XV2hm9eIG0_31zoxJ1jlrG=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ordered fish pakora and the eggplant curry for take out, and both dishes were really tasty! The pakora still has a nice crunch to it even though I was delayed 15-20 mins to pick it up. Price is fair, would order again and try other dishes as well**There were more pakoras than the picture shows;they were being eaten on the drive home👍🏼**","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOUAc88ztHANTBTifOXse6udeHgBzLP1XxfO9ky&fid=0x0:0x5306a4347950c7f7"],"When":"2024-8-13"},{"Name":"Angel K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXki7lSOZ8eGdsXwy5XDEH06JQyFv66wnh1_34j8OAQdytKSQk-=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We got the lunch special which included pop.
Delicious butter chicken. Just enough portion for a good price.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP0CdO_ON6VqUUPUw4JIdEuTNj582iENxr8TYkK&fid=0x0:0x5306a4347950c7f7"],"When":"2024-10-17"},{"Name":"rajat wadhwa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKV4aA2M-diDjHp_F6a1ME3IszmBqop0JwpuwNYQjGytAbwqA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"5-Star Review:

This was my fourth time visiting this restaurant, and as always, the food was absolutely delicious and amazing! Their Manchurian is an absolute must-try—one of the best I’ve ever had. The Dal Makhani and Karahi Paneer are equally outstanding, packed with flavor and cooked to perfection.
Every visit here has been a wonderful experience. The quality of the food and the consistency of flavors never disappoint. Highly recommend this place to anyone looking for a memorable dining experience!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Victoria","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJAO4yPpx0p9iLW4iLWQ3P4gHSOyfD1COujQXpjOtVn931Fdw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"At first when I opened this was already very disappointing barely any sauce.. then took a bite and it was so dried out it was awful. Very disappointed. Butter chicken always good but the wings were absolutely AWFUL!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOnnRlCXKV7H7af36RY3rCc-28k1vEznFIl_8on&fid=0x0:0x5306a4347950c7f7"],"When":"2024-7-3"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Kylie Gayon Woo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWbxaF6A7WGi_ORpIehjp6sKn8x_LA2CUlDHfin8e218U-8eh2Iqg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of the best Thai restaurants I’ve been! Everything was great. We ordered Pork jowl, papaya salad, pad kra pao muu, and mango sticky rice. Highly recommend the papaya salad and pork jowl. They go perfectly together. Cute interior and clean.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOO2gnHrpUXbNEZPE23YYUEPV7-L0DLHCHgU8EN&fid=0x0:0xa1ccf70607323eb4"],"When":"2024-7-20"},{"Name":"Sandra Leung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVxzPjHNR60FtVdbK8IRtw9xCOLCbXchw0PqhcTgltEFJNNYSgQFA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Stumbled into this place after playing golf nearby and saw all the positive reviews.  They have a great lunch combo for $23 which includes a drink (I chose Thai iced tea) and appetizer (opted for the spring roll) and a main dish.  This is a great value for a lunch set and I left stuffed and satisfied.  I chose the hat Yai fried chicken and the bowl was huge with very generous portions of perfectly fried chicken.  Will definitely come back and try the rest of the menu. Also thoroughly enjoyed the 90s vibe of the place.  The decor was very cute and loved how the bill came inside an old cassette tape case.  Extra touches that just added to the overall dining experience","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM5zCZxmSZFkQaFprrp_gderVdLgkWKBV--DG8u&fid=0x0:0xa1ccf70607323eb4"],"When":"2024-7-12"},{"Name":"Jasleen Kaur","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJq_mX4JcS2qCxDJUdxLM5cEoBdw7wYfyUdfHLGfdunsmqsnw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The best Thai food that I have ever had in a long time. The service is quick and efficient. The flavour profile of each dish was unique and amazing.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNCyS1VldO8DrVeiEX4h84cKCBRvKpsvSDt4FIS&fid=0x0:0xa1ccf70607323eb4"],"When":"2024-8-5"},{"Name":"Jamie L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWIsaaODpzZi62wV-93lE__3OFGYxafaFgdJgxMDBfyIfS_ESBX0w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best Thai I've had in lower mainland.
We had papaya salad, pork jowl, pad krow pao muu, and finished off with mango sticky rice.
Pork jowl is a must must try, the meat was so tender and flavorful, with two sauces that went so well together. I wrapped the meat with green papaya salad amd it was out of this world.
Must try out this place if you like Thai food.
We will def. Come back to try their other menus.
They even had the sinus-clearing thing in the bathroom! Authentic.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNemDpU_njCp4pjkr3kp5g1_dlbDpancqfxIujl&fid=0x0:0xa1ccf70607323eb4"],"When":"2024-7-21"},{"Name":"Pauline","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWJGkluLFawzRkcvB0xy93FJ2AGT8gSexVqXi8tpT0shbwpkvB8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Craving Thai flavors in a cozy atmosphere? Their dishes are bursting with authentic Thai tastes, and the servers are super friendly, sharing their personal favorites to help you decide. It's like a little slice of Thailand right in our neighborhood.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNMpH6a8SynKVwK_m5JRNgWejXNsW_-D9x_K3Od&fid=0x0:0xa1ccf70607323eb4"],"When":"2024-2-22"},{"Name":"Sieu Ngo (SomethingN)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKIolnpeHK_Fih9cjGEHkA4wfLWBN6-uwLZ0o_InC0i9vNg8A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Was recommended by a friend to try out Soi Ram for the first time and it's absolutely amazing!  The restaurant was super busy towards the end of our meal and I can understand why.  So glad there's an authentic Thai restaurant  near our home.  My family and I loved pretty much everything we ordered.  We had the Soi Ram Fries and Muu Ping with sticky rice to start.  Followed by Prawn Pad Thai and Red Curry with Chicken and for dessert, Mango Sticky Rice.  Definitely coming back soon.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPXH8x56ssYAXs3gW9ZoYj9bE9XOe1eJErfmOJi&fid=0x0:0xa1ccf70607323eb4"],"When":"2024-5-13"},{"Name":"Winnie Chen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXWeJPpw7ILy-eSHYtnntg0W05T0QO_JdebWvdeaLSSnFbNMBo=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My family and I visited the restaurant 3 times in February! 4 - 9 people on different visits. We loved the setting, the food, the value and the service.
We particularly loved the fried chicken, garlic fries and chicken pad Thai!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM5z3CYjuKrzXjeri4sInkLby7UBsnlG2FYyKKn&fid=0x0:0xa1ccf70607323eb4"],"When":"2024-2-25"},{"Name":"Steven Huhn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUjPgKgZCO5PZiQnT0cs9yON3NEoowbu1SmDyHWquv1i9Z5rrCk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My co-worker brought me to his son-in-laws restaurant where we met Brian and his wife and they are amazing. They started this with a childhood dream and the dream is amazing. The food is exceptional and like nothing I have found since my trip to Thailand. Cool vibes and great atmosphere. And authentic ideas that make your culinary experience next to none. This place would out do any place in Vancouver bar none. I highly recommend eating here.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Vanshik","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU4kf7IV3L7GzOeWeSCwC0K2Ccms7H0IiFf_Oy1HASgYToRA-W0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I recently visited here for my friend's birthday, and overall, it was a pleasant experience. The food was delicious, and our server was polite and attentive, making our dining experience enjoyable.

However, we encountered an issue when it came time to pay the bill. There was a scanner on our table that mentioned a 10% discount if we posted a story on Instagram. We followed the instructions and posted the story, but when we went to the billing counter, we were told that the offer was outdated and no longer valid. This was quite disappointing and misleading, especially since the scanner was still on the table.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPoShKbE3yP_pzlxKPGUAaG1wBZ-5RE-Ebe_5r3&fid=0x0:0x8d64d8eea4db2059"],"When":"2024-8-3"},{"Name":"Abhilasha More","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWWGt7LPO5T8zSIMQfEqYAtmyFggn7yhYxqzKStzn2UkrBCRkn2Dw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I was so tempted to visit this place after seeing their instagram post. So recently visited their Surrey location. Taste and ambience were not very appealing. Washrooms need maintenance and regular cleaning. Few of the items from their post were not available at time. Chicken lollipop is totally different from the original recipe. Doesn’t taste good with barbecue sauce. No issues with the parking. Plenty of parking available as part of the strip mall. Looking forward to trying food at their Langley location.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPXEo0Npc_kJFgXvGrhc8TfSvrIEOpwrBgLSCD4&fid=0x0:0x8d64d8eea4db2059"],"When":"2024-8-29"},{"Name":"Devineah Prasad","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXX1DFa9bRk6bvv1_M-orvwe0-273w8OFGry_kkVxXgLnOAtjdI1w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"It was my first time at this restaurant with my work friends we had a good time here. The food was pretty good. The service was kinda slow at the time we came in because there were not a lot of people at that time. The atmosphere was pretty nice, clean and stylish. I would give this place 3.5 stars out of five.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPH0R9JtbH-6mzK6NkBFfmdwNOy6qXfBtd0HXao&fid=0x0:0x8d64d8eea4db2059"],"When":"2024-5-27"},{"Name":"Jasmeet Panesar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUMcW_c7YsWe00hzXLDJ2iEEuUE-CmlYgwh53vkobZL3QO3bow=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The perfect Indian restaurant to visit . The food is filled with flavours . I really enjoyed the malai chicken tikka and cream chicken . The service and ambience is top notch. Their Christmas decoration   Is so beautiful .","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMaKGhCKrhrtjFfwDzEaAfbmHfzkBIn5NtF2W-K&fid=0x0:0x8d64d8eea4db2059"],"When":"2024-11-26"},{"Name":"Kamal J","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVPtrJUF5Ih34UhFvAmR5C5WZDqD3Oo-SV1XzaS7cVv1WiGar8f=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The speciality cocktails were beautiful and delicious! The appys and Shahi paneer we had were also very yummy!! We will def be back to try more of their menu!!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO3feD57vepIyBC5MayTFuSRxWFs5IHE3eoEGGf&fid=0x0:0x8d64d8eea4db2059"],"When":"2024-9-7"},{"Name":"Sarah Kaigon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLjjEwjY98ZEuTDXtUHTSbj-wCBC7_WjPiokJYrjyW8CLDt0Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The first time I tried the food I had impressive packaging/bags with logos. I loved the chicken pakora which had 2 mint chutney containers as it was crispy fried chicken pieces that tasted amazing. I did get what appeared to be a black cardamom seed in my curry which was bitter & ruined that portion of my meal, however, the naan were flavorful & fresh. The chicken pakora was so memorable that I ordered it again within a week but was disappointed when I opened the box. It was breaded chicken breast chopped into pieces (potentially leftovers being re-worked into pakora??) & although the breading was flavorful the chicken was dry with only 1 container of mint cilantro chutney. Maybe different chefs so hopefully the next time I take a chance it will be better.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNUnSX3ReUN-1O6Y0nRXENBT4Q1QfgoabDTrcAV&fid=0x0:0x8d64d8eea4db2059"],"When":"2024-11-12"},{"Name":"Nadeem Zia.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWMvuVKaJ5RspKjafdw7NuycDlSlwvLOTMgiMvYKB8ZcmZ9sQ7d7w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of the best Dasi Live Grill restaurants.🙂 It was our first time here, but we loved the delicious food, friendly service and lovly ambience. We got few veg order and all are testy and fresh.
Dikshah took our order, and she was friendly and helpful. Thanks","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOYuUY4LTKY7q4FrjkNjzUGSwbsp81D44GkIfDY&fid=0x0:0x8d64d8eea4db2059"],"When":"2024-6-10"},{"Name":"Sandeep Patel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWUPXpjfuhMT06CDlElzdABigOc3yyD8mJ_731K4OtRygYmbVPS=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The quality of the food was exceptional, with flavors that delighted the palate. [{"Name":"nadine Horwood","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX444VqGhqsb13DWSE8cS2NTZfh0UetAK47_g5--7ZIkaW0Awfu2Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Salt and Steak is an absolute gem! From the moment we walked in, we were greeted with friendly, attentive, and personable service that made us feel genuinely valued as customers. The attention to detail was remarkable, from the perfectly timed check-ins to the thoughtful recommendations.

The food was nothing short of exceptional. Each dish was a masterpiece, perfectly seasoned to tempt the palate without overwhelming it. The portion sizes were just right—generous enough to leave you satisfied, but not overly indulgent. Every bite was a testament to the chef’s expertise and passion for flavor.

The atmosphere struck the perfect balance between cozy, classy, and casual, making it an ideal spot for both a relaxed dinner and a special occasion. It’s clear that every aspect of this restaurant, from the ambiance to the menu, has been designed with the customer experience in mind.

I highly recommend Salt and Steak to anyone looking for a dining experience that combines outstanding service, delicious food, and a welcoming environment. This place is a true standout!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOfBrT-Ysex42YZ36PGFv526MR-CkSJcYaoHvIp&fid=0x0:0x4f9729eea2d6fdd3"],"When":"2024-12-21"},{"Name":"Zahid Hossain","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIryPjidW1ZBvazYBWd-8cwUlTBR_aj1lknM1ct4ZVsHcg5WQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My wife and I recently dined at Salt & Steak Restaurant and had a very good experience. We had the rib-eye steak, which was perfectly cooked and paired with sides of mushrooms, mashed potatoes, and asparagus. Our server, Shahrukh, provided attentive and friendly service. We were very impressed with both the quality of the food and the excellent service. Highly recommended!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOHYyXt27Z7HTn0IpVW0UxZErFOMpFHrZn2xR2U&fid=0x0:0x4f9729eea2d6fdd3"],"When":"2024-12-23"},{"Name":"Aamir Bajwa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVFZcT4ZtqNrAjIj78GQfx5nBrWP0ezsiibA2jOCDaMj9tV6ovN=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best Halal Dining place for memorable occasions. user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Anjana Ramesh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX_u2BnNG3bLDugh5sSEw9Wh8vzwOrNIoCcKHn7L3I4N1E2ifrPEg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Incredible place with a fantastic atmosphere! The aesthetics are on point, creating a perfect vibe for a relaxing visit. Hands down, the best chai I've had — it’s absolutely worth traveling for, and they even offer a sugarless option, which is great. We also enjoyed the masala fries and the cheese chutney sandwich, both of which were delicious.

There’s plenty of seating, and the variety of food options is impressive. The masala chai was especially outstanding — very Desi. The washrooms were also clean and well-maintained, which is always a plus.

If you're in the area, this place is a must-visit. Totally worth it!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOLPaCeBUKXZhOOE95Hjo6pLsujz0pGjTmI7zEW&fid=0x0:0x33e9859f9737cf25"],"When":"2024-12-4"},{"Name":"Dr. Naresh.R. Thumati","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXZe9i5l3lcphUrpMV7UIgJLbGmYTbI6xZPxyGLcsocFMCumCPI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Its been long time I wanted to visit Chaiwala since their entry into Canada. Today, I have had this chance to taste Chaiwala at Nordel for a casual business meeting. What a perfect place to hangout with friends,
Family and even for business meeting. Great ambience, service and food. It took me back to my back home days to see those Indian softdrinks, biscuits, and snacks. You can have Limca, fanta, Parley cookies and other snacks. Perfect desi feel.

We ordered Coffe, chai, Samosa cones and Bombay sandwitch. I must admit, I haven't found such a good Indian coffee in Surrey so far. Its exactly how we make coffee at back home. Luved it. Also meeting partners said the chai is awesome. Bombay sandwich is typical desi style how they make it in India on road side trucks. Good taste. Samosa are also good but I would say it could have been done better. But not disappointed. So awesome food. They have got many other items to taste but it was my business meeting and could not explore their full menu. Definitely a good place to hangout with friends and family for a tea/coffe and samosa, especially on a Rainy day in Vancouver. They also have special desi style frappuccinos .. must be good choice on a hot  sunny day. thank you Chaiwala for bringing this home experience to us in Surrey. keep growing and we want to see you like another Tim hortons or starbucks. Goodluck.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOYwC-K6X0oE0sGxorjy_mho7HdP_IK4rpiK5ww&fid=0x0:0x33e9859f9737cf25"],"When":"2024-8-1"},{"Name":"Aditi Bhavsar-Vaidya","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXJfnrP4b6L_aruXJcdyMiWuTJNssQeB-jV5H_Q-V35MXID4oJu=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Good place to have a quick snack. Food portion is very small. If you are too hungry you might end up ordering 2 3 items!
Food is tasty! We tried Samosa cone, bun omelette, Malai boti naan, chicken tikka naan, breakfast meal, Falooda and chaai ofcourse!
The beans in breakfast meal had too much cinnamon in it so don't quite like the taste. Samosa cone was a hit for us!
Overall good place to hang out with family and friends.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNM-Yt5KLgPDcQ8s7GqiE3dyENduwpypnFKFWWR&fid=0x0:0x33e9859f9737cf25"],"When":"2024-7-23"},{"Name":"Ghazal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWUxPjakfUDfUlOphLX0NHrhY3j03bOfl1WB2qtK88VIEBoxSUc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very nice cafe with creative drinks and street food options. It was our first time here and we ordered a cold drink and pani puri. We really like both. They also brought us samples of their hot drinks and we liked the karak chai as well.
Overall good food and great service!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMfnsfL2Nm3WOQdmooBqx3IgXytNFUdxXLGXMhY&fid=0x0:0x33e9859f9737cf25"],"When":"2024-6-19"},{"Name":"Rub Nawaz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWVLuJJiE7dcIUD2Pb1gMI1AFYespjwRqrT-Gi7aOWncXuojQlYdw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently visited Chaiiwala at their Nordel location while visitng Surry and had an absolutely fantastic experience! The food was incredibly tasty and authentic, with a wide variety of options to choose from. But what really made my visit stand out was the exceptional customer service - the staff were friendly, attentive, and made sure I felt welcome throughout my meal.

To top it all off, the music playing in the background was perfect - it added to the cozy and vibrant atmosphere of the restaurant without being too overpowering.

Overall, I would highly recommend Chaiiwala to anyone looking for delicious food and a great dining experience. I can't wait to go back and try more of their menu items!"","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPwu93zLl2k-p5YXvBXflCSL-nFsRAUPjkTPRzl&fid=0x0:0x33e9859f9737cf25"],"When":"2024-8-4"},{"Name":"Zaheen Brayan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVOOSuX6lFg8v7bPiDI_8nRyGbv6FQ4t_15QV-2mkB5F6R9lUcRUQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Edit: Chicken in chicken tikka tasted stale. However, I’m not reducing the ratings as it never happened before. Please check and make sure that it doesnt happen.

Best chai in Surrey (or maybe in whole Vancouver!)
May be a bit difficult to find a space to dine in as they have limited seats.
Usually very busy in the weekends. Especially in the night.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMYQrb6GZKEbA04tgV0ZPgtdg52bG-Nor7IaOXQ&fid=0x0:0x33e9859f9737cf25"],"When":"2024-8-21"},{"Name":"salman lalani","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKzRjgMCbiCUsN80HctnqUaAn_unicELZ_9XdRGNU3d8EKl4w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had great dine in experience at Chai wala Nordel crossing. Loved the service and ambience was on point. Saleem sir made us laugh and gave us an excellent service. Will definitely recommend!!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPb8ZDZ7mQOtEk_L9rUl_v0WfppODZz_tRH6Afj&fid=0x0:0x33e9859f9737cf25"],"When":"2024-10-14"},{"Name":"V A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVkmGVBCanJaIOvp8G-T0mVOXgfvSnBYnJwvPaqPMYfr6hZtLJeMw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fun little spot, with great food and drinks. The chai and the rose falooda were awesome.
We also got masala fries, samosa chaat and a butter chicken wrap. All of which were awesome.

The service was quick and great. You order at the front and can pick it up when it's ready.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNC_vuIu9ijidYtQ4C-wCtljGIULZLrhdschMOy&fid=0x0:0x33e9859f9737cf25"],"When":"2024-2-16"}]

[{"Name":"Ronald Lam","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV1AA0COaI7rivDW2feSPCNyXG0VQ-phrOsoMTKHPA9vE24xGU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very nice restaurant for casual Nepalese dining. Staff are friendly, helpful, & very professional. Food is excellent! Lots of food & beverage options. Prices are very reasonable. Our server, Smriti, was so awesome & took time to explain & described individual dishes in detail for us. She really made our dining experience pleasant & truly memorable. Very happy coming here & we will definitely be coming back again. Highly recommended to come dine here!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMD7EUBGMPUs3V7wbWkCZQa8yWkBm3cA7bb0OJ0&fid=0x0:0xa0203bd6c5b9e93a"],"When":"2024-11-16"},{"Name":"Kritika Gupta","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWJLRWIRRKk2KitBlVrb77u7ZV3R_6Id-4ilasCxJKohxG0DmTy=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Tried this place recently for Indo Chinese! Totally worth the visit. We tried the Tandoori fried paneer momos, chilli garlic noodles as well as steamed paneer momos. All vegetarian options were good in taste. Servers were helpful and swift with the order. Highly recommend.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP5TzDAHNxcGHoIOapQXkd3FNDMKZwoNy0Tuym_&fid=0x0:0xa0203bd6c5b9e93a"],"When":"2024-11-8"},{"Name":"Beatrix Cendana","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXrgEz8zi1JhWvuye6FwpWxBtelZ_X_lIGR9nTlf8HQ6_8C9mu0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time I came here I already liked the vibes! We tried the lollipop chicken (spicy was wow🔥🔥🔥🔥🔥). If you don't like spicy they won't put chilli. we also tried stir fried momo (goat) and steamed chicken momo. We LOVED it so much! We would definitely come back soon. Nepali garlic noodle was also good!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM_kglwgCoQKTgd_B8f3fVM8YSdl16g4ScBol9u&fid=0x0:0xa0203bd6c5b9e93a"],"When":"2024-9-23"},{"Name":"soumya rastogi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVoOSf5EEwUectWj3FTSaat7hv9FbQGSvRLEa5sv_VJj63pc71U_A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently visited Momo Factory , The menu offers a wide variety of options, catering to different tastes, and the food did not disappoint.
The staff was friendly and attentive, making sure they provide us best service
Overall, momo factory  exceeded my expectations. Whether you're there for the food, the drinks, or the atmosphere, you won’t be disappointed. I’ll definitely be back and would highly recommend this spot to anyone looking for a great dining experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPc0vIPnEqu0WXbqqBkhl2n7QCDxgDTC2mde96n&fid=0x0:0xa0203bd6c5b9e93a"],"When":"2024-9-2"},{"Name":"tanu vashist","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLj9jsSW09z2ma9Yy5La6fkg3jWZew9UwMwN76BWA0atb_Tvg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had an amazing time at momo factory. Drinks are so so gorgeous and sooo tastyyy.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM8w9zG9WXdn3veaG-iNZyLlppPtBfBqAvF3g7L&fid=0x0:0xa0203bd6c5b9e93a"],"When":"2024-12-22"},{"Name":"Jada Bella","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXk4eJPQiPN0doxEbBetSuoWkSSao1AosPsva1Aa0RHDgZh_c8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Today was my second visit to this place. Beautiful 😻","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOpcuhwZ22hzY5kL_S3pTrjiFF8dXpbX16f1f3W&fid=0x0:0xa0203bd6c5b9e93a"],"When":"2024-7-28"},{"Name":"Pranav Mahajan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVkREuA7BcLRJGA2l4iRxrpgLjdRwL6hhjhML7LuW_dUO9nx0-c=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Out of the box. We watched a video on you tube. We had johl, butter and tandoori momo's along with fries for little one and manchow soup for ourselves. I can assure you will not disappoint. They even have Bubble tea now which is a great addition for a fun family meal!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMa6IFDJ-woziCWWiqEaYmSH4RQtHvBa9D7x7Je&fid=0x0:0xa0203bd6c5b9e93a"],"When":"2024-7-10"}]

[{"Name":"Shibu Rajan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXIz_kKAATx_i2c_nrvy_zHkQjCRhqVBiAvNKpGM65arMKjwg3XWw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very delicious food. Loved the ambience. Went with family and we had ordered Chicken Dum Biryani, Schezwan Noodles, Garlic Naan, Goat pepper fry and double ka meetha. All the dishes were so yummy. Looking forward to going there again.
Diya did an amazing job and was very accommodating.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOI3lTbngtA3JFqtFzRhTwThATIC804oXNow2a2&fid=0x0:0xb33d57667a1bf477"],"When":"2024-10-3"},{"Name":"Reviews by Sammi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocISDh89r6cb4qraK-PQHcAYlErtdTLP1KdmJhJ7Ok-e4HGOlA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had an amazing dinner here at bahubali today😍😍😍 we ordered a mixed tandoori platter with butter naan and Hyderabad dum goat biryani. It was awesome, I loved the biryani, after a decade I had good biryani.
We ordered Paan as well and it was good I loved its cute packaging, definitely coming back for more dinners.
Food, Service, Atmosphere 10/10","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPbcyfJnZNHibQxgYNsBcoqsDpB41J8gmKRuYc7&fid=0x0:0xb33d57667a1bf477"],"When":"2024-12-22"},{"Name":"actionj007","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL3vSkBAqKJl0vg8_AMzQD5EEGhEVeYS2de8UbzcFClZ51w9xM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Came to Bahubali Biryani House from a recommendation of my co-worker who said they had the best Hyderabad biryani in GVRD.

The inside of the restaurant looks very fancy and clean.  The service could be a bit better.  For example, the waitress took away the bucket that had our utensils and paper napkins to refill but didn't bring it back.  Another situation was when our water jug was empty but none of the waitresses (3 of them) just stood around by the bar and didn't offer to help refill it.

Now to the food ... my family ordered the Chicken 65 Semi-Dry Appetizer, Veg Hakka Noodles, Roti, Parantha, and Hyderabad Goat Dum Biryani.

The Chicken 65 was ordered non-spicy but it came with a punch.  It was super tasty with the spices and spicyness so luckily we ordered the noodles, roti and parantha to help offset it.  Noodles were delicious however the roti and parantha was just alright.  the star of the meal was the biryani.  It was our first time  trying Hyderabad biryani and it didn't disappoint.  The goat was very flavourful and spicy (even though we asked for non-spicy) so luckily the Raita helped cool the spicy level down.

Overall I would highly recommend this restaurant.  Will be coming here again in the future.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNxCZp8Gq2LgBhl2te25S_9XFEKz666DZQENrk_&fid=0x0:0xb33d57667a1bf477"],"When":"2024-9-30"},{"Name":"prakash reddy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXb2WRqNb5f2Tgpd1sO4jH5VtFZFQPVCPvbnhXcb3wVT6qPFWIk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Bahubali Indian Restaurant offers an authentic taste of India with a wide variety of delicious dishes. The ambiance is warm and inviting, with decor that reflects Indian culture beautifully. Their butter chicken is a must-try—rich, creamy, and full of flavor. The staff is friendly and attentive, providing excellent service that enhances the dining experience. They have a great selection of vegetarian and non-vegetarian options, catering to all dietary preferences. Prices are reasonable, especially given the generous portions. Overall, Bahubali Indian Restaurant is a fantastic choice for anyone craving authentic Indian cuisine in a cozy setting. Highly recommended!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPHyHyQp_67CoZxCqd2pYXvXuTGTUUiz_NeCVX3&fid=0x0:0xb33d57667a1bf477"],"When":"2024-10-15"},{"Name":"AMD AMD","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWzPVmRQNMQ2YAQxy3zniqjil09YepOShmsliNT69loAl5-o6RZ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I am writing this review about the goat biryani I received. Unfortunately, the dish was completely inedible. The goat meat was tough, dry, and tasted as if it had been cooked months ago. It seemed like old pieces were mixed with fresh ones, which was very unappetizing. I paid $64 for a meal that I wouldn't even consider serving to anyone.

This was extremely disappointing.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPxGIaAp6Pfkl_smCGQdv208-jV6v3x13FXjI-l&fid=0x0:0xb33d57667a1bf477"],"When":"2024-12-3"},{"Name":"Sheetal Pandita","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUwnHbG10zg7YaAEo0q-LJeaWwbii4P2pYJmElXSwqAMfP0nWsj=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently dined at Bahubali and it was a delightful experience. The flavors of the dishes were vibrant and authentic, showcasing the rich diversity of Indian cuisine. Each dish was expertly prepared, from the aromatic biryani to the flavorful curries, all made with fresh ingredients.

The ambiance was warm and inviting, making it a perfect spot for both casual dining and special occasions. The server Navjot was exceptionally attentive, ensuring every guest felt welcomed and satisfied. Their knowledge of the menu was impressive, offering great recommendations that enhanced our meal.

Overall, I highly recommend Bahubali  for anyone looking to enjoy authentic Indian cuisine in a welcoming environment. I can't wait to return!
Music was good too 😍","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMLoDflJFt6NWO_dUjx46DuboeM1pBd-PKYa7Iw&fid=0x0:0xb33d57667a1bf477"],"When":"2024-9-20"},{"Name":"Himaja leo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLK0o1E84JQ_7M4M0-c1DK4VdNjhiwqQw03r2q5r0k8sRTADA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Bahubali Biryani House, located in Surrey offers an authentic Indian dining experience with a focus on biryanis. Known for their generous portions and flavorful biryani varieties, the restaurant brings the richness of Indian spices to the forefront of every dish.
I particularly love their Hyderabadi Goat Dum Biryani and their Rumali Roti with Butter Chicken.
I also enjoyed the Vijayawada Fry Piece Chicken Biryani and Paneer 65 Biryani, which come with classic sides like raita and salan.
Also try their appetizers, they have both veg and non veg options.
I loved some of their mocktails too.
The family pack biryani is huge and a good portion for 4-5 people.
End it with the double ka meeta dessert.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNDzCuKrOUhVS_Qi9uJ2zTscGmzJb9jhyBDAxLc&fid=0x0:0xb33d57667a1bf477"],"When":"2024-10-24"},{"Name":"Khushnuma Baria","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV4h6CCK0EQax6SgHKx94NIQAhlZyc0o6HPMdFK6gESLKX07dEzag=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The portions are  huge. It is value for money. One biryani can be eaten by two folks.  Biryani rice was very smooth and the appetizers are also very interesting , made well and huge. Try to ignore the loud music.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMo9IX0SqWut928oTMVoYatyKHpUsmlQyuP2fUT&fid=0x0:0xb33d57667a1bf477"],"When":"2024-9-14"}]

Highly recommended.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMiGoY1toDaO1ki1Xh-YUfPQQaciIah-PnYqHbI\u0026fid=0x0:0x54e43a6f835f4e15"],"When":"2024-10-11"},{"Name":"Devineah Prasad","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXX1DFa9bRk6bvv1_M-orvwe0-273w8OFGry_kkVxXgLnOAtjdI1w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've always wanted to try this place. Lots of options in the menu. Pricey but portions big which makes up for it. Our server was amazing, super friendly.\n\nWill come back again!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNoDYN0qt7XbHIUyr52MXpcAcIYvKGNx2EjCkEr\u0026fid=0x0:0x54e43a6f835f4e15"],"When":"2024-9-11"},{"Name":"Brian Campbell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV59YkAzqkuHaVw9qeidTV4USN4Yv0Z4ZaYDj3k-63z5r_KKs8MFQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Second time here! Loved the food, and the desserts are the obvious reason to come here! It's a great place for a family \"dessert only dinner\"!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM20eVD_DqaTxaVHqAyp12dJxkY0myNR8Mh-7_4\u0026fid=0x0:0x54e43a6f835f4e15"],"When":"2024-12-15"},{"Name":"Janet","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUJLdrp4_-PzGWs8I7cbVIruptxWktGjE-_19gAKtYsnjV7T8DB=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Plenty of parking outside and love the restaurant decor! The design of the menu was visually appealing, loved that many photos were included. Ordered a pizza and a dessert, the pizza was decent but not that special, the dessert was a skillet cookie and more notable. Skillet cookie came with ice cream and chocolate at the side, while the cookie was warm and had plenty of toppings. Service was friendly but not that efficient, had to ask three times for water refill.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMkVBh5GHguE5uMBWR-Hrx1ZF8qI13GJhN8bUWh\u0026fid=0x0:0x54e43a6f835f4e15"],"When":"2024-7-28"},{"Name":"Beata K.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIAzT-wv8xhkKEWiVQyTg0Tp2oaWtQTkFz0dR8sHOpNKB3u_A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Overpriced. Parfait was good, but waffles very crappy presentation, too much ice cream. Not going again . We waited too long, even so people before us came later and got their food first. And I didn’t know all food is halal……….and for tip, no 15%, it starts with 18%…. One plus- lots of parking, maybe because it’s pricy and not what expected based on photos…i don’t know how they got 4.6 rating","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO5w8iZ75SoetebPbSqsURduIA54gVV0MrULIx9\u0026fid=0x0:0x54e43a6f835f4e15"],"When":"2024-7-20"},{"Name":"Shabbir Hasim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUH8xK9SlJsdoc5DfEoB5FlFoU9-aoRbJheLKUaqIAfjk4NlYPF=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I have to say, the lotus milk cake at D Spot restaurant is hands down one of the best desserts I've ever tried. My family also indulged in the mango ice cream with crêpe, while my son devoured the cotton candy, milkshake, and cotton candy ice cream. The desserts are truly out of this world, and we absolutely love going there. Thank you!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMKHnBmbC5cpzrnfg0ot2NjDTUjFvgIcVFAldZm\u0026fid=0x0:0x54e43a6f835f4e15"],"When":"2024-8-18"}]
