One huge thumbs up here is the size of the salsa and sour cream that comes with the nachos, finally someone gets it right.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMEZT4MDd3bm_iT_ZEv_MOfiP-w3AQGDoAON12M&fid=0x0:0xff652bf97dac55e1"],"When":"2024-5-19"},{"Name":"Kristen Spanza Pedersen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXwMYGtMaY38AyOIyeZrSjTZDF17egD_3KNJBhIZHF7YSCyq7gTtg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wow.  I need to become a regular.  Dog friendly patio and great service.  15% cheaper than white spot for exceptional food.   I've been a couple of times and you can tell that the kitchen really cares about food quality all the time.  Huge smash burgers, beef drip and salad were all the best we've had in years.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"DLH","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKNxoVJChN19TlxEyh2PqXcySZWcsWGp-pw0aGewSStRgeU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Update Aug. 15/23:

We’ve been several times since I first reviewed.
Here is the new menu with the Summerfest $5 menu now integrated into the regular menu, note new lower pricing too.
There are also $5 drink deals that are not on the menu, ask if they don’t tell you about them.
We returned today for the Loaded Smash Burger ($11), comes with 2 Pattie’s, bacon, cheese, lettuce, onion and fries. This is a full sized portion, not the smaller Summerfest burger.
We also ordered DF Pickles and Torpedo Shrimp.($5 ea.) before we knew the burger was so filling.
See new pics.

Have eaten in years ago, received good service then and great service today when ate in on the patio. They are taking Covid precautions with staff now wearing masks for the public’s comfort even though not mandatory, social distant dining, sanitizer at every entrance, wipe down of pin pad before/after use and name/phone # taken for contact tracing.

On a week day it was not too busy on the patio or inside. Service by Sheila was friendly and attentive. Shared plates of Fish and Chips and Beef Dip were excellent. Individual containers for ketchup, packets for salt, pepper and vinegar were provided, as well as our request the au jus be split for 2 sharing. Cutlery brought after ordering.

Already looking forward to returning for the fish and chips which were flaky, lightly battered and crispy.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO5Gc6SXCWYuX9Rrl5LcW25IM70W1SUsEtWY9Y&fid=0x0:0xff652bf97dac55e1"],"When":"2020-7-14"}]

[{"Name":"Malwinder Singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUKtE4fV2M3fW6sJO18IdMP1Kn5pLF-EIwqQO41wFYUP78bLlni=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I went to this joint and ordered two slices of cheese pizza for my son and ordered 7 Gluten Free Chicken Bites.

Firstly, The girl served me burnt pizza slices, I attached the pictures for your reference. My son tried to eat it, but wasn't able to hence he left it as it is. I wondered why and tried a bite of the pizza myself, and it was so disgusting in taste as well.

Second, She also burnt the chicken bites as well, But they were edible, hence won't say much about them.

I would not recommend this joint to anyone.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPbKs67rohqc7TeiLpWWbjNgDzykGw9DsGisdpZ&fid=0x0:0x27a0922ad2719de6"],"When":"2024-6-21"},{"Name":"Sukhdeep Singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLE-jpLAO17PHNZkFTSaqeG6xpL9k6TGDvXdtXXQoJNs1BWtg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Such a great experience, i ordered tandoori chicken pizza that,s such a great taste i like from moths. A person on front  iqubal singh dealing with respect.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP40zygbCKITNaYGV6MqWmfJJPnd3g3LN1nBzEz&fid=0x0:0x27a0922ad2719de6"],"When":"2024-7-25"},{"Name":"Charlie Kirk","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI_7DXLDAAxjcXzwJL5VQRE9dO69UsXuzkjkwo2Zgn6CBemRA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I order the same pizza every week after I play hockey at  midnight in delta. Drive home to Langley and me and my wife each ate a piece and the dough was all raw in the middle. I could’ve rolled it out and made a new pizza. We were busy with the kids the following day so I waited till the next day to call. Customer service said they would give me no refund or credit because I didn’t call same day at 1am? There is also no way to get in touch with the store itself that I could find without going there in person.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO6AQ9tL3GprA-ONtYwZ36e-9LEBPfpZewCYeVa&fid=0x0:0x27a0922ad2719de6"],"When":"2024-2-26"},{"Name":"Arsh Sall","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKoXJksDHASduh0qCN4c4TUh-woJeBoHMqJRNqmysgY2hWBlg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I visited their Guildford location for Panwar Pizza, but the paneer was out of stock. So, I specifically went to this location and ordered the pizza, requesting it to be made slightly spicy. However, when I ate the pizza, it was extremely spicy—so much so that I couldn’t even eat it. It was very disappointing, and the staff didn’t seem to care when I complained.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cory Philip","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKLefITYIG5ehOvaeYlNpUJ5cxHy48e4ogF4jNkMkk76c0dsg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The pizza is 8/10 good.
The pickup special Medium 1 topping for $9.49 is what I get most times. Half pepperoni Half Bacon.
The Air-conditioning works which is nice and there are a couple places to sit.
I live close by so I go often.
The staff are nice.
The owner Inder is nice.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMTolUFgBFGEGcNYOuHMSOJHjreQpZnKMHxZBIv&fid=0x0:0x27a0922ad2719de6"],"When":"2023-8-26"},{"Name":"Updesh Rampal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUYtwhhBEPXJDvv8N-weMS5cILTgWwuem_uDha2Af0Z4KRqs6Gn=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went there Oct 27 night best customer service i ever received from a pizza store. And everything was really warm and fresh. Looking forward to visit again and again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Harinder Gill","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW8-X8tP0Uvwb8Jdpw_gx_d9EST4DIITdTEBKZ0x3cj9JXB9Q1y=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We have visited at their closing time, however they gave us very good dealing and the guy who works at night is super friendly and very professional, the food was also good","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Arman Singh Thind","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ9eYYh9ieSbOLcvurEs8JLqPzJdEXlNVmZA34XQ7y0zV6mxw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of the best pizzas I ever had in my life. Cheers I will see u again. Great service good price . Keep up the good work.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMNs0KkR5N6g0ceDQIYqYcg5gQH-VIbSGJB6QF0&fid=0x0:0x27a0922ad2719de6"],"When":"2021-11-27"}]

[{"Name":"Munro Stuff","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWj0Wcuk6ox5dfAeJ4fAaMbhX_F-nzzt3p5oc_f0hBd0NpbGSM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Enjoyed our lunch here. Friendly service and good menu. Both the combo B and C were nicely presented, fresh, and tasty. Appreciated that they request customers ask for wasabi/ginger in order to minimize waste!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMWJYF7lvrUMY0PELN6VFLv5kwNgRKdIJ0yrBKH&fid=0x0:0xf6bddd82220ada13"],"When":"2024-11-16"},{"Name":"Diana L.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIW2kdRGGLj1j8iotZR8u_6cJvN47azaqWmh-dWmP_2e6mQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"3.5. Never been here so went for the basics just in case. I like how in their Dynamite roll they had two prawns (vs only one with a lot of batter). However the batter or fried ness of it, tasted like it hadn’t been deep fried in fresh kill. Had that darker look where it has been re deep fried twice or thrice over.
The yam roll was so so, the yam itself was still crunchy and not soft or thoroughly cooked. The rice and seaweed are fresh.
However, looks like a nice and clean place. Staff are very courteous. I’ll be back as prices are reasonable! Oh and lots of parking.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP3z8Ixd3uVop-M0vJP_d2o60i0zVUuuBmHNSU&fid=0x0:0xf6bddd82220ada13"],"When":"2017-11-2"},{"Name":"Mori","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUzjNclSLYHoLurDMy1z6lBJJfgC1i3gQXUk28JpQQw8EIfuYkF=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Ordered from this place through Uber Eats and we ended up ordering:
Assorted Tempura
Chicken Yakisoba
Chicken Katsu
California roll & Chicken Teri roll with Black Rice
Dynamite Combo

It took about an hour to get our delivery and off the bat, we had a missing item and unfortunately it was the Dynamite Combo - which was what I was looking forward to the most since it included nigiri.
Aside from the missing item, the tempura was great, the batter on it was a perfect ratio to the veggies and prawns and the chicken yakisoba and katsu was up to par with most Japanese restaurants we've eaten from.

The cali & chicken teri roll with black rice was a bit of a miss for us as the rice was moderately hard and didn't taste like it was fully cooked.

Although this place wasn't terrible, the missing item and the high prices for what you get was a bit off putting for me. Not saying that we wouldn't try this place again, but we will definitely try other places before revisiting.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPiVV3SThl7KnscwJ29KU9gFhR9WXieHHDOMCXJ&fid=0x0:0xf6bddd82220ada13"],"When":"2022-9-9"},{"Name":"Alex","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIjFHGtwIzveQOQjqcUkPmPkjaJlaH08sYYGOWsca-S0Ncj9A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"It's about what you what expect from a "sushi" run place like this..  The staff are actually pretty rude, it's all about turning tables per hour with their mediocre food.  This place sucks, there are better places near by that are beoetter value.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Hailey Marie Hartman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW-hNTxh2UYMvVaHJkaD6_G2Fjmuiq56y_dqbMawQvIBYfgn6k=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been coming to this sushi place for almost 7 years! And they are the best I’ve found, everything is fresh and tastes amazing! Service is always friendly and they even remember my order when I forget to ask for no ginger or wasabi lol you guys rock!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kyle Blake","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJNFcbCQ39fGXxRQtPXHo2eBeLhsWLS92wriEf_ty70muDA_A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Tiny avacado roll like you get at a gas station... the smallest nib of weak wasabi. Ordered 3 rolls all together and got 3 packets of soy sauce","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPSJRSgO-utvy1HFRsp9eFE2eqIo1PsVBn6Q9Ro&fid=0x0:0xf6bddd82220ada13"],"When":"2024-4-28"},{"Name":"Scythian 77","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUTCZVi8qUH6MixmE15xPL0-_3rz_xNDLzk8xuiwECIp9MYhLV4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"ive ordered before from here they sell fas staion style sushi they will go out of business soon give it time theyll eventually collapse","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dhruv Anand","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX5no7BGOEmOfFvCM2Og4Ox2wgvigMevZFPDxw0o5I3WeRqKuh0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Nice food, amazing vibe, kind hosts and amazing food. Doesn’t get better than this in my opinion. This is also an amazing place for introverts because of the chill vibe and low amount of interaction. It is also really cheap.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPr1ZY5zaFusM3NrJ2QZi72SeGuS-ZMPLHDJPUF&fid=0x0:0xf6bddd82220ada13"],"When":"2022-10-30"}]

The meats were tender, and everything was fresh and hot. We ordered rice platters, chips with hummus, and the portions were generous—our employees even took leftovers home. Great quality, great pricing, and highly recommended!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"PARNEET KAUR","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXEEPVdBd7GknxoXFap1bv6Z6GMdOxFKTSHsdid7dxbpLUB3Zg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently ordered food from Donair Bite, and it was absolutely fantastic! The flavors were fresh, delicious, and perfectly seasoned.
The donair was packed with juicy, tender meat, crisp vegetables, and the sauce was perfectly balanced-not too sweet, not too overpowering. The portion sizes were generous, leaving me completely satisfied.
Beyond the food, the service was quick and friendly, and the overall experience was great. If you're craving a high-quality donair or any tasty meal, I highly
recommend checking out Donair Bite. I'll definitely be returning for more!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Priya","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUnPugMJUYNWTF7dVlrE9Cg4VZLyx474-PkMJW__55FAtcWkQU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I tried falafel and chicken platter of this place. This place is highly recommended if you want good quality and quantity of food between $10-20.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Deep Gill","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXZVLGMHMUZAYCxMMueVKgssKT4TQJ5m_MkImESlHT-bTNh1ZWd=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"16 dollar for this, subway is better than for this, you will get at least good quantity","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM7O7GewuANrcpfORdIktovf0mvzt5VOOOB9Hkh&fid=0x0:0x4a3cf0895297c2e6"],"When":"2024-12-11"},{"Name":"Ramon Carfrae","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJbjvo-PB7ZluRHdv76jBuAd7OTik1mTEXOQPMPuCJOV2Ov4A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time going to this place today and it was delicious. I really hope they keep their quality of food and service as time goes on because this place is on my route and I loved the food today. The woman working there was friendly and professional.

I have been checking out a lot of Donair places lately and this one is in my top 3!

mmm mmm!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"A Z (futyh_ag)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU5cJP6wFheKfz62vSlcPb207ZDQuO80KTxeX1k1o7FblbZGcZosQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Something definitely happened here. It used to be my favourite donair in Vancouver. I drove all the way back to get a chicken donair since I’m no longer working on the island. Unfortunately, it just tastes so not good as before. The chicken is dry, it’s not juicy and chewy anymore. I don’t know if it is overcooked or just the ingredients are not as fresh as before. Sauce is less. Lettuce are not well separated. Veggies, meat and sauce are not well mixed. The price is still the same, but quality is a lot lower. It definitely doesn’t deserve my time drive back.","Images":null,"When":""}]

Decoration is beautiful inside 😁","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNPbHIvvzQmUzn_t6atRPsNUizcCL4UizcstV1z&fid=0x0:0x5dbfdcfd226228c9"],"When":"2024-12-2"},{"Name":"Nick","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUGjptqH3FdoeLfdSjPWQygL5KEsM_ui4pClg77BekGUD0E-Q_8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Possibly the most westernised Thai food we've ever had. Didn't expect everything to be this sweet, even the dishes that weren't supposed to be slightly sweet seemed like dripping with sugar. The server was nice but I wouldn't recommend this restaurant.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO1vD_oXCDs0H1yl7p5KLyXNGStgRtC2cdLD-oK&fid=0x0:0x5dbfdcfd226228c9"],"When":"2024-8-13"},{"Name":"Treesa Jose","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXFAcEvrf5W4OuIeuAB0aqqRE5Cp6_m6FulMnOH78o-tGG2Cn__OA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I had previously given this restaurant a 5-star rating a few years ago, but unfortunately, my recent experience fell short of my expectations. Even the same food that we ordered during our previous visit did not meet our expectations. The chicken wings were good. The beef satay wasn't great and the desserts were very disappointing , both for the price and quality. The service was extremely poor. Despite being the only customers, we had to repeatedly call our server to place our order, which was frustrating. Overall, a disappointing experience compared to my previous visit","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP2XsSgvShTVjGX0kOK-488OrH3Yi3ZwoKyKWsB&fid=0x0:0x5dbfdcfd226228c9"],"When":"2024-5-8"},{"Name":"Jason S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUqRIxw09yeU8jDKKDJphGFR8Woa_AB93yhSLS_h8RI3kBX7HAo=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of my favourite Thai restaurants in the lower mainland.
Their yellow curry is so luscious and flavourful balanced over their rice.

A genuine treat I enjoy that I drive out of the way for.
Great lunch specials.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Prabash Maduranga","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVxbdLsgTlzOO3PwAwsa1fA3jREaTKjqsq5sBWIks4HU7AHLFr3aQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had the lunch special and i thought it was great value. The fish sauce with chopped chillies on the side is surprisingly uncommon in Thai restaurants in BC and it was a great to have that catered to.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPiXgkYlJh3kRX377AQ-QRt_RxrjRTNO9D2Ln-G&fid=0x0:0x5dbfdcfd226228c9"],"When":"2024-9-13"},{"Name":"Blake Matthew","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW60DTdMT6IuKEzA0hM3GKPvcHwIgwqfMA_Vmc4aiNtt_6vGpSA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I ordered food for my girlfriend (she is Thai) and it was absolutely horrible and so disappointing. Would not recommend.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN7Z_FcwrL3h9OFXzktr7IYWeS_Pzt3zOfR1dlZ&fid=0x0:0x5dbfdcfd226228c9"],"When":"2024-9-20"},{"Name":"Tomo w","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUH7bgxIOPDZsA8wtpT0yJypQm_QzZTYq6SCrE5qF6WR2_dAlRP=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I got pick up, dinner for two. I love Thai food. This restaurant is my go to in Surrey.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"LX X","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVKt0o0nBq514HJq0Lya5ttJ854_HKIhbCnRPuElbiWePQLX2wh=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Pad thai is very bad, it is dry, plain and super sweet

[{"Name":"Anurag Sharma","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLuNWZNGEXcZYuxJm3PAALeRt53oSt1Pks2yfZ8cIUcOqDeBA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This was the worst experience I’ve ever had. The girl with glasses at the front desk was extremely disrespectful. I ordered food, but we weren’t even offered water. Meanwhile, the table next to us received friendly greetings and prompt service. They were served their food before us, even though we had ordered first.

I had ordered one plate of chole bhature and one gobi paratha. After waiting 15 minutes, only the chole bhature arrived, and the paratha never came. Frustrated, I decided to leave without finishing my meal. To make matters worse, the girl with glasses charged me for both the chole bhature and the paratha.

The service was absolutely pathetic. I’m never coming back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM47rULbtWwz2tpUrb2mzQDX5bQtXnIazAoJjZz&fid=0x0:0x3f418a1902bbb472"],"When":"2024-12-14"},{"Name":"Alyssa Jade","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVP3BT6QCtKzYrodkNhl4oehDqhZVLsZk1_86M1pnEIZ3rC6PVmBQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We live in the okanagan but come out to
Vancouver a couple times a year and we will now add this to the list of stops we make every trip down to Van.
I’m not Indian but still received amazing service and suggestions aswell as education. Their cashews are soo good, easy to bring home and store, the aloo paratha is so fresh and perfect for a road snack. Prices are good and store is clean.
We will be back 100%, thank you Baba Sweets 🙏🏼","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNer_-rZOz1NxQcVhx0r_Z4mRQiIo0gF-hSFClw&fid=0x0:0x3f418a1902bbb472"],"When":"2024-9-6"},{"Name":"Simran Singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKNClaMWehPTTWtbhjwVN9uXg1xejwqrwQN6zcDewXYBIiw1A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"One of the best sweets shop on Scott road. [{"Name":"Raviendra Madugalle","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW4uSti5RtYJISGgBTK64N3UvnE0RQMNNyvHQyHnJXUNKlh6o9k=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Tried a flavourful Indian Thali. Packed with Indian spices. Great variety of selections to choose from the menu. The staff is very nice and pleasant. We were recommended here by a friend. And we greatly enjoyed our dining experience.

Highly recommended !!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOqHl3ucILf94pdv3W5gl4jfShEnYbjEh9ziuHO&fid=0x0:0x5a590360d726859a"],"When":"2024-11-26"},{"Name":"Shahan Taneja","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKmIBYY2kL3VGe-r_FhrX08WYXS5iI0zJsrAH5UGxV9oFRQnsec=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food was good and personal favourite is veg thali. I also like dosa and coffee here. The portion size is good. Service is also nice. The decor is very soothing with good vibes. It’s worth a try.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO_SDATgvNEZR2q4POIme1W6JQuaOEAyx2r5fBN&fid=0x0:0x5a590360d726859a"],"When":"2024-12-16"},{"Name":"Abdul Ali","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX6A-2UkJSQuzxRI3b5SiNokbRUgJ6lOWebAPsInCI4BZY1eRdJaA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A hidden restaurant in Delta, BC. Absolutely delicious Masala Dosa and Fish Thali. Affordable  , Large Portion and mouth watering delicious.

Also we ate at there another location at Henderson Center Mall in Coquitlam.  Was delicious food there too.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN2Bsi4hyjgVkVAsM72BSIkrJYHKkV1yS_i4nEi&fid=0x0:0x5a590360d726859a"],"When":"2024-7-22"},{"Name":"AWAIS THE BOSS","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWFR2cYPf0wPxYiA1s-uSEkyon-hcTMvm8LJq6BY3cw9K_NYCzp=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Desi Dosa Madras is a delightful culinary gem that brings the authentic flavors of South India right to your plate. From the moment you step in, you are greeted with a warm and inviting ambiance, coupled with the tantalizing aroma of freshly prepared dosas. The menu offers a wide range of options, from classic masala dosas to innovative fusion varieties that cater to every palate.

The dosas are perfectly crisp on the outside and soft on the inside, complemented by a variety of flavorful chutneys and a piping hot bowl of sambar. The freshness of the ingredients is evident in every bite, making the meal not just delicious but also wholesome. The standout for me was the Mysore Masala Dosa, which had the perfect balance of spice and flavor.

The service at Desi Dosa Madras is exceptional, with friendly staff who are attentive and knowledgeable about the menu. They go above and beyond to ensure a pleasant dining experience.

Whether you’re a fan of South Indian cuisine or a first-timer exploring it, Desi Dosa Madras is a must-visit. The combination of authentic flavors, excellent service, and reasonable prices makes it a standout spot for anyone craving a taste of India. Highly recommended!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNTPrra21pRW_5YVMyI08rgnSby-SvdPSwwMhTb&fid=0x0:0x5a590360d726859a"],"When":"2024-12-3"},{"Name":"Jasmine Jasmine","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIAMYJt7r_I9uLzj_L5_Ayv1BM6ZSUnB0izETrjD06CDNEyww=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Terrible food, staff and seating. When you enter this place they wouldn’t care about seating you to a place suited for your group size. We ended up changing our seats 4 times cause our group was not satisfied. The seats were either too tight to comfortably sit at, or literally outside the washroom. The food served was cold and tasteless, one of our items was undercooked and almost tasted like old food. We were brought the wrong order twice and our beverages were forgotten about. Finally when we just wanted out of that place we were charged for the food we had sent back. Instead of feeling sorry for us and giving us any alternatives, we were handed a bill of 50$, for the food we barely ate! We had to book another place close by, to eat our dinner. There was a time when this place was good and food was worth while but not anymore I guess.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gurjot Singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI8a-bEYf2tOjO3X0uunG1i72NDQmDvedMGhMYubzV2uJfhiQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"They are good. But now they are decreasing the quality of food and increasing prices. I got fully burnt dosa.
My last experience was not good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP-WjoFDvvI6iYyQXHYKdLX6UfC8N6yA537iPuU&fid=0x0:0x5a590360d726859a"],"When":"2024-9-2"},{"Name":"Justbeing Sam","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWM9hiJK-AfVP-qSHlK2ogC-KKU9aHv9jB-f8Zpy8fNkox9PG5e=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Went to this place after long time with family. We had great time delicious food. We ordered masala dosa platter and fish curry thali and veg noodles. Food was really yummy no complaints there. However, when we asked for extra sambar and sauces ( 1 time extra) we were charged for it as sambar quantity was less and 1 extra should be given as courtesy and 2nd time shuld be charged. Prices are genuine but paying extra for sauces n sambar hurted.

Update: Went there again had a great time but food and customer service quality has been decreased","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOSUCEzYT2thWnrLiWyNSfqhjz2CYD9aSQAm_09&fid=0x0:0x5a590360d726859a"],"When":"2023-2-16"},{"Name":"Manik Passi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVH_gfcPHOChMCHRzzmQffU138Sko8LLUzb68J8nqVpFeIuoVHb=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Today we again went there. Last time my gf put a review about the soup and today when we order soup again there they saw us and get offended and the staff was really rude. Today they make the soup full of water intentionally. I think they dont want us to come back because we put a review. Here are the pictures of the soup full of water and it was tasteless. Really unprofessional thing. They just want to take a revenge. Very very disappointed and we waste our money here. The sad thing was that we came here every three to four times a week but now not at all. We would be happy if the owner of the restaurant saw this review and taught their staff to behave themselves.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNU6ZiE78LJ1u4McKemEddCbhwt8uu7JGencL3i&fid=0x0:0x5a590360d726859a"],"When":"2022-9-26"}]

[{"Name":"jessiekaurshergill","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV6vi0RzCa2RIYMvTOvd6Zi05nAVpR7-2tNSFCfJwGh1BRO5Si8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"well, i go here almost every week and today, i was there at 18:26 and i was waiting for my order. I simply n nicely asked if they can make my coffee first!!. The lady in all black, at the counter there told me (with a great ego) , “WE KNOW HOW TO SERVE GUEST”, I just wonder if i questioned their service? You guys seriously need to teach your employees what to say when 🙄🙄 AND HOW COME HER HAIR ARE ALWAYS OPEN WHILE WORKING IN A FOOD STORE","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"James R","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVtjhmlLtc__TA_6ftkINn1xpVHmaHrDjFOE1Nwq00mndKLOalw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Another Annacis island location that is just garbage no matter how loud and clear you talk they ask to repeat an order 3 times and still get it wrong also I’m pretty sure a sausage McGriddle comes with more then just to pancakes and a sausage piece. Seriously how do you mess up so bad.  As for milk in the coffee and still get cream. Take yourself off autopilot and listen to the orders that come through stop assuming. I’m done with shopping anywhere on annicis your all garbage locations who don’t care because you know people will come through. Deplorable services","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOk5hzVDFoYitkUCXBWtqkZXFgwfrQV1bf7VJDW&fid=0x0:0x1750ee8f431c31c2"],"When":"2024-10-7"},{"Name":"Payana","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVgF2ikKnyuTF1a9jgYb178XCkQxeZXYfbgfTJZe1ETmdOMjNDH=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Food always fast and fresh and great staff. NOTE to the lady preparing the burgers ; Please consider washing your hands or using a cloth to wipe down counter tops. As using your palm/hand to wipe off the excess food from the counter top to the floor then proceeding to prepare my burger wasn't quiet sanitary!!.. felt disgusted","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jennie H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUPNtzJqMkXpM_yl5Xcpp4sVRpDlXELrNOIdb5rE1olC4vT6ifG=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Frequent this location whenever I feel the occasional craving for McD as it is quiet and very clean. The fries are always fresh too.

This time, I ordered curbside and the staff member was very nice, had a big smile and very polite!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Review Truly","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ1r_p5CbqF95zJ9gAkSPraeDU5TCpW6jzLmdNlgbvA3ye31A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Dear management team,

I am writing to formally lodge a complaint regarding the poor service and unprofessional behavior I encountered from the Manager Ravneet (I am not sure if it’s correct name, I don’t see any name batch on them) at your McDonald's store located at 1285 Clivedon Ave, Delta, BC, on November 24, 2024.

I placed an online order (Order #2106) and went to the store to pick it up. When I received my order, but upon reaching home, I discovered that the hashbrowns, a water bottle, and the Happy Meal box were missing. I immediately called the store to report the issue but received no response. After several attempts, the manager, Ravneet, finally answered the call. When I inquired about the missing items, she told me that they had been left on the counter, implying that it was my mistake for not picking them up.

Despite explaining the situation, Ravneet did not make any effort to resolve the issue or offer any assistance. She spoke in a dismissive and rude manner, which I found completely unacceptable. As a loyal McDonald's customer, I expect better treatment and respect, not only as a consumer but also in my interactions with staff.

I request that the management team review this matter and provide an apology for Ravneet's unprofessional conduct. I would appreciate a resolution to this issue, as I believe customers should be treated with courtesy and respect at all times.

Thank you for your attention to this matter. I look forward to your response.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOfO6YwjJOzKDQsGCnAzmmas3OQPV-8e7Z-cv5p&fid=0x0:0x1750ee8f431c31c2"],"When":"2024-11-24"},{"Name":"CriticalBeee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUf9vcBYCB2s0D1bzgz2NSuPZl2c3ejXsXj-abxr-eQaUZcTMs=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This is one of the worst mcds to order delivery and for dine-in. Reading past reviews, the reoccurring complaint is the watered-down orange juice and the constant wrong orders.  My wife ordered here because it's the only location popping up on doordash. We spent over $50, and we received no eggs on our sausage egg griddles, and all our orange juices had to be thrown out. Whoever manages this particular restaurant does not care how the staff are trained, or they are purposely making wrong orders to save on food cost. I've stopped going in-house, as my orders are always wrong. You'd think with the mcdonalds warehouse being on annacis island, they would have fresher products. As an ex-shift manager, for Mcds of 10 years. Never again would we order from this location.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jarrod Barnes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIeceTJmLEsKqP3iHvd_c-fehr0LcThFXSXyKK1RGkHIPBo0A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I go there often for breakfast however the shrinkflation has hit here to! When ordering OJ with my breakfast meal, its orange colored water.. I've complained many times but no change at all. Owner must be saving a buck.. typical of todays world. Dont get the OJ!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ashley Ford","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJzg2RBJZaohk7hmO1_bzLlthUJHQ1LXkGlEaQP1PQGtYu0JA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Order burgers with no onions. They put onions and scraped them off. They forgot a couple. If I hadn't of checked.omg.. I have allergies and if I had eaten it I would have been sick or worse. They just don't care I guess. Mc Donald's sure isn't what it was","Images":null,"When":""}]

They forgot to deliver the main dish- rice. It was around 11pm and we obviously ordered through Door Dash for convenience. We kept calling and no one answered the phone so I had to go in and asked to speak to the \"manager.\" He said that they gave the driver 3 bags (rice was in this bag with attached receipt) but the driver failed to deliver it.  We had already contacted the driver prior to going to the restaurant and the poor man was adamant that the restaurant only gave him 2 bags. The manager even said to show us camera footage but didn't think that was necessary over rice. lol. Also, why would someone lie about that so I believed him. I got to find out when I got home that the manager contacted the driver (while I was waiting for my rice to be cooked) and admitted that they didn't give him the rice. The manager lied to my face!! The manager gave me my rice and also gave an extra order of butter chicken but didn't apologize for any inconvenience. Customer service is horrible and its too bad because the food was really good. They were willing to allow Door Dash take the negative criticism for their own fault. It's okay if you make a mistake, just be accountable for it. Never will I order from here again and I will be sure to spread the news to all my friends and family. This restaurant should really consider getting a new manager, a smile goes a long ways!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Harsimran Kaur","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKKQkG1XNRBA8CtjSdrzQ4CI-hipUHzY3iH9N_9X9zVBCIDkGA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food is very tasty and the employees are very good and the atmosphere is awesome. user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Jaga Rana","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVH1EcPpxv4Oo1wlSzoqciKZomQ98duiH3QpBNeR6lJ6id3rEd8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"5 Tara is a must-visit! The ambiance is vibrant yet relaxed, making it an ideal spot for both dinner and drinks. The menu is diverse, featuring both traditional favorites and innovative dishes. I highly recommend the grilled lamb—it was tender and bursting with flavor.

The drink selection is equally impressive, with creative cocktails that perfectly complement the food. The staff went above and beyond to ensure we had a great experience, providing attentive service with a smile.

Overall, 5 Tara delivers an exceptional dining experience. I can’t wait to come back and explore more of the menu!.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Bhupinder Singh N/A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWri-UxbcxBJCrNxZwaxy6prSwxL_WzPDI2dSW631CAKUqXXAU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"5 Tara is an absolute gem! From the moment I walked in, I was greeted by a warm and inviting atmosphere. The decor strikes the perfect balance between modern and cozy.

The menu offers a fantastic selection of dishes, and every bite I tried was delicious. The highlight for me was the signature dish—flavorful and beautifully presented. The pub also boasts an impressive drink list, with unique cocktails that are perfect for unwinding.

Service was exceptional; the new restaurant staff was attentive and knowledgeable, making great recommendations. Whether you’re looking for a casual night out or a special occasion, 5 Tara is the place to be. I can’t wait to return!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Javin Dass","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLdJRPxyPvRrPHYBvLhxuighvUSthQg3C5TeScSY5uzf7W9LXg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Oh, where do I even start with this "5 Tara" experience? First off, $10 for entry to an event organized by Diamond Events? Wow, what a steal! Too bad we weren’t told it was a chaotic mess masquerading as a 'gathering'. So, we show up, ready to enjoy our evening, and what do we get? A cozy table until, of course, they decided mid-meal to shuffle us off to an isolated corner like we were the last people invited to the party. A real treat, especially when we were busy eating.

Then, as if that wasn’t enough of a delightful surprise, the manager actually had the nerve to come over and, in an incredibly generous move, inform us that we didn’t even need to pay if we weren't part of their next mess of an event. So kind, thank you! I was starting to think maybe I had made a terrible mistake paying for this chaos.

And let’s talk about the pre-reserved seating for the event organizers because, of course, there’s no need to give your paying customers a heads-up about that, right? Who doesn’t love being blindsided mid-meal? Next time, how about putting up a big sign outside the pub, “Hey, if you’re not part of the club, enjoy sitting in the back like a forgotten afterthought!”

Oh, and the food? A culinary masterpiece. The fries were passable, but the wings? Let’s just say I’ve had better wings from a 7-Eleven microwave. Maybe the event was supposed to be a test of how much nonsense customers could tolerate before they completely lose their appetite because trust me, you’ve passed with flying colors.

5 Tara? More like 1 star for effort, and that’s being generous. If you want a true experience of mismanagement and disappointment, look no further than this place. 5 stars? Yeah, right. Try 5 disasters.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Arjun Tyagi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWopm7CB27Brsn2nZf_ZcGMYA1rC2xZn0gFS2Ev_B4zUk8mX8MoIQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Overall this was a great experience. The server was fantastic, polite and attentive the whole time we were there. The food was awesome, cooked and spiced well. The only area of improvement was some of the drinks like the Moscow mule for example, didn’t taste authentic with ginger beer and wasn’t served in a copper mug (not the end of the world but just being specific). I will definitely be back again, the spicy mango margaritas, tandoori chicken, paneer tikka and lamb was perfect.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOSZVqg9YCMm6RHvyP8PZTwsYbYsUkYjRiMqi8_&fid=0x0:0x9c823e839d5debb3"],"When":"2023-12-31"},{"Name":"Vishwas Jaggi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXwtPd42uIUyzvEd5kS1jqW3hYQtlRdCeWcZFJTyPIiZDnmiMwXbQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I recently visited 5 Tara with friends, and unfortunately, it was a deeply disappointing experience.

We were charged $10 + tax per person as an entry fee, which we paid expecting a well-organized and enjoyable evening. Upon arrival, we were given a table, so we assumed it was fine to settle in. However, while we were eating, organizers came over and abruptly asked us to leave the table, claiming it was reserved.

This was incredibly unprofessional for several reasons:
1. Charging an entry fee without sufficient seating: If there was no space available for us, we should not have been allowed to enter, or at least we should have been informed beforehand.
2. Giving us a table only to make us leave mid-meal: This was not only inconvenient but also disrespectful. Had we known, we would have chosen a different venue.
3. Ruining our evening: Being asked to get up while eating left my friends and me embarrassed and frustrated.

This was an unacceptable experience that made me regret bringing my friends along. The lack of organization and poor treatment of customers was disappointing, and I sincerely hope no one else has to go through this.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Harjot Singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI37LYTqmApn4lS3FGuXMcEA_RH2yxlcVmAgHJ4s6Wh5tZAhg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently visited 5 Tara, and I must say, the experience was fantastic! The food was absolutely delicious, full of authentic flavors that really hit the spot. The atmosphere was warm and inviting, perfect for a relaxing meal. The new management is doing a wonderful job, and it clearly shows in the improved service and overall experience. I highly recommend this place for anyone looking for great food and good vibes!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Baram Singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLYuukw1Fnpap1KNNmJyIeeuRoPJ9sika-Vivh69arY9xaYig=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If you’re looking for a cozy spot with a laid-back atmosphere and great service, 5 Tara Pub is a fantastic choice. The pub offers a vibrant yet relaxed ambiance, making it perfect for both casual outings with friends and more intimate gatherings. The menu features a diverse selection of drinks, including a great range of beers. The food complements the drinks perfectly, with classic pub fare that’s delicious and generously portioned. Simran(a gorgeous girl), who works at 5 Tara Pub, is truly a standout when it comes to customer service. Her friendly and welcoming demeanour immediately puts guests at ease, and she always goes the extra mile to make sure everyone feels taken care of.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shamsher Sandhu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKja2791iBFM_sKFnf1-bnroAcSrpRQRz5GljqtLJYreIIYyA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"“Extremely Disappointing Experience”

I had high expectations for 5 Tara & Pub, but unfortunately, it was one of the worst dining experiences I’ve ever had. The service was painfully slow, and the staff seemed uninterested and inattentive. It took over 30 minutes just to get water, and our food order took nearly an hour to arrive, despite the restaurant not being busy.

The food was a disaster. It was cold, tasteless, and lacked freshness. The portions were small for the price, and the presentation looked sloppy. To make things worse, the drinks tasted watered down and overpriced.

The ambiance wasn’t great either. The place felt dirty and poorly maintained, and the loud, unpleasant music made it hard to have a conversation.","Images":null,"When":""}]

Ordered 4 sushi party platters (sashimi platter and rolls) and there was more than enough food for 12 Americans 😜 The fish was fresh and the price was great! Edamame, egg rolls, and fish apps were all delicious. The staff were friendly (I called them 3 times to change my pickup times), the space is small but oh so cute. user_reviews: [{"Name":"Simran Gosal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKPmqYJW7o1Cey3OqfluBQCQ162C7WOlyuz7zdVwj7G7Zn0Ug=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I ordered large Pizza from their store. Half Shahi paneer and half butter chicken. I asked the employee to make chicken side spicy (to add green chilis) instead they added jalapenos. These are the jalapenos that came out of one slice. I literally took out 2 bowls of these from 5 slices of Pizza. After then I called the store not to get refund just to tell them that this happened. They were arguing that they didn't put jalapenos at all. I used to go to this store regularly but after what happened today I will never go to this place again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNZHk0eEpBoUNm2LX2_mrpcO6GZPQ4uWzeba5lP\u0026fid=0x0:0xec0cf41da8385ccb"],"When":"2022-7-3"},{"Name":"Vida Corvus","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXqINKLe9b1hKofrDcCLAKEL-6hQV6fdy1HehcGnPVwrDjBQXY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Been looking for a good pizza place in surrey for sometime, and this place is it. The trick is to order well done. The crust has the perfect amount of crunch/texture","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPKSQBXAzBzCNTRUBTqEWZPM_tWW0HrtofnRzzp\u0026fid=0x0:0xec0cf41da8385ccb"],"When":"2023-4-29"},{"Name":"Zain Shyanne","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWwljMDRLcobSHBOYATSkUfyA8eUV6IQqD-3N5acOVGljmLFao=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been ordering here since I was a student at LA Matheson at least over 14 years. The recipe is unchanged to this day and it's the best pizza in Surrey hands down. There are lots of places that make Indian vegetarian pizzas but Prime Hut does it best. The crust and cheese is just perfect and flavourful you can actually taste the oregano. The owners themselves are extremely humble and nice I wish more people supported them they haven't even changed their prices as much in years. Back in the high school days some kids wouldn't have money and they'd still give them slices.  I recommend this place whenever I can.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Damanpreet singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLuk02oj_BxJheWLjV-KgR_DTVu1qUELQ_w4OXU60cFY4xGdA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"one of the best places in PG ! 100% recommended ! Staff is so friendly and polite ! always smiling faces !! Thanks prime pizza team 😊","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Daniel Ming Lui To","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUEnpNKEVxnP6-lBlHcK5NFcIkPpx3EuMdI9qk5Miv4GOofSrn_=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Prime Hut Pizza is awesome.  I run school programs in the Surrey School District and whenever we have a staff event or student event in our program we use Prime Hut Pizza.  They are local, they went to Surrey Schools (awesome) and they're delicious. We never have ANY leftovers.  Their Gluten Free pizza is also amazing - some say it even taste better than their regular pizza (which is also amazing).  I really encourage anyone in the Surrey/ Delta area to give Prime Hut a call!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Richard Kish","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU7ycvrk6h2EgX33KYv5Ceieh7bFehxG3h5f_c56EQetMf0PNdbrQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Delicious. A nice balance of toppings to dough. We tried a pepperoni and mushroom and a veggie pizza to test them out. Everyone loved it. We’ll certainly go back to explore other ‘za","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lucky Bryan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVLnBe66fzAP1HI9HURHb9zcqHbrYN9fymWk6YX7-QXKqfTZds=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been going here for 15 years. There pizza is very thick and juicy. Easily the best pizza in surrey by my standards. Try there chef special my favourite, hawaiian, supreme, house special. It is amazing. I live abroad and i crave this pizza when i am abroad. It is that good! The prices are only 11-12 for a large.  You just cant beat that in the city.  It is a family owned business and the couple are extremely nice and humbling.  They have a couple of tables inside if you want to eat in. It reminds me of a indian street food place.  A great feeling.  Love street food in india. Make sure you tell them to.make it medium spicy and add cilantro and garlic. I always recommend this place to my friends. If you seriously dont like this pizza.  Something is wrong with you.😂 Thanks ! They have been in business for so many years for a reason .  It makes me quite angry about the complainers.  Definitely not deserved for an amazing business that has been here throughout the pandemic and well before.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Grace Hight","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXaiqZL0PaVgsNwbJaTUqTKS088FCn8p-8Ez3bD1jaXvMSmqg2I=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have only ever had the vegetarian pizza from Prime Hut, but each time I have it has been delicious! Their food is always very consistent. I have never been disappointed when I have ordered from them. Lots of toppings on the pizza and very good quality overall especially for the price.\n\nI highly recommend them!","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Malwinder Singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUKtE4fV2M3fW6sJO18IdMP1Kn5pLF-EIwqQO41wFYUP78bLlni=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Before Boston Pizza, I had no idea that a Gluten-free Pizza or Pasta could be that good. I went inside just browsing and checking, in the Surrey's Scott road area, restaurant by restaurant, asking if they have Gluten Free options in their menu. I didn't find many options till I landed in Boston Pizza. It was second time when I tried Boston Pizza and it was fun. The service was amazing. We were given ample amount of time to decide our order. Regular checks were kept to make sure that we liked the quality of the food. Our server was very courteous, we really enjoyed our meal and I am definitely visiting again, not just for the food, but for the experience too. Thank you for your hospitality.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"wendy khanna","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXtNkT9-AmY0g3JtP1X_NWMIcXO0CTuTIPba5cHpQuBWdMtW9XE=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"On Saturday Nov 2nd/2024 we made the reservation at Nordel Way,Surrey location for 7:30 PM specially mentioning that we would like to watch Hockey game.When we reached there we were given seats in the family side where hockey wasn’t on,we requested to turn on at least one tv for the game,service was pretty slow,drinks we ordered were so bad, cocktails not upto the mark,no fizz in soda,tap beer didn’t taste like beer,so we decided to go somewhere else,we tried to tell our server,who looked like one of the owners,flashing his gold chain and branded shirt,didn’t even consider anything,no discount was given,we paid the full price for drinks which we couldn’t even finish.we were very disappointed and we DO NOT recommend this place.Very bad experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNyhcOaayzcRrhOd_tgSoYYbOqYiTupLXnUPdPU&fid=0x0:0x9c4803b090bd3282"],"When":"2024-11-5"},{"Name":"Tammi Lewis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI3sMr8_TU5QWTi_uYmRzM3ClsR7ktzzGF2ZhRRfrHwSVmDOw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have to say Amy served us tonite and she was amazing. She made our dining experience so much better then we expected.   You are lucky to  have such an awesome employee.   She was really great","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"shane yochim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIBeDDxH7390AWSRmm5Spx1H9wYSumrHzG3-5AyVZKJrCZQ9A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very fun atmosphere when we walked in we were seen by a host and seated right way. We got a nice table and our server was there within 2 minutes to greeted by our waitress Amy. This was my first time at this location and was very impressed by the service we received, as we never had to try and flag down our waitress she was always there to ask if we needed anything. We asked for a few recommendations for what to eat as this was my first time taking my father to Boston Pizza. She was very knowledgeable about the menu and help us with our choices. The food was great which I expect as I have gone to various Boston Pizza's and the food is always good. But the service at this location was great as some times at other locations it is not up to this standard and need to get the server's attention to come over.  Will definitely be choosing to come to this location a lot more after this great experience.

For anyone that wants to have a great time visit this Boston Pizza and ask for Amy to be your server and you will be happy that you did.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sunny Kaler","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUeoeVUjOlOdUgGYZloH7jcZQ1Io1Z_iuN89vupUJZJ2DQjwWmU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent service and food was great. Previously i had really bad experience at this location however when i went here the other day it seemed like completely new staff and management. Our waitress knew the menu items so well that she made some really good reccommendations. Manager came by to make sure food was great. Will definitely make this my favourite location goong forward.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMhQ08lDrMLJLxPnl1WTobSXDN-jmVJ-bmnrk84&fid=0x0:0x9c4803b090bd3282"],"When":"2022-4-10"},{"Name":"Shane OMac","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJZ0lKiVXEpPppO3fkSLHYjbtYbzK1-p9Qt_zJfbYoi6PGdRg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Usually my go to place for UFC fights but unfortunately this is my first complaint. Food was good like always but the service was probably the worst I've ever had in my life.

From the get go it took around 30 minutes to get my first drink and get food ordered(arrived at 530pm and it was dead). And from then on it took roughly 30 minutes to order a new drink everytime. We had to start ordering 2 drinks at a time to combat this. I don't know if my and friend and I are that ugly but it seemed like our waitress wanted nothing to do with us. Never asked us how our food was and 3 hours in, half our table was full of plates because she wouldn't take them(I didn't say anything cause I wanted to see how long it would take).

Nights like this we usually drop around $200 per person. Today was about $80 per person due to the lack of service and it wasn't that busy. We would've spent more if we were able to.

At the end I grabbed the both our tabs and opted to not leave a tip. She took the receipt, looked at it and threw it in front of me, gave me a passive aggressive "have a great night" and walked away. Like if you hate your job that much just quit.

Sorry BP Nordel but we won't be back. I hope she doesn't scare away any more customers for your sake.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO26vy9XZ94PJCjhUJrNBYaNe6yvoQ9PXTvRTYn&fid=0x0:0x9c4803b090bd3282"],"When":"2024-6-2"},{"Name":"Ashraf Rajan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLZ9zUW6cOZjf-Iuzby4BlIAcLcMAtU6qRwxNFvboqY82228g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is our usual BP- John on the lounge side was great, he has been our server our last few visits. He is courteous, efficient and great to chat with! user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Ambreen Shayan Jiwa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocItG5lawIQ8vCJkDAy7Vi2ir3oYGvHahPNJUimX4Q5kFGRiBQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had our first dining experience at this place on Sunday, and it was truly memorable! I absolutely loved the beef nihari paired with butter and garlic naan – such a perfect combination. We also ordered Karahi, nihari, biryani, white rice, and naan. While the nihari was outstanding, I feel the biryani and Karahi could be improved. However, the overall experience was fantastic!

The customer service was exceptional, and the portions were generous for the price. The staff was incredibly friendly and accommodating, which made the meal even more enjoyable. As a lovely gesture, they treated us to complimentary halwa, and we ended our dinner with chai that was simply delightful.

Though they forgot to pack our rice, we went back the next day, and they more than made up for it. Not only did they provide fresh rice, but they also surprised us with complimentary pudding, which truly made our day. Their effort to ensure customers leave happy speaks volumes about their dedication.

I absolutely love this place, the food, and the wonderful staff. It’s my new go-to spot, and I can’t wait to visit again ! :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOc8_JF-qMMVvu9gxZGjKby0nRXfu109PE4_u9_&fid=0x0:0x2ad142169329c803"],"When":"2024-11-19"},{"Name":"Mome Gul Hussain","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWiL1X3cC7fXdd0lDgy8_Qkd_vGlNUJA7-IAryj3jW7mNMV8Qhd=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went to Zaiqa for the first time and we enjoyed everything we ordered.  Their barbecue is sizzling hot and well done.  We asked for everything mild and they tried their best to accommodate us.

The chicken kharahi was also delicious but next time I would ask for less oil.

Their service was amazing.  Our waitress made sure we got the barbecue first and then waited until we were ready to bring the main course.

Will come here again!  Good Pakistani food ♥️","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOS5Ix9bLl0mfXnYv0is3llnIa39xi6kjXJzmTH&fid=0x0:0x2ad142169329c803"],"When":"2024-6-16"},{"Name":"Sazzad Hossain","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK5JzPg_HbQTCfL-RL2N4qcAmAyjkRuMRE7Ps-o51NovewMwA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Had dinner with family. All the food was delicious except the chicken dum biriyani. The biriyani was definitely not fresh. Mutton Karahi and Spicy Fish Fry was very good. So was Chicken Malai Boti Kabab. The portion was huge and we made the mistake ordering more than what we could eat. Overall good dining experience. Highly recommended.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPgO-3wHDFuZZcEIILNpGw4sGn_vLZugToi0whT&fid=0x0:0x2ad142169329c803"],"When":"2024-9-12"},{"Name":"Zohaib Khan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocInqpW_ukF-xdqFrg9EpUave-0STedwoC4IBw40rUqVb7lTCA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Not bad but would not try it again.  The pace of customer service is slow and nihari was mildly warm.   The space is extremely tight especially the unneeded design of table legs.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM0fNI3AuF3e4Hxr-UfwXvUE3n6POFUqy089GcN&fid=0x0:0x2ad142169329c803"],"When":"2024-10-28"},{"Name":"Noori Videography","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVmvA2KxAOBAZa1LXJyhwOOOpA_olClaygAyivsmLb3wY2TKD5E=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I am sharing these photos so everyone can have access to their menu.
The food was really good, service was perfect. The only reason I gave them 4 star is because there were some mosquitos when we were eating and they bothered us 3 to 4 times.
Overall it’s one of the best places to go and have Halal food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOMVjrSenqdxR7otIGXNOyQ57gxBFwidatESBI4&fid=0x0:0x2ad142169329c803"],"When":"2024-8-9"},{"Name":"S H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKp3LJKRD3uSU_ba2FJjRbfwQin7qfmkU1gaUcNx-FCKpdXCw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Unexpectedly stumbled upon this little gem, and it was by far the best Pakistani food we’ve ever  had. We had Lahori Chargha, Shinwari Mutton Karahi and butter chicken. All were divine, but the Chargha was to die for. Exceptional service and experience. Thank you. We’ll definitely be back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNKAfe8cvEpeirfx48DVFIxDBAK2BSrDSJRWNBh&fid=0x0:0x2ad142169329c803"],"When":"2024-8-26"},{"Name":"AWAIS THE BOSS","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWFR2cYPf0wPxYiA1s-uSEkyon-hcTMvm8LJq6BY3cw9K_NYCzp=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Zaiqa Restaurant is one of my favorite spots for buffet dining, offering an incredible variety of dishes that cater to diverse tastes. During my recent visit, I was impressed by the balance of quality and quantity. The buffet spread featured an array of dishes, including authentic Mughlai curries, biryanis, freshly baked naans, and a variety of flavorful kebabs. The highlight for me was the live barbecue station, where the chefs prepared succulent, smoky meats right in front of us.

The vegetarian options were equally satisfying, with dishes like paneer tikka masala and a rich, creamy dal makhani standing out. The salad bar was fresh and vibrant, offering lighter options to balance the meal. For dessert, the spread included traditional sweets like gulab jamun and kheer alongside cakes and pastries, ensuring there was something for everyone.

The ambiance of Zaiqa is warm and welcoming, with attentive staff who made sure our dining experience was seamless. The restaurant was clean and well-maintained, and the food stations were replenished regularly. What stood out to me was the value for money – the buffet offers a premium experience without being overly expensive. I left feeling satisfied and looking forward to my next visit. If you love diverse, flavorful food, Zaiqa is a must-visit!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipObiZi_laiRwXBOl_0W8HrJW15wraVurZNvk4aN&fid=0x0:0x2ad142169329c803"],"When":"2024-12-16"},{"Name":"Khizer Rathore","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKe6vYwQ2CYBs84GAien2aRZdmoUBiyD93lfD7Dr_ZfeSD5WA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Came to this place with my best friend. Really loved the food (Darbari meat platter was amazimg). Employees and manager were very nice and hospitable. We were surprised when at the end we were given free chai, loved the place overall and will definitely come back when we get the chance.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMFUKuDzr98xNChqtcG1RK5oFYvaizvIsSp0P6V&fid=0x0:0x2ad142169329c803"],"When":"2024-9-2"}]

user_reviews: [{"Name":"Ayesha Goonesekere","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLWGmgkdQEbWhbfzpAU_EjOXM0Mcy-oGBte6ptZvh_UTzLpzg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If you're searching for an authentic taste of Mexico, look no further than \"Dos Amigos\". This gem of a restaurant offers a culinary journey that tantalizes the taste buds and transports you straight to the heart of Mexico. From the moment you step through the door, you're greeted with warm hospitality and a vibrant ambiance that sets the stage for an unforgettable dining experience.\nNow, onto the main event—the food. Prepare to be dazzled by a menu that boasts a delightful array of Mexican delights, each dish bursting with flavour and made with the freshest ingredients. Whether you're craving classic favourites like Tacos and Burritos or eager to try something new like Baja Fries, \"Dos Amigos\" delivers with authenticity and flair.\nIn conclusion, \"Dos Amigos\" is a five-star dining destination that combines exquisite cuisine, vibrant ambiance, and top-notch service to create a truly unforgettable experience. Whether you're a seasoned foodie or simply looking for a taste of Mexico, this restaurant is a must-visit.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNJKVo0-8v2FuR8zVsvFREJUtXuuXjzWWpIsOg\u0026fid=0x0:0x9b3267e69b167c65"],"When":"2024-2-15"},{"Name":"AJ R","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLo4tIvUrcwNXdNPm8MhPpZgzsQXb-_lGpW8MEceFXJ5buZ1dI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dos Amigos offers a taste of authentic Mexican food as well as a few deliciously unique items. The California burrito is my favourite on the menu, but you can’t go wrong regardless of what you choose. The Baja Fries are deliciously loaded with all kinds of good stuff and their food is packed with flavour. The staff is consistently wonderful. I strongly recommend coming here to try out their food or finding their food truck around the city!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPzAwnsiFIOeDyKldhDNYM7p-g91GSxJ6jkS96R\u0026fid=0x0:0x9b3267e69b167c65"],"When":"2024-4-8"},{"Name":"I. C.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWTNWiJiousbYFXzfbHov9vOwA0UYMWBqO5aZRJpHZNKdWU7hNI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Highly anticipated Dos Amigos Tex-Mex has opened their restaurant location in Delta! I visited them tonight and the foods are as amazing as their food truck and now with the comfortable eating experience at the restaurant! The service was awesome and their chefs always make sure the foods are hot when they serves it to you. They have a few items that are only available at the restaurant! 😉 So definitely look forward to come back again!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPsL0x8jxRoqzKxanx5rUMCbziFJu1mD61sHM9R\u0026fid=0x0:0x9b3267e69b167c65"],"When":"2024-2-18"},{"Name":"Wesley Parker","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVaDH2JPeGPZgw6Q4OU0xJpIL3eZp_7GDwcFtYnT6kOIdaO470=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is our second year having Dos Amigos catering our fall community party and it was another great success. Great food. Friendly faces. Definitely would recommend for your next event.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM4oQ8644FtXLzkBg84oDozm8RBhPN_Zd-nijZz\u0026fid=0x0:0x9b3267e69b167c65"],"When":"2024-9-11"},{"Name":"Ash Fernandes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU3oPFVQR8x8ozO3y-w9Wgj0XPrhmlTMQ7lmwCGr9pnvSmiBLxr=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dos Amigos Tex Mex will never disappoint you! user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Anne Bandejo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJpzaJELo0GxrfTA0EO0Gpgr5MHPWoIDk-eZWKz5286ue3SlQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We have been here so many times before this review. Me and my husband consider this restaurant the best Filipino Restaurant we have been to in BC.
Food is good but presentation is excellent. Meaning food per se has some room for improvement but how they plate their dishes is well thought of in my opinion.
I would say it is a gem every Filipino and Filipino dish loving Canadians need to discover.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMuwDcCA2ELKewJYxtY0v0JAGzHBV4aPBDe1sL2&fid=0x0:0x5e00bc0bd8602a01"],"When":"2024-2-26"},{"Name":"Michelle ROQUE","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVD5Ft2yZYkozXs1swLhpIu0nnpqHjqQIX3ls8oMAIBKwcM8hbs=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"All the dishes are good!!
Clean environment.
Servants were nice & polite.
Prices per dish:from $13- $20","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOqTfHd4__K05ZtMgZOMWruL7IwLjGeTvOwYkIf&fid=0x0:0x5e00bc0bd8602a01"],"When":"2024-12-17"},{"Name":"Daniel Nguyen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWuNUvmwvw8AcLQ688TX5PDDz6FyvOl-76asYWzHQaFu9x2IzjvAQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Lumpia Shanghai was fried in old oil. The rolls were dark and slightly bitter

Tapsilog was so dry it was literally the same as beef jerky with no flavour. The salsa that came with was clearly a couple days old because the tomato’s were all soggy and chewy

Chicken sisig was so salty I got nauseous 1/3 of the way through. The meat was brown from the extreme amount of  sauce they used.

Kwekwek was absolutely over fried and the batter wasn’t fresh.

Avoid at all costs…. Considering that other restaurants like epic grill are nearby.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNEqDZEdG2e41ynMBF7m1alsWCdobjku1XwL1eB&fid=0x0:0x5e00bc0bd8602a01"],"When":"2024-7-20"},{"Name":"Edgar Ignacio","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV7oexz4qXoBKr6ujKuYxwMvlf16ckv-ovFMKFmC4nzUqeMSoelFA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This Pinoy restaurant is truly exceptional! The customer service is top-notch; they promptly replaced our undercooked barbecue without hesitation. The servers are fantastic, ensuring our water was topped up before we even ran out. I highly recommend this place for an outstanding dining experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOuxd-S2GXLR0KDvzzo6kP3QE_8h85jp7NWoQPQ&fid=0x0:0x5e00bc0bd8602a01"],"When":"2021-2-6"},{"Name":"Robert D. Serrano (Dombet)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLR_5ygdPJ2yTk5BPVoia-A-wQcfDBneny4142q_0o9TVyh1yU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The service at this restaurant was excellent.
The staff was polite and attentive, going above and beyond to provide a wonderful eating experience. The was delicious! Great value for money! The portions were generous and the taste is exceptional. We definitely recommend this restaurant to our friends and family back in Kelowna BC , if they ever visit in Surrey BC.

La Mezza Grill is a great restaurant!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Richard Glasner","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVlFSX_UUx6rW0lix6i7dkX9lVOSyBZB-F5xxqlskw_ZqxWVSPR=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Just went to the attached store to get my wife Filipino foods and decided to  try out the restaurant as we are looking for good food from her home land. [{"Name":"Munro Stuff","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWj0Wcuk6ox5dfAeJ4fAaMbhX_F-nzzt3p5oc_f0hBd0NpbGSM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Samosas were a good size and pretty tasty, but on the greasy side. Dipping sauce was just okay. Service wasn't very friendly.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOx4e3fy4Wbwuc_R2AVFxKnOc4xOJbVkVJGJHZA&fid=0x0:0xeb80e44cf0ad9cde"],"When":"2024-11-6"},{"Name":"Karan Verma","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXWihmhxBivvzIZnhihtWNCltuvgnwqnp8QHTn_L10JQlGd3LQbhA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The overall experience at this restaurant has consistently exceeded our expectations. We have become frequent visitors due to the consistently exceptional quality of the food. Each time we dine here, we are met with flavors that are both bold and satisfying. The dishes are expertly prepared, showcasing the chef's skill and attention to detail.

One aspect that stands out is the remarkable speed at which our orders are served. It's impressive how quickly the food arrives at our table without compromising its quality. This efficient service adds to the overall enjoyment of the dining experience.

Furthermore, the staff at this restaurant deserves commendation for their attentive and friendly service. From the moment we step through the door, we are warmly welcomed and made to feel like valued guests. Their knowledge of the menu and willingness to accommodate any special requests further enhance our dining experience.

In terms of affordability, this restaurant truly stands out. The prices are more than reasonable considering the outstanding quality of the food and the level of service provided. It's refreshing to find such a combination of excellence and affordability in one place.

Apart from the savory dishes, we have also explored the sweet side of the menu, and we were not disappointed. The desserts offered are a testament to the culinary skill present in this establishment. Whether it's a delectable cake or a mouthwatering pastry, each bite is a delight to the taste buds.

In summary, this restaurant has consistently impressed us with its exceptional food, speedy service, friendly staff, and reasonable prices. It has become our go-to place for a satisfying meal, and we highly recommend it to anyone looking for a memorable dining experience. Whether you're craving savory delights or indulgent desserts, this restaurant is sure to leave you thoroughly satisfied.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP1k6_nBE3ii_KwfumUVZ3ovO0cIkDhyrY6qdvX&fid=0x0:0xeb80e44cf0ad9cde"],"When":"2023-5-15"},{"Name":"Emily Wong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL5bA-Xs_JlP7CP18cRm7Tdhg7AlD6yMRzCOimrSNOFT2zx4A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Diamond sweets has become one of my all-time favourites. Every time we order the food is absolutely delicious and the left overs are just as good! Definitely one of my go to comfort foods and will be a customer for many years to come!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNAiC3_QBi5QSvfnTdexqetfNLxCtRkv-2LNaS4&fid=0x0:0xeb80e44cf0ad9cde"],"When":"2023-8-23"},{"Name":"Lorraine Clement","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKN2aaC3dpWM1PjjhRmZ0XmNC-R_fOAMbas1Bej8qGsLb5aCg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Bought 12 pieces Samosas take out, 8 chicken samosas and 4 veggies samosas.
For 12 samosas they only give 2 small tamarind sauce. I asked for another one but apparently I have to pay for it.
What a ripoff.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipODJc24hMWSQLjRokZ9v4u3pTrOS8_YZtqqcl-Y&fid=0x0:0xeb80e44cf0ad9cde"],"When":"2024-5-2"},{"Name":"Aanandita sharma","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJkeIC75lZyV0zPbQry6TKMuMJtXmmFbMwjDEzhLV6J_YOHfg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I ordered samosas at this restaurant and while I was waiting there, I saw this fly(insect) sitting on there sweets. When I told the associate working there about the fly, she just started at me for a second and she literally ignored me and didn’t bother clearing it up. This is the second time I have encountered an insect on the sweets at this place. Also, I have found a hair in there chana bhatura before. This kind of service is not at all acceptable. Worst place ever","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOgihaB9i3noE1eIYp5LpAjp1Ew1U4St5I9HGTr&fid=0x0:0xeb80e44cf0ad9cde"],"When":"2023-12-24"},{"Name":"Amandeep Kaur","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK-WmyorsmMYaNgeFZNJaMcL_waRVqYi2F099r2hu2XIdfRSg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This location is absolutely a great . They all are very welcoming specially girl Sukh who was really nice .","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shil","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXsV7Li5Jgp9k-xPSTQtrZkig3UUhG1qRg9w_h_92fFwUVGvDyV=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"It's a good place for eating quickly and is reasonably priced too.
