user_reviews:
[{"Name":"D SAM","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVAPZJhKwbwofRMAxzu-Q9mFomEMmhsUcyi8-_CMghvFMl0UXMbEw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Ordered Tofu Pancit for take out which was not on the menu. They happily accommodated. I enjoyed it very much. The aroma of garlic was really strong if you are fond of it. I would’ve much preferred it though if there were more vegetables like broccoli, snap peas, mushrooms among others not just carrots and celery. Food always cooked fresh. The staff are friendly in person and over the phone.

Came at another time and ordered sisig and chopsuey . Food was freshly cooked.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM7T1-eLpsT2XiZlp4f7nGzDqJM2Ve7pmvwePnN&fid=0x0:0x82b70a1f6fc39e88"],"When":"2023-11-27"},{"Name":"Rnie Javier","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUWHBJV1K3x0Py3tvNiDVtisKTRGCoVAv4fDYdGg2N10daP8wS2=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"If you like Filipino food and would like a restaurant that is not ‘turo-turo’ style then this is a good place to come try. The menu has a lot of different options to choose from. The sinigang and pork bbq are generally my favourite Filipino food and the flavours are on point with how they should taste. However, I wouldn’t say anything is pulling me to come back. Also, the service is not very attentive.. they do not come and check in on you at all. If you need something you have to go up to the counter to get their attention. Overall, this is an authentic Filipino restaurant that I would recommend to others if try if they never had our cuisine and don’t already have a Filipino friend to feed them this food at their home ;)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPwKAv-tRF0HQOZQudhcFOOdGFNKWzp7sSo6jEN&fid=0x0:0x82b70a1f6fc39e88"],"When":"2022-7-18"},{"Name":"Rupert Cruz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXt8ml-zyELcJn5n7mbMObX0OVwwAVyqI04N4IqTyH4TJ2dVGE=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I will be as fair as I can. We dined-in 6pm Sunday evening as we are in a habit of supporting family owned restaurants in our city. There were only another couple at the restaurant who are almost done and are about to leave. So in short, my wife and I are the only customers in the restaurant at that moment. We are courteously given 2 glasses of water together with the menu... would be better if it was followed by a nice "hello/good evening" gesture. They are not rude, but not pleasant either.

We are starving and ready to order. Unfortunately, we have to catch their attention to let them know we are ready. The servings came in not long after. Food is okay but the portions you get for what you pay is not acceptable. Expensive to say the least. Isang platitong inihaw na liempo costs us $18.75, Pancit Canton for $16.50 (good for 1 person).

At this point we are THE ONLY CUSTOMER inside the restaurant, yet our glasses of water wasn't re-filled and not one crew passed by to check on us if everything's okay.

When we were done and ready to pay, we are waiting if they would at least take a glance on us. I guess we can just storm out and they wouldn't even notice. I finally just called their attention and paid my bill shortly. Again, WE ARE THE ONLY CUSTOMER PRESENT THAT TIME.

Food portions and service really need to improve. I dont mind paying a premium so long as it is worth it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOdKx2wqThbm5z88AO5ox9A8V-Q99z5LeTdzq3y&fid=0x0:0x82b70a1f6fc39e88"],"When":"2023-10-23"},{"Name":"Cheska Ferolino","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXiXbF7Xn7d5rwIp_rXgYIbDlVgBfLQEe-Wkodr7Do6Mr3l80Jq=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Ordered sisig with pork bbq thru doordash today . Everything taste so good until i felt something was sharp and lucky didnt swallow it .","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNputaqr9uqlll7PZ4Caxkx2NDncfBganc2-Fvy&fid=0x0:0x82b70a1f6fc39e88"],"When":"2024-5-12"},{"Name":"Liane Villarin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJb99wshYftg9gkbUpPO4Xfy9DjJeZ0hQzGJpXD8gNW0Phq_A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"We just had our family dinner here tonight and we are the only customer at the moment. Unfortunately, the food is not good as before. The red flag is when we order the whole egg pie for our dessert, and when we're starting to slice it to put it into small plates, we noticed MOLDS on the top of the egg pie. Like it was from their display fridge with lots of food inside. Was thinking, isn't all the food in there is contaminated? Nasty. Horrible. Unacceptable.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Desiree Gache","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWMZ4KiKCrQ5mJQ089Xq8HgurbxXWSxUZe08xGwBK16BUbL5EpQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I usually order for takeout from here and my favourites are the lumpia and dinuguan, a little pricey but the food is so good it’s worth it. They also have a big variety of different dishes which I like so I would definitely recommend","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cristina","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWoN4uAgedw6IPp-TuJoYuwBVPII_f6vTjOwYXgMMvIHnobRtM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"We dine in here last sunday and about to order the server gave us the menu with a paper and pencil and told us to write down our order. No eye contact with customers if we need something we have to stand and go to the front and ask them. Food is ok nothing special. The Richmond location is better than here.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Maxxie Espiritu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK7Shst6JzjmLm6iM_c1vcFzXQtk1wIK_Uz4u4sm-151ZyR7w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"We bought pancit palabok small party tray cost of $65. We send back the palabok because you can taste the used oil,dry and bitter after taste. We ask them to taste it and as per the cook he said it’s fine.We requested for refund or atleast half of the price but they said it was already half and I said yes it was because it was thrown on the garbage when we try to eat .According to the staff still under review by the owner to decide for the refund and they will call us back still nothing. They have new cook now no wonder their foods taste different. I don’t recommend this restaurant.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Jaspreet Singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX09QhfmDtxlFV3WckJosIM0mBEvtFOZtFUKR9VV5SLouQGps8h=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fresh Slice, a popular pizza chain, often receives positive reviews for both the quality of its food and the service provided by its staff. Here are some common highlights mentioned in reviews:

Great Pizza Quality: Customers consistently praise the freshness of the ingredients and the taste of the pizza. The crust is often described as light and crispy, while the variety of toppings allows for a customizable experience.

Quick Service: Many reviews note that Fresh Slice is known for its fast and efficient service, particularly during busy hours. The pizzas are typically prepared and served quickly without sacrificing quality.

Friendly Staff: Customers frequently mention the friendly and welcoming demeanor of the staff. Reviewers appreciate how staff members engage with them, creating a positive, pleasant experience at the restaurant.

Affordable Prices: Fresh Slice is also praised for offering good value for money. Their pricing is often seen as reasonable, especially considering the quality and portion sizes.

Clean and Comfortable Environment: Many people appreciate the cleanliness of the locations and the comfortable atmosphere, making it a good place for casual dining with family or friends.

Overall, Fresh Slice is highly recommended for those looking for tasty pizza at an affordable price, with many customers highlighting the attentive and friendly staff as an added bonus.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ramandeep Kalsi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI8s3o_xLhYjstMy3R-6Yl1luXHq_Ya3qpQRUpAXRx0PHs07WQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Pizza was great, pretty clean place, the guy was great, friendly and suggested the best deal. user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Jay Singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUKd0kfX1MQvPvRKGk-shQIJ7xXwI945y_qFolUS1rm1Sj_iuEM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing! Drove 70 minutes to get here and it was well worth the trip.

Their dosas are fresh, crispy on the outside, soft on the inside, and definitely flavourful.

We ordered two different kinds and both arrived with ample filling. The accompanying sambar was full of flavor, screaming "freshness".

Their coconut and spicy chutnees are on point --- not too spicy but definitely packing heat :-)

The venue has a low key, small business vibe.

The interior decor has cool cartoon murals, and the staff are responsive, considerate, and attentive.

Service is quick and the seating area, serving dishes, and cutlery are all clean and well maintained.

We will definitely be back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOHt3IcM0ikyYP8OwSPdHBzQGoJ2XRrzouQSB03&fid=0x0:0x1b8344423d85ddb0"],"When":"2024-12-8"},{"Name":"Suresh Mokana","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXj50jH37kOlzVUA6QZ8y-2AYs5_cGOQ58Hi0wHSj2wo5oVgJpDnw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Dosa enthusiasts can try this place, although the biryanis may not meet expectations. [{"Name":"Sagar Ghevde","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUitU8STg7kqtTuY_zwHZI-IFfb4KvcO243KQ80Dr3LIfwA4snmgA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Kathmandu Bar and Grill offers a cozy atmosphere and a delicious selection of authentic Nepalese dishes, including popular options like momos and flavorful curries. The staff is welcoming and the food is rich with traditional spices, making it a great spot for anyone looking to try something different. While service can be a bit slow during busy times, the overall dining experience is enjoyable, with reasonable prices and generous portions. It's an excellent choice for casual dining and exploring Nepalese flavors.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMfUoq6L6ExEPoc_nrjGh9biFbgin3AkkXS7vZU&fid=0x0:0x85fe86fbbce82bcd"],"When":"2024-10-16"},{"Name":"Julie Wong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIPmd5iDJyTKCeIx6n2PB-cxz_JZewAB3u_T7KLww-OPs1Q_Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Diverse flavors and excellent use of different herbs and spices. The space is generally quiet, and I see a lot of people ordering takeout from here.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNt0ilXtSKguIL756JT0Wrjq-N7cajEH3rLCUg6&fid=0x0:0x85fe86fbbce82bcd"],"When":"2024-7-27"},{"Name":"Monster Alive","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVBCwzV2fBW-aqNyUDo9PAn82ZOw7tIyMywMxsXRX6v-VhwqPEe=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Outstanding Food, Disappointing Customer Service Experience

I visited Kathmandu Bar and Grill on a Friday night, expecting to enjoy a pleasant dining experience. While the food was undeniably excellent, our overall experience was marred by disappointing customer service.

We arrived around midnight, as the restaurant advertised closing at 1 o'clock. Upon inquiry, we were informed that the last order would be taken at 12:45, which seemed reasonable. We proceeded to order, thoroughly enjoying the Nepali traditional soup and other appetizers.

However, our dining experience took a turn for the worse when we attempted to order our main course around 12:30. Despite the restaurant not yet reaching its supposed closing time, we were abruptly informed that the kitchen was closing and they would not be able to take our order. This was incredibly frustrating and made us feel uncomfortable, especially since we had already made our dining plans for the evening.

While we appreciated the offer of takeaway, it was disappointing to be denied the opportunity to enjoy a sit-down meal as originally intended. The discrepancy between the advertised operating hours and the actual service provided was unacceptable, leaving us with a sour impression of an otherwise promising establishment.

In summary, while Kathmandu Bar and Grill boasts outstanding food, the subpar customer service experience leaves much to be desired.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMbCpL6DbilHV_r3Y23qMaWcjTXt1FDSqK3ZVj6&fid=0x0:0x85fe86fbbce82bcd"],"When":"2024-4-25"},{"Name":"Gurkirat","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW5rNVJu0-bVM9CBg1YbKcpRzQD610AZj9oSPpTB4GRGKRviE3n=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The food is  good, but the service was really bad.  Also we spent a total of $120. I still left hungry. I suggest that they increase their portion size because the large chow mein will only feed one person and the chilli chicken is also very less according to $20 for a large, the platter was good but jhol momos were average","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipObU4daYcyGEZGvVCH30tGDj_eVyvAId-Oix96L&fid=0x0:0x85fe86fbbce82bcd"],"When":"2024-5-19"},{"Name":"Aditi Bhavsar-Vaidya","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXJfnrP4b6L_aruXJcdyMiWuTJNssQeB-jV5H_Q-V35MXID4oJu=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The restaurant is great with wonderful ambience. Complete Nepal vibes- the decor and traditional Nepali songs playing in the background!
Very hospitable staff. Tried Jhol-Momos, they are super delicious! Decent food portion and reasonable rates.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPYfjZD6UZHXfBWrBlfREUH4SBq5YU7zbvPIyNQ&fid=0x0:0x85fe86fbbce82bcd"],"When":"2024-7-24"},{"Name":"Sukhpreet Singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUOPusrGcOR1FCQcbw_WpLDK9PP3Yf5_3ev0Ctt6flBY5xajt5rjA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great food and sweet workers. The owner is really sweet as well. He was making sure we were being served well by a new employee and also gave us a free meal since our order was mistaken. Prices are reasonable as well. Would recommend it for sure!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kanu Sharma","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUqjz7Y1Odhsn6eQ1YKb_xjFrYNr1IrQD4j66zWHOCrIl7uVfDY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Its a good place if you are craving chinese/nepalese cuisine. I was craving for thukpa so visited it. We ordered veg thukpa, monchow soup, steamed momos, chilli momos, mushrooms, nepalese noodles. Everything was served quickly. Servers were polite. Food was delicious. We customized spice level as medium and i think we did the right thing. Ambience was soothing with touch of buddhist culture in the background. They do have deal of the day but sadly it was not available the day we went. So a bit disappointed coz the pamphlet in the table mentioned about deal of the day which we can get free if the server doesnt inform us about it. But when asked it wasn’t available. That feels like a fake promise to a customer. But otherwise it was affordable and delicious. Will surely visit again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMwN0iZtZe-UsFeAi75krCF0oF8bkFmjrhm_nYH&fid=0x0:0x85fe86fbbce82bcd"],"When":"2024-3-15"},{"Name":"Rahul Sharma","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWh6de9c5krsyJ_mb57qMO72iLvs-oKOPq6EMT8NHgITXxm3OhT=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was impressed! The Hakka Noodles were on point and loaded with veggies, while the Chicken Burger was juicy and seasoned perfectly. The vibe was chill, and the staff was super friendly and helpful. Definitely worth a visit - I'd rate it an 8 out of 10.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMMPm0E9YutaS0cTTVaKWKEupD0q0Mz5k7G2Nqx&fid=0x0:0x85fe86fbbce82bcd"],"When":"2023-4-26"}]

[{"Name":"Safesaif_ 21","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVdWJ6aoYbvHsfGcXWimREVk4QyQMSCYyeceILzMwqjvtobBR28=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Such a chill spot to have some really good halal food. The double crunch burger and the loaded fries are the best. And don’t even get me started on the mango milkshake 🤤","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPUVy9C665ejA3OLMfP_0F_05rXxSWNpkyMTzKU&fid=0x0:0x74e48e7000e7ef20"],"When":"2024-10-13"},{"Name":"Hamza Hydri Syed","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWXQMloeZZXC5acdLr6-P3HFLpQP_ZypzL4n0k4ALz2HPa4qXyHkg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We have stopped here to grab a bite couple of times when visiting Vancouver. The food is typical Pakistani cuisine - good selection of burgers and Mughlai. I loved their Chicken Karahi (which goes well with their Butter Naan). Their Biryani is good, very tasty and typical Karachi version. The kids love their burgers and chicken wings. Ambience is good and family friendly. Serving could be improved, the single person taking orders, serving and cleaning up was difficult task.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOgjFTf6Z4oyF06stNGL8GmmfMJk6i4glkfuhCc&fid=0x0:0x74e48e7000e7ef20"],"When":"2024-10-19"},{"Name":"Shery On The Move","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVmAA3VItm5d-LzZjMzSS_FZs12aHSse1X5w-nXQqVmdbUvhBBJ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I didn't expect I would be so impressed when I come and dine in here. Here are the compliments that I want to highlight. ⬇️

The restaurant is cosy, with a nice atmosphere and a beautiful table with a bell/call button attached.

I ordered loaded fries, cheese bombers, mega crush burger, and philly cheese steak burger.

Loaded Fries
If you are familiar and favourite of loaded fries American style like me, you will like it here. Even though the portion is not big like American style but it's full enough for two people sharing. I very much like the combination taste of sauce, cheese, cilantro, etc. It's a twist of South Asian style, and overall, it's flavourful.

Cheese Bombers
I expect cheese bombers to be like a chicken popcorn size, but it came with a huge size! 5 pieces are good enough because they're full with cream cheese inside it (with jalapeno).

Mega Crush Burger
I don't know how to comment about this burger. Double thumbs up 👍🏻 👍🏻.

Philly Cheese Steak Burger
It's good, but the meat is not that much. I totally can understand the price I paid for this burger.

I went to the ladies' toilet and I'm very satisfied with the cleanliness but my husband said men toilets are not good.

Kudos to the waiter who worked that day because she's amazing, friendly, and attentive. Please keep up the good work whether it's on peak hour or not.

Date of visit : 2 June 2024
Time : 9:00pm-9:52pm","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOLak-R-gpv1NqeLVAGVVY3j5UuNaP0xeWgUMu5&fid=0x0:0x74e48e7000e7ef20"],"When":"2024-6-5"},{"Name":"J. A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXYN8Bfqly5qLcn9ccU2neEREXryexnxM7M2bRJCuWPZG91P4jN=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Spicy Fried chicken is better than Chicken world. Worth every penny as it’s halal.l and amazing in all ways. Every dish tastes fabulous. We are regular here and will continue to be. Our go to place and its affordable too.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO40T34rEMTbXgyK-i6_wIBbBTHUeOJsKpcGAHe&fid=0x0:0x74e48e7000e7ef20"],"When":"2024-7-7"},{"Name":"Nimrat Kaur","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJOrza_eWiJ_hv7LqrqFD4wRzWp8oOdk8QSaOUN0Q502AutVA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This restaurant is a hidden gem! The food was absolutely incredible — the goat karahi is a must-try. The balance of flavors was spot on, and the ingredients were clearly fresh. I loved the creative take on classic recipes. The ambiance was cozy and perfect for a relaxed evening out. Highly recommend for food enthusiasts!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mahadi Hasan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWfiL2JeXUIO6XBft-JLtjCK1lreoojcMtT3EjzAFDLFxK9ccQHKg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"With all my complement and excitement I went there couple of times more and found out that the quality has been compromised drastically. The biriyani which i loved mostly lost it's charm. Yesterday i went there and took the biriyani.  There were 3 pieces of meats in total but without any leg pieces what used to be with 5-6 leg pieces. They dont have fried chicken anymore. They only have chiken wings and look at the photo. The shape and size of wings. I dont know why they withdrew regular fried chicken. Totally disappointed. It was my 5th visit to them yesterday but it won’t happening again. I am not going there anymore.

It was my 2nd visit to them. I went there in brunch buffet and that was pretty good. Last night it was not a buffet but we orders one full chciken biriyani and  4 pieces of fried chicken. I added the photo and you guys can reffer to it. I have got in total 7 pieces of chciken with biriyani alone. It was so satisfying tbh. The fried chciken price is a bit high though (13$ for 4 pieces) but it was worthy enough overall. We have also got a complementary gajar ka halwua from the owner. Its a straight 5 star for them.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMqBH6lqSJURP59AmwaR0tmr1mQh79IoTk2cF1S&fid=0x0:0x74e48e7000e7ef20"],"When":"2024-10-14"},{"Name":"Zeeshan Sohail","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXQzSgXcEIo5d0fY039IL3LLi7k1i-9eyjB9u0xnur9BQekUdtD=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fantastic addition to the local karahi scene. Black pepper heavy Chicken Karahi which has a different kick than a tomato base one. Arguably one of the best Karahi spots in BC. They also happen to serve great Fried Chicken, Karachi Bun Kabab and Fish Burger. Friendly staff and a spacious comfortable dining area. Highly recommended.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMfvOEqGejLHiBx0wcMoJuJybIbxJoS-TDOy63l&fid=0x0:0x74e48e7000e7ef20"],"When":"2023-12-13"},{"Name":"Adhham Farook","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUjlk1T4nE85S8cF73uGl6Bcox-MpnOySZS44DlC3EXuJDnJwJz=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Unpleasant experience!
We dine-in for the Saturday buffet.  There was very little items in the spread.  While eating the chicken Kadai . After noticed the blood in the half cooked chicken,  we all stopped eating and informed the waitress but she seems to not bothered about this! Someone walked up to me and told that they can change the chicken for me but we all lost appetite after seeing the blood. When I went to pay the bill , the same person ( who walked up to me) proudly told that they have given me a 10% discount to compensate the unpleasant experience that we have to go through. Even though I told them I did not eat and they can consider not to change for my meal but they seems to be only happy giving 10% on overall bill. After I asked for the printed bill , the guy told me that he can give a coupon for my next visit. They should had a basic curtsy to say sorry for the experience we have to face and they spoiled my wife's birthday dinner. Thank you for your wonderful service!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMkfGKk6UopJ4BbzWcqRDohVLdKE_cwQMekNNQT&fid=0x0:0x74e48e7000e7ef20"],"When":"2024-10-20"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Matthew Ng","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLy9bXSl0bCSpsYP99yXuPAW_5FwxGPENTl6uhu9DC87YI9Ew=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Most Authentic Chinese Seafood Restaurant In Surrey/Delta.

Definitely everyone’s go to spot for affordable (from$15-20) high quality chinese food and dim sum.

I have been there numerous times. Never had to wait for a table ever. Their service is always quick and efficient. Their food is always prepared fresh and at a great price.

I recommend coming here and supporting local chinese businesses in Surrey, there is not many around.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMgdaVeuEOBus9xrh7K18Kbg_YB7Cp4VWn214SB&fid=0x0:0x3bd80f68e9954cab"],"When":"2024-12-23"},{"Name":"Jason P","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVwQ6VrAafrL568UtVUXBwRugwDfBdgtXm5PLgDAxdMUbNAFin6DA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"When I think of Chinese cuisine, Surrey Delta border area would be the last place that would come to mind. We were glad that we tried this place. Compared to other Chinese restaurants like Neptune Seafood Palace or Lux in Langley. This place was considerably cheaper but did not cut corners on taste and portion.

Definitely authentic Szechuan cuisine that I would visit with family again. Glad we have a place near enough when craving Chinese food. And we don’t have to go all the way to Richmond or Burnaby to satisfy those cravings.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOyArAl5fY7zXFOZknNT-NdKdUguOCSix_45lcM&fid=0x0:0x3bd80f68e9954cab"],"When":"2024-7-4"},{"Name":"Juan Carlos “Juan Carlos Cornejo” Cornejo Alfaro","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWK4DOcCHxY1jpQnKxnbwF-UesUsqTxeScFt7XgsrdyP9nM6xIb=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place is a really good option for Chinese food and some others Asian flavors. The service in this time was great! The food not too salty not too simple, just the right amount, points to the chef! The tables are clean, big for families, the website has the menu! They give you tea and water when you have the dinner. The drinks are excellent too. In general good option and prices are reasonable to the amount you get! You have parking, and washrooms are clean! When you go everybody say thanks you and goodbye!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPFSPAJXpN0N6iH55YqvsMwHtJ3Z6HTIHOy564X&fid=0x0:0x3bd80f68e9954cab"],"When":"2024-4-27"},{"Name":"Edgar Ignacio","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV7oexz4qXoBKr6ujKuYxwMvlf16ckv-ovFMKFmC4nzUqeMSoelFA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"ChongQing on Scott Road is one of my favorite Chinese Restaurant in Surrey. The hospitality here is top-notch, and the staff always make you feel right at home. Servers are always available to cater to your needs and they refill your water before they run out. The ambiance are very nice with soft music playing in the background. You must try their dimsum, it is one of the things this restaurant is known for. I can't get enough of their fantastic lunch combos - not only are they delicious, but they're also incredibly affordable. Every item on their menu is a culinary delight, leaving you satisfied and craving more. Their restroom is also one of the cleanest and well maintained even on busy days. A must-try for anyone looking for a memorable dining experience. Highly recommended!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNEPBR18uOt527dbWqrRSXYMxDl3Z_y1UW2H8D4&fid=0x0:0x3bd80f68e9954cab"],"When":"2020-9-28"},{"Name":"Brandon Lieu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV1l6wN98L8CMs2OejtfywOkLZPKh8R8jVEhQtWEIkzvjWy4Xk9=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Reasonably priced dim sum and good quality. If you want to treat yourself but not drive into Richmond, Vancouver, or Burnaby come here!

The food itself was good, and way better value than the fancy restaurants in Richmond and Vancouver. The service was lacking but it's not surprising as it's the case with most Chinese restaurants on the lower mainland. The restaurant was big and the decor was nice inside.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPALIazpInL0AlepSd0QgwiS6MupGUspNSHsuVA&fid=0x0:0x3bd80f68e9954cab"],"When":"2024-1-7"},{"Name":"Mariena Bui","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU6Nw1jeBXne8haJacgZytBHrMEqU2gmOMAF3l5QWK0CwO3rXPJ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I stumbled across this restaurant online and decided to give it a try and I think the food turned out really great! I got take out and ordered a few things to try. My favourite dish I would have to say is the beef rice noodles.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMJi-KVeIDBa1MhH_eEfPgLSA6rVaXrXocE6rHH&fid=0x0:0x3bd80f68e9954cab"],"When":"2024-6-3"},{"Name":"Brigette Liang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXF1kXER1LlBHb9RdZnWZZc3NBsE5BSLhNihhsmcpKDIULO8mQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I was so disappointed by the level of service I received at the restaurant. My friends and I ordered the fried wontons and when it arrived at the table, it was just fried wonton skin. When we talked to the staff, the manager insisted that there was a small amount of filling in it. I can assure you there was ZERO filing. He would not admit to any wrongdoing or false advertising.

Additionally, throughout dinner the staff kept clearing plates before we were finished eating, even though the restaurant was not full and they didn't have any need for the table. They cleared food that we intended to eat and asked if it was okay to clear it after the fact.

Avoid this restaurant. The food is mediocre and so is the service. I've added a picture to show you how flat the wonton SKIN is. Honestly I should have taken the time to take pictures from many angles to assure you there was no filling, but they kept trying to clear the plate.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOT2NWGVbNldCM1BCUyTQYO6kRgdUOe8Wh7wRmY&fid=0x0:0x3bd80f68e9954cab"],"When":"2024-8-21"},{"Name":"Konackht C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKXCBdANkwZ4yOHkfJssD6q4GBWyH6bKgKSjqdgLXrTPg8_uF0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Food is mediocre, not too good. The staff is problematic. Over the years all the familiar and good staff all left. The waiter staff still there are all lazy. I was there half an hour before closing with the family. No one check if we needed tea refills. When my kid walked over the counter to ask for some tea, the manager and one woman were hiding in the corner, busy counting and dividing cash money from tips. Very lousy service. At least do that AFTER your customers are serviced. Not recommended.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"a Natu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVkkJyNgnmmp-MozHsEh9Z4IsHH5-V_MXErSphecFoISVhBbrQD=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We went in during happy hour at 8:30. It looked pretty busy. However, we were seated quickly.

Absolutely phenomenal service by Olivia. Very attentive and checked on us frequently! Very kind and nice

The drinks were delicious, especially the bellenis. Nats lager was smooth and wasent bitter

The food was pretty good! However, I am a bit peeved at the portion for the new home style potroast, could have used more beef. The cabanara bacon and shrimp were by far the best dish we had. The double patty burger was good and bit dry and saucy, causing the bun to get soggy towards the end.

The atmosphere does feel a tad outdated, and it was odd that there wasn't anyone dining in the patio despite the propane pyramid heat towers being on.

I would recommend dining at White Spot Scott & 72nd","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNTID8O7SHL6gm-EMkUk4aEe7_j2WGAzHsHEJOr&fid=0x0:0x7800341a68048ef9"],"When":"2024-10-26"},{"Name":"P Nguyen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVlXs2TzM2uknqo2ufsT0wYUNB2JKpkK3UD6GmafGZl0UHRXQ4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The waitress was all alone most of the morning today and did an amazing job. Thank you for such a great experience. We noticed how hard you were working and how many tables you had to cover for the 3 hours we were there! Commendations to you.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Malika Rajput","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXXwjsKSCBTHtrFnPBGQOp04ejp9n9OiuNZfWNOiAiavTLukbdy=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It was our first time here and we ordered chicken broccoli cheese from the mains, the taste, the quality of food, was exquisite, delicious food I must say one of the best food in Surrey. The dessert was yummy too. Khushi and Rachel hosted us very well. Thnks guys for the lovely service.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPfYO2sjFoZ7AMZcwpB6OXCt9jjCJo58ALQ74oJ&fid=0x0:0x7800341a68048ef9"],"When":"2024-7-13"},{"Name":"Amy Chan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUamHxgbXpYwrJI1uE5cJUYfe1wmxOQk5ygeSabzKwSDEQZmU3C=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The dish I order is a bit salty and hard to continue to finish. I sit down 5-10 minsites and no server service me instead service a couple come in after me first. Piss me off. I never have this type service like this at this location.  I suggest this salmon bowl should have rice or pasta on the bottom of the dish otherwise if the taste is salty still have something to cover salty taste.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP7DyCfLW_joZrJCNTqMUN3ISuaMFUZ785bDG45&fid=0x0:0x7800341a68048ef9"],"When":"2022-3-17"},{"Name":"Elaine Krieger","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJqca55JKLo2CtLPs0ypMqXymmEJvPpJYLTfqpCdUCMeqJ2Jw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Went for breakfast on a Saturday, was able to sit with in 5 to 10 minutes. Staff was polite. Saw only one large table which appeared to be almost completed eating. We ordered and had a lengthy wait for our food. On arrival of our breakfast the Benedict egg was cold and a film had formed on the hollandaise sauce. I requested smash potatos and what received was hashbrowns. Had to wave down server to inform and she went back to get the proper potato request. At no time did anyone ask about how either ordered meals were. My partners orange wedges on his fruit plate was old and shriveled. He also indicated his meal was luke warm. The coffee was poor. First watered down then next strong. We were disappointed in the meal considering we haven't ever been disappointed til now at this restaurant. We ate, paid and left. Don't like making a review but quality of food was not on point considering cost to go out now a days. The food this day was a two star at best and service people were polite but didn't check in on meal quality or ask anything else but brought bill when we waved down. Don't expect much but do expect to have a better meal then going to fast food take out place.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Aryan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIT00CLWcaOpcQpmT__3s14Pusgfk_TfBSYLMAr81DWz9ThVA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"We came here for late lunch. It wasn’t really busy at 4:00pm so it’s very quiet. Great food and decent price. The service was okay, servers were not really friendly except for one who came to asked if we’ve been helped. Our server didn’t offer dessert until we asked. Overall, not so bad.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOxmFX6Kipfkp-ztnph47zubguzQuy1qvHv4Jey&fid=0x0:0x7800341a68048ef9"],"When":"2024-4-20"},{"Name":"Mounika P","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUlrnW_AFUjRmmd7lKhMq5nZT_eiPE-cEtUlqvjcjDqoy9no7qI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I loved their Nat's Caesar drink and Zoo sticks. Rebecca, who served us, was incredibly friendly and went above and beyond to make our meal enjoyable." 😊 Over all, we ordered Zoo sticks, sea food fettuccine, Caesar’s and Teriyaki Chicken Donburi Bowl for our lunch.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMyE0iu9JGb1JBg61F5gF57z6Fc9r7N5b6nj2rO&fid=0x0:0x7800341a68048ef9"],"When":"2023-10-8"},{"Name":"Sid Gautam","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXhQ-Qq3dP0Pl0ECbL5cG0WCU5h5SIOalcy_m_m0chxYSw3KuprxQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Standard as expected, service staff is polite and accommodating.
*Post review update*
Initially I had given them 3 stars, which I thought was fair, as the service and food was as expected and nothing over and above. But White Spot team reached out asking what they could have done to get 5 stars, I didn't reply to them, but bumping up to 4 stars for their consideration. Shows they care about their customers.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Nina Gonn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVYgtJKjrCSOUlyi9_4PJDFRUUPLSNGQKERGyBXxgT7s2s0z-VX=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We have never experienced Afghan food.  This restaurant was recommended to us by a local person in Surrey.  We met my relatives at this restaurant and had a fabulous meal.  It is a small cozy restaurant.  Good food and service.  I live in Washington, state but if I am ever up near surrey again I would go back for sure.  The picture I am including was a 2 person sampler plate.  It looks like a lot of rice but under that mound was also a tender delicious lamb shank.  We chose this because everything sounded good and we could not choose just one or two dishes.  We had quite a bit leftover which we enjoyed the next day.  Worth a try! We 🥰 it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNhF299bAIRSI_D_0BE1PTfzspckRCM52g_TzSe&fid=0x0:0x193a24edded79634"],"When":"2024-11-9"},{"Name":"Jennifer Robin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL7gaaybLnNaTPGBnNOIeI5Ft_r0k4bSz0f4paXDTD087upxg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We tried mantu for the first time, they were delicious! I didn’t want to share them with my husband, next time we will need to order two. The staff were also very friendly. It was all around a great first impression and we will be back! :)

It was our first time trying an Afghan dish, please reply to let me know what to try the next time!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMW4kyLG2a9oJqXc4v8fjyxaytqeADJ-pzCdcue&fid=0x0:0x193a24edded79634"],"When":"2024-12-15"},{"Name":"Hillbillytc","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV833YeKMKJfxtYeKhRHVRSrikZoFOcCapKBwyEFBOnxiCMeXAZ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The atmosphere is cozy. The three dip appetizer, chicken korma and vegetarian mantu (like a gyoza). The waitress was not sure what gluten free meant but she said most of the saucy dishes don’t have flour so they should be gluten free, either is or it is not.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNXEhKBvd4S6JSy5c6nZ3E6Gv-dQUUpPl7wVHHX&fid=0x0:0x193a24edded79634"],"When":"2024-11-15"},{"Name":"Asad Raquib","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU7rtU11CxT0fodBl73a9UEIvQjIX5NMHx0OoO5M21-KUs2CVye=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We ordered a platter for two. It was more than enough food for two people at a great price. The food was really great. I forgot the dishes' name, but it was worth it.
Highly Recommended !","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP4tHVkTBedU7z_idwNIYx7Q8247X2jq1nkb5lf&fid=0x0:0x193a24edded79634"],"When":"2024-11-4"},{"Name":"Macho Ma","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWToXpU3H3YB3xkMOp6uUKU5gePr0KH9w6w89u7rGCD3siyx0IX=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Big portion and the meat is ok with reasonable price
Servers there are nice👍🏻","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPmVHipvlg47H9ioGWS6OziEDNULNIz-N3uFEdi&fid=0x0:0x193a24edded79634"],"When":"2024-12-16"},{"Name":"A & L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKgVx9_IdtWK_-ZI3dVJlsTixCRpCT-hautNr97y_a12jkyWQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We really enjoyed the potato bolani and pakawra (which is a bit potato pakora or bajji in Indian cuisine). We eat a vegan diet and are fairly picky about where we eat; we were missing authentic bolani like the ones our Afghan sister used to make for us when we lived elsewhere; the bolani here tasted just as good, and is quite large too (see photo - wider than one of the chairs). The hummus was average, and had too much garlic for our taste but that's ok. The wait staff Mushavar and Tanu were super friendly as well, for which we're grateful. <3","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPuvkW4r8lV6Y2KQxWDa4Y2S5XZtukP6TZgNfl_&fid=0x0:0x193a24edded79634"],"When":"2024-9-8"},{"Name":"Kevin (KC)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVrZpzDcm4xbgvb_oOynyP_bQvwIe7l-wMoPIs8L4UeVZ-waBkO=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Great Afghan Food in Surrey!

Decided to try out some Afghan Food for some post-workout dinner and found Pamir Diner nearby. It wasn't too busy during dinner time on a Sunday and I was able to get seated right away.

I ordered the following:
- Kabuli Palaw & Lamb Shank
- Beef Kebab
- Qaimaq Chai (pink tea)

The Kabuli Palaw & Lamb Shank was delicious. The lamb meat came right off the bone and complimented the rice really well. The flavors and texture of the dish were great, it reminds me of Biryani which I also love. One Con I would say about the dish is that the side of potatoes and the sauces could be a bit more generous in my opinion.

I also ordered a side of beef kebab which I thought was great flavor wise, but it did seem a bit dry in my opinion.

To top off my meal I decided to try out the Qaimaq Chai (Afghan Pink Tea). It does take some time to prepare since it's made to order, but it was definitely worth it! It was creamy, refreshing and hot to help digest the food.

Service here was great, and the staff were friendly. Interior was clean and cozy with good lighting. Only thing I would mention is regarding the seating - the tables are a bit on the taller side, so unless you're a tall person then it might feel slightly awkward when eating, but honestly it's not a huge deal, just something I observed while dining in. Also they do have TV's inside the restaurant but I noticed it was just being used to play Spotify music - would be pretty nice to have a variety of Afghani music videos playing or something or maybe just have it on the sports channel.

There's plenty of free parking in this lot, so you'll never have to worry about finding where to park. The place is relatively easy to get to as well. It's just along Scott Road (120 ST).

Overall, this is a nice place to grab some Afghani food here in Surrey. Do check them out!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPWmwe5LuEDl8A9IbgaY3r9POZ-RJsi9i2Ny9Ao&fid=0x0:0x193a24edded79634"],"When":"2024-6-10"},{"Name":"Tiana Brw.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUDDTCg5k_MkV2Y6s4oTsX_2MLY-4KNX5OYzIqD2obObePTyqQf=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time having Afghan food.. For 2ppl we order Pamir Platter.. that was amazing and delicious. It’s pretty big portion for two. Server and service is great 👍🏼","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOo8jO7KRPqOw7PlG3WFuptgBb32SDe1VSi_jhi&fid=0x0:0x193a24edded79634"],"When":"2024-10-7"}]

This pizza was loaded (12 toppings) and delicious. Would definitely order again.

user_reviews: [{"Name":"RAVNEET CHEEMA","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKvhwO6Uci6AjBqW7baZKiJu-JAGC4lBWykF7q10awaP8GImw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best Pizza on Scott Road - Must Try their new Shahi Paneer Pizza \u0026 Chipotle Paneer Pizza!\n\nIf you're looking for the best pizza near me in Delta and Surrey this place is a hidden gem! Their Shahi Paneer Pizza and Karahi Paneer Pizza are absolute game-changers. Packed with rich, authentic flavors, both pizzas offer a perfect balance of spice and cheese for a truly mouth-watering experience. As a vegetarian, it's hard to find good options, but their vegetarian pizza selection is vast, and the quality never disappoints. The staff is friendly, and the service is quick. Whether you’re craving something traditional or looking to try something new, this pizza joint is a must-visit for all pizza lovers in Delta and Surrey!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOGZrsznZBLN-y6KFiHGHPXQYvuIPxtRrCt1e1a\u0026fid=0x0:0x8dd5bb037ff7e814"],"When":"2024-10-8"},{"Name":"S.S. S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIqnlpmS2LqkmFx3GKnagT0peZM_wzsT02yD9iVdMiLnjtA_A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I got a pizza ( ordered toppings specifically) and an additional topping was added to it … didn’t ask for it… and when a call back to query the scenario was told it was added to make it taste better. Huh ? Are you eating it ? What happens if someone had an allergy / dislike ? Threw it out. 35 min drive home and we get this ?? Been ordering pizza here for decades and unfortunately the level of empathy has changed with the ownership . Owner couldn’t understand where I was coming from. Was very polite about it when I called and felt disheartened.  I wasn’t rude and felt low listening to the lady.  Please don’t mix me up for another customer. I’m sure you help many people as you are a popular place.  I didn’t call right away.  This owner didn’t value people’s time and money with getting orders right.  Now the gentleman owner there provides great service.  Keep it up !","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Xinwen Chen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI_lPXtoBU_PNOnrlu1KYZTSIHYynMDsK4a2zkUOhUlboCruw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently tried both their pepperoni and Hawaiian pizzas, and I was really impressed! The crust was perfectly crispy, and the toppings were fresh and flavorful. The pepperoni pizza had just the right amount of spice, while the Hawaiian pizza was a great balance of sweet and savory. The service was quick and friendly, and the overall experience was fantastic. Highly recommend this spot for anyone craving delicious pizza!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Aston Chaboyer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ9luQ1RKtVKiYrPxpVcLMEPHxOngYc7TgW7ZzhRDbCwOYKbg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We order from here all the time. user_reviews: [{"Name":"Jacqueline Kinuthia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWEf8DTwHB3_eKgWgcdteQxXAat-nw7g5sdztBtnifcli4_RbTt=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently visited this ice cream shop for the first time, and it was such a wonderful experience! The older gentleman behind the counter was incredibly friendly and welcoming. He took the time to explain the different menu items and even shared some recommendations. The ice cream was delicious, with unique flavors that made it hard to choose. The shop has a cozy, inviting atmosphere, and you can tell they put a lot of care into both their products and their customer service. Highly recommend stopping by if you’re in the area!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNM4IEIfkervspgWzTuvq7Vxp3buQEzmq1L2IvG\u0026fid=0x0:0x23b9ed9c0ec125aa"],"When":"2024-10-27"},{"Name":"Amrita Nayak","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXJgJ3b8LMBlPc7G1Rv8sy6cyH33IeJwYGYkw6c-i8ocBKF5odAKg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This late-night gem is a great spot for satisfying ice cream cravings, staying open until 3 AM. Parking is conveniently available right in front of the shop, making it easy to drop by. The selection of ice cream flavors is impressive, and what's even sweeter is the friendly, welcoming service from the person behind the counter. We also tried their karak chai, which was spot on — strong, flavorful, and perfectly balanced. It’s a fantastic place to unwind, especially when you need a late-night treat.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOTTMBZ7wIPDdJxnp1kleV5iTKZ2Em0losbzYoo\u0026fid=0x0:0x23b9ed9c0ec125aa"],"When":"2024-11-10"},{"Name":"mbaisheka","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV1jUVoX1Q1cFDu0YCF6WUyqzT8JiUsAOfV363X86N7z_4OzV2Y=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"IceCream Wala !!! Best ice cream in town . They have a vast variety of ice cream choices and desserts ranging from scooped ice cream to Falooda to Kulfi  to Paan. They also have a variety of yummy cookies . You have the option to also taste their different icecream choices . We ordered the Karachi special falooda , it was extremely flavourful with a fireworks of a variety of flavours that were utmostly delicious and satisfying at once . The owner is very kind and friendly . The staff are very polite as well . Great decor , music and ambience . We loved our experience and definitely recommend . You won’t be disappointed.  We will be returning customers . No questions asked . 😊","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOdu6n3SDGyP6IcRSSsq7BiKHTinw09v_g-rOxh\u0026fid=0x0:0x23b9ed9c0ec125aa"],"When":"2024-7-20"},{"Name":"Tanisha Sharma","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVQLOvZMBMpbuULuR26tfoj4Ur1VRgXpWfMk7HGW3J9yK0RNa8KCA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ice Cream Wala is the ultimate late-night spot! Whether you’re craving something sweet after dinner or just hanging out with friends, this place hits the mark every time. The vibe is nice, the staff is so friendly, and they make you feel right at home. Their ice creams are amazing, but let me tell you—THE FALOODAS! They’re on another level. Creamy, refreshing, and just perfect. If you haven’t been here yet, you’re seriously missing out!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMR-cUXE6QW5qxgdNlC6MkN57cqGSfji9TIrN3o\u0026fid=0x0:0x23b9ed9c0ec125aa"],"When":"2024-11-16"},{"Name":"Muhammad Shaikh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWQdjWdse-YfR521WDC20Axq29mXN4Dhyt3fqivYTAjlsaQ3qxXyw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Simply amazing in all quality,customer service and on top everything is Halal means(gelatine is plant based). user_reviews: [{"Name":"Ryan Lipscombe","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVQFQFjPiW8rPDeDn9QETTo6TRuWstGhXh8ebbvZaiTERyve7M=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best place to eat if you work in the area. If you're short on time, there's hot food you can pick right away. You can also phone ahead if you want something on the menu and don't want to wait.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMuDRCSnzTXAEg38Gv5PLAOaRFSuscHalhHeIyy\u0026fid=0x0:0x3b16da3a2de176e5"],"When":"2024-11-27"},{"Name":"Farzam","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIooZPCPPfH5D4G1f5pX_06Fqf4UZb5reyqU1DQAFjZqgdcZ04=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My breakfast at Hadi's restaurant was delightful! The owner's warmth and friendliness added an extra charm to the morning. The simple yet spacious setup of the restaurant made for a relaxed start to the day. The breakfast options were delicious and satisfying, offering a perfect way to kickstart the morning. The kind service and pleasant ambiance made this breakfast experience truly enjoyable. I highly recommend starting your day at this place for both the delicious breakfast and the wonderful hospitality!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN2kkKwvzotYxkd94w2arfLISirb_cGPjkCOzfQ\u0026fid=0x0:0x3b16da3a2de176e5"],"When":"2023-12-9"},{"Name":"Jeff Astle","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJqpBD1la32QOHRh35fAqT7JCPqLBjqkr5aE2XHbEfgBcBEOQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The food is delicious all around, and fairly priced. Their business model is making it difficult to justify going, though. Between 11:30 and 1230, expect to wait up to 30 minutes in line. Then after that, they're out of food. Spending more than half my lunch break up waiting because they don't want to pay another employee is a bit frustrating.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Joseph lieu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWrHfDzsFsRShVEzr2PKE2oX1jaG4cxkhU0kHD4Zh7Fh-yAowEa=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A Gem of a Restaurant with Amazing Food and Stellar Service\n\nI can't say enough good things about this restaurant! Every time I visit, I'm greeted with warm smiles and treated like family. The staff here truly go above and beyond to ensure a wonderful dining experience. The food is consistently delicious, with a wide variety of options to satisfy any craving. Whether you're a regular or a first-time visitor, you'll feel right at home here. Don't hesitate, give this place a try – you won't be disappointed! P.S try the wonton soup with everything included, it’s delicious.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNVN7gJsAftUBN0o70WDtUcZ392f4NzKI5yJKIz\u0026fid=0x0:0x3b16da3a2de176e5"],"When":"2024-2-22"},{"Name":"Ron Chandra","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXMUKEp9NFVbFVKFyxQlhQ50VwTmMMSQVQjHTfLly7PyXiMeq63Vg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is a hole in the wall kind of place in the industrial area in the Tilbury are of Delta, the breakfast is great, the Asian food is excellent, nothing is greasy or super salty, they take pride in the fresh food they cook. If you work in the area it’s definitely worth checking out, the food is quick and fresh. They are even open on Saturday for the hungover sat morning blue collar workers.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kyla Peck","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVFsRFGfQBc04cvbiKLoX0cfV9VneZU54J-Ub276gHLYJVuDqEN=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This diner is simply perfect. Staff team is friendly and caring. Menu is rotating, options are different each day of the week. Food is home style cooking, tastes delicious, with clean and great quality ingredients. I just love how the overall experience reminds me of the good old days.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Damian Brown","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVzJt2mshcCmJU9XbBU-uZyGrPK7lWS4Jkqj1hy8k8U9GBIdJ4L=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had some spicy chinese dish, the company I work for treated me to. Best I've ever eaten was very satisfied. Can't wait to visit again !","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alan Iwaasa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLnN8rfrxsCESPI1UU7kLxqgkgZsqh2ZmYA_xlfP5C_3nI3Yw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love this place! Feels so local and family run. The food’s delicious and the staff are very friendly. So good, planning to come back here often.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP_akhPyZpjBXSArXS2v5SmFX65jK8ZZuxzHln4\u0026fid=0x0:0x3b16da3a2de176e5"],"When":"2023-7-25"}]

I ordered online","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPc9hfZNTFUFqfM4haNQ1s1d_kb_QckiQmwqsZ_&fid=0x0:0x9215bf530296ea5c"],"When":"2024-9-23"},{"Name":"Natasha Orlova","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUsk9ioxJFKlba8oEpMmwuuW8_groenFhNnDdLOY92Ps1afjiM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"AMAZING is an understatement. The pizza here is fresh, the ingredients are high quality and you can really tell when take a bite. They don’t cheap out on the amount of toppings and the way they do their crust... crispy and delicious.
We love their tandoori chicken and butter chicken pizzas. When we want to change it up, their ham and pineapple and pepperoni are also absolutely perfect.

The samosas, oh wow, we keep going back for more!! The beef samosas are loaded with beef, it’s not just veggie filler and some beef here and there. Definitely A+!!!

I’ve never had their butter chicken but my boss swears by it. Every time we order pizza for work lunches, he gets a butter chicken. He’s a picky eater so it must be good!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP4FfcnBizk4LThrR0-05trl8q23CHhE1lgSnNG&fid=0x0:0x9215bf530296ea5c"],"When":"2021-6-22"},{"Name":"Cheshta Rishi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXl9oHCY0JuZL8-QOjPlONwYEVNzCcCt3zrtBK_PIsrVo-az2GW=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I ordered a large Super Veggie pizza through their Uber store and ended us being charged $34.99 for just one, average, vegetarian pizza. Extremely disappointed with the taste as well. The pizza is below mediocre and I feel like my money was entirely wasted on this purchase.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNAz2tOU7FphxqXbFWPyaXSRt1OwcXdEDKX1iVX&fid=0x0:0x9215bf530296ea5c"],"When":"2023-7-29"},{"Name":"emily day","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKnpWqoZCSYgNQB0azKisdzxefC3lcYOaQMWGnTMO36dxnzpQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Honestly such a waste of time and money.
I call in advance 10-15 mins I’m told.  Well why am I waiting here for 30mins for two fish pakora??? Then to only tell me you only have one and have to give me chicken for the other AFTER IVE PAID FOR TWO FISH. That’s absolutely bs and terrible service. Then won’t even bother compensating me for there HUGE mistakes. Don’t waste your time calling and ordering especially when you have a lunch break period. Bs.
And now because they had to make the chicken the one fish is COLD.
And when I went back in for a FOURTH time to finally collect it they are still all standing around laughing my order is still not prepared and I still had to wait another 3mins.

I have been here for 30+ mins. B.S.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dilky Saparamadu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL9bBMCdfFU-Fl9uZFIrwYHU_dnyur2p-NQXTniZmQ69v2ZiQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love pizza in this place. [{"Name":"N T","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL0fPxCzYwVmpF7ny4zyQgH9VNWZ2SsZVnPmKq-71dWftNbjg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Walked and the place was absolutely filthy. Only two people inside so can't say they were busy. 3 people working in the back. If the store front of this dirty, I can only imagine what it looks like in the back where people can't see. The people on cash are very polite, helpful, and kind. Will not be back for the sanitary reason.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNOWRT97cGfSo0q-Qu6tMgYvqy36ejtiEqd3oLz&fid=0x0:0x40dd67bb2681cd94"],"When":"2024-9-22"},{"Name":"Jack Nunes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV2LYNLmRTbhdeRaRfSSWQfbXW4_0XyT8Wh3w4zVn7-_sIxtWs=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Ordered the Big Mary Spicy Combo with a Tatar Poutine.
The Poutine arrived with the lid left open and no cutlery to eat the Poutine. Because the lid was left open the Poutine arrived cold and dried out. I need to make my own gravy because evidently there wasn't enough put on the Poutine to begin with seeing as the cheese curds were not even melted. Horrible service and will not be ordering at this location again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNRk6FXY5OO-ENK1DoOmcyzKZ65hVNI2_LYbbXy&fid=0x0:0x40dd67bb2681cd94"],"When":"2024-12-3"},{"Name":"Jay Adalaja","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWFoPyCzUynl1AsPhbMBH-A2X8I_h-I-l64fQ5i1Zz08w0HliI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing Atmosphere and vive. The chicken was surprisingly very fresh and sumptuous, and their taters and sandwiches were also above the mark. Customer service was also commendable. Will definitely go there again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"skruee1","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUfWjO8H-_zZEsA5T1jjsMFdmesKtX-kQ-NvFatSyCzvHsBFJ6P=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I'm sorry but, we loved eating at this location till tonight.
Waited over 20 minutes for our food, and then when we asked to talk to someone about the wait...
There was no manager or anyone with any authority.
Not yelling , but just askng for some sort of compensation and the cashier started talking to the cooks  hindi or Punjabi, and they came to the pass, and both were glaring and trying to intimidate...
I don't understand how there is no accountability for for the way we were treated.
I'm sorry but we felt discriminated against....
Both my partner and I, work for companies that focus on diversity, and respect for everyone.
Diversity training needs to be implemented for employees  as everyone should adhere to those guidelines
Everyone","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Hadia Aslam","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKgeHSioMdHCaRYjk1n1Avir3XC4yfHWHDdma9gkyDtzOmcmg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I ordered 2 Sandwiches (one online through app and one in-person ) as there was an offer on the MB App Fried Chicken Sandwich day. I was asked to wait 15 minutes. I don't mind waiting as i believe one gets fresh food if the staff is taking time. However, To my surprise when i came home and opened up the bags, the chicken in the sandwich was super hard to chew, and super super cold. My house is just 5 minutes away so can't blame the distance. May be the burgers were pre made for those who avail the offer. I will never ever use these offers again that just waste your money and time. I feel nauseous as the hard chicken is just strucked in my throat. Not going again definitely.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Yuji Stobbe","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXR5Akk7izHKA3N-5_TikKoGlhcxqeNMIRk5wkM6_OWHPrO8YIw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I’ve been wanting to try Mary Browns for awhile. I heard they had good chicken. I got a free regular chicken sandwich for installing their app and I got a spicy two piece combo. The chicken sandwich was ok. Chicken was cooked well but lacked seasoning. The fries and macaroni salad were really good and the fried chicken was good with the spicy seasoning. I don’t think I would have enjoyed it without if I’m totally honest. All in all, a good experience, but I wouldn’t drive out of my way to go. If I’m in the area and craving some fried chicken, I’m sure I would stop in.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNRWAE6S6_J7ZW3HWwwQaNbMTVnTBLpd-hoEHU7&fid=0x0:0x40dd67bb2681cd94"],"When":"2021-10-11"},{"Name":"Prakriti Kanathia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUQHvJQXTkiNWwoL-Ali4rSgJJ9tz53i5kkpcShdgZy4P2cHDcizw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"We ordered potato Taters as I don’t eat chicken but there was a piece of chicken in it. And then when we approached them and told them about the situation, their manager acted so casually as if nothing happened.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jay Why","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWf6qVrRB2FWSP3f_QpdYqgSMlmFo0fYvO9JkGkahstgPZxGBo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Good chicken but kind of pricy. First time trying Mary Brown's and I must admit it was pretty good. The Taters was good and nicely seasoned, the chicken was tender and juicy, though I had the spicy one and it looks like they were just the regular chicken with hot pepper sprinkled on top. I ordered online and the order was ready as promised. The staff was polite and friendly. They are pretty expensive for what you are getting. My 9 piece combo was $35. At KFC, I can get a 12 piece with fries and 2 sides for $25 and at Popeye's, a 14 piece chicken, 2 large sides, and 7 biscuits is $39.99.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM0Nh7OBE-eExeqrTrrRKDaPcDMFd1agibvb8L3&fid=0x0:0x40dd67bb2681cd94"],"When":"2021-9-25"}]

[{"Name":"Ray","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXGVd5s-06Fr3JDo-bYWWNiziS7uiGN7g2hEorOk1Vp-qtDK_-cTg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Honestly, delicious. Modest looking place in the food court. They serve salads and hot Indian meals.

I had a paneer tikka kulcha, not knowing what to expect. The cashier said it would take 10 minutes. When it was ready she rang a bell and gave me a freshly prepared,  very hot wrap.

It was delicious, with creamy melty paneer and tangy veggies and spices. See for yourself! It was bursting with flavor.

I can say that it was very impressive,  and I definitely recommend. I'd like to come back to try their other items.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPgOr8MtQHhXty_7WIAhsJH9eBxpoaB9WPOnYYc&fid=0x0:0xeda723c3c1288d92"],"When":"2024-5-22"},{"Name":"Rohan Thampi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUSBP1xvuyRFzjXVwSjch6tqJ7Ds0TZbgrsFaDxXW5mQb8ZZNtC=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had the best chole bature, and mango lassi from here. Credits to Shipra for the excellent service and giving a sampler gajar ka halwa. Unlike most places, the lassi was thick, not too sugary, and  perfectly mango-y. Authentic indian cuisine experience","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gurman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUSx1waDOcsVkumEiZBaLq3WokW571WXs1z1jJ2eaBtIj9tUMc90g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great staff. Very kind and caring. Huge portion sizes. I tried chane bhature its so yum.
Kulche, sandvich and specialy summer drinks.
We love to order their cardamom tea and other snacks. Thank you so much salad n more team for making such a delecious and fresh food.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Garima kumar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJkiu35DXcXPECYpNAkJ0j0jMMFvsQavA-Em81hJW39m5twWg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Superb food . Shipra is also very courteous and make according to your preference.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP7T9e2vFREVAj8_xBHP5SQz7LOEp8L_jIlLmA1&fid=0x0:0xeda723c3c1288d92"],"When":"2022-10-14"},{"Name":"Navdeep Grover","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVZNNSXsM1NDPFQvtbGzlK-5eI16G_TXPtiIvNnTD2DBTf_ZIuVjQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Tdy was not a good experience at Salads n More. [{"Name":"Preetpal Sandhu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW8_WPWl-Di7av_JN_-3MBW33VvwXWih2BXVXgLUs8ghKmPj094=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Their pizza is delicious! I love to support local businesses and since they’ve opened they have not disappointed me. Very reasonable prices and the food tastes great each time. I especially like the loaded fries with chicken!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNEFKZjfZoiPN7x1b0X4_ZiQWKDcjxXQ7BzJLp7&fid=0x0:0xe37b370126f705c9"],"When":"2021-7-27"},{"Name":"Vijay Riar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJPd9po4cB1CJ3ept2LkvkCmEk03wyrzAdGKYNXmkToSW4WHg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve tried pretty much every Pizza place in Surrey/ North Delta and this one is by far the best.

The entire experience from placing the order , picking up the pizza and then finally sitting at home and enjoying  it, was absolutely exceptional.

I strongly recommend trying it if you are a fan of real ol school pies. I ordered a small house special and could only finish half and trust me, I can eat!

Great Pizza, great customer service and very fairly priced.

All boxes checked.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Masuma Mehri","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLw9qMlBP7sweufBcFidbM2cK8cQCePWNlkTXptFtsoqzXGJg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Pizza was amazing! The clam chowder has lots of thickening agent and not much cream.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMkAQlvW90J942EpYsNe5ZEGCQJhjq4ZQZfraAp&fid=0x0:0x81695ea7f6044254"],"When":"2024-7-31"},{"Name":"John Price","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKiZ3medNvpZKnxcMuCI3q6FXXHwTpSsBEJWl2A-_syn1czKw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I came here for lunch got in line placed my order 7 people came in behind me for the lunch rush each and every one of them was served food prior to me and I ended up waiting for 2/3 of my lunch break to actually get my food. Highly recommended!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNdhHw3YzYZcAAHWg_QVKxOckaibVLzmRnBq5bA&fid=0x0:0x81695ea7f6044254"],"When":"2022-12-15"},{"Name":"Jeff Astle","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJqpBD1la32QOHRh35fAqT7JCPqLBjqkr5aE2XHbEfgBcBEOQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Odd choices for their recipes. Clam chowder that has no cream, crab wrap drown in wasabi. If you're open to spend a bit more, Hadis is right across the street. If you're not looking to spend more, canco gas station on the corner has heavenly pizza slices.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ps H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXWZH4u5uxDfJNhnL_l8W1S4uIzr1H4HDeoj_eCHzg7xFQspTGN=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Ordered the Bibimbap - it was yummy, and very filling.  Good portions of each component.  The spinach was a little tough in the way that spinach sometimes gets.  I wish the egg had been over-easy, but that's just personal preference.  I have no similar bibimbap to compare this one too, but I will try there again.  They now also have something called "cup bob" on the paper menu - I look forward to trying that next time.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOIcOa3MBOm7S9gqsF3dyEze1473Y-01XRX--02&fid=0x0:0x81695ea7f6044254"],"When":"2021-1-27"},{"Name":"Greg Fong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIJ0L0WZdGVzWI2qBiBqWQhdpTibGG4KMYCjzD-Xhn7xYWmDpA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"DISAPPOINTING!!!!!!

According to Google, "Divine" means "of God or god-like, heavenly" or, informally, "excellent, delightful" - the two sandwiches (club house and montreal smoked beef) were anything but!!! Barely enough content to cover the miniscule, cheap white bread (see photo with a pen as a reference to size) along with nothing but a microscopic and stale carrot stick!

Horrifically disappointing!!! A toddler would be left hungry!

A poor excuse for a sandwich shop / deli. Paid close to $30 for basically 5 slices of Wonderbread! Tim Horton's quality AT BEST, and that's really pushing to be complimentary. Website very deceiving.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNsDDULzFkfGuXHSV955_eB4VLStVwvy_hZc4dD&fid=0x0:0x81695ea7f6044254"],"When":"2023-5-12"}]

Friendly staff and they had a well maintained facility","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNg0S65g5UjyMme_E-Sq_FKywKxPuohFsehtlIt&fid=0x0:0x1454995701ca095e"],"When":"2024-4-27"},{"Name":"Anmol Dhillon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIQKCh0cXaNiQlvZx0lWw1nr0yooVHZrtoqseVJVMyFeBsuIaU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Giving one star for their terrible service . She forced me to write this review","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ember N","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVAOVVSRZSBJ6e5O5jUUtiBAq23q-FcEx-8tVq1hmthlfDRNYcfgw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Ordered for take out. a bit expensive but a very very good option. portion is a bit smaller than dining in.

I would come back here again.

-2 because of portioning.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN6vzmVDPafnCdh6wCAbtxoAgt9A-IIVO8nnuzm&fid=0x0:0x1454995701ca095e"],"When":"2021-5-22"},{"Name":"Tim Dovey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU3hRqeSE1Ni6xzm8x3OJSAQIB3dlLAWPvVYWaVVzqKwaqg4vs=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Ridiculously small portions. We were told that we cannot order for atleast an hour because staff is busy preparing catering order. I do like the place but would not come back again or will suggest anyone concerning the attitude of the staff.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Clarissa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKHucsI2CeByMOdetMrELLicLCRgBagHzWBTkigcJ_31eEF8Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I used to love Chopped Leaf.. But today the quality is the worse. The food is not fresh, no sauce for Bangkok salad (which is essential and can’t eat without sauce). Phone calls were not picked up (I wonder the customer service might be same like other reviews that mentioned the worse customer service for this location). I order this for to go during my lunch time at work. Now I don’t have time to go back to store to get the replacement. This is mean I don’t have lunch today and starving until end of my work. Thanks to poor quality and no customer service from Chopped Leaf 😠","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNmYRFPxPCEDpM0QbRHF3LY_C_Doh3Y-rxTHrlK&fid=0x0:0x1454995701ca095e"],"When":"2021-11-27"},{"Name":"Mary Nekouei","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIv8Xb7KTjkaZ4fQRcOXzfkASZied89_V_VbQ7eWAvtuqQMWA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Unfortunately , they didn’t put the ingredients as shown in the picture and mixed them without asking .
I ordered Power spinach and no apples ,no feta cheese , very small avocado…
It’s not acceptable.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Evan Strain","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW2fqOdAnhxaiemFQS4XyDFhbiKrZRy07FxpcL2GXjAWO1I4RSA1w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love coming here for healthy and delicious food options.

This chopped leaf I probably go to the most, the place is clean and looks pretty cool. The staff are super friendly and the food they make is fantastic. I would recommend my favourite thing but the Sunshine, Caesar, (wrap or salad) and quesadillas are all top choices of mine.

This specific chopped leaf is also very generous and active in the community. They have donated food to a local park event that happens every summer called Summer Fun @ The Park.

The washrooms are clean, the prices are good for what you’re getting and you can order your food online for pick up.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN5AXXjupzfdihrvw3ZEClANLnENxLmCAVafA5C&fid=0x0:0x1454995701ca095e"],"When":"2018-9-9"}]
