[{"Name":"Vanika Vanika","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWi-xsR_M07Zdm4atI_oW8JYZDaYaRBghyEWsVUcQkN2g6ZAAI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Ordered through doordash. For noodles, ingredients said - bell pepper, broccoli and cilantro. While placing the order, I made a request to remove broccoli and cilantro and add onions instead. Also to make it spicy. But all I received is stale noodles with just bell peppers. Where are the onions? No spices either. They shouldn’t have accepted the order if they were not comfortable adding onions. Or could have given me a call to ask for extra charges if that was a case. Dumping the noodles as such. Waste of my money and time.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN4zgdLxolGZH-YnA1ttZKlzHt33cnuwxAwKezk&fid=0x0:0x558e4548dfee9769"],"When":"2024-7-13"},{"Name":"Kamal Deep","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocISsNx8-BOMzVsNID4P8cWoYB3mnthbkgojc38Yc4VDZw1gQg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Today, I visited the store and ordered two channa samosa and found hair in my food.
I asked the lady for solution and she asked that I can only get same order again but here the thing is if they can’t make my first order with proper food safe measures then how can I trust them for my second order
She say that they can’t do anything after this I asked her 50% refund still they refuse
Also they didn’t wear a proper hair net just using normal cloth covering head but still their hair was showing up
So, I wanna recommend people not to visit there if you are conscious about your health","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Omesh Parkash","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUhudgZBx87532WPIacVdXCMhOug70inEjzbyWcrgLC71XRm_ZK=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This Store provides with various delicious food items and its fully Indian touch. Me and my wife love their Kulcha, Burger and Noodles. Taste is awesome. Good customer service, polite behaviour and reasonable pricing.

Recommend everyone to visit and taste their food items.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOuE0Av4ECpjouVeYHXzFpyx5Sv0BDBcOzc3-ku&fid=0x0:0x558e4548dfee9769"],"When":"2022-2-27"},{"Name":"lovepreet kaur","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKL-gCSXPqgf75q0g5x11ATBXnVD7QKP2G3Ln0KIJ50s2Vv=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The worst place to visit yesterday i visit tat reastaurant and ordered some food and there is one hair in it
Satff didn’t follow proper guidelines and didn’t wear hair net
Overall serivice was not goo","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"ashish sharma","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL15EUvpvpbYdiwkRSUNgiSuMNzQ2WPWqojpoRzGC6J_slcWQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Misleading Prices and Dishonest Practices – Avoid This Place!

I went to this shop specifically for their advertised $3.99 Paneer Burger deal. I called ahead and ordered two paneer burgers, as that’s the only one on their menu. However, when I arrived to pick up my order, they charged me full price, claiming that the burgers I ordered were different from the $3.99 deal. To make it worse, the “different” burger they mentioned isn’t even on their menu! This felt like an outright scam to lure customers in with a deal, then charge more when it’s time to pay.

This kind of dishonest bait-and-switch tactic is extremely unprofessional and disappointing. I won’t be returning here and wouldn’t recommend this place to anyone. Stay away if you value honesty in your transactions!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Winnie Yu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKvghP3098IkIAe4kkjFWSk_6u2OsZ74hqmPaAghKEI06X6JQo=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love the food and everything about it.  Personal favourite is Kings Wrap! You get your money's worth! Foods are at a very decent price, allowing us to purchase multiple without breaking our wallet. If you are looking for comfort food on  Friday evening, or if you are tired of cooking and want something quick, reasonable price, and delicious.  This is the place to go! We come here almost on a weekly basis, sometimes twice a week. Yes, it's THAT good!!!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMTo_DrRmmjulVt07GZ9hPkwXTBNGCvirErzmSb&fid=0x0:0x558e4548dfee9769"],"When":"2022-6-4"},{"Name":"Ikram Abdullahi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXDmvQYDvJi9X4DB4U3orgGun_aKfyiZyh1OnfGJBaN3dPBUjQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Decided to try something new and got their aloo tikki. Disappointed would be an understatement because I could even take more than one bite. I’ve had aloo tikki before but never like this. The description is very inaccurate and it’s doesn’t taste good at all. So sad that my money went to waste and that I waited so long for something that doesn’t even taste good but definitely will not be back.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Vivek Bhatia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXEJfc3bFfutRnZtX2BKo2u5q_AftdVmBbIYHpYLbT_8q8t6ddT=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Food here is the worst I ever had. user_reviews: [{"Name":"Sim Virk","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIEMdmDuS1-MyWvk2ZEndLX7td2mii2DZ5NZPl8ZidBcpQqyg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently had a wonderful experience at Pizza Hut thanks to an employee named Ravi. She was exceptionally helpful and attentive throughout my visit. From taking my order to ensuring everything was prepared just right, her friendly and efficient service made the whole process smooth and enjoyable. Ravi also offered some excellent recommendations, which made my meal even better. Her outstanding customer service truly stood out, and I’ll definitely be returning to this Pizza Hut location because of her exceptional assistance.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ian Grimsdick","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVVNAwbGbAg7iHFZCH2ZcRPNQCqhdrLGjma3MI6N7NMRmpkI8DArQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"People here are nice enough but I ordered a pizza with double pepperoni today and there was basically 3-4 pieces of cup pepperoni per slice.  Definitely not satisfying at all.  Maybe it was done because it was the free pizza earned by points, but still.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Don Neto","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXzu77gqNywm6NtnXzdJv5O91vF9T253Z4JcoBCm_wPuFmMd7PK=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I go here a lot for a quick lunch. I always get the pizza of the day for $11.55 hard to find prices like that nowadays.  Sahil the manager even calls me on a first name basis which is nice 👍","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNCKVaSOJJ1qMM7zD1_-mqSgmU3_E_DORAn7O9R\u0026fid=0x0:0x8c7bbc1256c671da"],"When":"2024-5-15"},{"Name":"Ouroboros","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKc6BogbshF9HDAqiFbNx31zXviMfxfg0I7Fl6S4ptWmgXwuoY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Ordered honey bbq boneless bites and when I arrived home to eat them I discovered that they didn't have any sauce on them.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOFQtQtMofXsyay-oGxmxNyIHK3trjMYOG0k5QK\u0026fid=0x0:0x8c7bbc1256c671da"],"When":"2024-11-16"},{"Name":"Ivan H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW1afXLWpmD08BQBXxVfTxrd4nKMWx6OTonXYfbgxVCqCN3RtM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Since last time I took a survey from pizza hut and received a validation code for buy-one-get-one free, I use this code to order a pizza today(2025.08.10), the staff said to use the validation code, I need to go with the receipt from the last time, therfore she said recently pizza hut has an activity for $1 more to buy the second pizza. In the end, she didn’t let me use the verification code to get the 2nd pizza free， but instead charge me an extra dollar. Today, I am not upset about the extra dollar I had to pay, but rather about the entire transaction not being conducted with integrity. Additionally, when they provided me with a validation code, they did not mention that the previous purchase receipt had to be presented upon use. Now, asking for it at the last minute makes me feel that the staff deliberately made an excuse to avoid honoring the discount I was entitled to, which I find disgraceful. Overall, I had a very unpleasant experience purchasing pizza at the store today. I hope pizza hut will further train their staff to ensure that the offers you provide to customers are honored.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cath D","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWzQHskK5KSztGZIl15LsZGC-0SO5JLFSBm8yYaI0ONOMSUwlVY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"4th time receiving delivery and something is messed up. Ordered Pan pizza, it is not. One of the pieces is cut so small that it is swimming in the palm of my hand!  Tried adding a photo. Can't find it. Ordered 14 boneless chicken wings and only got 10. Cinnabons were so small , the icing was all over the lid from bouncing around in the box. There should be 10 in box, but only 8. Twice my order was missing the drinks, but I was charged and they do nothing about it. This will be my last order today. I know things happen and staff changes, but when there is something wrong with every order, it's time to quit.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nav puneet","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVT8sxruISiPNR-Gm9n7GsB_P_IGuhxIHodw0kMTJPc3GwLC8Lp3g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The pizza was a 5/5. I would recommend it to everyone to give it a try once. We ordered pizza in a box with 2 toppings each- one with green peppers and mushrooms, another one with green peppers and red onions. Do try it once 🍕🌟","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPSItYJ4j8747SgMG8Xco-TSWv0fcm1cc04GR7z\u0026fid=0x0:0x8c7bbc1256c671da"],"When":"2023-11-12"},{"Name":"Simran Atwal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWPnge-kcwx-R0_IZRybhR6vXLTF7z1shPoo87TR-dLDiM98Ddg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I usually hesitate ordering from this location as I've had quite a few bad experiences with them in past (wrong order, forgotten order, missing items, not following covid guidelines properly, etc.). However, keeping in mind the busy nature of this location I let it go each time. Today I decided to place an order online for delivery hoping it would go smoothly. As I opened the boxes in my kitchen I saw that half the slices were missing the cheese. In the past the staff has not been any one bit remorseful. Thus I anticipated they wouldn't be apologetic or accommodating this time either. Tired of dealing with them at this point. Will never be ordering from the Delta (Scottroad) Pizza Hut again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMBG37faD70jQKhKOoKwe5d_iRUWFjoEcb1oMHp\u0026fid=0x0:0x8c7bbc1256c671da"],"When":"2021-2-24"}]

Don't really want to sit down to eat a meal only to choke.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Richa Vashisht","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKi4xYEo3Ok4v-S58b2kMARxUUB6ZpyorsaWqZCpnC0kKvxmQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Sales associate was very nice and hardworking\nShe managed very well during busy hours inspite of being short staffed","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"SAY IT WITH","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWL36nbVhcThawQqolClVhJWG8_CmcFdNzDihh-PE9cY3aBMVw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This location is very clean and bright. Upon walking in I was greeted and helped right away. Not having been inside a Pita Pit for a while I asked a few questions to which the employee was very happy to provide answers. Service was quick and the selection of crisp veggies to add to my wrap were plentiful. Top it all off with a delicious end and I would say that I will definitely be back to order from here again very soon.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Myra El Masraya","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVeJJxwenHWklXoTEl9q8Yi096pDR_ziSwJ6U00VvkKFXeK12yb=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food here is so delicious and has a big portion. The servers are very friendly and they helped us take some pictures of our party as we were celebrating our girlfriend's birthday. We also had a room for us to have our party there. The restaurant is very clean and we use the same restaurant for all our birthday celebration parties. They also would play the birthday music and they bring a special dessert for the person who is celebrating her birthday. We just love it there.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOOLw0rLUAz7kYu-QxFV0I3gjnLEzdUnNaawuBf&fid=0x0:0xf69be2afe19b00bb"],"When":"2021-1-5"},{"Name":"Jay Why","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWf6qVrRB2FWSP3f_QpdYqgSMlmFo0fYvO9JkGkahstgPZxGBo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"First and foremost, the service was great. I recognized the lady that served us from the last time we where here and that was almost 5 years ago. I know that management have changed and I am glad they kept most of their staff. She made it a point to go around to all the tables and took the time to actually talk to everyone. Most restaurants nowadays you'll never see the waitress again once they have taken your order.
The food, on the other hand was a bit of a let down. The ribs were dry and bland, and the lamb was inconsistence. Some pieces were perfectly cooked while other were overcooked and very tough.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPDpHR1MYaiZvxmDnpuGKDA6aV8o66oSLN6hDrG&fid=0x0:0xf69be2afe19b00bb"],"When":"2022-12-12"},{"Name":"Kyle S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVAHrv12m1CC3kTdgJJdn2Ti6FOCLWHmeg0867bmV2m8DUkHyHW=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very good portions food is full of flavors, very fresh and delicious. The saganaki is amazing. Very big open restaurant. Super friendly service.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP8H0TsgWgT9Gb-Y6IVgPuDAgKzR-n_t12QJs22&fid=0x0:0xf69be2afe19b00bb"],"When":"2023-9-27"},{"Name":"Ebo M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJkGD-0dNKN-6VRV0xdkoDDzwv5oQSqe3xuMLUK2URhYLKK4Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I came to this restaurant years ago and I had such an amazing experience. The food was absolutely delicious. Coming here today the atmosphere and the service was  very good. The food on the other hand was  good but I felt like My roast lamb souvlaki  was missing something(I still ate all of it though lol). The staff is very friendly. The pricing is no different than any other Greek food restaurant and portions are generous. My son enjoyed his chicken souvlaki, I thought my Roast lamb souvlaki was ok, I definitely will be coming back here to try more dishes though .

Thanks,","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOb_pyQUTxwzDpGz8zfdn7RoXSO_-8_FdlAPWQL&fid=0x0:0xf69be2afe19b00bb"],"When":"2023-12-10"},{"Name":"Rehana Ali","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVKGe30Vbwwr1MgfFIcOA2wcccIVe7cC1kRrdz_ir2zhbDVyo6WWw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"After reading everyone's reviews I decided to go and check it out. It was my birthday dinner that my friends and I went to.
Just as we arrived the waitress brought us in to our table. It took them 15mins to bring us menu's and water. I had asked one of the waitress can someone help us and she abruptly said u just have to wait.
I was not happy at all!!
Finally when the waitress did come she did not very happy. We finally ordered drinks and appetizers.
There pop is horrible it is watered down.
Ur better off with water. We had to complain about that again our waitress seemed irraterd. Finally our appetizers arrived the chicken wings we're very salty and the cheese had a weird taste. Only thing was that the Calamari was decent.
At this point I am not happy with the food and the horrible service that we we're getting.
We all finally got our main courses that was decent.
I eat at alot of restaurants and put in reviews.
This is one restaurant that I don't recommend.
They need better customer service and the price they charge for food and drinks should be better then what we got.

My girlfriend had to ask the waitress if you do anything for birthdays and she was rude about it and said no we don't but I will bring u something this time.

I would like the owner of the business to contact me at there earliest convenience so we can discuss this further.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOFkqvjFow9mD10ajtILzC0ROKVmvTWcndu6RJj&fid=0x0:0xf69be2afe19b00bb"],"When":"2021-3-16"},{"Name":"Hemanjot Grewal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWim9Hu81iRvZGkfkh7wJuu43nsSaASxaHoEIOlrgfrtzj-7ao=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love their chicken souvlaki and the dip woth it. O my god and there rice😃❤️. One of my best decisions","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPx-4X0nZ1vjgRfmCeDIXpOHIFPugopZVY3kds7&fid=0x0:0xf69be2afe19b00bb"],"When":"2024-6-16"},{"Name":"D SAM","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVAPZJhKwbwofRMAxzu-Q9mFomEMmhsUcyi8-_CMghvFMl0UXMbEw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I love this place. The servers are always very friendly and helpful when you are undecided on what to order. I’ve tried their lamb souvlaki and vegetarian platter before. The flavours of the platter was just beyond amazing. Good portion size for 3 people depending on how hungry you are. The spices on the dolma I ordered today was very flavourful. I would only wish that they have more vegan friendly options.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM3b4ftkKgZl7_owe7zaTCU1k9FtXU4mkc-AxWI&fid=0x0:0xf69be2afe19b00bb"],"When":"2019-5-11"},{"Name":"Dennis Morgan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLuJucR5jIKbgTEv3gB31CNoSDXon2mhYRgCHlRCcS8somCKA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I Had a great dinner with my daughter, son in law, and granddaughter. The food was fantastic and one thing for sure you're not going to go home hungry, they sure know how to cook lamb and the calamari appetizer was excellent and plentiful.
It doesn't list the roast lamb in recommendations but I would definatly recommend it.
Keep up the good work guysc👍👍😋","Images":null,"When":""}]

The eggs are always done nicely. The chicken strips are fantastic here, highly recommended as they are light and crispy!! Been going to this location for years and have always had great customer service, good food and hot coffee! Nice its in the little mall as well if you need to do a bit of shopping. One of our favorite breakfast and family places to eat at!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNqgGtygocqY02E8OB7Ec4iDRZ184fMQ82SiaUA\u0026fid=0x0:0x27d17b9c7307c597"],"When":"2023-9-8"},{"Name":"Rick the Sensei","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJpixu8L3sNOw6nYNwAcLYVzSPD64H-rZ377kHFRZeipNdMRQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've never been here but I've seen it around. We were trying to go somwhere else but it was closed so we took the highway 10 and ended up here. It was already 1:30 p.m. for my kids were starving. Honestly I was expecting a greasy diner  like Danny's but I was wrong. Maybe I was extremely hungry but I was really satisfied with the food. My kids ordered a breakfast set that included pancake sausages sausages and eggs. The pancakes were really good it was not too fluffy but not too hard and not too sweet and not too salty. Just right. I ordered a cheddar bacon burger and it was pretty darn good much better than what I expected for a diner. The patty was not dry and not too thick (I don't enjoy too thick it overpowers the other ingredients) and a good slice of tomato, lettuce, and crunchy bacon. It wasn't soggy or drippy. Man all in all it was pretty darn good food much better then I thought it was going to be. I'll be coming back. And oh the fries and gravy were good!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jay Why","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWf6qVrRB2FWSP3f_QpdYqgSMlmFo0fYvO9JkGkahstgPZxGBo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Staff was very friendly and there was always someone coming a round to top up our coffee. Everything tasted pretty good though my burger was kind of small and the bun was stale. Ever had a dry piece of bread and then try to toast it? My bun was crumbing into pieces as I was biting into it. Overall it was a pretty good experience. I would come back in the future","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMtBlJDEaIAnPJhbtPwjcdhV3aIVoX_4W3-am3Q\u0026fid=0x0:0x27d17b9c7307c597"],"When":"2020-11-9"},{"Name":"Filip Pulpan (Filipos)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXQkzrR62le0PjlAmlvrGxMxeXfeixrbfKMP3Xa1-icknONYe_dEQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Ordered chicken schnitzel with shredded hash browns and red cabbage. Chicken was tasting weird like a processed meat. And taste of the whole meal was very plain. Cabbage tasted … well… not quite good. Very disappointing.\nOn a good side…. Service was great 😊","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPxHO23kE0fuZ3rea7iKe1CTbqW-RXmtkmwO8YQ\u0026fid=0x0:0x27d17b9c7307c597"],"When":"2023-12-1"},{"Name":"Cassidy Starchild (Cass)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU3rhlkFMpL-mxsowKvaMcnyEAb4M_1cLgDpp0VCtOdSBmb6DKyjA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Had the Big Brunch breakfast. Food was good and hot, service was friendly and efficient. Nice, relaxed atmosphere in a clean restaurant.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMPzZM7ZlOAPcVL6FBXLRo1TkfB8JPeX-oPV9Rz\u0026fid=0x0:0x27d17b9c7307c597"],"When":"2024-2-29"},{"Name":"Monika","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWbWWX5dAR4sTlmZWeglXfzxOXvz0yb2CgdnfdM-c3BKRcsoDxn=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I’ve been going to this Ricky’s for years now and have never seen such a short-staffed day. I went over the weekend with my family and there was no one to greet us or the people waiting behind us. We only saw one lady doing the entire seating and serving. She apologized the whole time, even though it wasn’t her fault, all while running back and forth to the front and to each table. With an entire queue of people waiting to be seated, you’d think the restaurant would employ/schedule more staff. Don’t burden a single employee to handle the entire space by theirselves! We were so disappointed and felt guilty just being there and adding more unnecessary stress to her day. Someone in the establishment needs to refer back to the Employment Standards Act before an outsider complains.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Debbie Jennings","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWMR8hqytR0EJVY6GYBiVyCCEsiXxk9wbUaRyQvoOy_I29wr_MqzQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Well, I must say this was absolutely  the best food I've had from any Ricky's the service was amazing. The food was awesome. I would definitely  go again any time, very friendly, family oriented","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNyFvS-8vzgimUA0gsLwcJsE8BBie_a7mUgn5kI\u0026fid=0x0:0x27d17b9c7307c597"],"When":"2024-3-1"},{"Name":"Baljit Saran","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLQA6lzXDsiVmoJ_80uL7EdWWiIm4cwLFnjPdAW1STqs9ZN7Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I come to Ricky`s every Sunday to enjoy a pitcher of beer with amazing wings and it is my favorite.\nThe staff is frienand attentive, making the experience even better. Highly recommend!!","Images":null,"When":""}]

In hindsight the website does have a small print of 19+ so i have to assume the chicken tenders on the menu must be marketed to the young at heart.

Great for wet fish and dry meat!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Emma H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIrOveRmN8b18g_LeQ7_uFEaeRYhYo_Aw8Bbsn6H-frhGc4ZQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"An old style pub with wonderful homemade food and a great selection of beverages, including lots of local craft beer. It's a real hidden gem!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"A Willems","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI7lPGykAC2QqhNmHyO9vFjlVxuXS8JKqhXU5Hg5a5AsE-YTw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great food, great service - both times we went! Love the open floorplan.
Great place to watch sports.
Good beers on tap.
Love the Portobello burger, avocado power bowl and mac and cheese. Good potato skins too!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNRn1ht0X1BTIVMn8NORhDgNFptTdAbqAKs_yYl&fid=0x0:0x9be71bce7fd2ca53"],"When":"2023-2-27"},{"Name":"Omar Plascentia Garcia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVxFeUWXfP60KHwVYL9J3bKZi_XZdQMIDzH47BU49kMhclJbfIi=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"*A Pleasant Surprise!*

"I'll admit, I've walked past the Pub many times, thinking it looked a bit... sketchy** But, boy, was I wrong! The moment I stepped inside, I was greeted with warm smiles from the lovely staff - and I mean lovely in every sense of the word...

The service was top-notch, attentive, and friendly. My waitress very knowledgeable and made excellent recommendations. But what truly impressed me was the genuine hospitality. It felt like they actually cared about dining experience.

And the food? Absolutely delicious! Although < if you don't have the RYE  for the pastrami sandwich it's ok that butter w condiments did the trick 😉> also who know my cocktail was little cheaper then my beer 😆..

I'm thrilled to have been proven wrong about this hidden gem. Don't let appearances fool you - Pub is a must-visit. Great food, beautiful atmosphere, and stunning staff I totally forgot to take Pictures coz my servicer tho.. lol

*Rating:* 5/5 stars

*Recommendation:* Don't hesitate, give it a try!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"R B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXvwlyjB4u92gNs2XkVMCtEEv1bbhznwa-XyALuorQtBg64Yw0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had the Cubano Sandwich which was excellent, my wife had Casadias which she loved. Will definitely be back, very clean, lots of room, tv's galore to watch your favorite sports on.
Service is great 👍","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNIDpQ29v6kIdejJNUcm17m8SR2YBYnA7dR_-Vx&fid=0x0:0x9be71bce7fd2ca53"],"When":"2023-11-12"},{"Name":"Betty Kwong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIM1K_xKF7aNtuzA88mQ3hwg3t5gx00K2EbOMWOAP-UBSCpag=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Wouldn’t bother coming here next time or spending money on them. Food is okay, Customer service needs to improve. Not even simple how are you or a greeting as soon as I walked through the door. Wouldn’t recommend. I think they are short staffed","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"jennifer young","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLIZgbrQLp1yIu7-u7v5WLayH0JUrvKf4ugYCbj1BZg52qA8A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I have been going here for years but stopped a few years ago as the brunch prices went up astronomically. Surprised that one of them still works there! Too bad as it's the only place like this around Ladner.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Munro Stuff","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWj0Wcuk6ox5dfAeJ4fAaMbhX_F-nzzt3p5oc_f0hBd0NpbGSM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had planned to pop in for a beer....but the beers were so great that we had to try a few kinds. And it was an excellent Happy Hour so we had to try a pretzel with cheese sauce...which was so good that we ordered more food and made a dinner of it. Diverse menu, nice decor, great service by Ella. Will definitely be back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMy5Bm0nuTOpAnZjuPtygc4JvHf9agmWt4ashb-&fid=0x0:0x775f3939f7f511d8"],"When":"2024-11-7"},{"Name":"Omar Plascentia Garcia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVxFeUWXfP60KHwVYL9J3bKZi_XZdQMIDzH47BU49kMhclJbfIi=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"_A Mixed Bag_
Gorgeous! The service? Friendly and attentive.
Unfortunately, the food didn't quite live up to the hype. I was genuinely excited to try, but they fell flat. Flavors were muted, presentation was lacking, and portions were small for the price .. feel sorry for the tip.. my wallet weeps, tho
It pains me to say it because the staff was lovely and the atmosphere was spot-on. But, the food – the main event – just didn't impress.
Rating:_ 2.5/5 stars
Maybe I just ordered wrong, that's it.. Try it for yourself, but temper your expectations
I'll stick to admiring their aesthetic, tho..","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNkaaDrGE4dtj-K58U9jeomSXuE_Rk55xky8d-z&fid=0x0:0x775f3939f7f511d8"],"When":"2024-10-1"},{"Name":"A.J. Canadian","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU0mITu_1OR_MuXzhVIkPjHjZnimy2Y-mI64r72OA1Zbucah6-N=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A great find in Ladner, Britannia Brewing has great tasting craft beer on tap, delicious food and spacious seating with a relaxing atmosphere. Great to sit, talk, eat or just enjoy a drink.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipONkMoVTwjhUTGqFaFMRQ1gWr640QUWrNgAAOFE&fid=0x0:0x775f3939f7f511d8"],"When":"2024-10-28"},{"Name":"D. S. H.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXJHQjUje9KisA5u93NxJkw1JL_FCRnXl3eZFy20rlaly3_hOQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The dog-friendly patio was surprisingly nice considering it's a repurposed parking area covered in artificial grass. Lots of potted plants, nice umbrellas for shade and good room between tables.

Happy hour offered good food at great prices.

The servers were friendly.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOmokuQHM_XU83F8EM7rYSQSwfgWmzkFYykNDfj&fid=0x0:0x775f3939f7f511d8"],"When":"2024-8-2"},{"Name":"Shirley Ann Harris","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLTufZ1O7YNqmevegFQNEbK68BixarB9ooeJyWD92O9OkSBiQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Where do I begin? I was having a craving for fish and chips. I found the Britannia Brewing right across the street from my location. I walked into an inviting trendy at Chic restaurant. I was met by a lovely lady and taken to a table. I'm not someone who likes to try new things and when I notice the fish and chips wasn't the typical fish and chips I was skeptical. I spoke to my waitress and she explained the dish in detail. She knows her menu. Well. I found the staff to be dressed in comfortable yet professional manner making the place feel very relaxed and inviting. I did order the fish and chips and they were the best I've ever had. The batter was not thick and over breaded nor was it greasy. The flavor was delicious! They gave me two large pieces and french fries. I love the homemade tartar sauce. I ordered a pop as well and they even brought a slice of lime in there which I thought was a nice touch. I'm especially impressed with the fact that they have three bathrooms. One is wheelchair accessible tastefully decorated. In fact the whole restaurant is tastefully decorated!  I will not hesitate to go back in order to recommend this to as many people that are willing to listen.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMXKShd1mPP3RLZleiMiBTr4WHfZNNwITCitKwe&fid=0x0:0x775f3939f7f511d8"],"When":"2024-5-13"},{"Name":"Ross McCutcheon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV17RLqBCwI7SSR47xRsCSTT37HMSG55hKmTlfuQXCdFOnVSNzm=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best try this one before the lineups start. Enjoyed all four choices on our beer flight. The burger from Twin River's was terrific as was the salad with sockeye. Just a great place.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNWmkI8jn9zmctMJb1uWDQ6pD2gWWphsLmGV_iT&fid=0x0:0x775f3939f7f511d8"],"When":"2024-5-16"},{"Name":"Pongo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXXT-qQCE1uUwfmES1FGLIpAmkroUlDIcsJZMXejhRkO1uA9CxO=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Haven't had a chance to try the beers yet, but the food here is excellent. Each dish we tried were distinct and well-executed. Though a tad expensive, I would order the duck wings again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO7eSyZTOJQBZhb93rXRUFU1y53HdqJ5fb_1qDy&fid=0x0:0x775f3939f7f511d8"],"When":"2024-6-10"},{"Name":"Sue Pierce","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXFDZvp0iO8IycCL1mvjrCRyoXBO8oRqjr35u3xz-iSc5cOkePw6Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I loooooove this place! Amazing food, excellent service, and cozy atmosphere!  I ordered the Ladner Power Bowl, which was so fresh and full of flavor. Looking forward to eating here again soon.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOV0Oeg17CocCmRjo6Ta6U0A7kbXigQD6Zu1XgT&fid=0x0:0x775f3939f7f511d8"],"When":"2024-11-30"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Raeburn MacDougall","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVIoXHoCNiCsL0dOjQhl4dr7HXmy8LsAXROqZKdAcT-ThcE0fCn=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ok I'm a pizza fanatic. I have tried many of the places between Richmond, Ladner and Tsawwassen. Each place I have reviewed has its own special qualities, and Grizzly Flatbread is no exception. Excellent customer service, big selection of pizzas and a happy hour from 2pm to 5pm even on the night of the Stanley Cup final game. High quality 10" hand made pizza for $10 dollars no limit on # of pizzas..👍. it was amazing I ordered 4 different kinds for our group of friends to go. Each pizza was amazing. If you haven't tried them yet I highly recommend you do. I can guarantee you won't be disappointed. I will definitely be having Grizzly again and again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPjvdJW7aSNIyZHUK8OlPS7jkbgdsHI4vI83tLi&fid=0x0:0x13d6b7d52babeea"],"When":"2024-6-28"},{"Name":"Pigpinkx","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWWApOQKcUKxk7JjR5oAkq09K5LHCIcyzvXSbNsSeNEYlgx6p8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I don't normally post reviews, but seeing such a good restaurant with a low rating on yelp compelled me to set things straight. This is an amazing pizza joint. There aren't many quality restaurants in Ladner, and I would hate to see a place like this shut down due to poor reviews. If you check on Google, you'll see that the majority of people who visited had a good experience. The first pizza I ordered from here was top-notch. I would definitely recommend this gem to others. Please give them a shot and don't be discouraged by the low ratings.

My favorite is the forager (+ bacon). There’s not enough pizza joints doing cream based sauces and this one is delicious!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPwMvG9aV3EGnEnAHvGICC5k98GDJn933rWhTh9&fid=0x0:0x13d6b7d52babeea"],"When":"2024-7-19"},{"Name":"Alexandra B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI34csndi8g_W5d38YtSOZDCRjtyMdXHMWvPlV136of0FURsg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Tried their pizza for the first time and every pizza tried was delicious. The dough is cooked perfectly. Our group tried the figgy piggy, max, forager (personal favourite) and the hot stuff. We were not disappointed with any of our choices. All of the toppings were very fresh. Service was extremely fast. Atmosphere is very clean, simple and the perfect spot to stop in for a quick bite.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mikayla W","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXrzwUPecZFd0iHu9hL83IJG4wPDLoRyYpqrkvrkbLlIbjS0Nw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"New favourite pizza place in Ladner! (and we have tried them all). Crust is crispy but also has a nice chew. Nice and thin wood fired crust. Toppings are great and fresh. Even the sauces (tomato and alfredo) are delicious and not too heavy. They are also extremely nice and very accommodating. Happy to have them in town and will order again!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPxrewLzffKW1-LEbqgU1m32IvL7PCbCZ6zW5tU&fid=0x0:0x13d6b7d52babeea"],"When":"2024-4-24"},{"Name":"Frias Fight Team","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXm2Sdehq7i7pnEbVbcNEui08_LITsNfGUL7YuPoicIubfTxMk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Delicious pizza, great flavours ingredients and a thin crust which I love. The forager pizza and the pepperoni are both phenomenal, I ended up ordering more while sitting down because they were so tasty. Highly recommend coming here and checking it out!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMT5oaFOXh9GtRIVV2vijUIg1_-76CwAF4SRaXs&fid=0x0:0x13d6b7d52babeea"],"When":"2024-4-13"},{"Name":"Max Erickson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVz3dwhz2Iz0uC9vQRsiPEcFdDiRVvnC_NMnW4Qw-l_l2eI6_M8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Tried the pesto chicken pizza and veggie/vegan flatbread.

Flatbread wasn't my favorite but it was still very good.

Pizza was very very good, thin, flavorful and well cooked. Will definitely order another pizza from here in the future. Can't wait!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOZ4Axi1wXaxLGJWQtkYArkfDJR4MaTKVtOVlF-&fid=0x0:0x13d6b7d52babeea"],"When":"2024-3-22"},{"Name":"Kj Deol","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIVZtlp5eFyS3gVRRAGabrjFjxQUXx7lFhnEHqMeeY8A4Q9vg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was in the neighborhood after a long time and noticed this place. Went in with my brother and ordered 2 pies which we got during the happy hour promotion. I'm a simple man so I had to get the cheese and the other one I was feeling adventurous and went with the rose. I was blown away with the flavor of the pizza as well as the bite into the crust.  I've got another reason to come back to this area more. 10/10","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nicolae Roman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXwrXM8xiI7NMfY6vYoUI-_JWhnu0tHltZBV8Xh9UxRwexx5sfL=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fantastic environment and really nice staff, the pizza is one of the best I've had from a oven pizza place. Glad to see there is something local in Ladner like this. They do sell slices aswell if you are just shopping in the area","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPeUQUxwkgyx4rUpTpIQ3oXxVtf0feal8xNRKgW&fid=0x0:0x13d6b7d52babeea"],"When":"2024-5-21"}]

Food prices elsewhere seem to be all over the place, but here they make an effort to be affordable and easy to access!

Great food presentation and a cozy environment to have a chat in.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM6mOFRQjq9MHi6Vngu1OXfx3F1nilc5Fp22jC_&fid=0x0:0x736d41a38b5157b2"],"When":"2024-11-6"},{"Name":"Elmira Nazari","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUS8psOPde-fgvVYsglTVKj-j9hpNdB1347mGr_T9d11yAStREO4w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Food was incredibly fresh and delicious. Super busy spot, so service was not the best, but they made it work. They have cold glass jap beer if you'd enjoy one.
- Aburi sushi was on point. Fresh with a g
nice texture and fatty flavour.
- special roles were well made.
- Mango tango roll was sweet and savoury deliciousness.

I order almost weekly and never ever regret it!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Aanand Singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUDzHd-80_Di6Z2Z8u-86wJPBJU44FXOvMRPh7WFunTmw96E82s=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great authentic indian food! Friendly service. Reasonable prices. Our new go to!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"ASHU RAINA","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXkcwzqhcYYUfV06ZomIp43dL6VwS328TE9DgDNX2AI2_zy9gTvew=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"We had paranthas for breakfast and faced issues with all of them. Ghobi parantha was all scrambled and Aalo parantha did not have salt in it. When communicated the issue with the staff, they tried proving us wrong. This is not customer service when you try to prove the customer's opinion or problem baseless/wrong. Won't ever visit again!","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"July M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWPev1MGk8g7gho65nL58g_fBB-niZ6_zdN_uI9W2I5IhKVkLnN=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I visited this coffee shop for the first time and specifically requested a non-sweet cookie, which was absolutely delicious, along with a latte. Both were perfect. The service was friendly and welcoming. Great experience overall!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMa53cVS6ZTDGxR1kO5-W8J5i_Jb_w2UAp_CV2z&fid=0x0:0xe18a2afd96eb49d4"],"When":"2024-9-11"},{"Name":"Minji Co","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW0cW7yUIGQwxewtq2t91XH-PweiJmGMnXmQUWs9lKXUa5ZbKC6vQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"They have some unique drinks on the menu but I ordered the traditional flat white which was delicious!! 👍🏻

Servers were all friendly and lots of parking in the area.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPpHysWn-PBRZQB9dltxyGu8wCZgNxFQvDTNLXV&fid=0x0:0xe18a2afd96eb49d4"],"When":"2024-8-3"},{"Name":"Alicia Archer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU94NoAUo-reqA_8E5P1ww6vS09a_CWhkBDXdwTYWveC0MNK1Qi=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Mid at best.

Ordered two simple drinks. Both were super diluted and bitter. They also didn't put the flavor shot in we requested.

Got home and mentioned our lack luster experience to family. Without even mentioning the name of the shop they already knew who we were talking about.

Just sad because the location and atmosphere suggest they'd be better, and the place was empty when we ordered so there wasn't even the pressure of a rush to explain the bad product.

Staff was polite enough though.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Christopher Cliff","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX48zUpRrirDLCbbcO1JxvHVyUc21lKplohfJf2oB7SfkpzE0Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great coffee shop in Ladner. Grab a coffee to go and hit up the thrift stores! That's what I do!

The layout of the coffeeshop makes sense, allowing for a lineup, a waiting area for orders, and a decent cafe / patio seating area.

I love the coffee, the selection of milk alternatives,  the vinyl that gets played, and rare these days: the washrooms are tidy and clean. (Though perhaps they are on the verge of needing a bit of TLC).","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMTAOSrxSaCOCACPaHfZJ7FuWXestAftlBtDHjz&fid=0x0:0xe18a2afd96eb49d4"],"When":"2024-8-9"},{"Name":"Kelly Argue","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVHguvt2mUYK3ZLLT7t42H3YMBdzPp4wF0FbC-_ZBGyrnECZG3faw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"This place has a great location and wonderful courteous and helpful staff.
There wasn't a lot of vegetarian options for savory treats so I got the almond croissant, which is a personal favorite. There was a lot of sweet filling and it was huge, not necessarily my style but it was still good.
I got a decaf caramel oat milk latte and the coffee was quite bitter and I had to put extra sweet in it.
All in all it was a good experience and I'll go back.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Christina","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVS2sq4B4h1VNEAHPNyMb13fPFbu4xvPJGto5RC_j2_kf5ywyBT=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I suspect they were having an off day the day we walked in for our one and only visit with them. We had the kind of experience that makes you regret pre-paying a tip that reflects great service.

It was not crowded or super busy in there. There were two tables free and no queue. A flat expressionless face greeted us and rang our order in. She promptly forgot our lemon loaf the minute we paid for it. Sat down thinking it might be brought to us but it wasn’t. Had to get up and ask for it. Got an apology. They gave us a dirty tea cup. Had to go up and exchange it. Got an apology. There’s no milk out for self-serve. Had to go up and ask for it.

I’m pretty low maintenance so it has to be exceptionally poor service for me to write this sort of review. Hoping this was a rare experience because otherwise it seemed like a great little cafe. Also, an unclaimed bag sat on the love seat the entire time we were there making us think someone was sitting there and perhaps just in the bathroom, but no. So there was a lovely seat left empty on a Sunday afternoon because staff were not really engaged.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nik Hik","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV8EtdPJeHnYK1rFp_5oxOZlQloWdY3g56lL9W_moBmlTS6JboP=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Have the pleasure of working in Delta and stumbling across this charming little place. Outstanding coffee, hands down best traditional cappuccino I've ever tasted. Food is incredible (particularly the chicken club). Great staff, consistently awesome service and products. Highly recommend!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPLuvf_-_rDZHj8RlHI0bzH9TQqwsze0353kjGC&fid=0x0:0xe18a2afd96eb49d4"],"When":"2023-6-2"},{"Name":"S R (RamRoad)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWTuRXqijs8BhgMnzK7J9Ym7JABL4HcxpwlRMGaThlIPkDrCTk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Not sure what happened but the espresso was top notch for years here until recently.   I gave it another shot today and it was bitter , less than 2oz (double shot) and left a horrible after taste.      Shame because this was the best coffee house south of the Fraser for a long time.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Paulina Pedrero Miranda","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXoiOld2vaC2Dv18bWNi8EDRiykD7MSCRsU3RK7RESh6xQghXxb=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Nice place to have breakfast, the ladies are very friendly and helpful, but here are a lot of options, great variety of coffee and hot beverages, baked goods salty and sweet, combo breakfast like sandwich and soup, the place is small but warm.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPto4Tcv79zG6wm8-hMzFijXMDbk6VfbBskpuyN&fid=0x0:0xc46381d25939e8fe"],"When":"2024-4-17"},{"Name":"Munchica","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXbQ6ACs51IPQJlRLrmnunOErED8bimOf5-y1uov4EWpuZvjQQjrA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Real homestyle classic foods here made with quality ingredients. I had the turkey brie melt which was delicious and fresh. Their speciality baked bread even had cranberries baked into it and they also added apple to the sandwich which was a nice touch making it both sweet and savory. I liked this place. Looking forward to try their Shepherd's Pie and quiches in the future.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO1SUtMM-P-A27VadSiRWle0B1kw2uPzjEnHynD&fid=0x0:0xc46381d25939e8fe"],"When":"2021-7-22"},{"Name":"Tiana Gordon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVYMz1yUZuEgKHa2uDK3PxaRYn4dyPS_QcB-fy1T_3nxy8-9jZy=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I went here to get lunch while working in Ladner one day.
I ordered a sandwich and told the person taking my order and making the sandwich I’m allergic to dairy. I also asked for gluten free bread (a preference, not an allergy, which I told them).
They seemingly had no knowledge of their ingredients and actually had to bring out their jar of mayo for me to read to see if it had dairy.
The person then asked me if I wanted cheese on my sandwich… I obviously said no.
It wasn’t until after I was back at my work site and took my sandwich out of the wrapping that I realized the gluten free bread they substituted was in fact cheese bread.
I’m not sure how they didn’t catch this after I mentioned at least twice that I’m allergic to dairy.
Needless to say I was incredibly disappointed to not have a lunch that day, and I would not be going back as it seems they are unable to accommodate dietary restrictions.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lee Gildemeester","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUmwK5TPiyJO9K2BikS-yqaHifl8H0QHLdeDujEGzwKhWsKSXQ7=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Love the homemade feel of the food but seriously lacking in ingredients. My tuna melt had twice as much bread as both tuna and cheese combined, and the potato salad, while enjoyable in its simplicity, needed more flavour. At $10 for a sandwich I expect more food than a minuscule line of tuna and so little cheese I need to closely inspect the sandwich to make sure the cheese is even there.

Also it’s rude when businesses prompt me for a tip on the machine when I didn’t sit down at eat in the establishment. I came in, ordered, and left to eat elsewhere. No service was provided so why am I being prompted to tip? Knocking a star off the review for greedy tipping prompt.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jordan Polgar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX7C0SgKQzDvqRzNpQxit3us52V-jc-OQYXuRvCyoY-5Z6qHBQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A quaint and unassuming little cafe, with fresh made soups, sandwiches, salads and hot beverages. Staff are friendly, and everything appears to be made in house. A wonderful spot for lunch.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMCHiNA59HmVj1yDQHkeoAwK4TBB3l1tp0-9OAO&fid=0x0:0xc46381d25939e8fe"],"When":"2017-3-4"},{"Name":"Mr Mckenzie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ_BxPYDr2y3voCm_NUkWQ4KNhyyaNBjo_DUK5jjIu-c33iKA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"If you like soggy a grilled sandwich - then enjoy, here it's microwaved and grilled, there's nothing gourmet about this place.
So disappointed","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Greg","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKEbsNJ3VwdzUJfJHVNQHq_iJl5Kf2D32xWuwwM8B1bnVunRA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"great Chilli and cheese pasta salad ..nice litte coffee / tea shoppe. .sandwich s made to order ...great staff..and good beef barley soup","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"John Autin (RJ’s Custom Detailing)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX6OJnMbuoaXAllJq-r8SXN2kVZVB-scSuLJA20qRNjh4A-4FzXSA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Everything I have tried at Cafe de Gourmet has been excellent.  Generous portions of their baked goods, easily 5 stars!","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Caleb Gallacher","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIHYEJtESOFHCZNx4k97gkuaJd71UDWV20zSPRKilwfYjkqKg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Not from here, yet I’m very impressed by their prices on beer. A 600ml beer is $6 - $8 which is nice on the pocket. The food here is good too. It isn’t renovated and not the most cozy place, but it’s the best place I’ve gone for a beer in a long time. Much better than the Rose and Crown and the Landing. The regulars seemed quite nice as well, along with the kind and honest staff. This place is a solid 8/10!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"David Holland","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIwojmWLax6tCAsluMeRYRcULAx9_6vDJad6FfkXbF3IYuaOOU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Speed's Pub in Delta is on the water, Fraser River, just up from the Ladner Harbour Boat Basin, by the Ladner Pier, in fact it is next door to Sharkey's Seafood Bar & Grille.
They served a respectable size piece of breaded cod, with the menu's listed fish & chips selection (cheaper as daily special on Tuesday).
A varied selection of both food choices and drinks. Draft beers included Guinness dark stout for a reasonable price!
The narrow patio by the water was pretty full when we arrived late in the lunchtime rush but as couples left, the two-tops by the water's edge became available for the 'later' lunch crowd or even happy hour guests.
Parking is available on the street and in front. With Sharkey's right next door, not certain how the parking is shared or gets too crowded?","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMJ6i4YMzV1jK5SNRM8YpvXPwFj0vp0OfziKADO&fid=0x0:0xe01f3ec377c88785"],"When":"2024-6-20"},{"Name":"Diane Leiter","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUyXk9fyDM9oMAi1nBBq-NeNkATe4RG0P2HwlXxGvuvY3BeYVaj=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Neighborhood pub with great atmosphere, and right on the water. Food was wonderful, ample servings, and a good selection of beer. Accessible to all. Very friendly and helpful service. I didn't have the kind of ice tea I liked, so she made it for me. Awesome.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO2BAgtq272CU8y8333I2_bkLbyO8DESAcahi0B&fid=0x0:0xe01f3ec377c88785"],"When":"2023-9-9"},{"Name":"Torchie 2010","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXJqYIiPOFAtESxtEjn8bxUeO-DrBaKlnQ5IbOahr9roKXwkjwj=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went to the Ladner Farmers Market and walked around and saw this Pub by the Dease island slough.
Had Fish N Chips and Ceasers to drink.
Very nice, nothing fancy
Sunday Special Fish n Chips Cod 19.99 for 2 pc","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN-3gI3ZnaFLVa-A67RahtL_JNFL7INtgjKPwQc&fid=0x0:0xe01f3ec377c88785"],"When":"2023-7-23"},{"Name":"Dani","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI0rASNM3UoTaBI1w_-GDXRfdkjX2-OvaVRSoBQ9UJje7neMw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great food & a great patio. So nice that they allow dogs on the lower part as well. Great weekly deals!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMKSUIwA1TaFhQhv60qdC0vsN5A212uasvEAx5b&fid=0x0:0xe01f3ec377c88785"],"When":"2024-7-8"},{"Name":"Chris MacDonald","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUaD_C5C9feF_MEkQ2fFDc5cG1u4m6lAVed4bAYShNFRcTb6uI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Dined for two of us for happy hour. And the staff held out the food to go until it was beyond the happy hour time limit and so not to give the deal. When brought to the staff she said she had nothing to do with it. Unfortunate to offer the happy hour time but then to force a cold takeout meal. Staff must give leniency to the time when arrival and departure or you're going to lose the regular s that come there for the time that you're asking them to. Shame on speeds.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shawn B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIiLz_Fvu2Z_sAsud0kUXYcpIhrTzSkTDXj-dxi9MqAOVzC5A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Good drinks, fish and chips could be ALOT better. The servers are nice and the service is good. It is definitely a decent place during the summer for a quick bite or a beer on the patio, I would stick to the beer or drinks only, pass on the fish and chips","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"54sputnick","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXRGGRadB2kuHfTripjCMYlzqw93kIJfA9P_HvEu2OVglBQNcU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Went on Sunday for the prime rib dinner. While the beef was tender, the Yorkshire Pudding lovely, the so called mashed potatoes  were terrible! Not really mashed, large chunks of partially cooked potato, very little mash. The thickness of the meat served was in our opinion too thick. In all, was not the Sunday roast dinner we had been looking forward to.
The server did tell us the head chef was not on site, soooo could explain it, but won’t be running back for more soon.😕","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews: [{"Name":"Gina Grape","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKjfpAS0e1J9DlXOCRvxRrfnAvo44TyYUw59aPp0ohD7GacQA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Taste and quality of the food is good. More than enough options to go with depending on what you are craving for.  I had lunch special that comes with miso soup - teriyaki chicken with  tempura; bro and wife went for udon soup, karaagi, and bento.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO3yQOGXsG8u4WU7FyMwu-L-c4lQhpBL7mADw6f\u0026fid=0x0:0x88b0154276b56a25"],"When":"2023-7-22"},{"Name":"Munchica","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXbQ6ACs51IPQJlRLrmnunOErED8bimOf5-y1uov4EWpuZvjQQjrA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent quality salmon here! You can taste the difference. The dinner combo bento E includes a bit of everything such as tasty fresh terriyaki salmon, refreshing sunomono salad, two spring rolls, salmon and tuna sashimi, assorted nigiri, and crispy shrimp and vegetable tempura. Service was awesome! Well done!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPKiWvOMfRJpaIwgkAQR2i3UCxKTE8N3lJIDTsT\u0026fid=0x0:0x88b0154276b56a25"],"When":"2021-7-3"},{"Name":"Joey Mullins","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVjA9hfj_Ijm7nk28n3Pwuv3ZUU8ObFM0Pq6x9qasT5gDb6RMN8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ladner sushi is the go to place when it comes to authentic food and great service. The cuts of sushi in the combos we ordered were fresh and tasty. We got more value then we expected for the money, especially with their after 4pm combo. The desert, which is either mango or green tea cheese cake, is too delicious for words. We will be coming again here soon!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMN7zU_C9vXdKIZ1MfrSexvGTrjwFQwULAnixE4\u0026fid=0x0:0x88b0154276b56a25"],"When":"2022-6-12"},{"Name":"Drd Cameron","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLxYa2qx-iJcYkg-8p-Wnm3pY-GsSAREUZ6W8RVzYEfVaabcA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My wife and I go here 2-4 times a month. She is vegetarian and I'm the fish lover. We love our food, service, and freshness, quality overall.  Plus reasonable prices. I'm always amazed at how many families eat here. The kids all seem to love their sushi.....","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"D","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocImPOcJCm5CCEOa5wt5zZstcHUVRP_7OnV_asTIaMaNpvwXFw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Fast service and a good-sized sockeye sashimi plate. Reasonable prices - dinner for two $31. The place is a little run down - the tables need re-surfacing (linoleum was peeling off), and the washroom could use a renovation.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMenPblL06POMJfv-ZIyzGC3x65kPjxYGczwhXM\u0026fid=0x0:0x88b0154276b56a25"],"When":"2017-11-13"},{"Name":"Hamed","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjViJ9EznENDd1HeEqpUkYuqmZFdKwptQI-w0AYNvWdb_l07iQpU7w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The quality of food was great. The food arrived bit late cause they do a lot of takeout.\n\nA must try sushi place in Ladner.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMvvi6PipUmbsi6I2Lmaa5OD3jlVYyWC8AxVg_5\u0026fid=0x0:0x88b0154276b56a25"],"When":"2024-2-27"},{"Name":"Simon Chung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV1hOsKIoj9bFpzabsd3fL9vgr9Zy2VYnc2w3EE29msDfHdYeWL=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This rating is less about the food than the exemplary customer service. I had left behind one of my personal belongings after eating there. As I was about to get into my car, the owner of the restaurant chased me down and returned my item. I was very grateful. Thank you, sir! I did enjoy the food;I ordered the beef bento box.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM2ocAt8PW0ZNqNOPyLO6JTSl-GjRNAejQ3I2GP\u0026fid=0x0:0x88b0154276b56a25"],"When":"2017-10-21"},{"Name":"Angie L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKwNm9A8ohrfnu_XFwYhP8N-ACXPuzjT8lHAp_d40ZyvMetcg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Portion is small. The bento sashimi combo was soso and a bit too cold. Sushi was okay. The wooden bento tray looks beat up and chipped. Should be changed. Service is good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP0SIT6rqqwqz1JWv4VR2RSxIqtnCxne6Wbp74r\u0026fid=0x0:0x88b0154276b56a25"],"When":"2020-1-17"}]

He really enjoyed the pizza and asked me to leave a review :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMdMC5FrC_lfohztBkNAiRIpwIdXBc_-FLKuNKE&fid=0x0:0xcf177a97095e5b7c"],"When":"2024-4-3"},{"Name":"大阪のただの旅人","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjURlp73KTwNhlMfzPxLKShc4VQKjji0cCIyPO6Iy8CjssIjmY9F=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I experienced good customer service!
Kindly and good smile!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kyla S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVKsxnJ6h9XgOZGp7G-opm0ZXiFvIrt6L7FHitbPL8EkbaeDMm7yA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"First time here! Ordered a heart shaped pizza online, came in to get it 20 mins later and they didn't make it. They didn't call because it was long distance but instead of making just a regular shaped pizza the exact same they figured to just not make it at all.

So I ordered at the counter and the same thing was going to be $7 more for a regular pizza shape!?! Then the phone rang so he thought getting the phone and taking their order for 6 minutes would be the best customer service, while I was at the counter waiting to re-order a pizza that I ordered from home.

He finally came back and we figured out a pizza...then 3 mins later (when I figured they might actually be making it) he called me over to confirm the receipt before they made it. What the actual f*¢k!?

Wait he's calling me again...asking me to cancel my order online now. I checked and it says "call the restaurant to change or cancel order". I have so much more confidence now that they don't even know their system.

I don't think I've ever hit the no tip button harder. Let's hope they don't spit in my, basically not cooked, kid's pizza.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOCEnDPJtRxpyQNSRUiFHWSY4og7edULq_zrzhX&fid=0x0:0xcf177a97095e5b7c"],"When":"2019-4-8"},{"Name":"Tania Michaud","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJMWTmbEy-8rR36r-pLexZJr9pdnnA4AatMZolVSlw7kMQdIA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I don’t usually write reviews, but after my experience I thought I’d write one up as feedback. My first impressing walking in wasn’t the best, they had the signs inside right infront of the door so it was really difficult to get in, quite hazardous for people with injury’s or disability’s. Maybe it was because it was 30 minutes before closing? But if you order a pizza they should expect people to be coming in before closing. So it felt quite unwelcoming. For the food I was disappointed after a spending $40 bucks on two medium gluten free pizzas that I paid extra for the toppings and didn’t receive them as I looked into the box at first glance I was disappointed. When I got home to eat the pizza, the crust was raw. I’ve had the gluten free pizza before and it’s been absolutely delicious, so to take a bite into raw pizza dough was unpleasant. I’m not sure if they weren’t familiar with the gluten free dough so they didn’t cook it long enough? I’m hoping next time it’ll be better, and it was just an accident. I’m hoping this feed back helps so I can write a better review next time.. that’s why I’m out three stars instead of one over all.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Pamp","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWMpR-jKX3SH-UAeP6exk1_-nuaVfXGkjLBfV_oNZ76gTZMqPHD=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"As soon as I took a sip of my hot chocolate, my taste buds started dancing. Best hot chocolate I've ever had. The sugar is a delicious add on. It's so sweet and more importantly, it doesn't taste like hot water. It actually tasted like hot chocolate. My taste buds thank Freshslice. The pizza was pretty good. But very greasy. I do not mind grease but if you do then don't come.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Navdeep Atwal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLBnbbwqP2WwMGb5scnRekCpGaeKpN6Yszv7RjqJIrRpcuIzYU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I never write reviews, but I really want to appreciate the owner. I placed an order which was not delivered even after waiting for an hour. I called the store, and the owner was genuinely apologetic even though it wasn't his fault. He remade the order and came to deliver it by himself within 15 minutes and also gave me coupons. Outstanding service and genuinely kind demeanor from the owner.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brett Gabelman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXpxmxG5dvgirTTPqbPMc_s8DXA8CndoB4hWgHURQxilkUTGKd1=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"It is quick and affordable pizza. Definitely not fancy but a good spot for a quick slice or an affordable pizza.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Simone J.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVS3fxG-cYEa7dmUP1lFMJ2_F3sRTKOJqfUMxWnmGGF5kzo43Yi=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Ordered 8 Chicken Bites with Garlic Parmesane Sauce, got 7 Chicken Bites and some burned pieces of batter, swimming in grease with no sauce in sight. Do yourself a favor and go somewhere else.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPPUgkulJmhZARwIppIjLbANkzEM8Aae9fnKTf5&fid=0x0:0xb17ec7b8f392cb48"],"When":"2024-7-14"},{"Name":"Kelsea Perry","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX-3dlGjgCHcKB_hnAp1nqcAbsA1tpkGddbU2u0CtaGUfkLQPVi=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Served an order of the cheesy pull apart bread that was both raw and soggy from grease. The dough was transparent. This is an ongoing health and safety issue from the look of other reviews. This place is going to make someone seriously sick.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO_3sO39nVm8skfplNmyT7Ze7ykJ1LMOyuGgTzO&fid=0x0:0xb17ec7b8f392cb48"],"When":"2024-5-19"},{"Name":"Rae-Rae","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWPCyVddTIP8SIkm6OkuBcnFk-xarfcwuv8l7lIHMRxU6aAkTxl=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"HORRIBLE. DO NOT COME HERE. DO NOT WASTE YOUR TIME.
I can’t believe they would serve this. My pizza wasn’t cut properly one is the size of a pinky and the other the size of a dinner plate and WORST OF ALL it is burnt. 2 slices are black. I can’t even tell which part is pepperoni and what part is cheese because of how dark the cheese is.

I called them IMMEDIATELY when coming home and the girl was extremely apologetic but all she said was we can give you next time. It was all next time. I wanted one today because my family is hungry but she kept saying it will be for next time. I then asked how will I know you would even credit me and she just said we will tell our workers and then hangs up to say we’ll call you later to properly speak to a manager. I got nothing. How are they still open?!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM7eDy-EAzSKPhEsbpz0lgVdujU_jNR6Gt1NJaI&fid=0x0:0xb17ec7b8f392cb48"],"When":"2024-1-19"},{"Name":"Monique Osborne","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUe9LHJ_aOGyJ7HExXyiv3mbzWz6qozugQbCLmKbOPSJNAjgrYl=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Just had a horrible experience. Check your credit cards for double billing. I'm usually very happy to please but I have to speak up on this one. Ordered on the app, when I received a notice it did not go through. So I phoned it in and paid cash. Low and behold my credit card was charged too. So, I brought the evidence with the coordinating order numbers to the restaraunt and the staff told me to dispute in on VISA. I call visa they say I have to wait 10 days. 2x 20 min waits later, I just got cut off on phone. I'm furious. This should have been an easy "return" my money to my credit card. I imagine I'm not the first nor the last. So check your credit cards for double billing.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Payne Dawson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJj9DW_0svFpqfBkXOGG7p4BCpRoX_AgEPBMEOJV4-LOZ5SSg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Me and My boyfriend ordered 3 mid pizza's thar had no taste and terrible texture. there are so many better options in the local area than this","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Silas Klassen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWTrT-4CPcQsCtkTuS5T1bM0WRJ_XDoq4etriFvn4_9_ZKDD84V=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I came for repizza Day where i can get a free medium pizza for giving them a box and i got told by the woman at the front  and their manager that it did not happen even when i show them the official rules and day it was happening. I am very disappointed as I did not have a lunch that day","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Richard Glasner","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVlFSX_UUx6rW0lix6i7dkX9lVOSyBZB-F5xxqlskw_ZqxWVSPR=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I just ordered a pizza 🍕 not only did the email say it was here 15 minutes before it arrived 15 minutes late but it's not fully cook and when I called to complain they just hung up!!! Sadly I will never ordered again. Worst customer service ever!!!! So they called back later and all they will do is send another pizza so as she said I can leave a bad review.  So I highly recommend not ever ordering for here. In today's economy customer service is at the top but they don't seem to care!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"William Griffin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIcC5_EkSwcvw2mKy6aunV7gktpKFDfov793tXx1HstKAKhdQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The time I order a pizza from this location they cheap out on the toppings, a crust normally is around 1 inch but not at this place the crust is more than half of the pizza barely any cheese and toppings. They are not making pizza they are making a flatbread. I would bet that the people making the pizza have never even tried pizza absolutely the worst pizza I’ve ever had","Images":null,"When":""}]

The food was so delicious. So fresh. So yum. Happy hour makes drinks affordable!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPW6foHIbGfcVXcqX6Y8DmNsJJy9boNuZ-o8RI4&fid=0x0:0xcbf2a40a858564d2"],"When":"2024-9-28"},{"Name":"Christina K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLVjQInhnlTpctqjtKkyBuOFC73N2d82UYBNLgtyl-x2vd3fSs=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Had a party of 12 for a Christmas get together on Dec 10. Place was not busy at all. After 20 minutes of being seated, no server came to take our drink order. I had to go to the front to find our server to ask for service (who was on her phone at the bar). Same happened when we were ready to order. She rarely came to our table. Had to leave the table several times to get our server. With an 18% automatic gratuity I guess she did not feel the need to put in the effort as she would be getting her tip no matter what. Food was good but service was poor. Tips should be earned for good service and not imposed. The service we received did not match the 18% gratuity that was imposed on us. For this reason alone, we will not be returning no matter how good the food was.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"sng1002001","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLTfKdGFrJyL8jc4znhIMXimj1BkuJ1S_SEthxZmoeo2Gf8Rg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Have a late night family dinner at the restaurant. Glad to find a sit down restaurant late at night.

Menu items are pretty standard. Good selection of drinks with special on certain day and hours. Servers friendly and attentive. Only complaint is that the fries were a bit soggy. May be it was late at night or pre-fried from an earlier batch. Too hungry to complain at that moment.

Definitely a good place to hang out and serve as the neighborhood watering hole.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOf6Z9srvvfv7OjCTaU7EUDVUEl5_1wUnqDI6FG&fid=0x0:0xcbf2a40a858564d2"],"When":"2023-7-10"},{"Name":"Susan Flesher","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVZrGHunFEVWLl-Tmw-7Cvt3W7vP_TNBTYw4HVnyszqxmDXbqE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went for dinner a couple nights ago and Deshae was great. She says she's new but her serving was accurate, friendly and prompt. I had the Fish Tacos! Yum!
My husband had a burger, which he says is always,r reliably, good!
Thankyou!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nafisa Nazmul","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXQ6V6OhfCWxPT6Qcukw2Lf3ApGG5qm9asyWHLVMjgu0yMiRWfw8Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Personal and cordial!

My husband and I went there to celebrate his big career achievement. We were in mood for Mexican food and they had decent reviews. We ordered three items: Chicken Thai Soup, Small Nachos, and DRY RIBS.
We loved Nachos and soup but dry ribs was below average (for our tastebud).
Our lovely waitress was engaging throughout our dinner so she quickly noticed that we didn’t touch Dry Ribs. We didn’t even ask for a takeout container. Our waitress made sure that we knew how important customer service was to them.
Therefore to our utter surprise, she came back with the bill while saying, “We took care of the Ribs.”
We wanted to clarify and mentioned that they didn’t charge us for the Ribs, to which she said that their top priority was customer satisfaction!!!

We tried to tell her that it’s an issue of personal taste which has nothing to do with their food, but they were firm with their stance!
In my three years in Vancouver, we never experienced so much warmth from a place. Their food, atmosphere made our celebration joyful but their management team made it perfect ♥️","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipONTQZOgWBenIxiPe5qaFYUyvLEjIOLkqPmqK1r&fid=0x0:0xcbf2a40a858564d2"],"When":"2023-7-22"},{"Name":"Ebrahim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXPIKcLlYsRXzj_NU-cKrILAfiV6rHoottOnSl1Co3QI6YN1537=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love the food here. Everything is so tasty here. The staff always take care of you so well.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN7JcTC2edGiOl8XSmPBQ3s6H66-JVOvNy1yS_y&fid=0x0:0xcbf2a40a858564d2"],"When":"2023-12-30"}]
