[{"Name":"Kaiti Luyt","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV6yOScSyx0mctSBHf70jnx-vlzy4EB9gjzKXJZfHbHC35asPNR=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an amazing meal at Ramie’s last night. This family-owned gem has recently opened a second location in Delta, and I’m so glad we gave it a try. Initially, I was a bit uncertain about the location, but it turned out to be absolutely worth it- and we’ll be back.

The food was delicious. The beef souvlaki was melt-in-your-mouth, and the portions were generous. My husband, who’s a big eater, had leftovers for the first time in history. The prices were very reasonable for the quality and quantity.

We also had the opportunity to take a peak at their newly renovated private room upstairs, which is available for rent. Seems like a great spot for a social gathering or work party.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNEF0bwypD9QGsSh6hZatC5Yo0vnPOchwPfmSXi&fid=0x0:0xa75fe21e2adf8a11"],"When":"2024-12-6"},{"Name":"Leslie Gilker","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJmai_3H3HwS9svez3CowLlSmWqOxBDd7lXlUwqseaCZnolLw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Tasty meal, good portions and great prices on their wine. Nice to try a new place and close to home on a rainy cold evening.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPflYGuAZP_5gbsTfBuD06XdnsjiB36dR2DNnVR&fid=0x0:0xa75fe21e2adf8a11"],"When":"2024-11-17"},{"Name":"L Johnson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVNXnB0qZV3V6VvXHSvI5L_5FB2A7crO3fFgJGGxEYx2B1_XBw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This Greek restaurant has been here for a long time, but seems to be under new management as of late September. The food is excellent, the portions are generous, the service is great (shout-out to our server, Kirsten, for taking such good care of us), and the prices are quite reasonable. I have had two excellent business lunches there, and went initially on the recommendation of a family member who indicated her dinner experience was superb. The prawn souvlaki is excellent, but isn't on the list of dishes to recommend below.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jefray Magnusentosa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKTJd1UTjgkSA4SqpXx8pkrkS04FkVspsUZlT_XZ-4g_PfSJA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"best Greek in lower mainland with best taste and best professional customer service, foods very fast to arrives. Restaurant ambiance is like in a fancy premium restaurant but with reasonable prices. Try their Greek style back ribs and it was top notch! Will definitely return to try their other menu!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMg0g0qrl1tNsM1E2cCgKmOOXyi-FFqMSQ610Uy&fid=0x0:0xa75fe21e2adf8a11"],"When":"2024-1-8"},{"Name":"Debbie Cullen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIpXJDxvfJVaBFAt1Jx2Yts3y75HqDad13DwrvCEz8i2tpwAQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This was our 2nd visit to the Delta location & it didn't disappoint. Spanakopita dinner is so delicious, best I've ever had. Our waitress was Kirsten, an absolutely delightful & efficient server. Lovely atmosphere too, we'll be back!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"James Adegboye","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUZ0nofPFbCsKol6tk2QNNP_y98-xtP9FSoEHYf9Rz-7efyJ4xMDg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Seems like a family run restaurant because it felt homely. The food was good and affordable. I had the lamb souvlaki and I really can't complain. The waitress was very welcoming. The atmosphere was quiet so my friend and I could talk. They close early so you have to get there early","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO2CIZz3koGf1MEVio-7buStyCPF0fgoiACkOEr&fid=0x0:0xa75fe21e2adf8a11"],"When":"2024-2-4"},{"Name":"Bella Marcellana","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWuNMsxjNQj4k3CDfGFcZW5BKv4g7-4u08Ctu57vopTUSMImPMH=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We drove from Vancouver to Delta for this place and it did not disappoint. The keftedes & calamari were so delicious and the ambiance was beautiful. Can’t wait to go back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPOnq3eamvECtfaqkkJFXiGkK1KfZh_TCtY-zUU&fid=0x0:0xa75fe21e2adf8a11"],"When":"2023-5-26"},{"Name":"Paul Yang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXn3m0AZWl28VYBOwUKfmGVllVddsvt-pe4tcU6-ebIHORKGYiIPQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We arrived around 7:20 ish and were rejected to dine in since they said the restaurant closed at 7:30pm. PS: It seems like every 5 star review will receive a Starbucks gift card from the restaurant.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNpHxqXnLGcWmkoMC4VuNna7Olf-S29OAvJnLeI&fid=0x0:0xa75fe21e2adf8a11"],"When":"2023-5-14"}]

[{"Name":"Madison G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVtZsEld-Yz5a2Swm5LesjF83lo03ZXPGgujeQvQiLn6WLaIuGx=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We ordered the Honey garlic Parmesan wings, mozza sticks, and Mac n cheese bites ! And they were all SUPER delicious. I highly recommend the HGP wings! It was a great mix of flavour! I would recommend ordering ahead of time because when I showed up to pick it up my food they were packed inside. I do wish they had two people at the front during rush hour to help with the flow of traffic. Maybe one person taking the online orders and one taking orders at the front because I did need to wait a bit to let them know my name. Either way, their food is very delicious, and they have a huge variety of wing flavours to choose from !","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMg9IoT8XmPkez5WQQF5fYPJel4ehHL8Prr_EUz&fid=0x0:0xa1ce476adc9b862a"],"When":"2024-6-17"},{"Name":"Parm Mann","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVHE0u-97kqTOD4PGwD81615zKrG7blg3TjYeRy2oRRaTlPZt0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The wings were amazing, both the regular and the fried wings! Fries were just ok, though they give you a lot. Poutine is a skip

My one complaint is I came on a Wednesday but the cashier forgot to give the wing Wednesday deal. I came back the next day with my receipt to let them know but was told they can't do anything because it's been a day. The food is good enough that I can overlook that annoyance though","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNBAwcTzVylCxvgReaafMQmHcKETjU7vH7_IfYG&fid=0x0:0xa1ce476adc9b862a"],"When":"2023-10-25"},{"Name":"Anthony D","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLiCKrN81h93D9flrP7vMUP_EHyYTxTt2xEpXssfa-QWwGh4A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dined in and did a pick up order via online app. Everything was smooth no issues and food was ready within 15 minutes. We were worried that staff might be upset if we changed to dine in but they even offered it when we arrived which was very nice.

Fries:
The serving is perfect for 2-3 people. firs were fresh, weren’t oily and tasted great. Crispiness is similar to Costco fries. Only suggestion is to have some ketchup laying around somewhere.

Wings - by far the best wings I had so far in Greater Vancouver. I’m from Toronto where we have a huge chicken wing scene. Vancouver severely lacks this and I was SO excited to find this place through a TikTok review.

The wings did not disappoint! Prices are super fair for the portions - we got Honey Garlic with Gar Par (One of my favorites from a chain back home). We got 2lbs - we hadn’t ate for the day and the 2lb + fries were perfect portions for 2 hungry people.

I’m looking forward to trying more items off their menu and more of wings!

Staff is super friendly too. This is a local Gem!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO5kHBSi1xtcdaPijgpwc8rXYKAm0sX25lG_5Eh&fid=0x0:0xa1ce476adc9b862a"],"When":"2023-5-5"},{"Name":"Vani_city Van city","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK2F5KckzTMfTrNaZqWOY10PmGBMznBJdnFNIayPiG-krBNjA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Food is tasty but slightly pricier compared to other places. The restaurant followed instructions on order delivery and food wasn't soggy when it got to me. Fresh and hot food . Will order from there again.

UPDATE: Unfortunately the restaurant isn't consistent. Ordered the exact same items on different occasions now and it wasn't the same. Not sure if they changed management. Saw a few other reviews about same issue, and very surprised by the owner's response. Please take accountability and make it right, do not make excuses. In the service business, one should take feedback and improve.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOJMEOA3u6dSCbOhikXNZj4b38lxRohb0EcGLcJ&fid=0x0:0xa1ce476adc9b862a"],"When":"2023-7-28"},{"Name":"Emma Bryce","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVkV2QE01SMTq5pWmdu7hEwuFK41S0j-1hMeveEqFezfjrBoDxg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Saw this place on Tik Tok and made the 1hr and 15 minute drive out. Wait was reasonable for any pizza joint and the wings were scrumptious. So many different things to choose from and they did not disappoint. Service was humorous and helpful, i’m really glad we came out to try!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP7myve6b8EQliJd0wgv8OWrllanP3Q4ComYfEb&fid=0x0:0xa1ce476adc9b862a"],"When":"2023-6-15"},{"Name":"Karen Qiu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU6GCT4a9XRttkQpqJqb28wNvbMPNXLYcgZEyOursXSh093iKU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It’s my second time visiting MN’A Wings Corner. Clean and simple shop offering great wings with tons of options. I’m a spicy lover but also bought non-spicy or less spicy for friends to enjoy. No wonder Devil Ranch is so popular- really addictive, but if you don’t eat spicy often, have your milk standby! Friends love Garlic Parmason (dry) and BC Girls (sweet taste).

Friendly staff and great service. Always open to feedback. Mayu, the new owner patiently asked me what do we normally like or if I would like to try something creamy or dry, explained what the flavour taste like and gave me recommendations, which made us a savory dinner with friends tonight.

PS: pictures were taken after 30mins on the road, still yum-yum! Gonna try pizza next time:)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP0gQ4IYZDSP-6CSrfo2R6NhLv5jYpjb0Z_LP0&fid=0x0:0xa1ce476adc9b862a"],"When":"2023-1-7"},{"Name":"OT","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIqcT-zkfZIx8U0I7pWWL7-kYHeUesJg7bStSZB3X1fHeLBEeqe=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great wings, friendly staff. Tons of sauce options. I had to get my wings without breading and they were able to accommodate. I’m keen to try their spicy flavours at some point, which they make in house.

Top left: honey bbq
Top tight: sweet chili
Bottom: spicy garlic parm","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNxa0Z6WbLLof5_RhZZWcUdThJGP1Xsphz5_4K3&fid=0x0:0xa1ce476adc9b862a"],"When":"2023-6-5"},{"Name":"Darren","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWOfPExYftWxqvIZMet7lotPlUSFXQ7unlUOpLlkeQpdPSdkf7x=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"How do I start this review, I had high hopes as this place has many 4+ star reviews. I bought the large meat lovers and my buddy got 1lb of buffalo bbq wings. My pizza was mid at best for $20 with tax, but overall could’ve been worse. Now for the wings, after getting home I took the wings off the pizza box and realized the issue, we had only received 1/2 lb of wings for $16. With the packaging it came to 0.73lbs. Personally this is ridiculous, $16 for 1/2lb of mediocre - dry - but relatively flavourful wings. Now the painful part, i was going to give them the benefit of the doubt and called to explained the issue, but was met with a condescending tone explaining they deemed 10-12 wings as 1lb which was most definitely not our case. I politely asked for a refund as I was quite frustrating but they just hung up on me. Mediocre food, less than paid for and unfortunately rude staff.

Update: I appreciate the fast response and have kindly uploaded the photo provided. I understand ~10 wings can weigh 1lb pre cooked. Unfortunately in light of this new information I still cannot personally recommend this establishment, the ~30% loss due to cooking, price point, quality of food and customer experience have just lost me.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM9Bfyl56eptSqBeF-u3mMnTKarZSr4KYvjVKur&fid=0x0:0xa1ce476adc9b862a"],"When":"2023-4-7"}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Praneet Raj","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU-I5iB9QpG5eztISNYObvNJI9swIkyqnUB25NJVMbN3zDz8_-1=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I ordered grilled chicken burgers from this McDonald’s location in Delta, BC, and the experience was satisfying. The restaurant was clean and well-maintained, which added to the overall positive impression. The service was quick and efficient, with my order being prepared in a timely manner. The staff were courteous, and everything seemed to be running smoothly despite a busy environment. The grilled chicken burgers were great , meeting my expectations for a quick and tasty meal. If you’re looking for fast service and a clean spot in the area, this McDonald’s is definitely worth a stop.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOIZTTJ8zDeP-klDe-YsViJIdk45VaduhBMF2TV&fid=0x0:0x6cfb50410b1b5274"],"When":"2024-10-10"},{"Name":"Rocky johnson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV-qbKTqm7jXjeR4bNESCYCbiBB0D1S1kiuff4Q-7RrKgiVG--a=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Stepping into this McDonald’s location, I expected the familiar consistency the Golden Arches is known for. Unfortunately, what I encountered was a far cry from the brand's usual standards. The food was presented in a haphazard manner—burgers seemingly assembled in a rush, with cheese sliding off the bun like an afterthought. To make matters worse, the burger buns were stale around the edges, further diminishing the overall experience.

The dining area itself was no better. Tables were visibly dirty and had not been cleaned in some time, with trash scattered around. To my shock, some individuals were even laying on the floors, creating a chaotic and uninviting atmosphere for guests.

What truly baffled me, however, was learning that this location does not honor complimentary drink refills for dine-in customers—a staple of the McDonald’s experience. It seems this franchise has chosen to deviate from the brand's norms and impose its own rules, leaving customers frustrated.

Adding insult to injury, the manager’s demeanor was outright rude when I inquired about the refill policy. Rather than addressing the concern with understanding, their dismissive attitude left a bitter taste far worse than the stale bun. I’ll be contacting corporate to seek clarity on whether this practice and approach are acceptable.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMFN7h8Qm4g5lUgQvMk6XF4G8xQaSTeyNCWYc5u&fid=0x0:0x6cfb50410b1b5274"],"When":"2024-11-19"},{"Name":"Adarsh Sivaprasad","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX4wLIi14ujjNuOiI0zrnXjP7vBI45ELITWJKrDSR6Rnzad9GvH=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Dear McDonald's Customer Service Team,

I am writing to formally express my dissatisfaction with the service I received at one of your locations. On [insert date], I placed an order that included four items, one of which was a box of chicken nuggets. However, upon receiving my order, I noticed that the chicken nuggets were missing. I immediately contacted the store to resolve the issue, but the response I received was far from satisfactory.

Firstly, when I called to report the missing item, the person on the phone provided a service that I found to be unprofessional. Not only was the resolution unclear, but the individual did not communicate the order code audibly, making the situation more frustrating.

When I visited the store in person to show my receipt and explain the situation, the staff did not even take the time to properly listen to my concern. Instead, they reacted by criticizing me and were unwilling to address the issue. I expected better from a global brand like McDonald’s, especially in terms of customer service and professionalism.

While the missing item was valued at only $8, it is not the amount but the principle of customer satisfaction and trust that is at stake. I believe that paying for an item and not receiving it constitutes a breach of trust, and the unprofessional handling of this issue only compounded my disappointment.

I kindly request that this matter be looked into and resolved appropriately. I would appreciate a refund for the missing item and any necessary action taken to ensure that this type of experience is not repeated for other customers.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOvNiaHAP01J5-MTpzLi8PhWRxwcLKXsq4qKJsI&fid=0x0:0x6cfb50410b1b5274"],"When":"2024-10-18"},{"Name":"amita Morker","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKvsZ5qFZb-WRJWkXiKEOAHm9ZqJPpaPiYkMLb4GWEfgDE0Wg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Rude service. Poorly made food. Sauce was not even on the inside of the burger. It's was wrapped around the outside on the bun. I've had multiple issues here. Poutine had cold cheese and gravy. Service was rude. I would not recommend. When I spoke to in charge Harman she did nothing to relieve the situation. Do not go here!!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNLcKui0XSm1tRZXuZgbHK5oYa9qSkzKqXKGHVY&fid=0x0:0x6cfb50410b1b5274"],"When":"2024-10-30"},{"Name":"Arjun Kumar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU8dzV51dWSvVh_Ew_XKNhFvmXHtngegIoXGetdts7J77ZmTXL4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food part of the place is as usual McDonald's.

On a Wednesday night , I assume all weeknights, around 8-9pm, the drive through took us around 15 or so minutes for 3 snack wraps.

Unless you are in a hurry, I would suggest check if there is a huge queue in front of you when you order.

Otherwise, 4/5 fast food!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Guru Simran","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVr0Pfr0xhcbOc2MhI8o0MpcBcHoJteCIa8Cg6tL6YVXRlE7n-i=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Worst experience here with food and staff. [{"Name":"a Natu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVkkJyNgnmmp-MozHsEh9Z4IsHH5-V_MXErSphecFoISVhBbrQD=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Epic garlic stuff crust pizza hands down the best stuffed crust pizza I had! Pizza hut stuffed crust is garbage, no filling, thin! Papa johns compared to this, taste like magic!

Had great service by a person named Akshay, wonderful gentlemen. On 11/29/24 at 1:30 for a pick up!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOaMwLqMNQqNsuBQ4amks90UXRiwITbRBgAF_q7&fid=0x0:0x1cf1ac02d30aef99"],"When":"2024-11-29"},{"Name":"N D","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI0-WuUYUEQLVwRVkL5g5jSRGlf8UIE_5XRbqwHwdtzrjKtiQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We recently did a large order for my sons bday. We have never ordered from any Papa John's locations before this experience. Before we confirmed our order we did call around to other places like Fresh Slice, Pizza Hut, Domino's and Apollo Pizza to get quotes. Out of everyone we called only Papa John's said Thank you for giving us an opportunity to provide a quote. Honestly the customer service and appreciation for our business is why we went with them. But I have to say we are very happy we did. The Pizza was very delicious especially the spinach Alfredo and everything went so smoothly.  We even got a call after to make sure everything was good. Thank you for the amazing service and delicious food.  We will definitely be ordering from you moving forward.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kellie Lok","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJBEodJfzXreZ9VCOYUE98DfuU5g08IKRYo3rXYnka5Xc_24w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We have been customers for years now and are very happy with this little gem in our neighbourhood! Their pizza is tasty and they have great service.  For example, there was an error in the scheduled pick up time and they made our pizzas earlier than I needed them. I went to pick them up as soon as I could and when I arrived, they told me they were remaking them because the pizzas were cold from sitting there. They also gave me a coupon code for my next purchase and one of the cooled pizzas for free.  It was very thoughtful and great service on their behalf. Good service is hard to come by now!!! Management is doing something right there. They will always be my go-to neighbourhood pizza joint :)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"georgia susheski","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVonT73Ed6O_A6z7oiiURRpX3VsVuc7mqo3_7780QgUNUjM1uAK=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"rudest delivery driver. tipped him 4$ on 10$ and told us he usually doesn’t except less than 20$. absolutely terrible service. regret even tipping 4$. definitely recommend ordering from a different location.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ice Blue","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU2OxzNcC686C8Df4qWEIDvPOMFQwDq-6n1qcBfBLTpa8PnEsc08A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I have ordered from this place multiple times, both on UberEats and through their official website.

Pizza is hot n fresh.
Delivered on acceptable times.
UberEats is the best route if you want FASTEST delivery.

The only problem I have with this location from other Papa John's locations are the portion sizes and toppings.

I have ordered medium and large size pizzas, and they are much smaller in size compared to all other locations.
If I order a medium, it looks like the size between a small and medium.
If I order a large, it looks like a size between medium and large.

The pizza itself is smaller, and thinner. I ordered non extra toppings/extra toppings. I never saw the difference.

Every single pizza ordered has had TOO MUCH CRUST, and less pizza. This is probably the biggest problem I would immediately point out.

Looking at the reviews, it seems something has changed in the past year or two.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Feb.5.2023

I have ordered three times since my last review, I will say that the quality of the pizza is better? I enjoyed them very much! There is less crust to pizza ratio now and it seems to be normal portions.

There is however, a new problem. I have ordered the buffalo chicken wings, and the wings had very little, to no sauce on them. This is extremely different from other Papa John's locations as they  all have it covered and slightly baked so the sauce is more marinated in with the meat.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPKuwzVRoi4uWLdO7wTaZiEbTStxOwREKYLoXGi&fid=0x0:0x1cf1ac02d30aef99"],"When":"2023-2-6"},{"Name":"RAVNEET KAUR","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIBaQ406LSKBWjdnsN9-zqUT5EtlUPzJ3J7XY9tG_RmB17quJI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is our family’s go to Pizza place. Not only is the food great, the owners and the staff are extremely polite as well. They are very professional and ensure that food quality is ensured during each visit. Would 100% recommend giving this place a try.
PS : the dipping sauces are to die for!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shagan Deep","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI_9BbqM31McAPaBxdo7HAdTXDxYx62-Ug3qJrFLIUSH5CzDA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of the greatest pizza spots.The quality is consistently up to par, the service is excellent, and the food is prepared quickly And delivery service too fast rather than other stores","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Simar Singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIIUCu3eFFyNe9kLThF1H929XgaAcpRi3jkuN5j2L2HIeZT_Ek=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Delicious pizzas and outstanding service!
Order on last Friday and It was fast. It was hot. It was tasty.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Rishi Sandhey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKV7NSGFBgAbPp47OE3oqzvHlSp75VxqcFm5is_gHhqHxTCxw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I have been coming at this location since last 3 years. I came here at 6:45 on Saturday November 2, 2024. This cashier girl has no idea on how to give proper customer service. I tried my best to be polite and not to create a scene here. I could tell by the look at her face she didn’t want to work and was pissed off to see me and other customers too. Didn’t reply to me and started making face when i tried to ask for something. One suggestion, if you do not like your job please quit. A lot of people are looking for jobs. Food is good as usual and other girls did a great job. Cheers to them :)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gagandeep Singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWXiOkW7-IzkR7241ngVsN6Gq-DJesJ_LKrhI1jI3GgL_r5tsq77g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Title: Good Option for Healthy Food, but Staff Could Improve

I recently visited Mucho Burrito and found it to be a good option for those looking for healthy food choices. The menu offers a variety of options that can cater to different dietary preferences.

However, I was a bit disappointed with the service. The staff seemed to be in a rush during busy times, which affected the quality of the orders. They didn't seem to pay attention to the amount of sauces and items they were putting in the bowls or burritos, which impacted the overall taste of the food.

Overall, Mucho Burrito is a decent choice for healthy eating, but the staff could be more patient and attentive to ensure a better dining experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPLtifeNTm6LKJsMCd3MdSpRYuZvLEF_KjpAS2e&fid=0x0:0xf11beeae61b238b7"],"When":"2024-2-13"},{"Name":"bhawna khullar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI0SXXLIljG-fcYo6MCkaB51HrbwaqVLzVWorWAx_nE4QPj7w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This store always serves the best. The staff is very friendly. Anshul always greets the customers with a smile. And the quality of food is also good.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"604 Canvas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJyFr0DzKCAa9QOoK-ZWpAXrHnsTkqCucD6tiG1nIfEi8_60Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I always have a fantastic experience at Mucho Burrito, and a big part of that is thanks to Chandan. Every time I visit, he’s working hard, providing excellent service, and always remembers my order. The food is consistently delicious, and Chandan's dedication and positive attitude truly stand out. Highly recommend this location for great food and exceptional service.

-Aman","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jay Why","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWf6qVrRB2FWSP3f_QpdYqgSMlmFo0fYvO9JkGkahstgPZxGBo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The food is ok at best. The tacos and quesadillas didn't have a lot of fillings. Half the rice in the burrito was still hard, like it wasn't properly reheated. If you ever had leftover rice in the fridge, you'll know what I mean. The service is hit and miss at this location. Sometimes it good, but today I had to wait a while. There were people behind the counter, but it seems like only one person is allow to serve the customers. I realize this is basically Mexican fast food, but for what they charge, I expected better.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMgMTekGvqRbsS9RT_OPPjYcermqyc3CZAgut7z&fid=0x0:0xf11beeae61b238b7"],"When":"2021-9-11"},{"Name":"Manreet Aulakh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLenyUu5M-FzhmSLndgj9KbOETYzkKpesPXeFFv7s1xVWrTCw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I’ve been a regular customer here for a while, and unfortunately don’t see myself coming back. I love jalapeños, so I was really looking forward to them. But when I went to pick up my order, the girl didn't even mention that they were out of jalapeños. I had to check myself, and sure enough, there were no jalapeños on either pizza. She said they were out of stock, but I don't believe her. I think she just forgot to add them. Then she gave me two tiny containers of jalapeños on the side, like that was supposed to make up for it. It was so disappointing. I'm so sick of this place. They have no respect for their customers' time or money. If you're thinking about ordering from them, do yourself a favor and go somewhere else.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Adiba Muzaffar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVuDQMjCZ29lDnoOzwczNSayn7fDGmqSVWxKC40X2KlmScasbtUTQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I'm a new customer for Bamon's Kitchen, and I have opted for their 3 days/week meal plan. I have been very happy with their menu, their service and the responsiveness over email. For me some of these factors come first and foremost as I wanted a reliable meal delivery service.

Now, coming to the food itself- the dishes have all been consistently good. I'm happy to say that the food isn't greasy (as a lot of other options I tried would always be), it isn't overly spicy and each dish is distinct.

The options are all vegetarian, yet there is a diversity to the combinations of vegetables. The dals have also been a broad set, and they don't rely on intense flavours.

I can vouch for the fact that the chef at work really knows what he is working with. Thank you for the wonderful food and service so far, and good luck to the team!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Suhas Uppin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVkDnYjGkhzsKLus7CXaIsz06j3OfXzSUsbOHMLMnjxMQursLoF=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I’ve had multiple issues with deliveries not following instructions. Despite repeatedly requesting that the driver call me if there is no parking and that I would personally collect the food, my order was left near the buzzer without any notification. As a result, I missed the delivery and my food. This lack of attention to detail is frustrating and disappointing. I hope the company addresses this issue to improve their service, but as of now, I can't recommend them based on my experience.
I missed my food on last day as well( happened twice in a month) and didn't got compensation.
Food is average Delivery is pathetic.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP4n_r8bRReeRi7_l48bM97OBnGItSUrozAb9PO&fid=0x0:0x338123af90eac97e"],"When":"2024-8-21"},{"Name":"tanmay Singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV-Lzy5G3y1H6AdFjPFiPmXao241cfX9ZL9p-jqo1yVfWMRmbR-=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I wanted to take a moment to express my gratitude for your amazing and delicious tiffin service. Among all the options I’ve tried, your meals stand out as the best! Whenever I have guests over, they always ask where I get such amazing food, and I never hesitate to recommend your service. In fact, several of my friends have started ordering from you as well.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Yash Shah","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUSrimn-algwsuH-Yup0zPJsAoS2ufT2Rn3OBkayXTmyhPdKMzmkw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The food is great—less oily and just right. No complaints about the quality. However, I’m giving 2 stars less because our deliveries usually arrived after 2 PM, which was super late. This might be because I’m at the end of their delivery route, so not everyone might experience the same issue. Worth trying if the timing works for you.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Hari Kansal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKZcEO19VQRatz9F93tFllkLlJuQuZnUsZAD7PNMg14xPUgkw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Bamon’s Kitchen always delivers on great tasting and unique food, both on the tiffin and their newly launched UberEats takeout (or pickup yourself).

We bought 8 items from the take-out menu to eat in the comfort of our home in Burnaby and we loved them all. Veggie burger combo, Philly cheez sandwich (my favorite, see photo), Gujarati samosa, Punjabi samosa, Manchurian + fried rice, noodles with veggie pork, masala fries, and chilli chicken drumsticks (also incredible).

We had a wonderful variety meal, in great quantities, that tasted so delicious and was so fresh.

We will definitely be buying all these items again, and we still have more than 2/3rd of the menu to try!

Bamon’s Kitchen is a new family favorite 🎉","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMgK9o2dnUI4gt6WSkJxF-HhZ1kGL46tLXO1fBQ&fid=0x0:0x338123af90eac97e"],"When":"2023-7-2"},{"Name":"Pratibha Umrariya","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXtPoZ5MQ8rRFy9qH3kxZi0RPs6yO2GrUhEks6wCD6V0nLdhIL6=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently tried their lunch tiffin service and was very happy with the quality, variety and the portion sizes of the food. Everything is vegetarian and well made, home cooked food. I found their pricing is very reasonable and everything was well packaged in recyclable packaging. I am a picky eater but still found their food to be excellent. Definitely worth it to order from them instead of going through the hassle of cooking, especially if  you are a student or like me; recovering from childbirth.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jen G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU_xHNPCGOksvG7r_6gmg3vstbGSF_01XgrdOGYFrYwwMYs7qQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Delicious affordable home cooked meals delivered to your door step in Vancouver. This feels like a dream. The team is prompt and courteous, and are quick to correct any errors too. Thanks, team Bamon! I only wish I knew about you earlier!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rishabh Jain","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUUtkiPsorBm8yNhYMNYU6Klm6ydvv0O8LJdWbi5SNeQiBHAnaLOQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love the food! I have tried couple of different options in Vancouver for a reliable tiffin service. Especially with my dietary restrictions, i wanted somewhere i could trust and Bamons has been absolutely wonderful and i love their food! It really does it hit home. Matar paneer is my personal favourite, has to be your go to tiffin service. Very prompt in responding with any changes as well as delivery service. With a busy schedule to balance school and work, this has to be my best decision opting for a their service. Even though the price point is on the higher side it’s fully justifiable.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"John Zak","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXiUYxjhD0zZyZkWLf0O-qFesnil2TXcRXcDvPfM5yIp3krrPI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I’ve been coming to Tidewaters Pub for about 3 years off and on with friends to watch UFC fights, but after today, I’ll never return. My partner and I drove all the way from Vancouver to watch the advertised UFC event, which you confirmed both on posters and over the phone. After sitting for 30 minutes waiting for the fights to come on, the waitress told us there was a “mistake” and that you may not be getting the fights after all. Soon after, she stood awkwardly by the entrance as the channel switched to football instead.

To the owner: Was saving $70 worth more than keeping loyal customers? The service was unprofessional, and your failure to honor your advertisement ruined what was supposed to be a great event. We had to leave and go somewhere else, only catching a few fights of what was an amazing card. You’ve lost three potential lifetime customers.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMLAplmuqDRUo7m3Sjt7U6LXuOWAuAl0f_VTfGh&fid=0x0:0x8f42765e4e33be26"],"When":"2024-10-26"},{"Name":"Thomas Webb","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIG2rUdfdVayGjk-HyxI4bVkd14Qji7qcSfebB4nd2zWFS27w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"They had a prime rib special. I could not have fed it to my dog!
Tough and full of grizzle. Less than a half inch thick and tough as nails. We complained as did the folks around us. Left hungry. They took our meals off the bill but gave us a lame excuse about the meat.
A real cook would have refused to serve it.
Very disappointed!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Richard Proctor","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUU4reTki5_DKZ68y-D-U91LkDlip7ln3Ocfw5-ZSYEfQqSejCW2Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time here since it was rebuilt. Nice open modern concept, great staff. Food was exceptional. Our server Devyn was upbeat & friendly. Little hidden gem under the Alex Fraser Bridge. Most definitely return.
The old pub was more like a house. Had a great patio off the back with horshoe pits. Sundays were breakfast buffets. A perfect way to cure the cause 🍻","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNeS9SMa0xH4FanDo3Ys67jJJR4Xf3rldX55leB&fid=0x0:0x8f42765e4e33be26"],"When":"2023-5-6"},{"Name":"Suman Bilkhu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWgOEqlVcR-SHJwu_c7T9FCQhKLIbhYsmGic_lANm34xi4hCfo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"No one seated us we were told to sit anywhere but there was no available seats..so we awkwardly waited around..sanitizing could be done better as well.. Calamari was good..wings were ok.  The burgers were underwhelming..the smallest underdressed burgers we have ever had at a restaurant!  1 slice of tomato and a single leaf of lettuce with a couple of onion slices..the smallest by and smallest piece of salmon..chicken from the chicken burger was nice and juicy though.. definitely not worth the price you pay..I make bigger better burgers at home :( do not recommend..","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOqV-99Wjro_MHA7jCBQRfL87u9aHr9e_kHplLI&fid=0x0:0x8f42765e4e33be26"],"When":"2020-11-24"},{"Name":"Crystal R","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX_nxdLIQfssGlpPXMfFbkpP82SZjuMBG0bae_WoDvcJnyOM6Eu=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Nice pub with nothing else close by. Service and food was slow. Food was mediocre but typical pub food. Heard the pizzas were good though. Will try that next time.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Angela Jeffery","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUtGyld6d4wIU2Lb7oe7xsoiq4r77iaBdF6nkFQ8ek01eF1q7c=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A bit difficult to get to especially when Google maps says turn right off the bridge. Lol. You need to exit for River Road.
Clean, bright, TVs weren't too loud so you could have a conversation, and nice server. Fries were amazing; fluffy inside and crispy outside. As a poutine they were good too, but had mozzarella cheese instead of true cheese curds. Hawaiian chicken burger was good. Reuben was great. Granville Island Winter Ale on tap is always a win.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMU9TiBvrrFknYUQJFcims3_TdAhpAXDC7YNztC&fid=0x0:0x8f42765e4e33be26"],"When":"2019-11-18"},{"Name":"Pixie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUPQUjFSbkcAo6EvYOja47J4GX0ejm240O00cyAhKVz3-pSo_Qi=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Their nachos are delicious. Friendly staff, great service, always a pleasure.
Great variety of dishes. All so tastey.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN43dxSLSwjOzJ6h_zUH43anAgFblPMtfKM-eRr&fid=0x0:0x8f42765e4e33be26"],"When":"2021-9-12"},{"Name":"Monika Dean","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVnFA3HgIab-NpASiEI9eKQ2eoN5GXH1ujtzJHiG3V4yJlOKpDG=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great service, and excellent happy hour menu 3-6 pm, with some items half price. Would recommend getting the refried bean tostada 👌🏻","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOtU6qaK7W7zRJQFz4ECsolXl9PzOLmrbCmpXMu&fid=0x0:0x15866ec4c70b949d"],"When":"2024-11-19"},{"Name":"Giancarlo Sagastume","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVudspcS1irgBZJQESSNdRKc2axTVFpv6bBW-jBfiYsnKYJ4n6q0A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The beer was cold and delicious, blown away by how good the food was, stopped in while visiting from the east coast of the states. My sister lives locally and always talks highly about this place. She has brought me a handful of brews back to me when she came to visit me. I'm glad I got to stop in person myself this time. I Would definitely make it a point to stop here if you happen to be In the area.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMVROuX7I9aHi2kh1489WTexyXLlzxJo_y6B2qd&fid=0x0:0x15866ec4c70b949d"],"When":"2024-5-31"},{"Name":"Marcos Garcia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVrIx99K0w17o1_jz1_EhQur2HjhBKK7Idj_Dw1mjT3aruNUbguXA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I tried El Diablo Burger, and it was sensational. Paired with any beer, and that's going to be an amazing dinner for you. I really like stouts, but unfortunately, they had none, I ended up getting a german style pilsener, which was pretty good, but I hope next time there're some other options of the dark side.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOWhEHSixzldYr2IAFIxBr51CUyIc1qFfx8YbXu&fid=0x0:0x15866ec4c70b949d"],"When":"2024-8-9"},{"Name":"Redwood T","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKi8BxE8SywOnxg7xf2JWjo4tQzJgEEsYHi9F8iXpNvqnZzIg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Super friendly staff, comfortable place to hang out. Excellent beers (and a variety to choose from) and amazing food (the tacos are so delicious). Absolutely nothing to complain about. The happy hour three tacos and a beer is a deal!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Andrea Cosi Villalva","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWBoMQFJbbx9QzLLbwhkjs92uV4pggDyUiO9c0dYJ0RDxehyxie=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing beer. Birria dumplings and refried beans tacos were amazing. Service is 10/10!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPrdu8JpxUdnqUaEzhq9xSAdTcnHMWiVo9oPKaF&fid=0x0:0x15866ec4c70b949d"],"When":"2024-11-16"},{"Name":"Yeseul Rachel Park","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVq_DXRTaHaz7GKDg7IoJa8nS8imqLxCsxz1LLKpDj4JKhQp0PF=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We visited last Monday afternoon to try their craft beers and some tacos. Few people were there, so it was very quiet which was nice for us🙂 We were not that hungry so only tried a chicken taco, and it was declicious. We love their IPAs😍 Also grabbed a few of IPA cans to go. Will visit again to try other beers with tacos.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMgZatIepHN12_Qm0qGaYBJrF3pwijBErEwGe4c&fid=0x0:0x15866ec4c70b949d"],"When":"2023-3-30"},{"Name":"DLH","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKNxoVJChN19TlxEyh2PqXcySZWcsWGp-pw0aGewSStRgeU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"As ND locals I had heard and followed this local brewery for some time. Hubby is the beer drinker, I am not so it took a @welovedelta #dinearounddelta Instagram contest win for a $50 gift card to bring us for our first visit.

There is a nice outdoor patio area, good thing as it was already a full house on a Saturday (5pm) inside.
There is communal, 2+ and bar seating.
We sat at the bar, fun to watch the action and talk with the servers learning more about the beers.

We ordered a flight ($8) that they picked for us (4 light) after hubby was asked for his preferences.
Two were fruity and I really liked those. Hubby enjoyed them all and they went well with the Jerk Chicken Taco ($5.75) and Rajas & Mushroom Tostada ($5)- they are starter sized and the menu changes monthly so check the website for current IPAs and food menu.
We both had the House Burger w/house-made tortilla chips/salsa ($16) that was one of the best burgers we’ve had.

Highly recommend. We’ll definitely be back, gift card or not.

Located in an industrial/retail area along the Fraser River.
Not a lot of parking.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMqpv8qVhhb7RL8ECwnI4zff5UOwvn6H8kcH5E&fid=0x0:0x15866ec4c70b949d"],"When":"2022-4-12"}]

[{"Name":"Marley Mckenzie cook","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX5n4XAwgV26WrtDQFOwKexjEHrP8ok0rq2RztGWysEOnM29r4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Avalon chocolate milk is one of my favourites even thought it’s expensive. First time checking out the Avalon retail store / restaurant, food isn’t bad but isn’t the best either, I was hoping it was going to be very good with all the hype but was disappointing. The cranberry sandwich was good but the soup was mediocre at best. I ordered the soup of the day and was told it was chowder but I don’t know what it was.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPIeacDaRgm4fGxiMFBb1FjkVT0ehX9KtO3wWc&fid=0x0:0x9989efaf569f1934"],"When":"2024-10-13"},{"Name":"Jenn Barnett","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVzqUWXbP6zEojwPISobVMwfU_yJ6gYFAzXSwx30ZfFRB-hR2aprw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"You can purchase milk, eggs, ice cream and all sorts of dairy products. Also bread, cold drinks and snacks. There are daily lunch specials. Plus coffee and muffins.
The staff are friendly.
Plus seating inside and outside.
A real gem in Burnaby","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOV-1oHvZzP1lvYa94mi_6fjn0HnZEGp-h89i_A&fid=0x0:0x9989efaf569f1934"],"When":"2023-7-2"},{"Name":"D M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIuH80L8_wM6G7Idu7S0eKOFlHvGcslndhZ413VSdhWvBY9nw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"They should really consider, lowering their price a small sandwich with bare minimum ingredients and a side of small bag of chips with a drink should not be 17$ !  Very over priced ! And to think they ask for tip on top of that is insane.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN0uB2KyLwozflrhdHHOE8KGcmXe8WsnkAalRbO&fid=0x0:0x9989efaf569f1934"],"When":"2024-12-3"},{"Name":"J Chow","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX5nTjAm8gcoM8KEoMc5sPDIPLKdZEtk_2xDDFiiYwdxxyp1qQ7=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Honest and affordable food served here! They're not winning awards for innovation or amazing luxury ingredients but the simplicity is part of the charm. You're just eating in a cozy store. Kitchen is open and people are friendly! My chicken pasta special was great on a rainy afternoon!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMoY2ExAsBLCrBRpThTFPEIXp1Ndvd5gWDguPgn&fid=0x0:0x9989efaf569f1934"],"When":"2023-11-13"},{"Name":"Y. Cherski","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK-7SLlKKRW0Rqcp9wRXFlvt6gbh0rtI7PMIroLgxETtGiPwQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"After walking along the Fraser River in Burnaby Fraser Foreshore Park, we decided to have a quick bite but quickly realized that being in an office/industrial area, we don't have much choice. Luckily, Old Farmhouse Kitchen was still open and very close. Since we came forty minutes before closing, I didn't get to try food items I was interested in since they ran out of them. We still got a few things, including vanilla milkshake and latte, to highlight Avalon's main product, which is milk. I tried Avalon produce before, so I was delighted with both items. The milkshake was simply perfect and not too sweet. The interior is pretty cool and cozy with lots of great decorations. We ended up getting some milk produce to go. Overall it was a great experience, and I can see myself coming back. I only wish this joint was located somewhere more accessible.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN0t5eUGwQjR3t3Mx5aFApNwoYDr2Of-iPuf2aW&fid=0x0:0x9989efaf569f1934"],"When":"2019-12-2"},{"Name":"Tami A.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXlJNR4R1uitr082NvPNP_ir27Y4tUaJxwY3uezJWRMn0aqL2I-=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Nice cozy little restaurant with fresh local food and Avalon Dairy products for sale on site. Good daily specials, and an outside patio area.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMiQwe2BJaQv_-nPdoL5noBdjqUlxuRTz1leYyK&fid=0x0:0x9989efaf569f1934"],"When":"2024-7-1"},{"Name":"Rae Nason","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLrCw7M-pseb2AZi8wT9Qnwdaq2jr_70LDDM9v2l_e5mRJVMQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Ok people coffee is good when it's hot lol but I've never had a chef salad with zero veggies 😅 come on guys","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMT4_mS_RBABUYp3TPxQPPNixli_IMB9rkvkSPC&fid=0x0:0x9989efaf569f1934"],"When":"2024-6-7"},{"Name":"Vee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLNqo7GsNEXpPBVCqGGWsNLS6BGEH4QfuZNVx2RABtSfESedQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The cafe is located near the industrial area and hence a little out of the way. It is near the Fraser river though, so a meal before or after a walk by the river is always fun!

The servers were friendly and food was served promptly. The food seemed fresh and I also bought a chocolate cookie. It was great! It wasn’t too sweet; just right for my taste buds!

I’m not sure if there are discounts for the diary products sold here, but they do have a variety: milk, yogurt, ice cream, and even homemade soup! I purchased one to try and it was savoury, but it is still best to have it in store.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMdnNOk8kE6n_zCpEbhVLa8N8gKvnvIFUSL0Ox2&fid=0x0:0x9989efaf569f1934"],"When":"2019-8-25"}]

[{"Name":"Nathan Woods","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWYlKwIGO9PHjqLgc7mRGN7qYIzJ_Yb1JOij4343pL12ye4fG4D-w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Gotta say, hugely disappointed.

I ordered the simplest thing, Chicken Strips, in the 1st period. Halfway thru the 3rd, even after asking about them in the 2nd, I got nothing.

Funny thing is, against my anti tip culture for service that doesn't really provide service (this is walk up service) I gave 15% tip.

Exasperated, I asked for a refund, they gave it to me, but kept the tip...

Don't expect stellar service, perhaps don't even expect service...","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNH2Djeiq8EVsLIRuJCr0QeP7Xt473HwWxw1stu&fid=0x0:0xd131c3be079520e"],"When":"2024-10-20"},{"Name":"Sarah HANNOU","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWQX2z45WwD0hzxpFqSQJZOqDrOt1Df2EUd7mXfxRf0wpaAe9km=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"First time here and will be back!
The butter chicken was good, a little too spicy for me but the cook gave me some sour cream... I do appreciate the gesture and attentionate service!
Thank you.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNHJ2Rohb4LH74NNJrAAh0KKn3VXamOMyWxdZBi&fid=0x0:0xd131c3be079520e"],"When":"2023-11-1"},{"Name":"Amanda Blair","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWBKFBw8SroBAGXNKvzouMmO8fdZe7vuOXyQlpvzAw4a6qHwY1MXA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Muni* and staff are great. (Four Winds IPA) food is good. Very dissappointed","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Donna Vital","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWznp7NUh9jGhisskg6IpFyxqVxlW120LfYnoCoMKI2GOWNwmc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My daughter has played at Tilbury for years. For the last couple years we have regular scheduled practices on Tuesdays - which we (as adults) look forward to and call ‘Tilbury Tuesday’. The parents head upstairs for dinner, laughs and wait for our kids to join us after they practice. Patricia and her staff are fantastic - even remembering what we order and how we like it. BTW - BEST burger you’ll ever have! Thank you for years of outstanding service.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brittany Malcolm","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI5LCsCjTHJvCCC_WseHPQJ4691cQzdvPUMY93TmU61PbfjyA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We love this place! Warm and welcoming and go above and beyond for me and my kids every time we come in. We are in our 6th season of hockey and always look forward to our tilbury games and practices so we can eat and enjoy the atmosphere. The food is good and the staff is friendly, hard working and I continue to be impressed by how they handle the busy times and quick turnovers between ice times.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"charlie75meep","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUKwYvvk-RDg2_p5lhcfW8LVi1SP7xOZdvvzXbcEScz3vOYSzpx=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great place for a good lunch/ dinner. Great staff, Owner is a very good guy.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"John Morris","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLwrINq5lT8oIFaKRsb9wQ5-qyPksj4ZX06EhtbdPd9WlY_AQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing staff! [{"Name":"Devin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWZXQ0j0-Oxo1lENe7epB3fe22RHqlVyqh8Qg3P2f8ataiCqdu6=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Worst donair I’ve ever had, super bland. Lacking major flavour. Chicken was dry on top. Service was super slow considering the amount of people in the “shop”. They should call it a lettuce wrap as that was mainly what was inside the donair. Tiring to eat, won’t be back. Save your money and go to Quiznos down the street! Wish I did…","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM8JC2SynFZaYcHaN7RDHe9xq4oMmDQtOIXDbFf&fid=0x0:0x7e6ecb4efe31d64"],"When":"2024-5-8"},{"Name":"Mehran Meets World","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXGX-1vHIbmT-pBZJH0-rDXoHHwiYEEQdSvlIdVEnIQgEvv0DJh=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The food tasted OK. The chicken was somewhat dry. Overall edible.

The customer service was good. The staff were nice and friendly, serving the food with a smile.  And they were very fast and efficient which is what I like. While I’m running around at work.

I hope the owner does his part and improves the food quality just a little bit more so than he can have everything a good restaurant should. They are almost there. Keep up the good work.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ps H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXWZH4u5uxDfJNhnL_l8W1S4uIzr1H4HDeoj_eCHzg7xFQspTGN=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Ordered a falafel wrap for take-out today, easy on the onions.  The website said "falafel stuffed in pita bread with lettuce, tomatoes, onions and feta cheese with tzatziki, garlic and hot sauce."  The falafel was good, the pita was great. There was feta, romaine, cucumber, and hummus involved.  Also something reddish that I couldn't identify.  Maybe beets? No idea.  I missed the tzatziki and hot sauce.  For the size of the wrap, and the quality of the pita, I will definitely order from here again, but I will pay closer attention to what is going in my sandwich when I do.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN5kPO4sg0ethJV9HxLjs8atYqBhNpbMRl_NAmX&fid=0x0:0x7e6ecb4efe31d64"],"When":"2021-1-27"},{"Name":"Kaden Burgart","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXu1Rsup3m3MPbG16zVQxfn21T20YBHribUgDYvN3Lh93KGSsbkqw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is probably my favorite shawarma place ever. It’s a hidden gem!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMFflXn_GO2fw7ak13RXEQeZMZLt0yWLtwya5cD&fid=0x0:0xc6da18482b0cdfa7"],"When":"2024-11-5"},{"Name":"Shaeli Finnie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX9swc8R2K-WPKeSpodeW9gMPefWym8hWzzaxuYb_8dEHf-eO8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I came and visited this bar today!
$12 pasta special and $17.5 for wings.
The pasta seemed like a good deal and the wings in B.C--- crazy expensive.
The beer was cold and the staff were extremely polite!
The place wasn't too packed and the pints are about average in price for a respectable establishment!
Only suggestions I could make are to diversify the staff!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Randi Foulkes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWoLXCTf8ZMlw2OJNLY_QrUyqBRUBWhNTjTSDcPwnhjldn_CBXGcw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love it! Great atmosphere and space! Food is delicious 👍 Waitresses were super friendly and very helpful. One of the only places I've found that serves Hopping mad cider!! Will be back for sure. They said they may start up a community shuttle service soon as well, pick up and drop off service. What could be better 😆","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNufSh_XFqa7dJfkA8t2x80hS2hHceVVKUKx7-n&fid=0x0:0xc6da18482b0cdfa7"],"When":"2018-9-15"},{"Name":"Tran Chung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW9eULK8-7j2U9Ze3f3qd5XAYcn_cs8--Jdb91h4DDxVjShDzqIaQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Came here on a sunny day and their patio is great. Drinks are good too. We ordered the nacho and beef sliders. Well, the food was not very good at all. The nacho was cold and not a lot of toppings. Cheese has congealed and did not have that classic stringy pull. Oh well. But the good news was that we brought it home added more cheese and banana peppers and warm it up in the oven, and it came out perfect. 👌 The sliders were very dry. The bread was like a few days too many in the freezer. Well again, we brought the sliders home, we swapped out for fresher buns and made our homemade beef patties, and the sliders turned out perfect 👌.  I want to like this place because it is only two blocks away from our house, but I rather walk 30mins to Match for better food or just cook at home. 🤷🤷🤷","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOIymzm0hgCDF6KJmyCEiZzrJ2TVP_a_JereGCN&fid=0x0:0xc6da18482b0cdfa7"],"When":"2023-5-7"},{"Name":"Lorna Holmes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWLGTiz7X8ca9yPQGHnezPpPq3Z134oRRYTfLLhiDOE2Wbgxc-9=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Always a pleasant experience in my lovely neighbourhood pub.  We were warmly greeted and our server, Ashley, was wonderful.  She took great care of us and our lunch was very tasty and perfectly portioned.  Will definitely be back.  Thanks Ashley!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lekha Reddy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWmJGhl1-4gmLsjhODLv0EBv4db0I65Xj_LQ4N38nJXAbHQF354=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Located in Port Royal neighbourhood, this place gives all the cozy cabin vibes with good food and drinks. The nacho melts that were on special were just so so good. Red hot wings were on spot with perfect spicy flavour we wanted. The waitress was not really checking on and had to call quite a few times for cutlery, plates and more orders. Definitely going back for food and drinks","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMQXuFR_yMLBpvZ4qwtFRGIVrRaXMUvFaxmjXXh&fid=0x0:0xc6da18482b0cdfa7"],"When":"2021-11-9"},{"Name":"Coffee Zombie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU8RAVr6dsNMwjj0MLGbHc5BBD175kjOU3AHcl6iAJKIyIjRsJl=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Just an average pub, nothing special.  It's in the middle of nowhere far from public transport which has its pluses and negatives.  If they setup a roadblock down the road Frankie's would give them some work.  Just straight down the middle average.  The food choices were okay with pizza and Yorkies and good size portions.","Images":null,"When":""}]

I have never seen delivery more than 30 min.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"meedool","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVqOAqZgWECUgDQqDgB6RT0rl1kxJU4z1POZnOP0Q3VEK5KM9qs=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Absolutely terrible service, the food is terrible. Some parts of the menu used to be decent, but now they are terrible too. Staff seemed unfriendly and pissed for some reason, food took way too long to be made, and the store smells like a butcher shop for some reason; of raw meat.

Pizza tastes frozen and reheated too. Used to go there once in a while but I forgot how terrible it was. Definitely not going back. Just go to Queensborough Pizza, it's so much better and it's really good.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Vishal Goyal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXi4u-i5CXrp6ymv6Vl8g03bSSYZcGDX8NEXmd3LzvtkRh_tF3OZQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Title: A Slice of Heaven: New West Pizza Delights

New West Pizza in New Westminster is a culinary gem that has quickly become my go-to spot for a satisfying slice. From the moment you step inside, the inviting aroma of freshly baked dough and savory toppings greets you, setting the stage for a memorable dining experience.

The menu boasts a wide array of options, from classic pepperoni to inventive gourmet creations, ensuring there's something to please every palate. What sets New West Pizza apart, however, is the quality of their ingredients. Each bite bursts with flavor, thanks to the use of fresh, locally sourced produce and premium meats.

Not only is the pizza top-notch, but the service is also exceptional. The staff is friendly, attentive, and always eager to accommodate special requests. Whether you're dining in or opting for delivery, you can expect prompt and courteous service every time.

The cozy ambiance of the restaurant adds to the overall charm, making it the perfect spot for a casual meal with friends or a cozy date night. And with generous portion sizes at reasonable prices, you'll leave feeling satisfied without breaking the bank.

In conclusion, New West Pizza in New Westminster is a must-visit for any pizza lover. Delicious food, friendly service, and a welcoming atmosphere combine to create an unforgettable dining experience. I can't wait to return for another slice of heaven!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Stephanie Krushinsky","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV3fmFXutFrt3LbgshWkzotw65tphKrSFQ47wyAISm4tROsygMMhg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Pizza was amazing..wings were just..wings no drumettes.Deep fryer oil needs to be changed as it makes wings taste like old oil.. would not order the wings again.9$ for not very great tasting wings and no drumettes? Also..white sauce costs extra? I thought that usually this was something you could order anywhere. Without an extra cost.. I would order some pizza again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM74eeyxBSYkndHt_ogpZwGzTX7ciOQ9al0Gket&fid=0x0:0x4ba2a276347e36ab"],"When":"2022-1-23"}]

[{"Name":"Helen Liu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKI-mzgGlleZ4ePt7mDYbQ4Gabh9zw-OBKk6bKlySQQQboerA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent service! Food is delicious. We ordered curry beef stew, stir fried vegetable, and pan fried shrimps. My favorite is the pan fried shrimps. They are really tasty. We also ordered the shrimp dumplings but I forgot to take a picture. The atmosphere is great too.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP8-vtXXRnLQjyEeAAuL35jbb-rsGBTqTSnPnNw&fid=0x0:0xf373ff8003b6d0b5"],"When":"2024-11-17"},{"Name":"minnie li","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKRoQOlIxvrw__7xun_s22_XplGfNg8u2NALefXOOF5MWkjHg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a wonderful experience at this Chinese restaurant. The atmosphere is fantastic, with a spacious, high-ceilinged dining area that feels very comfortable. Unlike many other Chinese restaurants, the tables here are generously spaced, giving diners plenty of room without feeling cramped. The dim sum selection is excellent, offering a wide variety of tasty dishes. One of the standout features is that there is no extra charge for tea, which means you can save a bit and order an extra dish instead.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO-elniB3Hl2xWWwsMV20UfYj7JPo45Q9rbfB5_&fid=0x0:0xf373ff8003b6d0b5"],"When":"2024-10-16"},{"Name":"Peter Powell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWEWICjNsYatccfG8tJU6H4w44FxzrmrGxqQilpFtPRJqpzz2xy=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Comfortable dining room and good service. Our group had a set dinner with suckling pig. All the food was very good. The pig was delicious, crispy skin that was delicate and crunchy. The meat was tender and moist. Enjoyed every dish although the chicken was a little dry (common problem) even the dessert was great, black sesame balls in almond flavour milk","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPQwBTYDYQZcj-v30N7LNcD4G_NH0PQNi6H4BI0&fid=0x0:0xf373ff8003b6d0b5"],"When":"2024-8-4"},{"Name":"Jenny Ma","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUgIEDkB2PzsQAjZtJxzL5NwawLrCpei_X1mvBSmllmI0Q-tBD5=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Both the dim sum and service here are great! The location is kind of weird and a bit challenging to both find and navigate out of with so many blocked paths/streets. The har gao, har cheung, fung jow, and pai gwut were all tasty! We didn't have enough enthusiastic eaters to try more but I'd love to come back sometime to taste more of their menu!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP-35rkTyMgdRaBUJ03HfzyFPeW_rVUCeeUzPA7&fid=0x0:0xf373ff8003b6d0b5"],"When":"2024-10-20"},{"Name":"Kanako Sakurada","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKYybgPjG_d3LYq66Ui47Ocd_2PMrfkKaju5V_L0IyVTR19lQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Higher end Cantonese restaurant at starlight casino. Good food and great service!

We usually come here for suckling pig (pre-order needed). It’s like Peking duck but with crispier and thicker skin. I just felt a bit uncomfortable being stared at by the pig.
Other foods that came with the combo were very good. I liked rock cod with veggies dish and sesame ball dessert.

The restaurant is spacious and airy. It has relaxed and laidback vibe.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPOrHfWbSHxs67lYnTOsmhjez8_1w-Mn96PBLgU&fid=0x0:0xf373ff8003b6d0b5"],"When":"2024-5-12"},{"Name":"Stephie N","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXd0_eqzaDNFpYKxu_At0QKV_opW1IXDZ3BtSf_D5LFw7-X91jS=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We love going to Kirin Seafood Restaurant for dim sum. Unlike other dim sum restaurants, we always feel well-treated here. The service is detailed and prompt. Since we are not Chinese, we can’t say for certain if the dim sum is authentically made, but we love it! We always enjoy visiting this place and always will. I apologize for my poor photography skills; my pictures don’t do justice to their delicious dim sum.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNlG2wAPlH7JowuXk90cPCEDk3XOcsvTxfgnNzL&fid=0x0:0xf373ff8003b6d0b5"],"When":"2024-5-26"},{"Name":"Yan Jie Pan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVWtJgsuhwRId0t1MOzd5ywiIXfrBfIFDTo7UODkLUu9At3EXtegw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Our friends invite us to come for lunch here, and now I’m in love with their lunch menu 😻 so many options of dim sum, and you can taste that it’s freshly made, I enjoyed them so much, and the egg tart is a must order!!! I can finish a plate of egg tart by myself 🤤 everything is worth trying, I want to come back again to try the others!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMMok6cppc8y5jMaY6pPG6bkffjl_g7zGArNij8&fid=0x0:0xf373ff8003b6d0b5"],"When":"2024-5-10"},{"Name":"Craig Johnson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLHYc_KX8jVjM1EqjfvQu304OSChoZgYUkr4ijG-TFif8471A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Juicy Siu Mei and perfectly cooked Pan Fried Prawns are our favorites this visit. The eggplant dish was overwhelmed by the fish paste and oil. The ham hock dish, on special now, was cooked well and served cold similar to poached chicken. The Beef Rice Noodle texture and flavor was perfect despite having very little beef.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPGK2CzBM8uZWE1_1erm4yOs5IgF0Ns69XqSmx_&fid=0x0:0xf373ff8003b6d0b5"],"When":"2024-6-18"}]

[{"Name":"K. Saru S.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLMsrj9d8axiVSlv1H9uFsbBTHch0nQkaKz28f75Vbf2tUW7g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Bought two bags of specialty beans from here. Got a Honey Sidamo (Ethiopia, light roast) and Arara (Colombia - medium roast) You know the coffee beans are roasted really well and balanced when there were barely any grind left stuck on the grinder. Brewed the Honey Sidamo with 4/6 pour over method. The taste and flavor of the Honey Sidamo is amazing. For me, it tasted more like lemon tea than coffee. For those who enjoys floral and fruity flavor, you would enjoy this as well. This is highly recommended!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMBUcwSsZJ4DxT0u1Bo21igmuPplKHHfXdiU5GJ&fid=0x0:0x3395f263dfdabb03"],"When":"2024-5-9"},{"Name":"Gabriela Balderer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUvL_NwElSDk_T_Fp3DU6NIAzMDxWUS06lppoxSgJwJev_DMvWS=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Such a nice coffee place. I really like to spend some time here.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMIHDAqpFgskpnQ-zl1YECvSk7jxbhrpbNRVk7J&fid=0x0:0x3395f263dfdabb03"],"When":"2020-8-27"},{"Name":"Chung Chan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIv417o6PEawEaP0eXzd4rP90b_iDoIklpAw9WpFk3QzA06pQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’m here from Seattle for work, I was so pleasantly surprised to find in an industrial area, such good quality coffee, that also gets brewed well by their barista. I tried the espresso and pour-over. Really nice people too!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Barish Golland","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWNmkSOq8UYBZOSQwpstPtS8Lj4bD0Vl7E6gUFRlXJs_gMOTMA3Lw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing delicious hand crafted lattes and cappuccinos, my go to coffee shop on the way to work.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP92UajFqGZnGofFR2fu8ilDJkc5ucWn6M3-mBL&fid=0x0:0x3395f263dfdabb03"],"When":"2024-9-11"},{"Name":"BR","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVKvHcZB7xb4n8CF1jxejOIwoYqPKN4SdZc0qIjcZcbAYMjdkneNA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Surprisingly nestled within the industrial complex, this coffee shop is a hidden gem. With its cozy ambiance, friendly staff, and delicious brews, it's the perfect spot for a midday pick-me-up or a quick break from the daily grind.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNXUyBKDQxX95dUjKLlhsxFDRmemaV5ZEwuNioG&fid=0x0:0x3395f263dfdabb03"],"When":"2024-2-29"},{"Name":"Smoothmot","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIepB1eJgsrC54GE4Y0XET65FRIezIL_SQzA0hNuwfYlpsYDw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This one is a gem to those specialty coffee lover out there. Got the Honey Sidamo and its higly recommended.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nathaniel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKM4r3pmD7z8b5oWmwErBLihgCjU8FZHLmtpCuqk6oIObl9umkP=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Exceptionally good coffee. They sell several excellent espresso blends. This is high end third wave coffee. They make great lattes and flat whites. They've recently started baking their own baked goods. And they're extremely nice people. Great service.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Amy Wang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJlaZV4z1GSNQgtMG9hYK3ozWT9ugSJ0xiZfykhr39odRBl5w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This roastery is absolutely amazing! To my surprise, I must say I had the best latte in a very long time! The owners very kind and talented (look at that latte art).

I picked up a bag of Annacis Islander and a bag of caffeineholic. Both are amazing and my friend asked me to pick up two more bags of AI since she loved it so much too! Keep up the good work guys :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMMPCNzrTKug-Pi2XD7wTNvkac4b7sqVXt-w-Zg&fid=0x0:0x3395f263dfdabb03"],"When":"2021-7-23"}]

[{"Name":"Edward Dolejsi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUDxcmmjByq2PodkDyOmt0Pk9lStn4g7-jleRMZfYgkQApvrbl6=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I don’t drink much, but I enjoy Fat Tug IPA by Driftwood Brewery from Victoria, BC. Last summer, I had some business at the Shelter Island Marina & Boatyard.
It was lunchtime, and I noticed this neat pub, TugBoat Annie’s Pub & Grill, so I decided to go there for lunch. Boy, what a surprise! They serve Fat Tug IPA on the tap! I started going there regularly, first for the beer, then I discovered their excellent food selection and made friends with their friendly staff.
You guessed it, I love this pub. It is a hidden treasure if you enjoy great pub food, friendly staff, and a nice and relaxed atmosphere. This endorsement may be subjective, but I love this pub, and I highly recommend it. Look for it by the river at the south end of Graybar Rd, in Richmond.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Steve Whalley","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXfD1baKjTO6OdWwruKgoRJEY7SRS7ivY7vqDVBaVOg96TYxNLDpg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Great place to come to. The servers are attentive to your likes and needs, friendly and positive. This is a place to remember. If you feel like taking a walk along the road after your meal it's nice to enjoy viewing the boats in the marina.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kevin Bush","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVCGxyYiPTdzevWdjSNVHFBYA6Syuv_fFL3qDuvq1li4-ZD_QE=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Just discovered this place today by accident and all I gotta say is I’m a fan. Definitely be coming back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMtykWQRgvOqAJPj2azweY_Q0rG7DqKsJSZUH_E&fid=0x0:0x94c83aa359d6149b"],"When":"2024-7-5"},{"Name":"Tricia Boneham","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUpaDZfQMP9gmE6Fd5t47ayR--tBtj_k7CI8MNtfWS-Z2f3dZ79=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Victoria is such a great server! Everyone there is great but I've had Victoria the most and she really makes coming there enjoyable.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Hyon Sui","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIuJpfnqbtKpv73_xuNkvTDmAwnSVuJH-iGvm7FwVfLnHARSA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great food with great service.
Had chicken strips with fries and soup.
Will recommend to friends for casual.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNPGL2RmFWteDeLYswm-p6lTxuARrUbzuLF_4v-&fid=0x0:0x94c83aa359d6149b"],"When":"2024-6-16"},{"Name":"K B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKrsPzNsW1O_hkIP_0QuLDRbghqgnsupvuSVQrpaYQQxW7EMRop=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Waitress was great food was too
I loved the French fries, and the chicken club was perfect 👌
Nice place for lunch","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPgozaG-nvZLnYQ4T0-PosQj5UHQ3V9imETVawf&fid=0x0:0x94c83aa359d6149b"],"When":"2024-4-23"},{"Name":"D. James C.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXOgX71xwuGQJkLntlLXyDCHS3HWLYNhpDb8t2zmY-nv5R6n7gdew=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Fast service.
