user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Iris and Scott Wedding","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXjUefdZRNJMcCgmMMfLYQWeR_K3UNo-piHulpCkZYKBV6iOBA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Huge kudos to the D/6 Bar and Lounge team!

We did a partial buyout for our pre-wedding welcome party - where everyone was coming from out of town - and the staff treated us so well. We received so much feedback from our guests about how delicious the food was, and how good the bartenders were. Seriously, the vibes were absolutely superb and the staff were just the best.

Huge thanks to Maria who looked after us and even organized a special surprise with presenting and slicing our wedding tasting cakes! It was so lovely of the GM to also come to our section and introduce himself and chat with us.

Overall, our party at D/6 was wonderful and we really appreciate everything they did. I couldn't recommend this place more. It's a magical place behind the bookcase, after all.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNT-nB722DBPuZH3m8ehVVQ-1RRYJmLd7IlJ6Yv&fid=0x0:0xa5ceb3ac151f73cd"],"When":"2024-9-26"},{"Name":"Michelle Siaril","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVvNHVR_L-5eCK2usU0kQoT055SV9vB2qDNPyrA7CmG9QXO2IM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I had high expectations for this place which it didn’t quite deliver. First, cocktails just weren’t to our taste, with them being either too sweet, too strong, etc. While this could be due to preference, we did consult with the server about which types of cocktails we prefer and her recommendations seem to have missed all the marks. Second, this place was very loud both from music and the patrons chatting away, certainly not matching the upscale location. Lastly, service could have been a lot better, with us having to wait a long time for service and needing to signal everytime we needed something.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPz8Z2Gf8dx0AQqpRt0NNic8W7UZuFX0LlvmrI&fid=0x0:0xa5ceb3ac151f73cd"],"When":"2024-8-14"},{"Name":"A C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVnyUT5qR1q83BkWB2zCwnsqdLsc_SBXOjVUzSTlxYzil0MFcNy=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Enjoyed a Thursday night fire show at D/6 with the girls.

Had a couple of drinks, their seafood platter, and their lettuce wraps.

Service from the server was mediocre as she didn’t seem to be happy to assist us, but I had a better experience with other staff - especially the bartender.

The food was not bad, but I have had better & fresher seafood elsewhere. The bulgogi lettuce wraps were good but nothing to come back for.

I would say the ambience, the fire show, and the drinks are their best features.

Would come again for a birthday or celebration!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOZLrqsRQl4q0_qW3nk3cbFdGKcE6Hh6Zsr3e-1&fid=0x0:0xa5ceb3ac151f73cd"],"When":"2024-4-12"},{"Name":"Darya Shestakova","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWu6uprkRcDwpuHfLGl7-pbvi_VNXLljaMreb-YExBI5WEoXuWnPg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Bravo to the mixology team! The cocktails here are so good and refreshing.
We liked the vibe of this lounge, and it wasn't too crowded on Saturday night at around 1am.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMEiNwkFSq9dFF26YOxZjafP-ttH995goPi6y7a&fid=0x0:0xa5ceb3ac151f73cd"],"When":"2024-10-9"},{"Name":"Keith Ver","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXVdqxLCf1LEt0AU82myo-eUqDcb2LcbdnfhupJTEW0sPAQ-qQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went here for the first time with workmates last weekend, and I think I can say that we all enjoyed! I like how cozy each area or table is. Like it fits and caters to whatever type of group of customers they have. For the food, I've tried their Chicken Karaage and Yam Fries. Both were delish! Their staff were also very accommodating 😊","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN4otw0vDzDvWbtPbVTWkjDK1sQyzEjgVVEdTZR&fid=0x0:0xa5ceb3ac151f73cd"],"When":"2024-4-18"},{"Name":"Jessica Hernandes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLwiQRdtHARYKmE3k2zWxN1rQkNRcAiMqHvA-Bmd9bz3eRD5xpf=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I recently visited a lounge with friends to celebrate the citizenship of two of our group members, and it was an amazing night! The atmosphere was vibrant, and we had a fantastic time. Our first server was incredibly attentive and even surprised us with a complimentary shot to toast the celebration, which added a nice touch to the evening.

While the energy in the lounge was great, I must mention that the DJ didn't quite cater to our song requests as much as we hoped. Nevertheless, it didn't take away from our enjoyment. Overall, it was a memorable night filled with laughter and good vibes!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lisa Evanoff","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJTeRf8QepHOIph3XBxAtAzqN5fryW7YuS53YKlz6bovYxrRA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"This is a beautiful space.  We came for the Happy Hour and cocktails were supposed to 30% off. Our bills did not reflect this and we had to ask and have the bills changed.  I read on other reviews that this is common practice so make sure you check.
Our server was attentive at first and then never came over for the last 45 minutes. We had to ask for water twice and had to go find her for our bill.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Anjolie Defazio","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU1YizHYFxLxtxUBIlPW-dvl7GzEq17MSna9wiuOGdOFdzZZPRN=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great atmosphere, waygu sliders were good, nice cocktail options, but service was the shining star! Stephanie was amazing! Great recommendations, super funny and personable. Definitely request her if you’re coming in.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"wah chi yip","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKKBykHMUbkrtJ4cwRRXsjOnAzAcOzwrpq-XVjovUt6A3trFQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A huge food court is located in the centre of the mall.  It will be very busy on weekend. But we are always finding good seats there, the staff keep cleaning up in this area. They keep it clean and tidy in the food court.
I think the management needs pay more attention to the lady restroom.  Many of the locks of the toilets are broken in late November and early December.  That makes a long line up on weekend.  This is an easy fixing issue. Please fix them while now.
The food courts has lots of chain restaurants and some are independence shops.  We are happy with our every visit there.
The high ceiling and the roomy big hall are good for all.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNOgbIBkROjVGBfSxz5fuWRCUAubX2qFuf7c3Q3&fid=0x0:0xab35da0ece61c8d3"],"When":"2024-9-13"},{"Name":"Gazal G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVNfRt6AYTRne5R5YyIlS82FlCPvw6yjMF8Wl3AyoUgCtB2w_8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely I Like this place and can easily recommend all the restaurants in the food court. I've tried almost all the dishes there. The quality is excellent, the ingredients are fresh and delicious, the taste and cooking are great, and the portion sizes are good value for the price.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNNUyuJyMd4Gl8RoCuFOLuwgqpv7CppCndPXVO1&fid=0x0:0xab35da0ece61c8d3"],"When":"2024-7-24"},{"Name":"Music Connection","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUJYlUykko32IqG4dCQwPvXR2iyPDw6jnVELvp95RNUSwA9c2bk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Nice experience.  Just bit pricey, but you find the stuff there.  Food is tasty. The ladies' Washrooms need attention, most of the locks are broken, soap dispensers do not work, which is frustrating.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMXoDnithDX8fTrGd4VnJmwDI68zKnXj0u0bMM2&fid=0x0:0xab35da0ece61c8d3"],"When":"2024-10-14"},{"Name":"Lisa C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKf-CGme76-m9PXmpoAfISvHXNhHUk5JXqrRbCswe2zXLs7xw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I'm giving the food court here 5 stars simply because there is a 100% gluten free restaurant called Hula. Its very hard to find safe places to eat when you have celiac disease. I always travel with protein bars because I never know if I'm going to starve out there away from my own kitchen.

Poke bowls, very tasty!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Annie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIhbC5qIdQVlSkoQNnkkhCGza3dQG41PTHELC8qxMiEuueGYQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Atsuta Teriyaki- would not recommend.  Chicken bento box - purchased at 1120am. Chicken was lukewarm and tempura yam was ice cold and soggy.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNGUaz1qQ3cCp1uVCf5Fw6xBUgNk2uoT_hmutxF&fid=0x0:0xab35da0ece61c8d3"],"When":"2024-8-23"},{"Name":"gold stream","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIMLKdGRVpixSTb9Y3fj1pK-hK-7pRtDNbg9D1Y6Usg47nrsw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Nothing special but the regular affair of food court food variety. Tables are kept clean most of the time.  The only thing I like is the open air vaulted ceiling structure, nice woodworks and bright.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Roohi Singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXdjo2W8S9L8Jr-ZYexQXxLQCVjDK00YpEJgATDlAXXqvAgvxBgRg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Super Best FRESHLY SQUEEZED WE LOVE IT WE LOOK FOWARD to always GO TO TWASSEN FOOD COURT
JUST FOR OUR MOST FAVORITE 😍
FRESHLY SQUEEZED JUICE
THEY ARE THE BEST 👌 SUPER GOOD
PUNJABI STYLE SUGARCANE JUICE and Smoothies are good too .... our kids LOVE ❤️ FREDHLY SQUEEZED JUICE ... BIG THANKYOU TO THE OWNER GURJIT JI FOR their BEST HOSPITALITY ... WE LOVE ❤️ FRESHLY SQUEEZED 😍","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO2RjK6yjbw5rzSfylC6YnLlh3Twj6zrajWia33&fid=0x0:0xab35da0ece61c8d3"],"When":"2024-1-23"},{"Name":"H Z","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXX06oymWkDMxT4IebTMvn6eubrd48cRIIwGbwWi3pEHWB8T2JN=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The mall is a great place for a family day out, especially on a rainy day.  There are plenty of brand-name shops and ample parking.  One slight disappointment is the general quality of the food court stalls; while KFC and A&W are predictable and consistent, all the other fusion or purportedly world foods don't quite cut the mustard for me - especially when you take into consideration how high the average ethnic minority population ratio is in Greater Vancouver area.","Images":null,"When":""}]

user_reviews: [{"Name":"YU U","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW0nH1IDVl5JKBE-6ym-GzRTN424F1AIj9FKlXASZfTI9-nMv1M=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This takeout sushi place is truly impressive. Besides the visually appealing and delicate presentation, the freshness of the ingredients reflects their commitment to quality. The fish roe adds a burst of flavor and a pleasant texture, enhancing the overall tasting experience. The balance of the sweet and salty sauce is just right, making each bite irresistible. The fillings are thoughtfully chosen, from the crispy tempura and the smooth, tender eel to the creamy avocado, creating layers of flavor in every bite. The pickled ginger and wasabi as side accompaniments elevate the overall taste experience, making it even more satisfying. Even when brought home as takeout, the food still retains its deliciousness, which is one of the reasons for their high ratings. If you enjoy Japanese cuisine, this place is definitely worth a try. Don’t forget to make a reservation in advance, especially during the busy weekend hours, to avoid a long wait.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP5yYChArBQzYNWqtjDawkQ1NIf-ODNMNLrq8cE\u0026fid=0x0:0xd4df1ce6442b9859"],"When":"2024-11-3"},{"Name":"Andrew Chin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ1q4rHiGlEwZjs6faiNEkgA2cWs0E2_Z5Tz0MibCCH2lgLnJg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Very generous portion for the price! Hot combo 1 chicken karaage plus one inari sushi. Everything was tasty, but wish the chicken was a bit more crispy and maybe a slice of lemon to go with it would’ve been nice. I will be back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMhqiLZiMilmvyGuv3Hbq5JBD0TITb8_VPJh5si\u0026fid=0x0:0xd4df1ce6442b9859"],"When":"2024-5-17"},{"Name":"Irish Anne","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU4mzmfi2ZFy2lvGx8jw53AUitZ2l0rMZyTKfAFfJTLaCIO43QM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Spent $50 for 3 rolls, chicken teriyaki and tempura. The ten piece assorted tempura only had 2 prawns in it. This place is quite expensive considering the quality of the food and taste. We were hungry and wanted a quick bite and not from the area. Save your money and appetite, drive elsewhere.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO4FIDJGPljIjkWvNNffMt3p4QnB068X8-AcqhS\u0026fid=0x0:0xd4df1ce6442b9859"],"When":"2022-9-23"},{"Name":"Jason Cheong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXuUPE5CCf7bhzxh9nhDhi2IHO8fQ2a05ZFtEpsPc5P0hbRhII=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I'm glad they switched their smaller rolls to 8 pieces. Chicken teriyaki roll is one of the best I've had... when you pay extra and add cucumber.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOfyou1d-ACB4uA3RiMmAvSdTnpnya9TrOi5E5M\u0026fid=0x0:0xd4df1ce6442b9859"],"When":"2024-1-18"},{"Name":"Lyle LePage","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXVecDL3Hmwv0Ta22PbQLiQI3kp6KtFBZ0Lloo0qHWVnpj1TzUq=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent local Japanese dive! Good value and decent portions. My go to order is the deep fried chicken roll and beef yakisoba.  My wife loves the special rolls, especially the Vancouver, River and Santa rolls. [{"Name":"Zeeshan Sohail","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXQzSgXcEIo5d0fY039IL3LLi7k1i-9eyjB9u0xnur9BQekUdtD=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of the most authentic Beef Bihari Kabab and Beef Nihari places in town. Wait times can get challenging during peak hours but the food never disappoints. Make reservations and order ahead and you're in for a treat. Recommended.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPno9Y4IJST_1Bm5zkfxeuHjDnRrwTuW3rmbI0k&fid=0x0:0x5cb3c8916b92d63c"],"When":"2024-12-10"},{"Name":"Mosammat Sayeeda Islam","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIL7Ridsklhzy0F-dTiRzeKjJ1HbiLtsL3eJWxmOsn450zj3DIo=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"We went to village BBQ last night and the waitress didn’t even say hi to us. I read the notice about 45 minutes time and understood but they didn’t even gave us water or said a thing! After 50 minutes I asked for water and then they gave us water. Ever since I asked for water that waitress was giving me an angry look. Everytime we said thx she would just look and roll her eyes and walk away. As if going to that restaurant and asking for water after 50 minutes was a crime. After 1 hour and 25 minutes we got our food and it was cold as if it was left out for a while after cooking. The beef bihari Kabab was good but would have been better if it was atleast warm. Most of all, we go to restaurant to eat not because we can’t cook but to feel relaxed and treated like guest which was missing there. I donno what is it with those girls that work there but they have some bad attitude .","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM4S43dXrVQOIZCuqu2QXZX0quW75IQRFRAPDBR&fid=0x0:0x5cb3c8916b92d63c"],"When":"2024-11-11"},{"Name":"Zargham Amer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJtEmcSO4oM1MO7tkZvkh3DG6vThWmTpDErildoA6Q32y1qOw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently had the pleasure of dining at Village BBQ Restaurant and was thoroughly impressed. The food was exceptional, with the tikka boti platter and beef seekh kebabs standing out as my favorites. Both dishes were perfectly seasoned and cooked to perfection. The service was equally amazing, making the entire experience delightful. I highly recommend Village BBQ to anyone looking for delicious Pakistani food and outstanding service. Always a great pleasure coming here!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNkaLxu60FXxgZVE2ZEomUU_Wzd9caARZJzyD03&fid=0x0:0x5cb3c8916b92d63c"],"When":"2024-5-24"},{"Name":"Ali Jaffer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWxBuzDsninlt9GBGcwFVCC48Wjy59DzbkKFiPBRKjZ81qqviGf=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Enjoyed every bit, great music, best food in Vancouver, surrey. Staff are amazing. Farhan and Shahbaz. These boys are so welcoming and always with a positive energy. The onwer Mrs. Irfan Ali is so hardworking.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO9szUYp7W8TxRIUBiogpVztyUjNK1jR_3m6bKr&fid=0x0:0x5cb3c8916b92d63c"],"When":"2024-8-25"},{"Name":"Muhammad Khan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXIV0jbJl9FA6bA_RfKt_nsNRMXRmlNEFPuiEyShHhH1LmeWP-d7Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing food. Tried the Bihari kabab and Nahari and they were both amazing. Naans are fluffy and very tasty. Will for sure be coming back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO4-Bpux5UzwQTR2wNVZrHQXg-wmbDiuzvCahZF&fid=0x0:0x5cb3c8916b92d63c"],"When":"2024-11-5"},{"Name":"Shahzaib J.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKhpzuDBP6wQm6OsAyV_ouA2XY93EeHvr2Uq9kXaQt2rnrq7A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Authentic barbecue. We had the chicken behari and malai boti with the puri paratha, and both were really good. The overall package with the chutney and salad makes it perfect. The ambiance is also nice. I am looking forward to trying the rest of the menu on the next visit.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM7ClnhO8MTsb4aYTVSOet4EtHGmTUKAxDSh3-P&fid=0x0:0x5cb3c8916b92d63c"],"When":"2024-8-6"},{"Name":"Saami Zee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV-w_OK7ySRR9lB0UkR8VKffsmBtc7M_TSWrJrw-fiTDuKJrF1n=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A must place to visit for authentic Pakistani cuisine which we hardly have in Vancouver.We ordered chicken behari roll ,chicken tikka and chicken seekh kebab the food was cooked to perfection and everything was so fresh .
Though we came to eat at 10:45pm but we got good service .
The server was very polite and doing her best to keep the customer happy.
I wish village bbq best of luck in their venture here in Vancouver","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNi8pmIAAXCRTzzrliZYF5UhX-s8475t7NItCKx&fid=0x0:0x5cb3c8916b92d63c"],"When":"2024-5-23"},{"Name":"Nadeem Zia.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWMvuVKaJ5RspKjafdw7NuycDlSlwvLOTMgiMvYKB8ZcmZ9sQ7d7w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Woo‼ excellent comeback; we have been missing delicious and traditional Beef Bahari Kababs, Beef Nahari, and fresh Naan.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPhqzIsqvzuX_G7GHGeby5eMxbclu_bcrM8PPlK&fid=0x0:0x5cb3c8916b92d63c"],"When":"2024-4-27"}]

[{"Name":"This food","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUaxcCslaGrcC0u202g67ni7XJGWWGyPYtSKkUjWo5gpcXXO0Yv=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Enjoyed my meal here for lunch today. I ordered the House Pho and the popular dish with the vermicelli, spring roll, lemongrass chicken, the red meat, and spinach beef roll. It was all very delicious and they are very generous with their meat portion compared to other competitors I’ve been to in Vancouver. Friendly service and attentive. It wasn’t very busy for a Saturday afternoon. Since Ive been coming to Ladner often I think this will be my new spot for comfort food in this area. Thanks for the lovely experience!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM3H8DgsTWL4bmzG-8oLEg7Fc8WaIkzy9n8uPJn&fid=0x0:0xa7336b586da3827f"],"When":"2022-8-14"},{"Name":"Munchica","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXbQ6ACs51IPQJlRLrmnunOErED8bimOf5-y1uov4EWpuZvjQQjrA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Service here was great. Had the beef stew noodle. The broth was rich, hot, and nice and clean tasting, and didn't taste like MSG broth but real broth. The downside here was that the beef placed on top was near ice cold...literally...no exaggeration. It was definitely below room temperature hard cold beef so I am assuming they refrigerate or freeze their precooked beef and just defrost or microwave it when someone orders the dish but reheat it unevenly. Other than that, overall this was a good experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM-d8qptLejM7p-bMoElt1IDIx3tmqpkHStqVKu&fid=0x0:0xa7336b586da3827f"],"When":"2021-7-2"},{"Name":"Steven","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIwhlFiHPSDGYcBNEBZjiV401CUR-8LRwpy-nj0JN_nYZzCJQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The portion of the banh mi was quite small and looked like they cut the meatball in halves instead of full meatballs - not what the picture looks like on the menu. The chicken and pork flavor on the rice dish were not the tastiest and on smaller side portion as well. The spring roll was ok and fish sauce was good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNA1966FNZO9b3CoLj2SR7nPborYHKOZAKxyLB4&fid=0x0:0xa7336b586da3827f"],"When":"2023-6-12"},{"Name":"Carlos Miranda","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUB4daJxQQkgICpxRva14F5-6b7EkrIChl-XMaudNJADEUdvdBstg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Quick and good service, the location has plenty of parking around and nearby and there is plenty of spaces in between tables. The food is good, the pork/beef was mostly fat so maybe that can improve? Aside from that, everything else was tasteful.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNom3C5ExUbffhXXZV3pW0Z7hVyV2GUa-VPbfN9&fid=0x0:0xa7336b586da3827f"],"When":"2023-4-17"},{"Name":"Shun","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV7ONYhfPtFR7GegIR-TSpTU1q050DlVJptNGajTfP2cS0Xb_ovIA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Rare steak & beef ball pho was decent, standard flavour. Bun cha vermicelli with grilled pork and spring roll is OK only (little oily). (***)

Single piece of overly-fried banana ~$4.50 was a lonely rip-off with hardly any 🍌 in it.(* one star) 👎","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM8jul9XF7RJqs7iqklYcanZSlvdadnL-T6-Ogw&fid=0x0:0xa7336b586da3827f"],"When":"2020-11-13"},{"Name":"Wendy Kan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIUUMkg9LUGDXoqYiP4Dz28YR3jha29JwaIMh-r1NAGkpgYpQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"House vermicelli $16.5 portion is ok (not big) but taste soso. Pho in Richmond is much better.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPzi_RXrEZ8Djr0KLJNi4-CcwSxYhdwo0jQb07D&fid=0x0:0xa7336b586da3827f"],"When":"2020-8-3"},{"Name":"Cody R","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLhnerVAy8-Mum3GU2BWejFe6BzrPQX43sScD2H9dZeYGkgNg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Ordered takeout from here. [{"Name":"Geoffrey Soo Chan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWQcaR0nV-f301qugbblmbSzzDi0gSLiXceZvOho8TB0lCL76oH=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The taco bowl Portion was on the small side but that didn’t take away from the wonderful flavors.  The grilled burrito was also tasty. The person who took my order was friendly and chatted with me while I waited for my food (which came out quickly despite the rush).  I would come here again if I had to wait for the ferry.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP682wWYlglsjcWuKtvVLgFz6KoDAW67ZGz_yan&fid=0x0:0xfad1578e12b30ee6"],"When":"2024-10-26"},{"Name":"Cailie Crane","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVOnYu3kRaeJ8J5LnpIFXVCmY9eR_qoaWzx73VJe8Z-N7brVhaorw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I told them that they forgot the guacamole, as shown in the photo. They said it was extra. False advertising.
Furthermore the toppings were so sparse, only scattered on the top later, leaving the chips underneath dry. But I didn't notice until after I ate the top layer of chips. When I pointed it out the lady rudely said "Oh they were fully loaded and you ate it and only now you complain." Ah well. Tempted to order again just to post "before" photos of the pitiful nachos.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNro2bNd941WFEVd8jm3p_rvdqnlfJS2uM8Dyz3&fid=0x0:0xfad1578e12b30ee6"],"When":"2024-10-23"},{"Name":"Bradley Scott","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIdXDtocJBcwGBKwHclqp33UOHzIlIwPQfgTpnHX-sfguLC=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Not satisfied with the quality of food. We ordered 2 enchiladas that were ice cold. Not even the rice or meat was heated separately before assembling. They substituted shredded cabbage inside the enchiladas instead of lettuce as advertised. The tortilla was cold and stiff. Salsa was not spicy at all. Cheese is liquid drizzled on. The new operators don’t know what Mexican food is.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Davesito","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLcJPCrI3jSn6uWx0opCkW78_1UORJ3MUCjvk7ZGRzPHJ7Vqg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Get snack size for the price of a full meal! Had the burrito bowl. Portion was very small for dinner. At least put more rice in! It’s inexpensive and might help you get better reviews.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sam H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWc51YkYLzoVzVn7vYgihiJdmbFAOjiSt3Gg_AosBwjSJv5WQ9M=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Contrary to most other reviews, I found the food here to be just as expected. Quick and cheap Mexican fare. Don’t expect fine dining and this place will exceed your expectations before the ferry ride.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sayesha Saleh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUWRcNGGsGlYVMXhW1eWwdAI9jbWt0eXaH44abP5Vb3D6nr7mM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Terrible food i have ever seen . All the ingredients were cold . We ordered sunrise burritos and let me tell you, it was just sucks. I would say rather take a water bottle from somewhere else than ordering from here . unprofessional staff. So called maxican food i bet they don’t even know what actual maxican food taste like . Staff just only know how to say hey there , literally annoying.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Christian Gregory","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWhLdvrCZvC_ZLWS5-IUWrBX6AQ9pVbqh_N_vb97KyKu65zTm59=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"To put it lightly .This is the worst so called mexican food I have ever had. I had the burrito and let me tell you .....garbage . Chicken dry, terrible salsa, the tortilla was as dry as they come way overpriced for what you receive.  DONT DO IT. Do yourself a favor and get anything else.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Julianna Raeburn-McCormack","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIn_6IIJVsIVV2dXu0O7Ni-agnAYQLaEPFyfKUApgB1hn_UTg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Holy hell – what a horrible food experience. Now I totally appreciate that this is fast food and I am at the ferry terminal on new years eve but still… I ordered a vegetarian quesadilla with guacamole on the side. Not especially challenging. (Or so I thought.) What did I get? A dry tortilla with a thin layer of corn, tomatoes, and black beans that was warmed up on a grill. Sounds like a quesadilla, right? No - it wasn’t. There was NO friggin’ cheese to hold the contents in the tortilla, so every time I picked up one of the tiny little bite-size pieces that the woman behind the counter chopped the quesadilla into (why???), the contents fell out because there was nothing to bind it to the tortilla. Couldn’t dip it in the salsa or the sour cream - OR the nonexistent guacamole that I paid an extra $3 for but that they just never gave me. I’ve attached a photo of the contents left at the bottom of the take away container. My hand is next to it to give some size context. (I can’t believe I paid $15 for this!)

The Icing on the cake was when I dialled the number on their website to try to arrange for some sort of refund and the recorded female voice said very unenthusiastically “Yeah, you can leave a message” - but no, I actually couldn’t because the friggin’ mailbox was full! (Of course it was…)

Even though the four women were behind the counter were very sweet, just avoid this place. They are really unclear on the concept.
